490018,111,650,2,12,1,78,9,Sīhaṅgulī {sīhanakho}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto kokālikaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
490019,111,650,13,27,1,133,14,Ekadivasaṃ kira kokāliko aññesu bahussutesu dhammaṃ kathentesu sayampi kathetukāmo ahosīti sabbaṃ heṭṭhā vuttanayeneva vitthāretabbaṃ. 
490020,111,650,28,55,1,130,20,"Taṃ pana pavattiṃ sutvā satthā‘‘ na, bhikkhave, kokāliko idāneva attano saddena pākaṭo jāto, pubbepi pākaṭo ahosī’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
490021,111,651,2,17,1,138,15,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto himavantapadese sīho hutvā ekāya siṅgāliyā saddhiṃ saṃvāsamanvāya puttaṃ paṭilabhi. 
490022,111,651,18,31,1,99,12,"So aṅgulīhi nakhehi kesarena vaṇṇena saṇṭhānenāti imehi ākārehi pitusadiso ahosi, saddena mātusadiso. "
490023,111,651,32,48,1,126,16,Athekadivasaṃ deve vassitvā vigate sīhesu naditvā sīhakīḷaṃ kīḷantesu sopi tesaṃ antare naditukāmo hutvā siṅgālikaṃ nādaṃ nadi. 
490024,111,651,49,55,1,38,6,Athassa saddaṃ sutvā sīhā tuṇhī ahesuṃ. 
490025,111,651,56,85,1,154,21,"Tassa saddaṃ sutvā aparo bodhisattassa sajātiputto‘‘ tāta, ayaṃ sīho vaṇṇādīhi amhehi samāno, saddo panassa aññādiso, ko nāmeso’’ ti pucchanto paṭhamaṃ gāthamāha– "
