490125,111,701,2,14,1,93,10,Api ruhaka {chinnāpī}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto purāṇadutiyikāpalobhanaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
490126,111,701,15,29,1,48,4,Vatthu aṭṭhakanipāte indriyajātake( jā.1.8.60 ādayo) āvibhavissati. 
490127,111,701,30,60,1,175,25,"Satthā pana taṃ bhikkhuṃ‘‘ ayaṃ te bhikkhu itthī anatthakārikā, pubbepi te esā sarājikāya parisāya majjhe lajjāpetvā gehā nikkhamanākāraṃ kāresī’’ ti vatvā tena yācito atītaṃ āhari. "
490128,111,702,2,20,1,161,18,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto tassa aggamahesiyā kucchimhi nibbattitvā vayappatto pitu accayena rajje patiṭṭhāya dhammena rajjaṃ kāresi. 
490129,111,702,21,32,1,67,10,"Tassa ruhako nāma purohito ahosi, tassa purāṇī nāma brāhmaṇī bhariyā. "
490130,111,702,33,39,1,55,6,Rājā brāhmaṇassa assabhaṇḍakena alaṅkaritvā assaṃ adāsi. 
490131,111,702,40,47,1,45,7,So taṃ assaṃ āruyha rañño upaṭṭhānaṃ gacchati. 
490132,111,702,48,75,1,156,21,"Atha naṃ alaṅkataassassa piṭṭhe nisīditvā gacchantaṃ āgacchantañca disvā tahiṃ tahiṃ ṭhitā manussā‘‘ aho assassa rūpaṃ, aho asso sobhatī’’ ti assameva pasaṃsanti. "
490133,111,702,76,83,1,52,7,So gehaṃ āgantvā pāsādaṃ abhiruyha bhariyaṃ āmantesi–
490134,111,702,84,104,1,93,13,"‘‘ bhadde , amhākaṃ asso ativiya sobhati, ubhosu passesu ṭhitā manussā amhākaṃ assameva vaṇṇentī’’ ti. "
490135,111,702,105,115,1,65,9,"Sā pana brāhmaṇī thokaṃ chinnikā dhuttikadhātukā, tena naṃ evamāha–"
490136,111,702,116,161,1,286,36,"‘‘ ayya, tvaṃ assassa sobhanakāraṇaṃ na jānāsi, ayaṃ asso attano alaṅkataṃ assabhaṇḍakaṃ nissāya sobhati, sace tvampi asso viya sobhitukāmo assabhaṇḍakaṃ piḷandhitvā antaravīthiṃ oruyha asso viya pāde koṭṭayamāno gantvā rājānaṃ passa, rājāpi taṃ vaṇṇayissati, manussāpi taññeva vaṇṇayissantī’’ ti. "
490137,111,703,2,24,1,122,18,So ummattakajātiko brāhmaṇo tassā vacanaṃ sutvā‘‘ iminā nāma kāraṇena sā maṃ vadatī’’ ti ajānitvā tathāsaññī hutvā tathā akāsi. 
490138,111,703,25,41,1,65,11,"Ye ye passanti, te te parihāsaṃ karontā‘‘ sobhati ācariyo’’ ti vadiṃsu. "
490139,111,703,42,63,1,85,13,"Rājā pana naṃ‘‘ kiṃ, ācariya, pittaṃ te kupitaṃ , ummattakosi jāto’’ tiādīni vatvā lajjāpesi. "
490140,111,703,64,94,1,161,21,"Tasmiṃ kāle brāhmaṇo‘‘ ayuttaṃ mayā katan’’ ti lajjito brāhmaṇiyā kujjhitvā‘‘ tāyamhi sarājikāya parisāya antare lajjāpito, pothetvā taṃ nikkaḍḍhissāmī’’ ti gehaṃ agamāsi. "
490141,111,703,95,108,1,141,13,Dhuttikabrāhmaṇī tassa kujjhitvā āgamanabhāvaṃ ñatvā puretaraññeva cūḷadvārena nikkhamitvā rājanivesanaṃ gantvā catūhapañcāhaṃ tattheva ahosi. 
490142,111,703,109,133,1,150,18,"Rājā taṃ kāraṇaṃ ñatvā purohitaṃ pakkosāpetvā‘‘ ācariya, mātugāmassa nāma doso hotiyeva, brāhmaṇiyā khamituṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti khamāpanatthāya paṭhamaṃ gāthamāha– "
490143,111,704,2,4,1,0,0,81.
490144,111,705,2,11,1,40,7,"‘ ‘ Api ruhaka chinnāpi, jiyā sandhīyate puna; "
490145,111,706,2,12,1,46,7,"Sandhīyassu purāṇiyā, mā kodhassa vasaṃ gamī’’ ti. "
490146,111,707,2,25,1,151,19,"Tatrāyaṃ saṅkhepattho– bho ruhaka, nanu chinnāpi dhanujiyā puna sandhīyati ghaṭīyati, evameva tvampi purāṇiyā saddhiṃ sandhīyassu, kodhassa vasaṃ mā gamīti. "
490147,111,708,2,9,1,34,5,Taṃ sutvā ruhako dutiyaṃ gāthamāha– 
490148,111,709,2,4,1,0,0,82.
490149,111,710,2,9,1,37,5,"‘ ‘ Vijjamānesu vākesu, vijjamānesu kārisu; "
490150,111,711,2,11,1,42,6,"Aññaṃ jiyaṃ karissāmi, alaññeva purāṇiyā’’ ti. "
490151,111,712,2,26,1,160,20,"Tassattho – mahārāja, dhanukāramuduvākesu ca jiyakārakesu ca manussesu vijjamānesu aññaṃ jiyaṃ karissāmi, imāya chinnāya purāṇiyā jiyāya alaṃ, natthi me koci atthoti. "
490152,111,712,27,35,1,53,8,Evañca pana vatvā taṃ nīharitvā aññaṃ brāhmaṇiṃ ānesi. 
490153,111,713,2,15,1,132,12,Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā saccāni pakāsetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi– saccapariyosāne ukkaṇṭhitabhikkhu sotāpattiphale patiṭṭhahi.
490154,111,713,16,35,1,95,11,"‘‘ Tadā, brāhmaṇī, purāṇadutiyikā ahosi, ruhako ukkaṇṭhitabhikkhu, bārāṇasirājā pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
490155,111,714,2,4,1,27,2,Ruhakajātakavaṇṇanā paṭhamā.
490156,111,716,2,7,1,26,2,[ 192]2. Sirikāḷakaṇṇijātakavaṇṇanā 
490157,111,717,2,11,1,78,7,Itthī siyā {rūpavatī}ti idaṃ sirikāḷakaṇṇijātakaṃ mahāumaṅgajātake āvibhavissati. 
490158,111,718,2,4,1,33,2,Sirikāḷakaṇṇijātakavaṇṇanā dutiyā.
490159,111,720,2,7,1,23,2,[ 193]3. Cūḷapadumajātakavaṇṇanā 
490160,111,721,2,15,1,96,12,Ayameva sā ahamapi so {anañño}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ukkaṇṭhitabhikkhuṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
490161,111,721,16,29,1,36,3,Vatthu ummādantījātake( jā.2.20.57 ādayo) āvibhavissati. 
490162,111,721,30,84,1,225,32,"So pana bhikkhu satthārā‘‘ saccaṃ kira tvaṃ, bhikkhu, ukkaṇṭhito’’ ti vutte‘‘ saccaṃ, bhagavā’’ ti vatvā‘‘ kena pana tvaṃ ukkaṇṭhāpito’’ ti vutte ‘‘ ahaṃ, bhante, ekaṃ alaṅkatapaṭiyattaṃ mātugāmaṃ disvā kilesānuvattako hutvā ukkaṇṭhitomhī’’ ti āha. "
490163,111,721,85,114,1,197,23,"Atha naṃ satthā‘‘ bhikkhu, mātugāmo nāma akataññū mittadubbhī bahumāyā, porāṇakapaṇḍitāpi attano dakkhiṇajāṇulohitaṃ pāyetvā yāvajīvitadānampi datvā mātugāmassa cittaṃ na labhiṃsū’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
490164,111,722,2,24,1,146,16,"Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto tassa aggamahesiyā kucchimhi nibbatti, nāmaggahaṇadivase cassa‘‘ padumakumāro’’ ti nāmaṃ akaṃsu. "
490165,111,722,25,30,1,40,5,Tassa aparena cha kaniṭṭhabhātikā ahesuṃ. 
490166,111,722,31,42,1,86,11,Te sattapi janā anupubbena vuḍḍhippattā gharāvāsaṃ gahetvā rañño sahāyā viya vicaranti. 
490167,111,722,43,67,1,166,20,Athekadivasaṃ rājā rājaṅgaṇaṃ olokento ṭhito te mahāparivārena rājupaṭṭhānaṃ āgacchante disvā‘‘ ime maṃ vadhitvā rajjampi gaṇheyyun’’ ti āsaṅkaṃ uppādetvā te pakkosāpetvā–
490168,111,722,68,91,1,119,17,"‘‘ tātā, tumhe imasmiṃ nagare vasituṃ na labhatha, aññattha gantvā mama accayena āgantvā kulasantakaṃ rajjaṃ gaṇhathā’’ ti āha. "
490169,111,722,92,144,1,343,44,Te pitu vacanaṃ sampaṭicchitvā roditvā kanditvā attano attano gharāni gantvā pajāpatiyo ādāya‘‘ yattha vā tattha vā gantvā jīvissāmā’’ ti nagarā nikkhamitvā maggaṃ gacchantā ekaṃ kantāraṃ patvā annapānaṃ alabhamānā khudaṃ adhivāsetuṃ asakkontā‘‘ mayaṃ jīvamānā itthiyo labhissāmā’’ ti kaniṭṭhassa bhariyaṃ māretvā terasa koṭṭhāse katvā maṃsaṃ khādiṃsu. 
490170,111,722,145,156,1,84,11,Bodhisatto attano ca bhariyāya ca laddhakoṭṭhāsesu ekaṃ ṭhapetvā ekaṃ dvepi khādiṃsu. 
490171,111,722,157,165,1,51,8,Evaṃ cha divase cha itthiyo māretvā maṃsaṃ khādiṃsu. 
490172,111,723,2,12,1,66,9,Bodhisatto pana divase divase ekekaṃ ṭhapetvā cha koṭṭhāse ṭhapesi. 
490173,111,723,13,52,1,214,30,"Sattame divase‘‘ bodhisattassa bhariyaṃ māressāmā’’ ti vutte bodhisatto te cha koṭṭhāse tesaṃ datvā‘‘ ajja tāva ime cha koṭṭhāse khādatha, sve jānissāmā’’ ti vatvā tesaṃ maṃsaṃ khāditvā niddāyanakāle bhariyaṃ gahetvā palāyi. "
490174,111,723,53,67,1,46,9,"Sā thokaṃ gantvā‘‘ gantuṃ na sakkomi, sāmī’’ ti āha. "
490175,111,723,68,75,1,69,7,Atha naṃ bodhisatto khandhenādāya aruṇuggamanavelāya kantārā nikkhami. 
490176,111,723,76,88,1,40,7,"Sā sūriye uggate‘‘ pipāsitāmhi, sāmī’’ ti āha. "
490177,111,723,89,106,1,94,11,"Bodhisatto‘‘ udakaṃ natthi, bhadde’’ ti vatvā punappunaṃ kathite khaggena dakkhiṇajāṇukaṃ paharitvā–"
490178,111,723,107,124,1,79,11,"‘‘ bhadde, pānīyaṃ natthi, idaṃ pana me dakkhiṇajāṇulohitaṃ pivamānā nisīdāhī’’ ti āha. "
490179,111,723,125,128,1,14,3,Sā tathā akāsi. 
490180,111,723,129,147,1,155,18,Te anupubbena mahāgaṅgaṃ patvā pivitvā ca nhatvā ca phalāphalaṃ khāditvā phāsukaṭṭhāne vissamitvā ekasmiṃ gaṅgānivattane assamapadaṃ māpetvā vāsaṃ kappesuṃ. 
490181,111,724,2,15,1,136,13,Athekadivasaṃ uparigaṅgāya rājāparādhikaṃ coraṃ hatthapāde ca kaṇṇanāsañca chinditvā ekasmiṃ ambaṇake nipajjāpetvā mahāgaṅgāya pavāhesuṃ. 
490182,111,724,16,23,1,48,7,So mahantaṃ aṭṭassaraṃ karonto taṃ ṭhānaṃ pāpuṇi. 
490183,111,724,24,49,1,185,21,Bodhisatto tassa karuṇaṃ paridevitasaddaṃ sutvā‘‘ dukkhappatto satto mayi ṭhite mā nassī’’ ti gaṅgātīraṃ gantvā taṃ uttāretvā assamapadaṃ ānetvā kāsāvadhovanalepanādīhi vaṇapaṭikammaṃ akāsi. 
490184,111,724,50,71,1,141,17,Bhariyā panassa‘‘ evarūpaṃ nāma dussīlaṃ kuṇṭhaṃ gaṅgāya āvāhetvā paṭijagganto vicaratī’’ ti vatvā taṃ kuṇṭhaṃ jigucchamānā niṭṭhubhantī vicarati. 
490185,111,724,72,87,1,136,15,Bodhisatto tassa vaṇesu saṃviruḷhesu bhariyāya saddhiṃ taṃ assamapadeyeva ṭhapetvā aṭavito phalāphalāni āharitvā tañca bhariyañca posesi. 
490186,111,724,88,106,1,144,18,Tesu evaṃ vasantesu sā itthī etasmiṃ kuṇṭhe paṭibaddhacittā hutvā tena saddhiṃ anācāraṃ caritvā ekenupāyena bodhisattaṃ māretukāmā hutvā evamāha–
490187,111,724,107,149,1,240,32,"‘‘ sāmi, ahaṃ tumhākaṃ aṃse nisīditvā kantārā nikkhamamānā ekaṃ pabbataṃ oloketvā ayye pabbatamhi nibbattadevate‘ sace ahaṃ sāmikena saddhiṃ arogā jīvitaṃ labhissāmi, balikammaṃ te karissāmī’ ti āyāciṃ, sā maṃ idāni uttāseti, karomassā balikamman’’ ti. "
490188,111,724,150,168,1,127,14,Bodhisatto taṃ māyaṃ ajānanto‘‘ sādhū’’ ti sampaṭicchitvā balikammaṃ sajjetvā tāya balibhājanaṃ gāhāpetvā pabbatamatthakaṃ abhiruhi. 
490189,111,724,169,174,1,19,4,Atha naṃ sā evamāha–
490190,111,724,175,198,1,143,17,"‘‘ sāmi, devatāyapi tvaññeva uttamadevatā, paṭhamaṃ tāva taṃ vanapupphehi pūjetvā padakkhiṇaṃ katvā vanditvā pacchā devatāya balikammaṃ karissāmī’’ ti. "
490191,111,724,199,231,1,246,28,Sā bodhisattaṃ papātābhimukhaṃ ṭhapetvā vanapupphehi pūjetvā padakkhiṇaṃ katvā vanditukāmā viya hutvā piṭṭhipasse ṭhatvā piṭṭhiyaṃ paharitvā papāte pātetvā‘‘ diṭṭhā me paccāmittassa piṭṭhī’’ ti tuṭṭhamānasā pabbatā orohitvā kuṇṭhassa santikaṃ agamāsi. 
490192,111,725,2,20,1,148,15,"Bodhisattopi papātānusārena pabbatā patanto udumbararukkhamatthake ekasmiṃ akaṇṭake pattasañchanne gumbe laggi, heṭṭhāpabbataṃ pana orohituṃ na sakkā. "
490193,111,725,21,26,1,45,5,So udumbaraphalāni khāditvā sākhantare nisīdi. 
490194,111,725,27,35,1,90,8,Atheko mahāsarīro godharājā heṭṭhāpabbatapādato abhiruhitvā tasmiṃ udumbaraphalāni khādati. 
490195,111,725,36,50,1,97,13,"So taṃ divasaṃ bodhisattaṃ disvā palāyi, punadivase āgantvā ekasmiṃ passe phalāni khāditvā pakkāmi. "
490196,111,725,51,111,1,326,44,So evaṃ punappunaṃ āgacchanto bodhisattena saddhiṃ vissāsaṃ āpajjitvā‘‘ tvaṃ imaṃ ṭhānaṃ kena kāraṇena āgatosī’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ iminā nāma kāraṇenā’’ ti vutte‘‘ tena hi mā bhāyī’’ ti vatvā bodhisattaṃ attano piṭṭhiyaṃ nipajjāpetvā otāretvā araññato nikkhamitvā mahāmagge ṭhapetvā‘‘ tvaṃ iminā maggena gacchāhī’’ ti uyyojetvā araññameva pāvisi. 
490197,111,725,112,148,1,315,36,Bodhisatto ekaṃ gāmakaṃ gantvā tattheva vasanto pitu kālakatabhāvaṃ sutvā bārāṇasiṃ gantvā kulasantake rajje patiṭṭhāya padumarājā nāma hutvā dasa rājadhamme akopetvā dhammena rajjaṃ kārento catūsu nagaradvāresu nagaramajjhe nivesanadvāreti cha dānasālāyo kāretvā devasikaṃ cha satasahassāni vissajjetvā dānaṃ adāsi. 
490198,111,726,2,19,1,138,17,Sāpi kho itthī taṃ kuṇṭhaṃ khandhe nisīdāpetvā araññā nikkhamitvā manussapathe bhikkhaṃ caramānā yāgubhattaṃ saṃharitvā taṃ kuṇṭhaṃ posesi. 
490199,111,726,20,58,1,192,26,"Manussā‘‘ ayaṃ te kiṃ hotī’’ ti pucchiyamānā‘‘ ahaṃ etassa mātuladhītā, pitucchāputto me eso, etasseva maṃ adaṃsu, sāhaṃ vajjhappattampi attano sāmikaṃ ukkhipitvā pariharantī bhikkhaṃ caritvā posemī’’ ti. "
490200,111,726,59,72,1,68,9,Manussā‘‘ ayaṃ patibbatā’’ ti tato paṭṭhāya bahutaraṃ yāgubhattaṃ adaṃsu. 
490201,111,726,73,77,1,26,4,Apare pana janā evamāhaṃsu–
490202,111,726,78,118,1,227,31,"‘‘ tvaṃ mā evaṃ vicari, padumarājā bārāṇasiyaṃ rajjaṃ kāreti, sakalajambudīpaṃ saṅkhobhetvā dānaṃ deti, so taṃ disvā tussissati, tuṭṭho te bahuṃ dhanaṃ dassati, tava sāmikaṃ idheva nisīdāpetvā gacchā’’ ti thiraṃ katvā vettapacchiṃ adaṃsu. "
490203,111,726,119,132,1,116,13,Sā anācārā taṃ kuṇṭhaṃ vettapacchiyaṃ nisīdāpetvā pacchiṃ ukkhipitvā bārāṇasiṃ gantvā dānasālāsu bhuñjamānā vicarati. 
