490242,111,740,2,17,1,110,14,Na santi devā pavasanti {nūnā}ti idaṃ satthā veḷuvane viharanto vadhāya parisakkantaṃ devadattaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
490243,111,740,18,55,1,189,25,"Tadā pana satthā‘‘ devadatto vadhāya parisakkatī’’ ti sutvā‘‘ na, bhikkhave, idāneva, pubbepi devadatto mayhaṃ vadhāya parisakkatiyeva, parisakkantopi pana maṃ vadhituṃ nāsakkhī’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
490244,111,741,2,13,1,103,11,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto bārāṇasito avidūre gāmake gahapatikule nibbatti. 
490245,111,741,14,39,1,212,23,"Athassa vayappattassa bārāṇasito kuladhītaraṃ ānesuṃ, sā suvaṇṇavaṇṇā ahosi abhirūpā dassanīyā devaccharā viya pupphalatā viya laḷamānā mattakinnarī viya ca sujātāti nāmena patibbatā sīlācārasampannā vattasampannā. "
490246,111,741,40,52,1,102,11,"Niccakālampissā pativattaṃ sassuvattaṃ sasuravattañca katameva hoti, sā bodhisattassa piyā ahosi manāpā. "
490247,111,741,53,61,1,55,7,Iti ubhopi te sammodamānā ekacittā samaggavāsaṃ vasiṃsu. 
490248,111,742,2,13,1,70,7,Athekadivasaṃ sujātā‘‘ mātāpitaro daṭṭhukāmāmhī’’ ti bodhisattassa ārocesi.
490249,111,742,14,39,1,158,18,"‘‘ Sādhu, bhadde, maggapātheyyaṃ pahonakaṃ paṭiyādehī’’ ti khajjavikatiṃ pacāpetvā khajjakādīni yānake ṭhapetvā yānakaṃ pājento yānakassa purato ahosi, itarā pacchato. "
490250,111,742,40,47,1,56,7,Te nagarasamīpaṃ gantvā yānakaṃ mocetvā nhatvā bhuñjiṃsu. 
490251,111,742,48,61,1,102,12,"Puna bodhisatto yānakaṃ yojetvā purato nisīdi, sujātā vatthāni parivattetvā alaṅkaritvā pacchato nisīdi. "
490252,111,742,62,73,1,118,11,Yānakassa antonagaraṃ paviṭṭhakāle bārāṇasirājā hatthikkhandhavaragato nagaraṃ padakkhiṇaṃ karonto taṃ padesaṃ agamāsi. 
490253,111,742,74,81,1,48,6,Sujātā otaritvā yānakassa pacchato padasā pāyāsi. 
490254,111,742,82,93,1,98,11,Rājā taṃ disvā tassā rūpasampattiyā ākaḍḍhiyamānalocano paṭibaddhacitto hutvā ekaṃ amaccaṃ āṇāpesi–
490255,111,742,94,107,1,65,9,‘‘ gaccha tvaṃ etissā sassāmikabhāvaṃ vā assāmikabhāvaṃ vā jānāhī’’ ti. 
490256,111,742,108,129,1,100,15,"So gantvā tassā sassāmikabhāvaṃ ñatvā‘‘ sassāmikā kira, deva, yānake nisinno puriso etissā sāmiko’’ ti āha. "
490257,111,743,2,46,1,261,34,"Rājā paṭibaddhacittaṃ vinodetuṃ asakkonto kilesāturo hutvā‘‘ ekena naṃ upāyena mārāpetvā itthiṃ gaṇhissāmī’’ ti cintetvā ekaṃ purisaṃ āmantetvā‘‘ gaccha, bho, imaṃ cūḷāmaṇiṃ vīthiṃ gacchanto viya hutvā etassa purisassa yānake pakkhipitvā ehī’’ ti cūḷāmaṇiṃ datvā uyyojesi. "
490258,111,743,47,70,1,81,14,"So‘‘ sādhū’’ ti taṃ gahetvā gantvā yānake ṭhapetvā‘‘ ṭhapito me, devā’’ ti āgantvā ārocesi. "
490259,111,743,71,85,1,58,9,"Rājā‘‘ cūḷāmaṇi me naṭṭho’’ ti āha, manussā ekakolāhalaṃ akaṃsu. "
490260,111,743,86,107,1,123,15,"Rājā‘‘ sabbadvārāni pidahitvā sañcāraṃ chinditvā coraṃ pariyesathā’’ ti āha, rājapurisā tathā akaṃsu, nagaraṃ ekasaṅkhobhaṃ ahosi. "
490261,111,743,108,163,1,289,38,"Itaro puriso manusse gahetvā bodhisattassa santikaṃ gantvā‘‘ bho, yānakaṃ ṭhapehi, rañño cūḷāmaṇi naṭṭho, yānakaṃ sodhessāmī’’ ti yānakaṃ sodhento attanā ṭhapitamaṇiṃ gahetvā bodhisattaṃ gahetvā‘‘ maṇicoro’’ ti hatthehi ca pādehi ca pothetvā pacchābāhaṃ bandhitvā netvā‘‘ ayaṃ maṇicoro’’ ti rañño dassesi. "
490262,111,743,164,173,1,37,5,Rājāpi‘‘ sīsamassa chindathā’’ ti āṇāpesi. 
490263,111,744,2,12,1,87,10,Atha naṃ rājapurisā catukke catukke kasāhi tāḷentā dakkhiṇadvārena nagarā nikkhamāpesuṃ. 
490264,111,744,13,35,1,130,17,"Sujātāpi yānakaṃ pahāya bāhā paggayha paridevamānā‘‘ sāmi, maṃ nissāya imaṃ dukkhaṃ pattosī’’ ti paridevamānā pacchato pacchato agamāsi. "
