490280,111,750,18,46,1,167,23,"Sace hi rājā adhammiko hoti, devo akāle vassati, kāle na vassati, chātabhayaṃ rogabhayaṃ satthabhayanti imāni tīṇi bhayāni upagatāneva hontī’’ ti ovadanto dutiyaṃ gāthamāha– "
