490334,111,775,2,7,1,24,2,[ 196]6. Valāhakassajātakavaṇṇanā 
490335,111,776,2,15,1,94,13,Ye na kāhanti ovādan ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ekaṃ ukkaṇṭhitabhikkhuṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
490336,111,776,16,59,1,157,25,"So hi bhikkhu satthārā‘‘ saccaṃ kira tvaṃ, bhikkhu, ukkaṇṭhitosī’’ ti puṭṭho‘‘ saccan’’ ti vatvā‘‘ kiṃ kāraṇā’’ ti vutte‘‘ ekaṃ alaṅkataṃ mātugāmaṃ disvā kilesavasenā’’ ti āha. "
490337,111,776,60,89,1,233,25,Atha naṃ satthā‘‘ itthiyo nāmetā bhikkhu attano rūpasaddagandharasaphoṭṭhabbehi ceva itthikuttavilāsehi ca purise palobhetvā attano vase katvā vasaṃ upagatabhāvaṃ ñatvā sīlavināsañceva dhanavināsañca pāpanaṭṭhena‘ yakkhiniyo’ ti vuccanti. 
490338,111,776,90,123,1,251,31,Pubbepi hi yakkhiniyo itthikuttena ekaṃ purisasatthaṃ upasaṅkamitvā vāṇije palobhetvā attano vase katvā puna aññe purise disvā te sabbepi jīvitakkhayaṃ pāpetvā ubhohi hanukapassehi lohitena paggharantena mukhaṃ pūrāpetvā khādiṃsū’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. 
490339,111,777,2,12,1,84,9,"Atīte tambapaṇṇidīpe sirīsavatthu nāma yakkhanagaraṃ ahosi, tattha yakkhiniyo vasiṃsu. "
490340,111,777,13,25,1,140,12,Tā bhinnanāvānaṃ vāṇijānaṃ āgatakāle alaṅkatapaṭiyattā khādanīyabhojanīyaṃ gāhāpetvā dāsigaṇaparivutā dārake aṅkenādāya vāṇije upasaṅkamanti. 
490341,111,777,26,64,1,222,26,"Tesaṃ ‘‘ manussāvāsaṃ āgatamhā’’ ti sañjānanatthaṃ tattha tattha kasigorakkhādīni karonte manusse gogaṇe sunakheti evamādīni dassenti, vāṇijānaṃ santikaṃ gantvā‘‘ imaṃ yāguṃ pivatha, bhattaṃ bhuñjatha, khādanīyaṃ khādathā’’ ti vadanti. "
490342,111,777,65,70,1,41,5,Vāṇijā ajānantā tāhi dinnaṃ paribhuñjanti. 
490343,111,777,71,100,1,162,20,"Atha tesaṃ khāditvā bhuñjitvā pivitvā vissamitakāle paṭisanthāraṃ karonti,‘‘ tumhe kattha vāsikā, kuto āgatā, kahaṃ gacchissatha, kena kammena idhāgatatthā’’ ti pucchanti."
490344,111,777,101,128,1,145,18,"‘‘ Bhinnanāvā hutvā idhāgatamhā’’ ti vutte‘‘ sādhu, ayyā, amhākampi sāmikānaṃ nāvaṃ abhiruhitvā gatānaṃ tīṇi saṃvaccharāni atikkantāni, te matā bhavissanti; "
490345,111,777,129,171,1,346,36,"tumhepi vāṇijāyeva, mayaṃ tumhākaṃ pādaparicārikā bhavissāmā’’ ti vatvā te vāṇije itthikuttahāvabhāvavilāsehi palobhetvā yakkhanagaraṃ netvā sace paṭhamagahitā manussā atthi, te devasaṅkhalikāya bandhitvā kāraṇaghare pakkhipanti , attano vasanaṭṭhāne bhinnanāve manusse alabhantiyo pana parato kalyāṇiṃ orato nāgadīpanti evaṃ samuddatīraṃ anusañcaranti. "
490346,111,777,172,175,1,19,3,Ayaṃ tāsaṃ dhammatā. 
490347,111,778,2,9,1,70,7,Athekadivasaṃ pañcasatā bhinnanāvā vāṇijā tāsaṃ nagarasamīpe uttariṃsu. 
490348,111,778,10,38,1,238,27,"Tā tesaṃ santikaṃ gantvā palobhetvā yakkhanagaraṃ netvā paṭhamaṃ gahite manusse devasaṅkhalikāya bandhitvā kāraṇaghare pakkhipitvā jeṭṭhayakkhinī jeṭṭhakavāṇijaṃ, sesā seseti tā pañcasatā yakkhiniyo te pañcasate vāṇije attano sāmike akaṃsu. "
490349,111,778,39,58,1,147,18,"Atha sā jeṭṭhayakkhinī rattibhāge vāṇije niddaṃ upagate uṭṭhāya gantvā kāraṇaghare manusse māretvā maṃsaṃ khāditvā āgacchati, sesāpi tatheva karonti. "
490350,111,778,59,66,1,70,7,Jeṭṭhayakkhiniyā manussamaṃsaṃ khāditvā āgatakāle sarīraṃ sītalaṃ hoti. 
490351,111,778,67,92,1,184,19,"Jeṭṭhavāṇijo pariggaṇhanto tassā yakkhinibhāvaṃ ñatvā‘‘ imā pañcasatā yakkhiniyo bhavissanti, amhehi palāyituṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti punadivase pātova mukhadhovanatthāya gantvā sesavāṇijānaṃ ārocesi–"
490352,111,778,93,137,1,236,31,"‘‘ imā yakkhiniyo, na manussitthiyo, aññesaṃ bhinnanāvānaṃ āgatakāle te sāmike katvā amhepi khādissanti, etha ito palāyissāmā’’ ti tesu pañcasatesu aḍḍhateyyasatā‘‘ na mayaṃ etā vijahituṃ sakkhissāma, tumhe gacchatha, mayaṃ na palāyissāmā’’ ti āhaṃsu. "
490353,111,778,138,146,1,72,8,Jeṭṭhavāṇijo attano vacanakāre aḍḍhateyyasate gahetvā tāsaṃ bhīto palāyi. 
490354,111,779,2,15,1,110,12,"Tasmiṃ pana kāle bodhisatto valāhakassayoniyaṃ nibbatti, sabbaseto kāḷasīso muñjakeso iddhimā vehāsaṅgamo ahosi. "
490355,111,779,16,29,1,116,12,So himavantato ākāse uppatitvā tambapaṇṇidīpaṃ gantvā tattha tambapaṇṇisare pallale sayaṃjātasāliṃ khāditvā gacchati. 
490356,111,779,30,46,1,98,12,Evaṃ gacchanto ca‘‘ janapadaṃ gantukāmā atthī’’ ti tikkhattuṃ karuṇāparibhāvitaṃ mānusiṃ vācaṃ bhāsati. 
490357,111,779,47,65,1,102,13,"Te bodhisattassa vacanaṃ sutvā upasaṅkamitvā añjaliṃ paggayha‘‘ sāmi, mayaṃ janapadaṃ gamissāmā’’ ti āhaṃsu. "
490358,111,779,66,71,1,36,5,Tena hi mayhaṃ piṭṭhiṃ abhiruhathāti. 
490359,111,779,72,84,1,90,10,"Appekacce abhiruhiṃsu, tesu ekacce vāladhiṃ gaṇhiṃsu, ekacce añjaliṃ paggahetvā aṭṭhaṃsuyeva. "
490360,111,779,85,103,1,171,18,Bodhisatto antamaso añjaliṃ paggahetvā ṭhite sabbepi te aḍḍhateyyasate vāṇije attano ānubhāvena janapadaṃ netvā sakasakaṭṭhānesu patiṭṭhapetvā attano vasanaṭṭhānaṃ āgamāsi. 
490361,111,779,104,115,1,93,11,Tāpi kho yakkhiniyo aññesaṃ āgatakāle tattha ohīnake aḍḍhateyyasate manusse vadhitvā khādiṃsu. 
490362,111,780,2,39,1,315,30,"Satthā bhikkhū āmantetvā‘‘ bhikkhave, yathā te yakkhinīnaṃ vasaṃ gatā vāṇijā jīvitakkhayaṃ pattā, valāhakassarājassa vacanakarā vāṇijā sakasakaṭṭhānesu patiṭṭhitā, evameva buddhānaṃ ovādaṃ akarontā bhikkhūpi bhikkhuniyopi upāsakāpi upāsikāyopi catūsu apāyesu pañcavidhabandhanakammakaraṇaṭṭhānādīsu mahādukkhaṃ pāpuṇanti. "
490363,111,780,40,67,1,198,25,Ovādakarā pana tisso kulasampattiyo ca cha kāmasagge vīsati brahmaloketi imāni ca ṭhānāni patvā amatamahānibbānaṃ sacchikatvā mahantaṃ sukhaṃ anubhavantī’’ ti vatvā abhisambuddho hutvā imā gāthā avoca– 
490364,111,781,2,4,1,0,0,91.
490365,111,782,2,12,1,42,8,"‘ ‘ Ye na kāhanti ovādaṃ, narā buddhena desitaṃ; "
490366,111,783,2,8,1,42,5,"Byasanaṃ te gamissanti, rakkhasīhiva vāṇijā. "
490367,111,784,2,4,1,0,0,92.
490368,111,785,2,12,1,42,8,"‘ ‘ Ye ca kāhanti ovādaṃ, narā buddhena desitaṃ; "
490369,111,786,2,11,1,45,6,"Sotthiṃ pāraṃ gamissanti, valāheneva vāṇijā’’ ti. "
490370,111,787,2,10,1,39,7,Tattha ye na {kāhantī}ti ye na karissanti. 
490371,111,787,11,18,1,52,6,Byasanaṃ te {gamissantī}ti te mahāvināsaṃ pāpuṇissanti. 
490372,111,787,19,25,1,53,5,Rakkhasīhiva {vāṇijā}ti rakkhasīhi palobhitavāṇijā viya. 
490373,111,787,26,33,1,61,6,Sotthiṃ pāraṃ {gamissantī}ti anantarāyena nibbānaṃ pāpuṇissanti. 
490374,111,787,34,50,1,79,10,Valāheneva {vāṇijā}ti valāheneva‘‘ āgacchathā’’ ti vuttā tassa vacanakarā vāṇijā viya. 
490375,111,787,51,69,1,161,17,"Yathā hi te samuddapāraṃ gantvā sakasakaṭṭhānaṃ agamaṃsu, evaṃ buddhānaṃ ovādakarā saṃsārapāraṃ nibbānaṃ gacchantīti amatamahānibbānena dhammadesanāya kūṭaṃ gaṇhi. "
490376,111,788,2,20,1,211,16,"Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā saccāni pakāsetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi– saccapariyosāne ukkaṇṭhitabhikkhu sotāpattiphale patiṭṭhahi, aññepi bahū sotāpattiphalasakadāgāmiphalaanāgāmiphalaarahattaphalāni pāpuṇiṃsu."
490377,111,788,21,38,1,115,12,"‘‘ Tadā valāhakassarājassa vacanakarā aḍḍhateyyasatā vāṇijā buddhaparisā ahesuṃ, valāhakassarājā pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
490378,111,789,2,4,1,32,2,Valāhakassajātakavaṇṇanā chaṭṭhā.
490379,111,791,2,7,1,23,2,[ 197]7. Mittāmittajātakavaṇṇanā 
490380,111,792,2,15,1,89,12,Na naṃ umhayate {disvā}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto aññataraṃ bhikkhuṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
490381,111,792,16,40,1,170,20,Aññataro bhikkhu‘‘ mayā gahite mayhaṃ upajjhāyo na kujjhissatī’’ ti upajjhāyena ṭhapitaṃ vissāsena ekaṃ vatthakhaṇḍaṃ gahetvā upāhanatthavikaṃ katvā pacchā upajjhāyaṃ āpucchi. 
490382,111,792,41,81,1,170,26,Atha taṃ upajjhāyo ‘‘ kiṃkāraṇā gaṇhī’’ ti vatvā‘‘ mayā gahite na kujjhissatīti tumhākaṃ vissāsenā’’ ti vutte‘‘ ko mayā saddhiṃ tuyhaṃ vissāso nāmā’’ ti vatvā kuddho uṭṭhahitvā pahari. 
490383,111,792,82,88,1,37,6,Tassa sā kiriyā bhikkhūsu pākaṭā jātā. 
490384,111,792,89,94,1,57,5,Athekadivasaṃ bhikkhū dhammasabhāyaṃ kathaṃ samuṭṭhāpesuṃ–
490385,111,792,95,108,1,91,10,"‘‘ āvuso, asuko kira daharo upajjhāyassa vissāsena vatthakhaṇḍaṃ gahetvā upāhanatthavikaṃ akāsi. "
490386,111,792,109,128,1,91,15,Atha naṃ upajjhāyo‘ ko mayā saddhiṃ tuyhaṃ vissāso nāmā’ ti vatvā kuddho uṭṭhahitvā paharī’’ ti. 
490387,111,792,129,174,1,215,28,"Satthā āgantvā‘‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ imāya nāmā’’ ti vutte‘‘ na, bhikkhave, idānevesa bhikkhu attano saddhivihārikena saddhiṃ avissāsiko, pubbepi avissāsikoyevā’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
490388,111,793,2,25,1,211,22,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto kāsiraṭṭhe brāhmaṇakule nibbattitvā vayappatto isipabbajjaṃ pabbajitvā abhiññā ca samāpattiyo ca nibbattetvā gaṇasatthā hutvā himavantapadese vāsaṃ kappesi. 
490389,111,793,26,37,1,95,11,Tasmiṃ isigaṇe eko tāpaso bodhisattassa vacanaṃ akatvā ekaṃ matamātikaṃ hatthipotakaṃ paṭijaggi. 
490390,111,793,38,45,1,47,7,Atha naṃ so vuddhippatto māretvā araññaṃ pāvisi. 
490391,111,793,46,52,1,56,6,Tassa sarīrakiccaṃ katvā isigaṇo bodhisattaṃ parivāretvā–
490392,111,793,53,71,1,79,13,"‘‘ bhante, kena nu ko kāraṇena mittabhāvo vā amittabhāvo vā sakkā jānitun’’ ti pucchi. "
490393,111,793,72,87,1,67,11,Bodhisatto‘‘ iminā ca iminā ca kāraṇenā’’ ti ācikkhanto imā gāthā avoca– 
490394,111,794,2,4,1,0,0,93.
490395,111,795,2,13,1,43,9,"‘ ‘ Na naṃ umhayate disvā, na ca naṃ paṭinandati; "
490396,111,796,2,9,1,44,6,"Cakkhūni cassa na dadāti, paṭilomañca vattati. "
490397,111,797,2,4,1,0,0,94.
490398,111,798,2,10,1,40,6,"‘ ‘ Ete bhavanti ākārā, amittasmiṃ patiṭṭhitā; "
490399,111,799,2,13,1,46,8,"Yehi amittaṃ jāneyya, disvā sutvā ca paṇḍito’’ ti. "
490400,111,800,2,28,1,131,22,"Tattha na naṃ umhayate {disvā}ti yo hi yassa amitto hoti, so taṃ puggalaṃ disvā na umhayate, hasitaṃ na karoti, pahaṭṭhākāraṃ na dasseti. "
490401,111,800,29,47,1,106,15,"Na ca naṃ {paṭinandatī}ti tassa vacanaṃ sutvāpi taṃ puggalaṃ na paṭinandati, sādhu subhāsitanti na cānumodati. "
490402,111,800,48,64,1,100,14,"Cakkhūni cassa na {dadātī}ti cakkhunā cakkhuṃ āhacca paṭimukho hutvā na oloketi, aññato cakkhūni harati. "
490403,111,800,65,77,1,100,10,"Paṭilomañca {vattatī}ti tassa kāyakammampi vacīkammampi na roceti, paṭilomagāhaṃ gaṇhāti paccanīkagāhaṃ. "
490404,111,800,78,81,1,16,2,{Ākārā}ti kāraṇāni. 
490405,111,800,82,110,1,144,22,"Yehi amittan ti yehi kāraṇehi tāni kāraṇāni disvā sutvā ca paṇḍito puggalo‘‘ ayaṃ me amitto’’ ti jāneyya, tato viparītehi pana mittabhāvo jānitabboti. "
490406,111,801,2,10,1,93,8,Evaṃ bodhisatto mittāmittabhāvakāraṇāni ācikkhitvā brahmavihāre bhāvetvā brahmalokūpago ahosi. 
490407,111,802,2,8,1,54,6,Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–
490408,111,802,9,29,1,116,13,"‘‘ tadā hatthiposakatāpaso saddhivihāriko ahosi, hatthī upajjhāyo, isigaṇo buddhaparisā, gaṇasatthā pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
490409,111,803,2,4,1,31,2,Mittāmittajātakavaṇṇanā sattamā.
490410,111,805,2,7,1,18,2,[ 198]8. Rādhajātakavaṇṇanā 
490411,111,806,2,15,1,90,11,Pavāsā āgato {tātā}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ekaṃ ukkaṇṭhitabhikkhuṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
490412,111,806,16,58,1,150,23,"So kira satthārā‘‘ saccaṃ kira, tvaṃ bhikkhu, ukkaṇṭhito’’ ti puṭṭho‘‘ saccaṃ, bhante’’ ti vatvā‘‘ kiṃkāraṇā’’ ti vutte‘‘ ekaṃ alaṅkataitthiṃ disvā kilesavasenā’’ ti āha. "
490413,111,806,59,94,1,185,28,"Atha naṃ satthā‘‘ mātugāmo nāma bhikkhu na sakkā rakkhituṃ, pubbepi dovārike ṭhapetvā rakkhantāpi rakkhituṃ na sakkhiṃsu, kiṃ te itthiyā, laddhāpi sā rakkhituṃ na sakkā’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
490414,111,807,2,23,1,132,15,"Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto suvayoniyaṃ nibbatti,‘‘ rādho’’ tissa nāmaṃ, kaniṭṭhabhātā panassa poṭṭhapādo nāma. "
490415,111,807,24,40,1,129,15,"Te ubhopi taruṇakāleyeva eko luddako gahetvā bārāṇasiyaṃ aññatarassa brāhmaṇassa adāsi, brāhmaṇo te puttaṭṭhāne ṭhapetvā paṭijaggi. "
490416,111,807,41,47,1,43,5,Brāhmaṇassa pana brāhmaṇī arakkhitā dussīlā. 
490417,111,807,48,85,1,261,30,"So vohārakaraṇatthāya gacchanto te suvapotake āmantetvā‘‘ tātā, ahaṃ vohārakaraṇatthāya gacchāmi, kāle vā vikāle vā tumhākaṃ mātu karaṇakammaṃ olokeyyātha, aññassa purisassa gamanabhāvaṃ vā agamanabhāvaṃ vā jāneyyāthā’’ ti brāhmaṇiṃ suvapotakānaṃ paṭicchāpetvā agamāsi. "
490418,111,807,86,99,1,109,12,"Sā tassa nikkhantakālato paṭṭhāya anācāraṃ cari, rattimpi divāpi āgacchantānañca gacchantānañca pamāṇaṃ natthi. "
490419,111,808,2,7,1,34,5,Taṃ disvā poṭṭhapādo rādhaṃ pucchi–
490420,111,808,8,27,1,86,12,"‘‘ brāhmaṇo imaṃ brāhmaṇiṃ amhākaṃ niyyādetvā gato, ayañca pāpakammaṃ karoti, vadāmi nan’’ ti. "
490421,111,808,28,37,1,22,5,Rādho‘‘ mā vadāhī’’ ti āha. 
490422,111,808,38,53,1,66,10,"So tassa vacanaṃ aggahetvā‘‘ amma, kiṃkāraṇā pāpakammaṃ karosī’’ ti āha. "
490423,111,808,54,103,1,232,35,"Sā taṃ māretukāmā hutvā‘‘ tāta, tvaṃ nāma mayhaṃ putto, ito paṭṭhāya na karissāmi, ehi, tāta, tāvā’’ ti piyāyamānā viya pakkositvā āgataṃ gahetvā‘‘ tvaṃ maṃ ovadasi, attano pamāṇaṃ na jānāsī’’ ti gīvaṃ parivattetvā māretvā uddhanantaresu pakkhipi. "
490424,111,808,104,128,1,120,17,"Brāhmaṇo āgantvā vissamitvā bodhisattaṃ‘‘ kiṃ, tāta rādha, mātā te anācāraṃ karoti, na karotī’’ ti pucchanto paṭhamaṃ gāthamāha– "
490425,111,809,2,4,1,0,0,95.
490426,111,810,2,11,1,34,6,"‘ ‘ Pavāsā āgato tāta, idāni nacirāgato; "
490427,111,811,2,12,1,42,7,"Kaccinnu tāta te mātā, na aññamupasevatī’’ ti. "
490428,111,812,2,23,1,108,16,"Tassattho – ahaṃ, tāta rādha, pavāsā āgato, so camhi idāneva āgato nacirāgato, tena pavattiṃ ajānanto taṃ pucchāmi–"
490429,111,812,24,40,1,51,10,"‘‘ kacci nu te, tāta, mātā aññaṃ purisaṃ na upasevatī’’ ti. "
490430,111,813,2,23,1,102,16,"Rādho ‘‘ tāta, paṇḍitā nāma bhūtaṃ vā abhūtaṃ vā aniyyānikaṃ nāma na kathesun’’ ti ñāpento dutiyaṃ gāthamāha– "
490431,111,814,2,4,1,0,0,96.
490432,111,815,2,12,1,45,7,"‘ ‘ Na kho panetaṃ subhaṇaṃ, giraṃ saccupasaṃhitaṃ; "
490433,111,816,2,10,1,42,5,"Sayetha poṭṭhapādova, mummure upakūthito’’ ti. "
490434,111,817,2,6,1,23,4,Tattha giran ti vacanaṃ. 
490435,111,817,7,27,1,89,14,"Tañhi yathā idāni girā, evaṃ tadā‘‘ giran’’ ti vuccati, so suvapotako liṅgaṃ anādiyitvā evamāha. "
490436,111,817,28,43,1,120,13,"Ayaṃ panettha attho– tāta, paṇḍitena nāma saccupasaṃhitaṃ yathābhūtaṃ atthayuttaṃ sabhāvavacanampi aniyyānikaṃ na subhaṇaṃ. "
490437,111,817,44,61,1,122,14,"Aniyyānikañca saccaṃ bhaṇanto sayetha poṭṭhapādova, mummure upakūthito, yathā poṭṭhapādo kukkuḷe jhāmo sayati, evaṃ sayeyyāti."
490438,111,817,62,71,1,33,4,"‘‘ Upakūdhito’’ tipi pāṭho, ayamevattho. "
490439,111,818,2,22,1,123,16,Evaṃ bodhisatto brāhmaṇassa dhammaṃ desetvā‘‘ mayāpi imasmiṃ ṭhāne vasituṃ na sakkā’’ ti brāhmaṇaṃ āpucchitvā araññameva pāvisi. 
490440,111,819,2,16,1,132,12,"Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā saccāni pakāsetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi, saccapariyosāne ukkaṇṭhitabhikkhu sotāpattiphale patiṭṭhahi."
490441,111,819,17,31,1,57,9,"‘‘ Tadā poṭṭhapādo ānando ahosi, rādho pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
490442,111,820,2,4,1,26,2,Rādhajātakavaṇṇanā aṭṭhamā.
490443,111,822,2,7,1,21,2,[ 199]9. Gahapatijātakavaṇṇanā 
490444,111,823,2,16,1,94,12,Ubhayaṃ me na {khamatī}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ukkaṇṭhitameva bhikkhuṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
490445,111,823,17,38,1,114,16,"Kathento ca‘‘ mātugāmo nāma arakkhito, pāpakammaṃ katvā yena kenaci upāyena sāmikaṃ vañcetiyevā’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
490446,111,824,2,14,1,119,12,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto kāsiraṭṭhe gahapatikule nibbattitvā vayappatto gharāvāsaṃ gaṇhi. 
490447,111,824,15,22,1,59,7,Tassa bhariyā dussīlā gāmabhojakena saddhiṃ anācāraṃ carati. 
490448,111,824,23,29,1,41,5,Bodhisatto taṃ ñatvā pariggaṇhanto carati . 
490449,111,824,30,41,1,81,10,"Tadā pana antovasse bījesu nīhaṭesu chātakaṃ ahosi, sassānaṃ gabbhagahaṇakālo jāto. "
490450,111,824,42,63,1,143,17,Sakalagāmavāsino‘‘ ito māsadvayena sassāni uddharitvā vīhiṃ dassāmā’’ ti ekato hutvā gāmabhojakassa hatthato ekaṃ jaragoṇaṃ gahetvā maṃsaṃ khādiṃsu. 
490451,111,825,2,10,1,84,8,Athekadivasaṃ gāmabhājako khaṇaṃ oloketvā bodhisattassa bahigatavelāyaṃ gehaṃ pāvisi. 
490452,111,825,11,18,1,81,7,Tesaṃ sukhanipannakkhaṇeyeva bodhisatto gāmadvārena pavisitvā gehābhimukho pāyāsi. 
490453,111,825,19,49,1,141,21,"Sā itthī gāmadvārābhimukhī taṃ disvā‘‘ ko nu kho eso’’ ti ummāre ṭhatvā olokentī‘‘ soyevā’’ ti ñatvā gāmabhojakassa ācikkhi, gāmabhojako bhīto pakampi. "
490454,111,825,50,84,1,173,26,"Atha naṃ sā‘‘ mā bhāyi, attheko upāyo, amhehi tava hatthato goṇamaṃsaṃ khāditaṃ, tvaṃ maṃsamūlaṃ sodhento viya hohi, ahaṃ koṭṭhaṃ āruyha koṭṭhadvāre ṭhatvā‘ vīhi natthī’ ti vakkhāmi. "
490455,111,825,85,109,1,135,19,"Tvaṃ gehamajjhe ṭhatvā‘ amhākaṃ ghare dārakā chātā, maṃsamūlaṃ me dehī’ ti punappunaṃ codeyyāsī’’ ti vatvā koṭṭhaṃ āruyha koṭṭhadvāre nisīdi. "
490456,111,825,110,121,1,49,7,Itaro gehamajjhe ṭhatvā‘‘ maṃsamūlaṃ dehī’’ ti vadati. 
490457,111,825,122,139,1,82,12,"Sā koṭṭhadvāre nisinnā‘‘ koṭṭhe vīhi natthi, sasse uddharante dassāmi gacchāhī’’ ti āha. "
490458,111,826,2,106,1,562,79,"Bodhisatto gehaṃ pavisitvā tesaṃ kiriyaṃ disvā‘‘ imāya pāpāya kataupāyo esa bhavissatī’’ ti ñatvā gāmabhojakaṃ āmantetvā‘‘ so gāmabhojaka amhe tava jaragoṇassa maṃsaṃ khādantā‘ ito māsadvayena vīhiṃ dassāmā’ ti khādimha, tvaṃ aḍḍhamāsampi anatikkamitvā idāneva kasmā āharāpesi, na tvaṃ iminā kāraṇena āgato, aññena kāraṇena āgato bhavissasi, mayhaṃ tava kiriyā na ruccati, ayampi anācārā pāpadhammā koṭṭhe vīhīnaṃ abhāvaṃ jānāti, sā dāni koṭṭhaṃ āruyha‘ vīhi natthī’ ti vadati, tvampi‘ dehī’ ti vadati, ubhinnampi vo karaṇaṃ mayhaṃ na ruccatī’’ ti etamatthaṃ pakāsento imā gāthā avoca– "
490459,111,827,2,4,1,0,0,97.
