490463,111,831,2,12,1,44,8,"‘ ‘ Taṃ taṃ gāmapati brūmi, kadare appasmi jīvite; "
490464,111,832,2,10,1,47,7,"Dve māse saṅgaraṃ katvā, maṃsaṃ jaraggavaṃ kisaṃ; "
490465,111,833,2,12,1,45,7,"Appattakāle codesi, tampi mayhaṃ na ruccatī’’ ti. "
490466,111,834,2,16,1,75,11,"Tattha taṃ taṃ gāmapati {brūmī}ti, ambho gāmajeṭṭhaka, tena kāraṇena taṃ vadāmi. "
490467,111,834,17,37,1,139,18,"Kadare appasmi {jīvite}ti amhākaṃ jīvitaṃ nāma kadarañceva thaddhaṃ lūkhaṃ kasiraṃ appañca mandaṃ parittaṃ, tasmiṃ no evarūpe jīvite vattamāne. "
490468,111,834,38,71,1,199,28,"Dve māse saṅgaraṃ katvā, maṃsaṃ jaraggavaṃ kisan ti amhākaṃ maṃsaṃ gaṇhantānaṃ jaraggavaṃ kisaṃ dubbalaṃ jaragoṇaṃ dadamāno tvaṃ‘‘ dvīhi māsehi mūlaṃ dātabban’’ ti evaṃ dve māse saṅgaraṃ paricchedaṃ katvā. "
490469,111,834,72,80,1,58,7,Appattakāle {codesī}ti tasmiṃ kāle asampatte antarāva codesi. 
490470,111,834,81,118,1,249,34,"Tampi mayhaṃ na {ruccatī}ti yā cāyaṃ pāpadhammā dussīlā antokoṭṭhe vīhīnaṃ natthibhāvaṃ jānamānāva ajānantī viya hutvā koṭṭhamotiṇṇā koṭṭhadvāre ṭhatvā na dassaṃ iti bhāsati, yañca tvaṃ akāle codesi, tampīti idaṃ ubhayampi mama neva khamati na ruccatīti. "
490471,111,835,2,47,1,324,36,"Evaṃ so kathentova gāmabhojakaṃ cūḷāya gahetvā kaḍḍhitvā gehamajjhe pātetvā‘‘ gāmabhojakomhīti parassa rakkhitagopitabhaṇḍe aparajjhasī’’ tiādīhi paribhāsitvā pothetvā dubbalaṃ katvā gīvāya gahetvā gehā nikkaḍḍhitvā tampi duṭṭhaitthiṃ kesesu gahetvā koṭṭhā otāretvā nippothetvā‘‘ sace puna evarūpaṃ karosi, jānissasī’’ ti santajjesi. "
490472,111,835,48,63,1,100,14,"Tato paṭṭhāya gāmabhojako taṃ gehaṃ oloketumpi na visahi, sāpi pāpā puna manasāpi aticarituṃ nāsakkhi. "
