490478,111,840,13,18,1,33,5,Tassa kira catasso dhītaro ahesuṃ. 
490479,111,840,19,38,1,111,15,"Tā cattāro janā patthenti, tesu eko abhirūpo sarīrasampanno, eko vayappatto mahallako, eko jātisampanno, eko sīlavā. "
490480,111,840,39,41,1,16,2,Brāhmaṇo cintesi–
490481,111,840,42,63,1,136,14,"‘‘ dhītaro nivesentena patiṭṭhāpentena kassa nu kho dātabbā, kiṃ rūpasampannassa, udāhu vayappattassa, jātisampannasīlavantānaṃ aññatarassā’’ ti. "
490482,111,840,64,109,1,282,35,"So cintentopi ajānitvā‘‘ imaṃ kāraṇaṃ sammāsambuddho jānissati, taṃ pucchitvā etesaṃ antare anucchavikassa dassāmī’’ ti gandhamālādīni gāhāpetvā vihāraṃ gantvā satthāraṃ vanditvā ekamantaṃ nisinno ādito paṭṭhāya tamatthaṃ ārocetvā‘‘ bhante, imesu catūsu janesu kassa dātuṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti pucchi. "
490483,111,840,110,132,1,129,17,"Satthā‘‘ pubbepi paṇḍitā etaṃ pañhaṃ kathayiṃsu, bhavasaṅkhepagatattā pana sallakkhetuṃ na sakkosī’’ ti vatvā tena yācito atītaṃ āhari. "
490484,111,841,2,19,1,169,17,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto brāhmaṇakule nibbattitvā vayappatto takkasilāyaṃ sippaṃ uggaṇhitvā āgantvā bārāṇasiyaṃ disāpāmokkho ācariyo ahosi. 
490485,111,841,20,31,1,80,10,"Athekassa brāhmaṇassa catasso dhītaro ahesuṃ, tā evameva cattāro janā patthayiṃsu. "
490486,111,841,32,59,1,150,19,Brāhmaṇo‘‘ kassa nu kho dātabbā’’ ti ajānanto‘‘ ācariyaṃ pucchitvā dātabbayuttakassa dassāmī’’ ti tassa santikaṃ gantvā tamatthaṃ pucchanto paṭhamaṃ gāthamāha– 
490487,111,842,2,4,1,0,0,99.
490488,111,843,2,10,1,45,5,"‘ ‘ Sarīradabyaṃ vuḍḍhabyaṃ, sojaccaṃ sādhusīliyaṃ; "
490489,111,844,2,12,1,48,7,"Brāhmaṇaṃ teva pucchāma, kannu tesaṃ vanimhase’’ ti. "
