490517,111,858,2,4,1,15,2,6 . Nataṃdaḷhavaggo
490518,111,860,2,7,1,25,2,[ 201]1. Bandhanāgārajātakavaṇṇanā 
490519,111,861,2,17,1,95,12,Na taṃ daḷhaṃ bandhanamāhu {dhīrā}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto bandhanāgāraṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
490520,111,861,18,26,1,81,8,Tasmiṃ kira kāle bahū sandhicchedakapanthaghātakacore ānetvā kosalarañño dassesuṃ. 
490521,111,861,27,31,1,64,4,Te rājā addubandhanarajjubandhanasaṅkhalikabandhanehi bandhāpesi. 
490522,111,861,32,90,1,432,51,"Tiṃsamattā jānapadā bhikkhū satthāraṃ daṭṭhukāmā āgantvā disvā vanditvā punadivase piṇḍāya carantā bandhanāgāraṃ gantvā te core disvā piṇḍapātapaṭikkantā sāyanhasamaye tathāgataṃ upasaṅkamitvā‘‘ bhante, ajja amhehi piṇḍāya carantehi bandhanāgāre bahū corā addubandhanādīhi baddhā mahādukkhaṃ anubhavantā diṭṭhā, te tāni bandhanāni chinditvā palāyituṃ na sakkonti, atthi nu kho tehi bandhanehi thirataraṃ nāma aññaṃ bandhanan’’ ti pucchiṃsu. "
490523,111,861,91,129,1,295,30,"Satthā‘‘ bhikkhave, kiṃ bandhanāni nāmetāni, yaṃ panetaṃ dhanadhaññaputtadārādīsu taṇhāsaṅkhātaṃ kilesabandhanaṃ, etaṃ etehi bandhanehi sataguṇena sahassaguṇena thirataraṃ, evaṃ mahantampi panetaṃ ducchindaniyaṃ bandhanaṃ porāṇakapaṇḍitā chinditvā himavantaṃ pavisitvā pabbajiṃsū’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
490524,111,862,2,16,1,128,13,"Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto ekasmiṃ duggatagahapatikule nibbatti, tassa vayappattassa pitā kālamakāsi. "
490525,111,862,17,32,1,111,14,"So bhatiṃ katvā mātaraṃ posesi, athassa mātā anicchamānasseva ekaṃ kuladhītaraṃ gehe katvā aparabhāge kālamakāsi. "
490526,111,862,33,37,1,42,4,Bhariyāyapissa kucchiyaṃ gabbho patiṭṭhāsi. 
490527,111,862,38,58,1,95,13,"So gabbhassa patiṭṭhitabhāvaṃ ajānanto‘‘ bhadde, tvaṃ bhatiṃ katvā jīvāhi, ahaṃ pabbajissāmī’’ ti āha . "
490528,111,862,59,76,1,73,11,"Sāpi‘‘ gabbho me patiṭṭhito, mayi vijātāya dārakaṃ disvā pabbajissasī’’ ti āha. "
490529,111,862,77,101,1,104,14,"So‘‘ sādhū’’ ti sampaṭicchitvā tassā vijātakāle‘‘ bhadde, tvaṃ sotthinā vijātā, idānāhaṃ pabbajissāmī’’ ti āpucchi. "
490530,111,862,102,119,1,90,13,Atha naṃ sā‘‘ puttakassa tāva thanapānato apagamanakālaṃ āgamehī’’ ti vatvā puna gabbhaṃ gaṇhi. 
490531,111,863,2,4,1,10,2,So cintesi–
490532,111,863,5,20,1,85,10,"‘‘ imaṃ sampaṭicchāpetvā gantuṃ na sakkā, imissā anācikkhitvāva palāyitvā pabbajissāmī’’ ti. "
490533,111,863,21,27,1,48,6,So tassā anācikkhitvā ratthibhāge uṭṭhāya palāyi. 
490534,111,863,28,33,1,32,4,Atha naṃ nagaraguttikā aggahesuṃ. 
490535,111,863,34,69,1,231,28,"So‘‘ ahaṃ, sāmi, mātuposako nāma, vissajjetha man’’ ti tehi attānaṃ vissajjāpetvā ekasmiṃ ṭhāne vasitvā aggadvāreneva nikkhamitvā himavantaṃ pavisitvā isipabbajjaṃ pabbajitvā abhiññā ca samāpattiyo ca nibbattetvā jhānakīḷaṃ kīḷanto vihāsi. "
490536,111,863,70,90,1,131,16,So tattha vasanto‘‘ evarūpampi nāma me ducchindaniyaṃ puttadārabandhanaṃ kilesabandhanaṃ chinditan’’ ti udānaṃ udānento imā gāthā avoca– 
490537,111,864,2,4,1,0,0,101.
490538,111,865,2,12,1,59,8,"‘ ‘ Na taṃ daḷhaṃ bandhanamāhu dhīrā, yadāyasaṃ dārujapabbajañca; "
490539,111,866,2,10,1,55,7,"Sārattarattā maṇikuṇḍalesu, puttesu dāresu ca yā apekkhā. "
490540,111,867,2,4,1,0,0,102.
490541,111,868,2,12,1,60,8,"‘ ‘ Etaṃ daḷhaṃ bandhanamāhu dhīrā, ohārinaṃ sīthilaṃ duppamuñcaṃ; "
490542,111,869,2,13,1,62,8,"Etampi chetvāna vajanti dhīrā, anapekkhino kāmasukhaṃ pahāyā’’ ti. "
490543,111,870,2,9,1,46,5,"Tattha {dhīrā}ti dhitimantā, dhikkatapāpāti dhīrā. "
490544,111,870,10,30,1,121,17,"Atha vā dhī vuccati paññā, tāya paññāya samannāgatāti dhīrā, buddhā paccekabuddhā buddhasāvakā bodhisattā ca ime dhīrā nāma. "
490545,111,870,31,63,1,253,29,"Yadāyasan tiādīsu yaṃ saṅkhalikasaṅkhātaṃ ayasā nibbattaṃ āyasaṃ, yaṃ addubandhanasaṅkhātaṃ dārujaṃ, yañca pabbajatiṇehi vā aññehi vā vākādīhi rajjuṃ katvā katarajjubandhanaṃ, taṃ āyasādiṃ chindituṃ sakkuṇeyyabhāvena dhīrā daḷhaṃ thiranti nāhu na kathenti. "
490546,111,870,64,72,1,58,6,"{Sārattarattā}ti sārattā hutvā rattā, balavarāgarattāti attho. "
490547,111,870,73,83,1,63,8,"{Maṇikuṇḍalesū}ti maṇīsu ca kuṇḍalesu ca, maṇiyuttesu vā kuṇḍalesu. "
490548,111,871,2,29,1,154,23,"Etaṃ daḷhan ti ye maṇikuṇḍalesu sārattarattā, tesaṃ yo ca sārāgo, yā ca tesaṃ puttadāresu apekkhā taṇhā, etaṃ kilesamayaṃ bandhanaṃ daḷhaṃ thiranti dhīrā āhu. "
490549,111,871,30,40,1,81,10,Ohārinan ti ākaḍḍhitvā catūsu apāyesu pātanato avaharati heṭṭhā haratīti ohārinaṃ. 
490550,111,871,41,61,1,159,17,"Sithilan ti bandhanaṭṭhāne chavicammamaṃsāni na chindati, lohitaṃ na nīharati, bandhanabhāvampi na jānāpeti, thalapathajalapathādīsu kammāni kātuṃ detīti sithilaṃ. "
490551,111,871,62,75,1,129,13,Duppamuñcan ti taṇhālobhavasena hi ekavārampi uppannaṃ kilesabandhanaṃ daṭṭhaṭṭhānato kacchapo viya dummocayaṃ hotīti duppamuñcaṃ. 
490552,111,871,76,115,1,357,37,"Etampi {chetvānā}ti etaṃ evaṃ daḷhampi kilesabandhanaṃ ñāṇakhaggena chinditvā ayadāmāni chinditvā mattavaravāraṇā viya pañjare chinditvā sīhapotakā viya ca dhīrā vatthukāmakilesakāme ukkārabhūmiṃ viya jigucchamānā anapekkhino hutvā kāmasukhaṃ pahāya vajanti pakkamanti, pakkamitvā ca pana himavantaṃ pavisitvā isipabbajjaṃ pabbajitvā jhānasukhena vītināmentīti. "
490553,111,872,2,11,1,77,8,Evaṃ bodhisatto imaṃ udānaṃ udānetvā aparihīnajjhāno brahmalokaparāyaṇo ahosi. 
490554,111,873,2,24,1,157,18,"Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā saccāni pakāsetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi, saccapariyosāne keci sotāpannā, keci sakadāgāmino, keci anāgāmino, keci arahanto ahesuṃ."
490555,111,873,25,52,1,150,19,"‘‘ Tadā mātā mahāmāyā ahosi, pitā suddhodanamahārājā, bhariyā rāhulamātā, putto rāhulo, puttadāraṃ pahāya nikkhamitvā pabbajito puriso pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
490556,111,874,2,4,1,33,2,Bandhanāgārajātakavaṇṇanā paṭhamā.
490557,111,876,2,7,1,21,2,[ 202]2. Keḷisīlajātakavaṇṇanā 
490558,111,877,2,16,1,100,12,Haṃsā koñcā mayūrā {cā}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto āyasmantaṃ lakuṇḍakabhaddiyaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
490559,111,877,17,41,1,212,22,"So kirāyasmā buddhasāsane pākaṭo ahosi paññāto madhurassaro madhuradhammakathiko paṭisambhidāppatto mahākhīṇāsavo asītiyā mahātherānaṃ antaro pamāṇena omako lakuṇḍako sāmaṇero viya, khuddako kīḷanatthāya kato viya. "
490560,111,877,42,95,1,420,45,Tasmiṃ ekadivasaṃ tathāgataṃ vanditvā jetavanakoṭṭhakaṃ gate janapadā tiṃsamattā bhikkhū‘‘ dasabalaṃ vandissāmā’’ ti jetavanaṃ pavisantā vihārakoṭṭhake theraṃ disvā‘‘ sāmaṇero eso’’ ti saññāya theraṃ cīvarakaṇṇe gaṇhantā hatthe gaṇhantā sīsaṃ gaṇhantā nāsāya parāmasantā kaṇṇesu gahetvā cāletvā hatthakukkuccaṃ katvā pattacīvaraṃ paṭisāmetvā satthāraṃ upasaṅkamitvā vanditvā nisīditvā satthārā madhurapaṭisanthāre kate pucchiṃsu–
490561,111,877,96,114,1,103,12,"‘‘ bhante, lakuṇḍakabhaddiyatthero kira nāmeko tumhākaṃ sāvako madhuradhammakathiko atthi, kahaṃ so idānī’’ ti."
490562,111,877,115,126,1,36,5,"‘‘ Kiṃ pana, bhikkhave, daṭṭhukāmatthā’’ ti?"
490563,111,877,127,135,1,13,3,"‘‘ Āma, bhante’’ ti."
490564,111,877,136,156,1,102,13,"‘‘ Yaṃ, bhikkhave, tumhe dvārakoṭṭhake disvā cīvarakaṇṇādīsu gaṇhantā hatthakukkuccaṃ katvā āgatā, esa so’’ ti."
490565,111,877,157,171,1,86,9,"‘‘ Bhante, evarūpo patthitapatthano abhinīhārasampanno sāvako kiṃkāraṇā appesakkho jāto’’ ti? "
490566,111,877,172,186,1,70,10,Satthā‘‘ attanā katapāpakammaṃ nissāyā’’ ti vatvā tehi yācito atītaṃ āhari. 
490567,111,878,2,11,1,76,9,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto sakko devarājā ahosi. 
490568,111,878,12,69,1,397,46,"Tadā brahmadattassa jiṇṇaṃ jarāppattaṃ hatthiṃ vā assaṃ vā goṇaṃ vā dassetuṃ na sakkā, keḷisīlo hutvā tathārūpaṃ disvāva anubandhāpeti, jiṇṇasakaṭampi disvā bhindāpeti, jiṇṇamātugāme disvā pakkosāpetvā udare paharāpetvā pātāpetvā puna uṭṭhāpetvā bhāyāpeti , jiṇṇapurise disvā laṅghake viya bhūmiyaṃ saṃparivattakādikīḷaṃ kīḷāpeti, apassanto‘‘ asukaghare kira mahallako atthī’’ ti sutvāpi pakkosāpetvā kīḷati. "
490569,111,878,70,84,1,134,12,"Manussā lajjantā attano mātāpitaro tiroraṭṭhāni pesenti, mātupaṭṭhānadhammo pitupaṭṭhānadhammo pacchijji, rājasevakāpi keḷisīlāva ahesuṃ. "
490570,111,878,85,92,1,52,6,"Matamatā cattāro apāye pūrenti, devaparisā parihāyati. "
490571,111,879,2,51,1,347,40,Sakko abhinave devaputte apassanto‘‘ kiṃ nu kho kāraṇan’’ ti āvajjento taṃ kāraṇaṃ ñatvā‘‘ damessāmi nan’’ ti mahallakavaṇṇaṃ abhinimminitvā jiṇṇayānake dve takkacāṭiyo āropetvā dve jaragoṇe yojetvā ekasmiṃ chaṇadivase alaṅkatahatthiṃ abhiruhitvā brahmadatte alaṅkatanagaraṃ padakkhiṇaṃ karonte pilotikanivattho taṃ yānakaṃ pājento rañño abhimukho agamāsi. 
490572,111,879,52,64,1,55,8,Rājā jiṇṇayānakaṃ disvā‘‘ etaṃ yānakaṃ apanethā’’ ti vadati. 
490573,111,879,65,78,1,39,7,"Manussā‘‘ kahaṃ, deva, na passāmā’’ ti āhaṃsu. "
490574,111,879,79,84,1,41,5,Sakko attano ānubhāvena raññoyeva dassesi. 
490575,111,879,85,100,1,119,15,Atha naṃ bahusampatte tasmiṃ tassa uparibhāgena pājento rañño matthake ekaṃ cāṭiṃ bhinditvā nivattāpento dutiyaṃ bhindi. 
490576,111,879,101,115,1,90,13,"Athassa sīsato paṭṭhāya ito cito ca takkaṃ paggharati, so tena aṭṭīyati harāyati jigucchati. "
490577,111,879,116,166,1,348,43,"Athassa taṃ upaddutabhāvaṃ ñatvā sakko yānakaṃ antaradhāpetvā sakkattabhāvaṃ māpetvā vajirahattho ākāse ṭhatvā‘‘ pāpa adhammikarāja, kiṃ tvaṃ mahallako na bhavissasi, tava sarīraṃ jarā na paharissati, keḷisīlo hutvā vuḍḍhe viheṭhanakammaṃ karosi, ekakaṃ taṃ nissāya etaṃ kammaṃ katvā matamatā apāye paripūrenti, manussā mātāpitaro paṭijaggituṃ na labhanti. "
490578,111,879,167,196,1,213,25,"Sace imamhā kammā na viramissasi, vajirena te sīsaṃ padālessāmi, mā ito paṭṭhāyetaṃ kammaṃ akatthā’’ ti santajjetvā mātāpitūnaṃ guṇaṃ kathetvā vuḍḍhāpacāyikakammassa ānisaṃsaṃ pakāsetvā ovaditvā sakaṭṭhānameva agamāsi. "
490579,111,879,197,206,1,63,9,Rājā tato paṭṭhāya tathārūpaṃ kammaṃ kātuṃ cittampi na uppādesi. 
490580,111,880,2,12,1,63,9,Satthā imaṃ atītaṃ āharitvā abhisambuddho hutvā imā gāthā avoca– 
490581,111,881,2,4,1,0,0,103.
490582,111,882,2,12,1,42,8,"‘ ‘ Haṃsā koñcā mayūrā ca, hatthayo pasadā migā; "
490583,111,883,2,9,1,45,6,"Sabbe sīhassa bhāyanti, natthi kāyasmi tulyatā. "
490584,111,884,2,4,1,0,0,104.
490585,111,885,2,11,1,37,6,"‘ ‘ Evameva manussesu, daharo cepi paññavā; "
490586,111,886,2,14,1,44,9,"So hi tattha mahā hoti, neva bālo sarīravā’’ ti. "
490587,111,887,2,16,1,81,12,"Tattha pasadā {migā}ti pasadasaṅkhātā migā, pasadā migā ca avasesā migā cātipi attho."
490588,111,887,17,28,1,41,6,"‘‘ Pasadamigā’’ tipi pāṭho, pasadā migāti attho. "
490589,111,887,29,37,1,51,7,Natthi kāyasmi {tulyatā}ti sarīre pamāṇaṃ nāma natthi. 
490590,111,887,38,61,1,151,18,"Yadi bhaveyya, mahāsarīrā hatthino ceva pasadamigā ca sīhaṃ māreyyuṃ, sīho haṃsādayo khuddakasarīreyeva māreyya, khuddakāyeva sīhassa bhāyeyyuṃ, na mahantā. "
490591,111,887,62,71,1,54,8,"Yasmā panetaṃ natthi, tasmā sabbepi te sīhassa bhāyanti. "
490592,111,887,72,91,1,135,17,"{Sarīravā}ti bālo mahāsarīropi mahā nāma na hoti, tasmā lakuṇḍakabhaddiyo sarīrena khuddakopi mā taṃ ñāṇenapi khuddakoti maññitthāti attho. "
490593,111,888,2,26,1,172,20,"Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā saccāni pakāsetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi, saccapariyosāne tesu bhikkhūsu keci sotāpannā, keci sakadāgāmino, keci anāgāmino, keci arahanto ahesuṃ."
490594,111,888,27,48,1,108,15,"‘‘ Tadā rājā lakuṇḍakabhaddiyo ahosi, so tāya keḷisīlatāya paresaṃ keḷinissayo jāto, sakko pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
490595,111,889,2,4,1,28,2,Keḷisīlajātakavaṇṇanā dutiyā.
490596,111,891,2,7,1,20,2,[ 203]3. Khandhajātakavaṇṇanā 
490597,111,892,2,14,1,91,12,Virūpakkhehi me mettan ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto aññataraṃ bhikkhuṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
490598,111,892,15,30,1,117,14,"Taṃ kira jantāgharadvāre kaṭṭhāni phālentaṃ pūtirukkhantarā nikkhamitvā eko sappo pādaṅguliyaṃ ḍaṃsi, so tattheva mato. "
490599,111,892,31,36,1,41,5,Tassa matabhāvo sakalavihāre pākaṭo ahosi. 
490600,111,892,37,41,1,43,4,Dhammasabhāyaṃ bhikkhū kathaṃ samuṭṭhāpesuṃ–
490601,111,892,42,59,1,90,12,"‘‘ āvuso, asuko kira bhikkhu jantāgharadvāre kaṭṭhāni phālento sappena daṭṭho tattheva mato’’ ti. "
490602,111,892,60,103,1,193,27,"Satthā āgantvā‘‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ imāya nāmā’’ ti vutte‘‘ sace so, bhikkhave, bhikkhu cattāri ahirājakulāni ārabbha mettaṃ abhāvayissa, na naṃ sappo ḍaṃseyya. "
490603,111,892,104,122,1,147,16,Porāṇakatāpasāpi anuppanne buddhe catūsu ahirājakulesu mettaṃ bhāvetvā tāni ahirājakulāni nissāya uppajjanakabhayato mucciṃsū’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. 
490604,111,893,2,32,1,277,28,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto kāsiraṭṭhe brāhmaṇakule nibbattitvā vayappatto kāme pahāya isipabbajjaṃ pabbajitvā abhiññā ca samāpattiyo ca nibbattetvā himavantapadese ekasmiṃ gaṅgānivattane assamapadaṃ māpetvā jhānakīḷaṃ kīḷanto isigaṇaparivuto vihāsi. 
490605,111,893,33,45,1,106,11,"Tadā gaṅgātīre nānappakārā dīghajātikā isīnaṃ paripanthaṃ karonti, yebhuyyena isayo jīvitakkhayaṃ pāpuṇanti. "
490606,111,893,46,50,1,39,4,Tāpasā tamatthaṃ bodhisattassa ārocesuṃ. 
490607,111,893,51,83,1,196,26,"Bodhisatto sabbe tāpase sannipātāpetvā‘‘ sace tumhe catūsu ahirājakulesu mettaṃ bhāveyyātha, na vo sappā ḍaṃseyyuṃ, tasmā ito paṭṭhāya catūsu ahirājakulesu evaṃ mettaṃ bhāvethā’’ ti vatvā imaṃ gāthamāha– "
490608,111,894,2,4,1,0,0,105.
490609,111,895,2,11,1,43,7,"‘ ‘ Virūpakkhehi me mettaṃ, mettaṃ erāpathehi me; "
490610,111,896,2,12,1,52,7,"Chabyāputtehi me mettaṃ, mettaṃ kaṇhāgotamakehi cā’’ ti. "
490611,111,897,2,11,1,79,9,Tattha virūpakkhehi me mettan ti virūpakkhanāgarājakulehi saddhiṃ mayhaṃ mettaṃ. 
490612,111,897,12,16,1,26,4,Erāpathā dīsupi eseva nayo. 
490613,111,897,17,23,1,103,6,Etānipi hi erāpathanāgarājakulaṃ chabyāputtanāgarājakulaṃ kaṇhāgotamakanāgarājakulanti nāgarājakulāneva. 
490614,111,898,2,27,1,156,20,"Evaṃ cattāri nāgarājakulāni dassetvā‘‘ sace tumhe etesu mettaṃ bhāvetuṃ sakkhissatha, dīghajātikā vo na ḍaṃsissanti na viheṭhessantī’’ ti vatvā dutiyaṃ gāthamāha–"
490615,111,899,2,12,1,41,7,"‘ ‘ Apādakehi me mettaṃ, mettaṃ dvipādakehi me; "
490616,111,900,2,12,1,46,7,"Catuppadehi me mettaṃ, mettaṃ bahuppadehi me’’ ti. "
490617,111,901,2,27,1,255,22,"Tattha paṭhamapadena odissakaṃ katvā sabbesu apādakesu dīghajātikesu ceva macchesu ca mettābhāvanā dassitā, dutiyapadena manussesu ceva pakkhijātesu ca, tatiyapadena hatthiassādīsu sabbacatuppadesu, catutthapadena vicchikasatapadiuccāliṅgapāṇakamakkaṭakādīsu. "
490618,111,902,2,11,1,80,9,Evaṃ sarūpena mettābhāvanaṃ dassetvā idāni āyācanavasena dassento imaṃ gāthamāha–
490619,111,903,2,13,1,43,9,"‘ ‘ Mā maṃ apādako hiṃsi, mā maṃ hiṃsi dvipādako; "
490620,111,904,2,14,1,48,9,"Mā maṃ catuppado hiṃsi, mā maṃ hiṃsi bahuppado’’ ti. "
490621,111,905,2,23,1,113,18,"Tattha mā man ti etesu apādakādīsu koci ekopi mā maṃ hiṃsatu, mā viheṭhetūti evaṃ āyācantā mettaṃ bhāvethāti attho. "
490622,111,906,2,8,1,60,6,Idāni anodissakavasena mettābhāvanaṃ dassento imaṃ gāthamāha–
490623,111,907,2,13,1,44,9,"‘ ‘ Sabbe sattā sabbe pāṇā, sabbe bhūtā ca kevalā; "
490624,111,908,2,12,1,46,7,"Sabbe bhadrāni passantu, mā kañci pāpamāgamā’’ ti. "
490625,111,909,2,23,1,206,18,"Tattha taṇhādiṭṭhivasena vaṭṭe pañcasu khandhesu āsattā visattā laggā laggitāti sattā, assāsapassāsapavattanasaṅkhātena pāṇanavasena pāṇā, bhūtabhāvitanibbattanavasena {bhūtā}ti evaṃ vacanamattaviseso veditabbo. "
490626,111,909,24,29,1,59,5,Avisesena pana sabbānipetāni padāni sabbasattasaṅgāhakāneva. 
490627,111,909,30,33,1,15,2,{Kevalā}ti sakalā. 
490628,111,909,34,38,1,39,4,Idaṃ sabbasaddasseva hi pariyāyavacanaṃ. 
490629,111,909,39,48,1,73,8,Bhadrāni {passantū}ti sabbepete sattā bhadrāni sādhūni kalyāṇāneva passantu. 
490630,111,909,49,74,1,149,22,"Mā kañci {pāpamāgamā}ti etesu kañci ekaṃ sattampi pāpaṃ lāmakaṃ dukkhaṃ mā āgamā, mā āgacchatu mā pāpuṇātu, sabbe averā abyāpajjā sukhī niddukkhā hontūti. "
490631,111,910,2,19,1,100,12,Evaṃ ‘‘ sabbasattesu anodissakavasena mettaṃ bhāvethā’’ ti vatvā puna tiṇṇaṃ ratanānaṃ guṇe anussarāpetuṃ– 
490632,111,911,2,4,1,0,0,106.
490633,111,912,2,9,1,31,5,"‘ ‘ Appamāṇo buddho, appamāṇo dhammo; "
490634,111,913,2,8,1,22,4,Appamāṇo saṅgho’’ ti āha. 
490635,111,914,2,10,1,87,8,Tattha pamāṇakarānaṃ kilesānaṃ abhāvena guṇānañca pamāṇābhāvena buddharatanaṃ appamāṇaṃ. 
490636,111,914,11,15,1,34,3,{Dhammo}ti navavidho lokuttaradhammo. 
490637,111,914,16,22,1,41,6,Tassapi pamāṇaṃ kātuṃ na sakkāti appamāṇo. 
490638,111,914,23,29,1,57,6,Tena appamāṇena dhammena samannāgatattā saṅghopi appamāṇo. 
490639,111,915,2,22,1,131,16,Iti bodhisatto‘‘ imesaṃ tiṇṇaṃ ratanānaṃ guṇe anussarathā’’ ti vatvā tiṇṇaṃ ratanānaṃ appamāṇaguṇataṃ dassetvā sappamāṇe satte dassetuṃ–
490640,111,916,2,12,1,46,6,"‘ ‘ Pamāṇavantāni sarīsapāni, ahi vicchika satapadī; "
490641,111,917,2,9,1,30,5,Uṇṇanābhi sarabū mūsikā’’ ti āha. 
490642,111,918,2,7,1,45,4,Tattha {sarīsapānī}ti sappadīghajātikānaṃ nāmaṃ. 
490643,111,918,8,17,1,52,8,"Te hi sarantā gacchanti, sirena vā sapantīti sarīsapā."
490644,111,918,18,27,1,36,5,‘‘ Ahī’’ tiādi tesaṃ sarūpato nidassanaṃ. 
490645,111,918,28,32,1,28,3,Tattha {uṇṇanābhī}ti makkaṭako. 
490646,111,918,33,48,1,73,10,"Tassa hi nābhito uṇṇāsadisaṃ suttaṃ nikkhamati, tasmā‘‘ uṇṇanābhī’’ ti vuccati. "
490647,111,918,49,52,1,20,2,{Sarabū}ti gharagoḷikā. 
490648,111,919,2,48,1,306,37,"Iti bodhisatto‘‘ yasmā etesaṃ antorāgādayo pamāṇakarā dhammā atthi, tasmā tāni sarīsapādīni pamāṇavantānī’’ ti dassetvā‘‘ appamāṇānaṃ tiṇṇaṃ ratanānaṃ ānubhāvena ime pamāṇavantā sattā rattindivaṃ parittakammaṃ karontūti evaṃ tiṇṇaṃ ratanānaṃ guṇe anussarathā’’ ti vatvā tato uttari kattabbaṃ dassetuṃ imaṃ gāthamāha–"
490649,111,920,2,13,1,51,9,"‘ ‘ Katā me rakkhā katā me parittā, paṭikkamantu bhūtāni; "
490650,111,921,2,12,1,56,7,"Sohaṃ namo bhagavato, namo sattannaṃ sammāsambuddhānan’’ ti. "
490651,111,922,2,15,1,83,11,Tattha katā me {rakkhā}ti mayā ratanattayaguṇe anussarantena attano rakkhā gutti katā. 
490652,111,922,16,24,1,46,7,Katā me {parittā}ti parittāṇampi me attano kataṃ. 
490653,111,922,25,33,1,77,7,Paṭikkamantu {bhūtānī}ti mayi ahitajjhāsayāni bhūtāni paṭikkamantu apagacchantu. 
490654,111,922,34,49,1,114,14,Sohaṃ namo {bhagavato}ti so ahaṃ evaṃ kataparitto atītassa parinibbutassa sabbassapi buddhassa bhagavato namo karomi. 
490655,111,922,50,63,1,123,13,Namo sattannaṃ sammāsambuddhānan ti visesena pana atīte paṭipāṭiyā parinibbutānaṃ sattannaṃ sammāsambuddhānaṃ namo karomīti. 
490656,111,923,2,19,1,105,13,Evaṃ ‘‘ namakkāraṃ karontāpi satta buddhe anussarathā’’ ti bodhisatto isigaṇassa imaṃ parittaṃ bandhitvā adāsi. 
490657,111,923,20,44,1,204,23,"Ādito pana paṭṭhāya dvīhi gāthāhi catūsu ahirājakulesu mettāya dīpitattā odissakānodissakavasena vā dvinnaṃ mettābhāvanānaṃ dīpitattā idaṃ parittaṃ idha vuttanti veditabbaṃ, aññaṃ vā kāraṇaṃ pariyesitabbaṃ. "
490658,111,923,45,56,1,83,10,"Tato paṭṭhāya isigaṇo bodhisattassa ovāde ṭhatvā mettaṃ bhāvesi, buddhaguṇe anussari. "
