490689,111,938,2,11,1,51,6,"Tassānukaraṃ saviṭṭhako, sevāle paliguṇṭhito mato’’ ti. "
490690,111,939,2,11,1,64,8,Tattha {udakathalacarassā}ti udake ca thale ca carituṃ samatthassa. 
