490729,111,957,2,4,1,29,2,Gaṅgeyyajātakavaṇṇanā pañcamā.
490730,111,959,2,7,1,24,2,[ 206]6. Kuruṅgamigajātakavaṇṇanā 
490731,111,960,2,13,1,83,11,Iṅgha vaṭṭamayaṃ pāsan ti idaṃ satthā veḷuvane viharanto devadattaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
490732,111,960,14,46,1,155,21,"Tadā hi satthā‘‘ devadatto vadhāya parisakkatī’’ ti sutvā‘‘ na, bhikkhave, devadatto idāneva mayhaṃ vadhāya parisakkati, pubbepi parisakkiyevā’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
490733,111,961,2,20,1,131,16,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto kuruṅgamigo hutvā araññe ekassa sarassa avidūre ekasmiṃ gumbe vāsaṃ kappesi. 
490734,111,961,21,33,1,88,11,"Tasseva sarassa avidūre ekasmiṃ rukkhagge satapatto, sarasmiṃ pana kacchapo vāsaṃ kappesi. "
490735,111,961,34,41,1,55,7,Evaṃ te tayopi sahāyakā aññamaññaṃ piyasaṃvāsaṃ vasiṃsu. 
490736,111,961,42,55,1,130,13,Atheko migaluddako araññe caranto pānīyatitthe bodhisattassa padavalañjaṃ disvā lohanigaḷasadisaṃ vaṭṭamayaṃ pāsaṃ oḍḍetvā agamāsi. 
490737,111,961,56,66,1,78,9,Bodhisatto pānīyaṃ pātuṃ āgato paṭhamayāmeyeva pāse bajjhitvā baddharavaṃ ravi. 
490738,111,961,67,86,1,102,15,Tassa tena saddena rukkhaggato satapatto udakato ca kacchapo āgantvā‘‘ kiṃ nu kho kātabban’’ ti mantayiṃsu. 
490739,111,961,87,128,1,236,32,"Atha satapatto kacchapaṃ āmantetvā‘‘ samma, tava dantā atthi, tvaṃ imaṃ pāsaṃ chinda, ahaṃ gantvā yathā so nāgacchati, tathā karissāmi, evaṃ amhehi dvīhipi kataparakkamena sahāyo no jīvitaṃ labhissatī’’ ti imamatthaṃ pakāsento paṭhamaṃ gāthamāha– "
490740,111,962,2,4,1,0,0,111.
490741,111,963,2,11,1,46,7,"‘ ‘ Iṅgha vaṭṭamayaṃ pāsaṃ, chinda dantehi kacchapa; "
490742,111,964,2,12,1,44,7,"Ahaṃ tathā karissāmi, yathā nehiti luddako’’ ti. "
490743,111,965,2,15,1,103,12,"Atha kacchapo cammavarattaṃ khādituṃ ārabhi, satapatto luddakassa vasanagāmaṃ gato avidūre rukkhe nisīdi. "
490744,111,965,16,21,1,47,5,Luddako paccūsakāleyeva sattiṃ gahetvā nikkhami. 
490745,111,965,22,34,1,107,12,Sakuṇo tassa nikkhamanabhāvaṃ ñatvā vassitvā pakkhe papphoṭetvā taṃ purimadvārena nikkhamantaṃ mukhe pahari. 
490746,111,965,35,51,1,93,12,Luddo‘‘ kāḷakaṇṇinā sakuṇenamhi pahaṭo’’ ti nivattitvā thokaṃ sayitvā puna sattiṃ gahetvā uṭṭhāsi. 
490747,111,965,52,69,1,116,13,Sakuṇo‘‘ ayaṃ paṭhamaṃ purimadvārena nikkhanto idāni pacchimadvārena nikkhamissatī’’ ti ñatvā gantvā pacchimagehe nisīdi. 
490748,111,965,70,96,1,165,19,"Luddopi ‘‘ purimadvārena me nikkhantena kāḷakaṇṇī sakuṇo diṭṭho, idāni pacchimadvārena nikkhamissāmī’’ ti pacchimadvārena nikkhami, sakuṇo puna vassitvā gantvā mukhe pahari. "
490749,111,965,97,121,1,152,19,"Luddo‘‘ punapi kāḷakaṇṇīsakuṇena pahaṭo, na dāni me esa nikkhamituṃ detī’’ ti nivattitvā yāva aruṇuggamanā sayitvā aruṇuggamanavelāya sattiṃ gahetvā nikkhami. "
490750,111,965,122,134,1,61,8,Sakuṇo vegena gantvā‘‘ luddo āgacchatī’’ ti bodhisattassa kathesi. 
490751,111,966,2,12,1,79,9,Tasmiṃ khaṇe kacchapena ekameva cammavaddhaṃ ṭhapetvā sesavarattā khāditā honti. 
490752,111,966,13,21,1,62,7,"Dantā panassa patanākārappattā jātā, mukhato lohitaṃ paggharati. "
490753,111,966,22,44,1,168,20,"Bodhisatto luddaputtaṃ sattiṃ gahetvā asanivegena āgacchantaṃ disvā taṃ vaddhaṃ chinditvā vanaṃ pāvisi, sakuṇo rukkhagge nisīdi, kacchapo pana dubbalattā tattheva nipajji. "
490754,111,966,45,53,1,69,8,Luddo kacchapaṃ gahetvā pasibbake pakkhipitvā ekasmiṃ khāṇuke laggesi. 
490755,111,966,54,74,1,138,16,Bodhisatto nivattitvā olokento kacchapassa gahitabhāvaṃ ñatvā‘‘ sahāyassa jīvitadānaṃ dassāmī’’ ti dubbalo viya hutvā luddassa attānaṃ dassesi. 
490756,111,966,75,90,1,65,10,"So‘‘ dubbalo esa bhavissati, māressāmi nan’’ ti sattiṃ ādāya anubandhi. "
490757,111,966,91,118,1,209,25,"Bodhisatto nātidūre nāccāsanne gacchanto taṃ ādāya araññaṃ pāvisi, dūraṃ gatabhāvaṃ ñatvā padaṃ vañcetvā aññena maggena vātavegena gantvā siṅgena pasibbakaṃ ukkhipitvā bhūmiyaṃ pātetvā phāletvā kacchapaṃ nīhari. "
490758,111,966,119,122,1,24,3,Satapattopi rukkhā otari. 
490759,111,966,123,170,1,257,35,"Bodhisatto dvinnampi ovādaṃ dadamāno‘‘ ahaṃ tumhe nissāya jīvitaṃ labhiṃ, tumhehi sahāyakassa kattabbaṃ mayhaṃ kataṃ, idāni luddo āgantvā tumhe gaṇheyya, tasmā, samma satapatta, tvaṃ attano puttake gahetvā aññattha yāhi, tvampi, samma kacchapa, udakaṃ pavisāhī’’ ti āha. "
490760,111,966,171,174,1,15,3,Te tathā akaṃsu. 
490761,111,967,2,7,1,44,5,Satthā abhisambuddho hutvā dutiyaṃ gāthamāha– 
490762,111,968,2,4,1,0,0,112.
490763,111,969,2,12,1,42,7,"‘ ‘ Kacchapo pāvisī vāriṃ, kuruṅgo pāvisī vanaṃ; "
490764,111,970,2,11,1,42,6,"Satapatto dumaggamhā, dūre putte apānayī’’ ti. "
490765,111,971,2,10,1,46,6,"Tattha {apānayī}ti ānayi, gahetvā agamāsīti attho; "
490766,111,972,2,14,1,104,12,Luddopi taṃ ṭhānaṃ āgantvā kañci apassitvā chinnapasibbakaṃ gahetvā domanassappatto attano gehaṃ agamāsi. 
490767,111,972,15,23,1,64,8,Te tayopi sahāyā yāvajīvaṃ vissāsaṃ acchinditvā yathākammaṃ gatā. 
