490770,111,974,2,4,1,32,2,Kuruṅgamigajātakavaṇṇanā chaṭṭhā.
490771,111,976,2,7,1,19,2,[ 207]7. Assakajātakavaṇṇanā 
490772,111,977,2,12,1,90,8,{Ayamassakarājenā}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto purāṇadutiyikāpalobhanaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
490773,111,977,13,52,1,139,21,"So hi bhikkhu satthārā‘‘ saccaṃ kira, tvaṃ bhikkhu, ukkaṇṭhitosī’’ ti puṭṭho‘‘ saccan’’ ti vatvā‘‘ kena ukkaṇṭhāpitosī’’ ti vutte‘‘ purāṇadutiyikāyā’’ ti āha. "
490774,111,977,53,79,1,131,21,"Atha naṃ satthā‘‘ na idāneva tassā bhikkhu itthiyā tayi sineho atthi, pubbepi tvaṃ taṃ nissāya mahādukkhaṃ patto’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
490775,111,978,2,10,1,60,8,Atīte kāsiraṭṭhe pāṭalinagare assako nāma rājā rajjaṃ kāresi. 
490776,111,978,11,27,1,115,14,"Tassa uparī nāma aggamahesī piyā ahosi manāpā abhirūpā dassanīyā pāsādikā atikkantā mānusavaṇṇaṃ, apattā dibbavaṇṇaṃ. "
490777,111,978,28,38,1,71,9,"Sā kālamakāsi, tassā kālakiriyāya rājā sokābhibhūto ahosi dukkhī dummano. "
490778,111,978,39,52,1,125,13,So tassā sarīraṃ doṇiyaṃ nipajjāpetvā telakalalaṃ pakkhipāpetvā heṭṭhāmañce ṭhapāpetvā nirāhāro rodamāno paridevamāno nipajji. 
490779,111,978,53,72,1,132,12,"Mātāpitaro avasesañātakā mittāmaccabrāhmaṇagahapatikādayopi‘‘ mā soci, mahārāja, aniccā saṅkhārā’’ tiādīni vadantā saññāpetuṃ nāsakkhiṃsu. "
490780,111,978,73,78,1,43,5,Tassa vilapantasseva satta divasā atikkantā. 
490781,111,978,79,116,1,311,33,Tadā bodhisatto pañcābhiññaaṭṭhasamāpattilābhī tāpaso hutvā himavantapadese viharanto ālokaṃ vaḍḍhetvā dibbena cakkhunā jambudīpaṃ olokento taṃ rājānaṃ tathā paridevamānaṃ disvā‘‘ etassa mayā avassayena bhavitabban’’ ti iddhānubhāvena ākāse uppatitvā rañño uyyāne otaritvā maṅgalasilāpaṭṭe kañcanapaṭimā viya nisīdi. 
490782,111,979,2,11,1,85,9,Atheko pāṭalinagaravāsī brāhmaṇamāṇavo uyyānaṃ gato bodhisattaṃ disvā vanditvā nisīdi. 
490783,111,979,12,29,1,78,11,"Bodhisatto tena saddhiṃ paṭisanthāraṃ katvā‘‘ kiṃ, māṇava, rājā dhammiko’’ ti pucchi."
490784,111,979,30,76,1,264,35,"‘‘ Āma, bhante, dhammiko rājā, bhariyā panassa kālakatā, so tassā sarīraṃ doṇiyaṃ pakkhipāpetvā vilapamāno nipanno, ajja sattamo divaso, kissa tumhe rājānaṃ evarūpā dukkhā na mocetha, yuttaṃ nu kho tumhādisesu sīlavantesu saṃvijjamānesu rañño evarūpaṃ dukkhaṃ anubhavitun’’ ti."
490785,111,979,77,107,1,149,21,"‘‘ Na kho ahaṃ , māṇava, rājānaṃ jānāmi, sace pana so āgantvā maṃ puccheyya, ahamevassa tassā nibbattaṭṭhānaṃ ācikkhitvā rañño santikeyeva taṃ kathāpeyyan’’ ti."
490786,111,979,108,145,1,190,26,"‘‘ Tena hi, bhante, yāva rājānaṃ ānemi, tāva imeva nisīdathā’’ ti māṇavo bodhisattassa paṭiññaṃ gahetvā rañño santikaṃ gantvā tamatthaṃ ārocetvā‘‘ tassa dibbacakkhukassa santikaṃ gantuṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti āha. "
490787,111,980,2,21,1,123,15,Rājā ‘‘ upariṃ kira daṭṭhuṃ labhissāmī’’ ti tuṭṭhamānaso rathaṃ abhiruhitvā tattha gantvā bodhisattaṃ vanditvā ekamantaṃ nisinno–
490788,111,980,22,34,1,58,8,‘‘ saccaṃ kira tumhe deviyā nibbattaṭṭhānaṃ jānāthā’’ ti pucchi.
490789,111,980,35,43,1,15,3,"‘‘ Āma, mahārājā’’ ti."
490790,111,980,44,51,1,18,3,‘‘ Kattha nibbattā’’ ti?
490791,111,980,52,72,1,120,13,"‘‘ Sā kho, mahārāja, rūpasmiṃyeva mattā pamādamāgamma kalyāṇakammaṃ akatvā imasmiṃyeva uyyāne gomayapāṇakayoniyaṃ nibbattā’’ ti ."
490792,111,980,73,80,1,18,3,‘‘ Nāhaṃ saddahāmī’’ ti.
490793,111,980,81,91,1,32,6,‘‘ Tena hi te dassetvā kathāpemī’’ ti.
490794,111,980,92,99,1,19,3,‘‘ Sādhu kathāpethā’’ ti. 
490795,111,980,100,117,1,108,13,Bodhisatto attano ānubhāvena‘‘ ubhopi gomayapiṇḍaṃ vaṭṭayamānā rañño purato āgacchantū’’ ti tesaṃ āgamanaṃ akāsi. 
490796,111,980,118,121,1,19,3,Te tatheva āgamiṃsu. 
490797,111,980,122,148,1,125,17,"Bodhisatto taṃ dassento‘‘ ayaṃ te , mahārāja, uparidevī, taṃ jahitvā gomayapāṇakassa pacchato pacchato gacchati, passatha nan’’ ti āha. "
490798,111,980,149,164,1,73,9,Bhante‘‘‘ uparī nāma gomayapāṇakayoniyaṃ nibbattissatī’ ti na saddahāmahan’’ ti.
490799,111,980,165,174,1,25,4,"‘‘ Kathāpemi naṃ, mahārājā’’ ti."
490800,111,980,175,183,1,20,3,"‘‘ Kathāpetha, bhante’’ ti. "
490801,111,981,2,14,1,56,8,Bodhisatto attano ānubhāvena taṃ kathāpento‘‘ uparī’’ ti āha. 
490802,111,981,15,26,1,35,6,"Sā manussabhāsāya‘‘ kiṃ, bhante’’ ti āha."
490803,111,981,27,37,1,32,6,‘‘ Tvaṃ atītabhave kā nāma ahosī’’ ti?
490804,111,981,38,50,1,50,7,"‘‘ Bhante, assakarañño aggamahesī uparī nāma ahosin’’ ti."
490805,111,981,51,65,1,55,9,"‘‘ Kiṃ pana te idāni assakarājā piyo, udāhu gomayapāṇako’’ ti?"
490806,111,981,66,84,1,125,14,"‘‘ Bhante, so mayhaṃ purimajātiyā sāmiko, tadā ahaṃ imasmiṃ uyyāne tena saddhiṃ rūpasaddagandharasaphoṭṭhabbe anubhavamānā vicariṃ. "
490807,111,981,85,114,1,214,26,"Idāni pana me bhavasaṅkhepagatakālato paṭṭhāya so kiṃ hoti, ahañhi idāni assakarājānaṃ māretvā tassa galalohitena mayhaṃ sāmikassa gomayapāṇakassa pāde makkheyyan’’ ti vatvā parisamajjhe manussabhāsāya imā gāthā avoca– "
490808,111,982,2,4,1,0,0,113.
490809,111,983,2,10,1,35,5,"‘ ‘ Ayamassakarājena , deso vicarito mayā; "
490810,111,984,2,8,1,35,5,"Anukāmaya kāmena, piyena patinā saha. "
490811,111,985,2,4,1,0,0,114.
490812,111,986,2,9,1,39,5,"‘ ‘ Navena sukhadukkhena, porāṇaṃ apidhīyati; "
490813,111,987,2,11,1,41,6,"Tasmā assakaraññāva, kīṭo piyataro mamā’’ ti. "
490814,111,988,2,17,1,112,13,"Tattha ayamassakarājena, deso vicarito {mayā}ti ayaṃ ramaṇīyo uyyānapadeso pubbe mayā assakarājena saddhiṃ vicarito. "
490815,111,988,18,34,1,94,12,"Anukāmaya {kāmenā}ti {anū}ti nipātamattaṃ, mayā taṃ kāmayamānāya tena maṃ kāmayamānena sahāti attho. "
490816,111,988,35,40,1,32,4,{Piyenā}ti tasmiṃ attabhāve piyena. 
490817,111,988,41,68,1,171,21,"Navena sukhadukkhena, porāṇaṃ {apidhīyatī}ti, bhante, navena hi sukhena porāṇaṃ sukhaṃ, navena ca dukkhena porāṇaṃ dukkhaṃ pidhīyati paṭicchādīyati, esā lokassa dhammatāti dīpeti. "
490818,111,988,69,88,1,138,16,"Tasmā assakaraññāva, kīṭo piyataro {mamā}ti yasmā navena porāṇaṃ pidhīyati, tasmā mama assakarājato sataguṇena sahassaguṇena kīṭova piyataroti. "
490819,111,989,2,23,1,172,21,Taṃ sutvā assakarājā vippaṭisārī hutvā tattha ṭhitova kuṇapaṃ nīharāpetvā sīsaṃ nhatvā bodhisattaṃ vanditvā nagaraṃ pavisitvā aññaṃ aggamahesiṃ katvā dhammena rajjaṃ kāresi. 
490820,111,989,24,31,1,66,7,Bodhisattopi rājānaṃ ovaditvā nissokaṃ katvā himavantameva agamāsi. 
490821,111,990,2,16,1,132,12,"Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā saccāni pakāsetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi, saccapariyosāne ukkaṇṭhitabhikkhu sotāpattiphale patiṭṭhahi."
490822,111,990,17,38,1,108,14,"‘‘ Tadā uparī purāṇadutiyikā ahosi, assakarājā ukkaṇṭhito bhikkhu, māṇavo sāriputto, tāpaso pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
490823,111,991,2,4,1,27,2,Assakajātakavaṇṇanā sattamā.
490824,111,993,2,7,1,21,2,[ 208]8. Susumārajātakavaṇṇanā 
490825,111,994,2,16,1,101,12,Alaṃ metehi {ambehī}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto devadattassa vadhāya parisakkanaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
490826,111,994,17,55,1,192,26,"Tadā hi satthā‘‘ devadatto vadhāya parisakkatī’’ ti sutvā‘‘ na, bhikkhave, idāneva devadatto mayhaṃ vadhāya parisakkati, pubbepi parisakkiyeva, santāsamattampi pana kātuṃ na sakkhī’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
490827,111,995,2,20,1,192,18,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente himavantapadese bodhisatto kapiyoniyaṃ nibbattitvā nāgabalo thāmasampanno mahāsarīro sobhaggappatto hutvā gaṅgānivattane araññāyatane vāsaṃ kappesi. 
490828,111,995,21,26,1,30,5,Tadā gaṅgāya eko susumāro vasi. 
490829,111,995,27,39,1,93,11,Athassa bhariyā bodhisattassa sarīraṃ disvā tassa hadayamaṃse dohaḷaṃ uppādetvā susumāraṃ āha–
490830,111,995,40,52,1,56,7,"‘‘ ahaṃ sāmi, etassa kapirājassa hadayamaṃsaṃ khāditukāmā’’ ti."
490831,111,995,53,70,1,73,10,"‘‘ Bhadde, mayaṃ jalagocarā, eso thalagocaro, kinti naṃ gaṇhituṃ sakkhissāmā’’ ti."
490832,111,995,71,86,1,57,9,"‘‘ Yena kenaci upāyena gaṇha, sace na labhissāmi, marissāmī’’ ti."
490833,111,995,87,115,1,175,22,"‘‘ Tena hi mā soci, attheko upāyo, khādāpessāmi taṃ tassa hadayamaṃsan’’ ti susumāriṃ samassāsetvā bodhisattassa gaṅgāya pānīyaṃ pivitvā gaṅgātīre nisinnakāle santikaṃ gantvā evamāha–"
490834,111,995,116,146,1,194,23,"‘‘ vānarinda, imasmiṃ padese kasāyaphalāni khādanto kiṃ tvaṃ niviṭṭhaṭṭhāneyeva carasi, pāragaṅgāya ambalabujādīnaṃ madhuraphalānaṃ anto natthi, kiṃ te tattha gantvā phalāphalaṃ khādituṃ na vaṭṭatī’’ ti?"
490835,111,995,147,161,1,64,8,"‘‘ Kumbhīlarāja, gaṅgā mahodakā vitthiṇṇā, kathaṃ tattha gamissāmī’’ ti?"
490836,111,995,162,176,1,54,9,"‘‘ Sace icchasi, ahaṃ taṃ mama piṭṭhiṃ āropetvā nessāmī’’ ti. "
490837,111,995,177,186,1,34,5,So saddahitvā‘‘ sādhū’’ ti sampaṭicchi.
490838,111,995,187,202,1,56,11,‘‘ Tena hi ehi piṭṭhiṃ me abhirūhā’’ ti ca vutte taṃ abhiruhi. 
490839,111,995,203,208,1,37,5,Susumāro thokaṃ netvā udake osīdāpesi. 
490840,111,996,2,19,1,59,11,"Bodhisatto ‘‘ samma, udake maṃ osīdāpesi, kiṃ nu kho etan’’ ti āha."
490841,111,996,20,44,1,133,17,"‘‘ Nāhaṃ taṃ dhammasudhammatāya gahetvā gacchāmi, bhariyāya pana me tava hadayamaṃse dohaḷo uppanno, tamahaṃ tava hadayaṃ khādāpetukāmo’’ ti."
490842,111,996,45,53,1,34,5,"‘‘ Samma, kathentena te sundaraṃ kataṃ. "
490843,111,996,54,68,1,86,11,"Sace hi amhākaṃ udare hadayaṃ bhaveyya, sākhaggesu carantānaṃ cuṇṇavicuṇṇaṃ bhaveyyā’’ ti."
490844,111,996,69,78,1,28,5,‘‘ Kahaṃ pana tumhe ṭhapethā’’ ti? 
490845,111,996,79,98,1,129,14,Bodhisatto avidūre ekaṃ udumbaraṃ pakkaphalapiṇḍisañchannaṃ dassento‘‘ passetāni amhākaṃ hadayāni etasmiṃ udumbare olambantī’’ ti āha.
490846,111,996,99,114,1,48,9,"‘‘ Sace me hadayaṃ dassasi, ahaṃ taṃ na māressāmī’’ ti."
490847,111,996,115,131,1,59,11,"‘‘ Tena hi maṃ ettha nehi, ahaṃ te rukkhe olambantaṃ dassāmī’’ ti. "
490848,111,996,132,137,1,27,5,So taṃ ādāya tattha agamāsi. 
490849,111,996,138,190,1,285,40,"Bodhisatto tassa piṭṭhito uppatitvā udumbararukkhe nisīditvā‘‘ samma, bāla susumāra,‘ imesaṃ sattānaṃ hadayaṃ nāma rukkhagge hotī’ ti saññī ahosi, bālosi, ahaṃ taṃ vañcesiṃ, tava phalāphalaṃ taveva hotu, sarīrameva pana te mahantaṃ paññā pana natthī’’ ti vatvā imamatthaṃ pakāsento imā gāthā avoca– "
490850,111,997,2,4,1,0,0,115.
490851,111,998,2,11,1,38,7,"‘ ‘ Alaṃ metehi ambehi, jambūhi panasehi ca; "
490852,111,999,2,9,1,43,6,"Yāni pāraṃ samuddassa, varaṃ mayhaṃ udumbaro. "
490853,111,1000,2,4,1,0,0,116.
490854,111,1001,2,13,1,41,9,"‘ ‘ Mahatī vata te bondi, na ca paññā tadūpikā; "
490855,111,1002,2,12,1,48,7,"Susumāra vañcito mesi, gaccha dāni yathāsukhan’’ ti. "
490856,111,1003,2,14,1,67,10,"Tattha alaṃ {metehī}ti yāni tayā dīpake niddiṭṭhāni, etehi mayhaṃ alaṃ. "
490857,111,1003,15,23,1,59,7,Varaṃ mayhaṃ {udumbaro}ti mayhaṃ ayameva udumbararukkho varaṃ. 
490858,111,1003,24,27,1,15,2,{Bondī}ti sarīraṃ. 
490859,111,1003,28,38,1,68,9,{Tadūpikā}ti paññā pana te tadūpikā tassa sarīrassa anucchavikā natthi. 
490860,111,1003,39,51,1,91,11,"Gaccha dāni yathāsukhan ti idāni yathāsukhaṃ gaccha, natthi te hadayamaṃsagahaṇūpāyoti attho. "
490861,111,1003,52,62,1,89,10,Susumāro sahassaṃ parājito viya dukkhī dummano pajjhāyantova attano nivāsaṭṭhānameva gato. 
490862,111,1004,2,8,1,54,6,Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–
490863,111,1004,9,26,1,84,11,"‘‘ tadā susumāro devadatto ahosi, susumārī ciñcamāṇavikā, kapirājā pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
490864,111,1005,2,4,1,29,2,Susumārajātakavaṇṇanā aṭṭhamā.
490865,111,1007,2,7,1,20,2,[ 209]9. Kukkuṭajātakavaṇṇanā 
490866,111,1008,2,18,1,136,13,Diṭṭhā mayā vane {rukkhā}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto dhammasenāpatisāriputtattherassa saddhivihārikaṃ daharabhikkhuṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
490867,111,1008,19,27,1,47,7,So kira attano sarīrassa guttikamme cheko ahosi.
490868,111,1008,28,61,1,175,23,"‘‘ Sarīrassa me na sukhaṃ bhaveyyā’’ ti bhayena atisītaṃ accuṇhaṃ paribhogaṃ na karoti,‘‘ sītuṇhehi sarīraṃ kilameyyā’’ ti bhayena bahi na nikkhamati, atikilinnauttaṇḍulādīni na bhuñjati. "
490869,111,1008,62,68,1,53,6,Tassa sā sarīraguttikusalatā saṅghamajjhe pākaṭā jātā. 
490870,111,1008,69,73,1,43,4,Bhikkhū dhammasabhāyaṃ kathaṃ samuṭṭhāpesuṃ–
490871,111,1008,74,87,1,57,8,"‘‘ āvuso, asuko daharo kira bhikkhu sarīraguttikamme cheko’’ ti. "
490872,111,1008,88,133,1,196,28,"Satthā āgantvā‘‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ imāya nāmā’’ ti vutte‘‘ na, bhikkhave, ayaṃ daharo idāneva sarīraguttikamme cheko, pubbepi chekova ahosī’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
490873,111,1009,2,11,1,87,9,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto araññāyatane rukkhadevatā ahosi. 
490874,111,1009,12,29,1,166,17,Atheko sakuṇaluddako ekaṃ dīpakakukkuṭamādāya vālarajjuñca yaṭṭhiñca gahetvā araññe kukkuṭe bandhanto ekaṃ palāyitvā araññaṃ paviṭṭhaṃ porāṇakukkuṭaṃ bandhituṃ ārabhi. 
490875,111,1009,30,40,1,71,9,"So vālapāse kusalatāya attānaṃ bandhituṃ na deti, uṭṭhāyuṭṭhāya nilīyati. "
490876,111,1009,41,49,1,80,8,Luddako attānaṃ sākhāpallavehi paṭicchādetvā punappunaṃ yaṭṭhiñca pāsañca oḍḍeti. 
490877,111,1009,50,58,1,70,8,Kukkuṭo taṃ lajjāpetukāmo mānusiṃ vācaṃ nicchāretvā paṭhamaṃ gāthamāha– 
490878,111,1010,2,4,1,0,0,117.
490879,111,1011,2,11,1,43,7,"‘ ‘ Diṭṭhā mayā vane rukkhā, assakaṇṇā vibhīṭakā; "
490880,111,1012,2,14,1,50,9,"Na tāni evaṃ sakkanti, yathā tvaṃ rukkha sakkasī’’ ti. "
490881,111,1013,2,38,1,211,32,"Tassattho – samma luddaka, mayā imasmiṃ vane jātā bahū assakaṇṇā ca vibhīṭakā ca rukkhā diṭṭhapubbā, tāni pana rukkhāni yathā tvaṃ sakkasi saṅkamasi ito cito ca vicarasi, evaṃ na sakkanti na saṅkamanti na vicarantīti. "
490882,111,1014,2,11,1,56,9,Evaṃ vatvā ca pana so kukkuṭo palāyitvā aññattha agamāsi. 
490883,111,1014,12,18,1,50,6,Tassa palāyitvā gatakāle luddako dutiyaṃ gāthamāha– 
490884,111,1015,2,4,1,0,0,118.
490885,111,1016,2,12,1,39,5,"‘ ‘ Porāṇakukkuṭo ayaṃ, bhetvā pañjaramāgato; "
490886,111,1017,2,10,1,40,5,"Kusalo vālapāsānaṃ, apakkamati bhāsatī’’ ti. "
490887,111,1018,2,29,1,197,26,"Tattha kusalo vālapāsānan ti vālamayesu pāsesu kusalo attānaṃ bandhituṃ adatvā apakkamati ceva bhāsati ca, bhāsitvā ca pana palātoti evaṃ vatvā luddako araññe caritvā yathāladdhamādāya gehameva gato. "
490888,111,1019,2,8,1,54,6,Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–
490889,111,1019,9,31,1,139,16,"‘‘ tadā luddako devadatto ahosi, kukkuṭo kāyaguttikusalo daharabhikkhu, tassa pana kāraṇassa paccakkhakārikā rukkhadevatā pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
490890,111,1020,2,4,1,27,2,Kukkuṭajātakavaṇṇanā navamā.
490891,111,1022,2,7,1,24,2,[ 210]10. Kandagalakajātakavaṇṇanā 
490892,111,1023,2,14,1,84,11,Ambho ko nāmayaṃ {rukkho}ti idaṃ satthā veḷuvane viharanto sugatālayaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
490893,111,1023,15,49,1,163,23,"Tadā hi satthā‘‘ devadatto sugatālayaṃ akāsī’’ ti sutvā‘‘ na, bhikkhave, idāneva devadatto mayhaṃ anukiriyaṃ karonto vināsaṃ patto, pubbepi pāpuṇiyevā’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
490894,111,1024,2,20,1,139,13,"Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto himavantapadese rukkhakoṭṭakasakuṇayoniyaṃ nibbatti,‘‘ khadiravaniyo’’ tissa nāmaṃ ahosi. "
490895,111,1024,21,36,1,113,13,"So khadiravaneyeva gocaraṃ gaṇhi, tasseko kandagalako nāma sahāyo ahosi, so simbalipālibhaddakavane gocaraṃ gaṇhāti. "
490896,111,1024,37,42,1,47,5,So ekadivasaṃ khadiravaniyassa santikaṃ agamāsi. 
490897,111,1024,43,63,1,142,16,Khadiravaniyo‘‘ sahāyo me āgato’’ ti kandagalakaṃ gahetvā khadiravanaṃ pavisitvā khadirakhandhaṃ tuṇḍena paharitvā rukkhato pāṇake nīharitvā adāsi. 
490898,111,1024,64,72,1,66,8,Kandagalako dinne dinne madhurapūve viya chinditvā chinditvā khādi. 
490899,111,1024,73,77,1,32,4,Tassa khādantasseva māno uppajji–
490900,111,1024,78,100,1,113,13,"‘‘ ayampi rukkhakoṭṭakayoniyaṃ nibbatto, ahampi, kiṃ me etena dinnagocarena, sayameva khadiravane gocaraṃ gaṇhissāmī’’ ti. "
490901,111,1024,101,104,1,21,3,So khadiravaniyaṃ āha–
490902,111,1024,105,121,1,72,10,"‘‘ samma, mā tvaṃ dukkhaṃ anubhavi, ahameva khadiravane gocaraṃ gaṇhissāmī’’ ti. "
490903,111,1025,2,30,1,139,20,"Atha naṃ so‘‘ handa tvaṃ samma, simbalipālibhaddakādivane nissāre gocaraggahaṇakule jāto, khadirā nāma jātasārā thaddhā, mā te etaṃ ruccī’’ ti āha. "
490904,111,1025,31,50,1,128,15,Kandagalako‘‘ kiṃ dānāhaṃ na rukkhakoṭṭakayoniyaṃ nibbatto’’ ti tassa vacanaṃ anādiyitvā vegena gantvā khadirarukkhaṃ tuṇḍena pahari. 
490905,111,1025,51,61,1,78,8,"Tāvadevassa tuṇḍaṃ bhijji, akkhīni nikkhamanākārappattāni jātāni, sīsaṃ phalitaṃ. "
490906,111,1025,62,70,1,68,8,So khandhe patiṭṭhātuṃ asakkonto bhūmiyaṃ patitvā paṭhamaṃ gāthamāha– 
490907,111,1026,2,4,1,0,0,119.
490908,111,1027,2,11,1,44,7,"‘ ‘ Ambho ko nāmayaṃ rukkho, sinnapatto sakaṇṭako; "
490909,111,1028,2,10,1,45,5,"Yattha ekappahārena, uttamaṅgaṃ vibhijjitan’’ ti. "
490910,111,1029,2,16,1,70,11,"Tattha ambho ko nāmayaṃ {rukkho}ti, bho khadiravaniya, ko nāma ayaṃ rukkho."
490911,111,1029,17,26,1,21,5,‘‘ Ko nāma so’’ tipi pāṭho. 
490912,111,1029,27,30,1,25,2,{Sinnapatto}ti sukhumapatto. 
490913,111,1029,31,38,1,52,6,Yattha {ekappahārenā}ti yasmiṃ rukkhe ekeneva pahārena. 
490914,111,1029,39,51,1,75,10,"Uttamaṅgaṃ vibhijjitan ti sīsaṃ bhinnaṃ, na kevalañca sīsaṃ, tuṇḍampi bhinnaṃ. "
490915,111,1029,52,70,1,116,14,So vedanāppattatāya khadirarukkhaṃ‘‘ kiṃ rukkho nāmeso’’ ti jānituṃ asakkonto vedanāppatto hutvā imāya gāthāya vippalapi. 
490916,111,1030,2,8,1,49,6,Taṃ vacanaṃ sutvā khadiravaniyo dutiyaṃ gāthamāha– 
490917,111,1031,2,4,1,0,0,120.
490918,111,1032,2,11,1,56,7,"‘ ‘ Acāri vatāyaṃ vitudaṃ vanāni, kaṭṭhaṅgarukkhesu asārakesu; "
490919,111,1033,2,12,1,61,7,"Athāsadā khadiraṃ jātasāraṃ, yatthabbhidā garuḷo uttamaṅgan’’ ti. "
490920,111,1034,2,10,1,39,7,Tattha acāri vatāyan ti acari vata ayaṃ. 
490921,111,1034,11,17,1,69,5,Vitudaṃ {vanānī}ti nissārasimbalipālibhaddakavanāni vitudanto vijjhanto. 
490922,111,1034,18,22,1,49,3,{Kaṭṭhaṅgarukkhesū}ti vanakaṭṭhakoṭṭhāsesu rukkhesu. 
490923,111,1034,23,27,1,46,3,{Asārakesū}ti nissāresu pālibhaddakasimbaliādīsu. 
490924,111,1034,28,38,1,86,10,Athāsadā khadiraṃ jātasāran ti atha potakakālato paṭṭhāya jātasāraṃ khadiraṃ sampāpuṇi. 
490925,111,1034,39,49,1,80,9,Yatthabbhidā garuḷo uttamaṅgan ti {yatthabbhidā}ti yasmiṃ khadire abhindi padālayi. 
490926,111,1034,50,53,1,15,2,{Garuḷo}ti sakuṇo. 
490927,111,1034,54,57,1,46,3,Sabbasakuṇānañhetaṃ sagāravasappatissa vacanaṃ. 
490928,111,1035,2,24,1,107,15,"Iti naṃ khadiravaniyo vatvā‘‘ bho kandagalaka, yattha tvaṃ uttamaṅgaṃ abhindi, khadiro nāmeso sārarukkho’’ ti āha. "
490929,111,1035,25,29,1,32,4,So tattheva jīvitakkhayaṃ pāpuṇi. 
490930,111,1036,2,9,1,54,6,Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–
490931,111,1036,10,24,1,69,9,"‘‘ tadā kandagalako devadatto ahosi, khadiravaniyo pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
490932,111,1037,2,4,1,31,2,Kandagalakajātakavaṇṇanā dasamā. 
490933,111,1038,2,4,1,23,2,Nataṃdaḷhavaggo chaṭṭho. 
490934,111,1039,2,3,1,11,1,Tassuddānaṃ – 
490935,111,1040,2,7,1,47,4,"Bandhanāgāraṃ keḷisīlaṃ, khaṇḍaṃ vīrakagaṅgeyyaṃ; "
490936,111,1041,2,6,1,40,3,"Kuruṅgamassakañceva , susumārañca kukkuṭaṃ; "
