491051,111,1088,44,70,1,243,26,Evaṃ tasmiṃ isigaṇe tattha vasante aḍḍhamāsaccayena añño gaṇasatthā pañcasataparivāro āgantvā nagare bhikkhāya caritvā nagarā nikkhamitvā dakkhiṇadvāre tādisasseva vaṭarukkhassa mūle nisīditvā bhattakiccaṃ katvā tattha rukkhamūle vāsaṃ kappesi. 
