491102,111,1108,78,80,1,11,2,Kiṃ guyhati? 
491103,111,1108,81,82,1,5,1,Kākaṃ. 
491104,111,1108,83,99,1,98,12,Iti kākassa guyhaṃ kākaguyhanti taṃ vadamānā kākena guyhavacanassa kāraṇabhūtena‘‘ guyhan’’ ti vadanti. 
491105,111,1108,100,110,1,32,6,Tena vuttaṃ‘‘ yena ca guyhamāhū’’ ti. 
491106,111,1108,111,156,1,273,37,"Dūraṃ gataṃ yena ca {avhayantī}ti dūraṃ gataṃ vippavutthaṃ piyapuggalaṃ yaṃ āgantvā nisinnaṃ disvā sace itthannāmo āgacchati, vassa kākāti vā vassantaññeva vā sutvā‘‘ yathā kāko vassati, itthannāmo āgamissatī’’ ti evaṃ vadantā yena ca avhayanti kathenti mantenti, udāharantīti attho. "
