491165,111,1132,2,7,1,19,2,[ 216]6. Macchajātakavaṇṇanā 
491166,111,1133,2,13,1,93,10,Na māyamaggi {tapatī}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto purāṇadutiyikāpalobhanaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
491167,111,1133,14,30,1,69,10,"Tañhi bhikkhuṃ satthā‘‘ saccaṃ kira tvaṃ, bhikkhu, ukkaṇṭhitosī’’ ti pucchi."
491168,111,1133,31,55,1,76,11,"‘‘ Saccaṃ, bhante’’ ti vutte‘‘ kena ukkaṇṭhāpitosī’’ ti puṭṭho‘‘ purāṇadutiyikāyā’’ ti āha. "
491169,111,1133,56,88,1,185,26,"Atha naṃ satthā‘‘ ayaṃ te bhikkhu itthī anatthakārikā, pubbepi tvaṃ etaṃ nissāya sūlena vijjhitvā aṅgāresu pacitvā khāditabbataṃ patto paṇḍite nissāya jīvitaṃ alatthā’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
491170,111,1134,2,11,1,76,9,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto tassa purohito ahosi. 
491171,111,1134,12,31,1,129,15,Athekadivasaṃ kevaṭṭā jāle laggaṃ macchaṃ uddharitvā uṇhavālukāpiṭṭhe ṭhapetvā‘‘ aṅgāresu naṃ pacitvā khādissāmā’’ ti sūlaṃ tacchiṃsu. 
491172,111,1134,32,39,1,51,7,Maccho macchiṃ ārabbha paridevamāno imā gāthā avoca– 
491173,111,1135,2,4,1,0,0,131.
491174,111,1136,2,11,1,41,7,"‘ ‘ Na māyamaggi tapati, na sūlo sādhutacchito; "
491175,111,1137,2,11,1,45,8,"Yañca maṃ maññate macchī, aññaṃ so ratiyā gato. "
491176,111,1138,2,4,1,0,0,132.
491177,111,1139,2,12,1,43,8,"‘ ‘ So maṃ dahati rāgaggi, cittaṃ cūpatapeti maṃ; "
491178,111,1140,2,13,1,48,8,"Jālino muñcathāyirā maṃ, na kāme haññate kvacī’’ ti. "
491179,111,1141,2,21,1,88,15,"Tattha na māyamaggi {tapatī}ti na maṃ ayaṃ aggi tapati, na tāpaṃ janeti, na socayatīti attho. "
491180,111,1141,22,36,1,70,12,"Na {sūlo}ti ayaṃ sūlopi sādhutacchito maṃ na tapati, na me sokaṃ uppādeti. "
491181,111,1141,37,63,1,124,19,"Yañca maṃ {maññate}ti yaṃ pana maṃ macchī evaṃ maññati‘‘ aññaṃ macchiṃ so pañcakāmaguṇaratiyā gato’’ ti, tadeva maṃ tapati socayati. "
491182,111,1141,64,76,1,55,10,"So maṃ {dahatī}ti yo panesa rāgaggi, so maṃ dahati jhāpeti. "
491183,111,1141,77,89,1,93,12,Cittaṃ cūpatapeti man ti rāgasampayuttakaṃ mama cittameva ca maṃ upatāpeti kilameti viheṭheti. 
491184,111,1141,90,94,1,24,3,{Jālino}ti kevaṭṭe ālapati. 
491185,111,1141,95,106,1,42,7,Te hi jālassa atthitāya‘‘ jālino’’ ti vuccanti. 
491186,111,1141,107,114,1,48,7,Muñcathāyirā man ti muñcatha maṃ sāminoti yācati. 
491187,111,1141,115,128,1,78,12,Na kāme haññate {kvacī}ti kāme patiṭṭhito kāmena nīyamāno satto na kvaci haññati. 
491188,111,1141,129,136,1,52,7,Na hi taṃ tumhādisā hanituṃ anucchavikāti paridevati. 
491189,111,1141,137,153,1,111,14,"Atha vā {kāme}ti hetuvacane bhummaṃ, kāmahetu macchiṃ anubandhamāno nāma na kvaci tumhādisehi haññatīti paridevati. "
491190,111,1141,154,168,1,118,14,Tasmiṃ khaṇe bodhisatto nadītīraṃ gato tassa macchassa paridevitasaddaṃ sutvā kevaṭṭe upasaṅkamitvā taṃ macchaṃ mocesi. 
491191,111,1142,2,16,1,132,12,"Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā saccāni pakāsetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi, saccapariyosāne ukkaṇṭhitabhikkhu sotāpattiphale patiṭṭhahi ."
491192,111,1142,17,34,1,89,11,"‘‘ Tadā macchī purāṇadutiyikā ahosi, maccho ukkaṇṭhitabhikkhu, purohito pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
491193,111,1143,2,4,1,27,2,Macchajātakavaṇṇanā chaṭṭhā.
491194,111,1145,2,7,1,18,2,[ 217]7. Seggujātakavaṇṇanā 
491195,111,1146,2,13,1,80,10,Sabbo {loko}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ekaṃ paṇṇikaupāsakaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
491196,111,1146,14,17,1,33,3,Vatthu ekakanipāte vitthāritameva. 
491197,111,1146,18,33,1,56,9,"Idhāpi satthā taṃ‘‘ kiṃ, upāsaka, cirassaṃ āgatosī’’ ti pucchi. "
491198,111,1146,34,63,1,173,21,"Paṇṇikaupāsako‘‘ dhītā me, bhante, niccaṃ pahaṃsitamukhī, tamahaṃ vīmaṃsitvā ekassa kuladārakassa adāsiṃ, tattha itikattabbatāya tumhākaṃ dassanāya āgantuṃ okāsaṃ na labhin’’ ti āha. "
491199,111,1146,64,95,1,151,22,"Atha naṃ satthā‘‘ na kho, upāsaka, idānevesā sīlavatī, pubbepi sīlavatī, tvañca na idānevetaṃ vīmaṃsasi, pubbepi vīmaṃsiyevā’’ ti vatvā tena yācito atītaṃ āhari. "
491200,111,1147,2,10,1,74,8,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto rukkhadevatā ahosi. 
491201,111,1147,11,30,1,106,13,Tadā ayameva paṇṇikaupāsako‘‘ dhītaraṃ vīmaṃsissāmī’’ ti araññaṃ netvā kilesavasena icchanto viya hatthe gaṇhi. 
491202,111,1147,31,36,1,48,5,Atha naṃ paridevamānaṃ paṭhamagāthāya ajjhabhāsi– 
491203,111,1148,2,4,1,0,0,133.
491204,111,1149,2,12,1,53,8,"‘ ‘ Sabbo loko attamano ahosi, akovidā gāmadhammassa seggu; "
491205,111,1150,2,16,1,64,11,"Komāri ko nāma tavajja dhammo, yaṃ tvaṃ gahitā pavane parodasī’’ ti. "
491206,111,1151,2,17,1,92,12,"Tattha sabbo loko attamano {ahosī}ti, amma, sakalopi sattaloko etissā kāmasevanāya attamano jāto. "
491207,111,1151,18,26,1,49,6,Akovidā gāmadhammassa {seggū}ti {seggū}ti tassā nāmaṃ. 
491208,111,1151,27,43,1,103,13,"Tena tvaṃ pana, amma, seggu akovidā gāmadhammassa, imasmiṃ gāmadhamme vasaladhamme akusalāsīti vuttaṃ hoti. "
491209,111,1151,44,59,1,71,12,"Komāri ko nāma tavajja {dhammo}ti, amma, kumāri ko nāmesa tava ajja sabhāvo. "
491210,111,1151,60,87,1,166,23,"Yaṃ tvaṃ gahitā pavane {parodasī}ti tvaṃ mayā imasmiṃ pavane santhavavasena hatthe gahitā parodasi na sampaṭicchasi, ko esa tava sabhāvo, kiṃ kumārikāyeva tvanti pucchati. "
491211,111,1152,2,24,1,116,15,"Taṃ sutvā kumārikā‘‘ āma, tāta, kumārikāyevāhaṃ, nāhaṃ methunadhammaṃ nāma jānāmī’’ ti vatvā paridevamānā dutiyaṃ gāthamāha– "
491212,111,1153,2,4,1,0,0,134.
491213,111,1154,2,15,1,63,11,"‘ ‘ Yo dukkhaphuṭṭhāya bhaveyya tāṇaṃ, so me pitā dubbhi vane karoti; "
491214,111,1155,2,16,1,62,11,"Sā kassa kandāmi vanassa majjhe, yo tāyitā so sahasaṃ karotī’’ ti. "
491215,111,1156,2,5,1,21,3,Sā heṭṭhā kathitāyeva. 
491216,111,1156,6,18,1,88,12,Iti so paṇṇiko tadā dhītaraṃ vīmaṃsitvā gehaṃ netvā kuladārakassa datvā yathākammaṃ gato. 
491217,111,1157,2,15,1,129,12,"Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā saccāni pakāsetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi, saccapariyosāne paṇṇikaupāsako sotāpattiphale patiṭṭhahi."
491218,111,1157,16,36,1,108,14,"‘‘ Tadā dhītā dhītāyeva, pitā pitāyeva ahosi, tassa kāraṇassa paccakkhakārikā rukkhadevatā pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
491219,111,1158,2,4,1,26,2,Seggujātakavaṇṇanā sattamā.
491220,111,1160,2,7,1,23,2,[ 218]8. Kūṭavāṇijajātakavaṇṇanā 
491221,111,1161,2,15,1,89,11,Saṭhassa sāṭheyyamidan ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ekaṃ kūṭavāṇijaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
491222,111,1161,16,40,1,203,24,Sāvatthivāsino hi kūṭavāṇijo ca paṇḍitavāṇijo ca dve vāṇijā mittikā hutvā pañca sakaṭasatāni bhaṇḍassa pūrāpetvā pubbantato aparantaṃ vicaramānā vohāraṃ katvā bahuṃ lābhaṃ labhitvā sāvatthiṃ paccāgamiṃsu. 
491223,111,1161,41,44,1,29,3,Paṇḍitavāṇijo kūṭavāṇijaṃ āha–
491224,111,1161,45,54,1,24,4,"‘‘ samma, bhaṇḍaṃ bhājemā’’ ti. "
491225,111,1161,55,101,1,275,33,"Kūṭavāṇijo‘‘ ayaṃ dīgharattaṃ dukkhaseyyāya dubbhojanena kilanto attano ghare nānaggarasaṃ bhattaṃ bhuñjitvā ajīrakena marissati, atha sabbampetaṃ bhaṇḍaṃ mayhameva bhavissatī’’ ti cintetvā‘‘ nakkhattaṃ na manāpaṃ, divaso na manāpo, sve jānissāmi , punadivase jānissāmī’’ ti kālaṃ khepeti. "
491226,111,1161,102,117,1,129,15,Atha naṃ paṇḍitavāṇijo nippīḷetvā bhājāpetvā gandhamālaṃ ādāya satthu santikaṃ gantvā satthāraṃ pūjetvā vanditvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. 
491227,111,1161,118,155,1,161,23,"Satthā‘‘ kadā āgatosī’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ aḍḍhamāsamatto me, bhante, āgatassā’’ ti vatvā‘‘ atha kasmā evaṃ papañcaṃ katvā buddhupaṭṭhānaṃ āgatosī’’ ti puṭṭho taṃ pavattiṃ ārocesi. "
491228,111,1161,156,176,1,88,13,"Satthā‘‘ na kho, upāsaka, idāneva, pubbepesa kūṭavāṇijoyevā’’ ti vatvā tena yācito atītaṃ āhari. "
491229,111,1162,2,14,1,117,12,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto amaccakule nibbattitvā vayappatto tassa vinicchayāmacco ahosi. 
491230,111,1162,15,24,1,54,9,Tadā gāmavāsī ca nagaravāsī ca dve vāṇijā mittā ahesuṃ. 
491231,111,1162,25,31,1,56,6,Gāmavāsī nagaravāsissa santike pañca phālasatāni ṭhapesi. 
491232,111,1162,32,43,1,89,11,So te phāle vikkiṇitvā mūlaṃ gahetvā phālānaṃ ṭhapitaṭṭhāne mūsikavaccaṃ ākiritvā ṭhapesi. 
491233,111,1162,44,56,1,48,8,Aparabhāge gāmavāsī āgantvā‘‘ phāle me dehī’’ ti āha. 
491234,111,1162,57,69,1,60,8,Kūṭavāṇijo‘‘ phālā te mūsikāhi khāditā’’ ti mūsikavaccaṃ dassesi. 
491235,111,1162,70,111,1,231,31,"Itaro‘‘ khāditāva hontu, mūsikāhi khādite kiṃ sakkā kātun’’ ti nhānatthāya tassa puttaṃ ādāya gacchanto ekassa sahāyakassa gehe‘‘ imassa katthaci gantuṃ mā adatthā’’ ti vatvā antogabbhe nisīdāpetvā sayaṃ nhāyitvā kūṭavāṇijassa gehaṃ agamāsi. "
491236,111,1162,112,122,1,24,6,So‘‘ putto me kahan’’ ti āha.
491237,111,1162,123,154,1,189,25,"‘‘ Samma, tava puttaṃ tīre ṭhapetvā mama udake nimuggakāle eko kulalo āgantvā tava puttaṃ nakhapañjarena gahetvā ākāsaṃ pakkhanto, ahaṃ pāṇiṃ paharitvā viravitvā vāyamantopi mocetuṃ nāsakkhin’’ ti."
491238,111,1162,155,171,1,70,11,"‘‘ Tvaṃ musā bhaṇasi, kulalā dārake gahetvā gantuṃ samatthā nāma natthī’’ ti."
491239,111,1162,172,191,1,69,12,"‘‘ Samma, hotu, ayuttepi honte ahaṃ kiṃ karomi, kulaleneva te putto nīto’’ ti. "
491240,111,1162,192,211,1,102,13,"So taṃ santajjetvā‘‘ are duṭṭhacora manussamāraka , idāni taṃ vinicchayaṃ gantvā kaḍḍhāpessāmī’’ ti nikkhami. "
491241,111,1162,212,225,1,72,9,So‘‘ mama ruccanakameva karosī’’ ti teneva saddhiṃ vinicchayaṭṭhānaṃ agamāsi. 
491242,111,1163,2,5,1,26,3,Kūṭavāṇijo bodhisattaṃ āha–
491243,111,1163,6,39,1,114,20,"‘‘ ayaṃ, sāmi, mama puttaṃ gahetvā nhāyituṃ gato,‘ kahaṃ me putto’ ti vutte‘ kulalena haṭo’ ti āha, vinicchinatha me aḍḍan’’ ti. "
491244,111,1163,40,50,1,40,6,Bodhisatto‘‘ saccaṃ bhaṇe’’ ti itaraṃ pucchi. 
491245,111,1163,51,53,1,6,2,So āha–
491246,111,1163,54,73,1,65,11,"‘‘ āma, sāmi, ahaṃ taṃ ādāya gato, senena pahaṭabhāvo saccameva, sāmī’’ ti."
491247,111,1163,74,86,1,43,8,‘‘ Kiṃ pana loke kulalā nāma dārake harantī’’ ti?
491248,111,1163,87,94,1,26,4,"‘‘ Sāmi, ahampi tumhe pucchāmi–"
491249,111,1163,95,112,1,79,12,"‘‘ kulalā dārake gahetvā ākāse gantuṃ na sakkonti, mūsikā pana ayaphāle khādantī’’ ti."
491250,111,1163,113,121,1,16,4,‘‘ Idaṃ kiṃ nāmā’’ ti?
491251,111,1163,122,163,1,205,30,"‘‘ Sāmi, mayā etassa ghare pañca phālasatāni ṭhapitāni, svāyaṃ‘ phālā te mūsikāhi khāditā’ ti vatvā‘ idaṃ te phāle khāditamūsikānaṃ vaccan’ ti vaccaṃ dasseti, sāmi, mūsikā ce phāle khādanti, kulalāpi dārake harissanti. "
491252,111,1163,164,172,1,41,7,"Sace na khādanti, senāpi taṃ na harissanti. "
491253,111,1163,173,198,1,119,18,"Eso pana‘ phālā te mūsikāhi khāditā’ ti vadati, tesaṃ khāditabhāvaṃ vā akhāditabhāvaṃ vā jānātha, aḍḍaṃ me vinicchinathā’’ ti. "
491254,111,1163,199,225,1,130,18,Bodhisatto‘‘ saṭhassa paṭisāṭheyyaṃ katvā jinissāmīti iminā cintitaṃ bhavissatī’’ ti ñatvā‘‘ suṭṭhu te cintitan’’ ti vatvā imā gāthā avoca– 
