491256,111,1165,2,11,1,63,7,"‘ ‘ Saṭhassa sāṭheyyamiṃda sucintitaṃ, paccoḍḍitaṃ paṭikūṭassa kūṭaṃ; "
491257,111,1166,2,12,1,59,9,"Phālaṃ ce khādeyyuṃ mūsikā, kasmā kumāraṃ kulalā na hareyyuṃ. "
491258,111,1167,2,4,1,0,0,136.
491259,111,1168,2,13,1,55,9,"‘ ‘ Kūṭassa hi santi kūṭakūṭā, bhavati cāpi nikatino nikatyā; "
491260,111,1169,2,14,1,71,9,"Dehi puttanaṭṭha phālanaṭṭhassa phālaṃ, mā te puttamahāsi phālanaṭṭho’’ ti. "
491261,111,1170,2,19,1,101,12,Tattha {saṭhassā}ti saṭhabhāvena kerāṭikena‘‘ ekaṃ upāyaṃ katvā parasantakaṃ khādituṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti saṭhassa. 
491262,111,1170,20,29,1,78,9,Sāṭheyyamidaṃ sucintitan ti idaṃ paṭisāṭheyyaṃ cintentena tayā suṭṭhu cintitaṃ. 
491263,111,1170,30,46,1,133,15,"Paccoḍḍitaṃ paṭikūṭassa kūṭan ti kūṭassa puggalassa tayā paṭikūṭaṃ suṭṭhu paccoḍḍitaṃ, paṭibhāgaṃ katvā oḍḍitasadisameva katanti attho. "
491264,111,1170,47,56,1,57,8,Phālaṃ ce khādeyyuṃ {mūsikā}ti yadi mūsikā phālaṃ khādeyyuṃ. 
491265,111,1170,57,72,1,99,15,Kasmā kumāraṃ kulalā na hareyyun ti mūsikāsu phāle khādantīsu kulalā kiṃ kāraṇā kumāraṃ no hareyyuṃ. 
491266,111,1171,2,43,1,223,31,"Kūṭassa hi santi {kūṭakūṭā}ti tvaṃ‘‘ ahameva mūsikāhi phāle khādāpitapuriso kūṭo’’ ti maññasi, tādisassa pana kūṭassa imasmiṃ loke bahū kūṭā santi, kūṭassa kūṭāti kūṭapaṭikūṭānaṃ etaṃ nāmaṃ, kūṭassa paṭikūṭā nāma santīti vuttaṃ hoti. "
491267,111,1171,44,57,1,127,12,Bhavati cāpi nikatino {nikatyā}ti nikatino nekatikassa vañcanakapuggalassa nikatyā aparo nikatikārako vañcanakapuriso bhavatiyeva. 
491268,111,1171,58,71,1,100,12,"Dehi puttanaṭṭha phālanaṭṭhassa phālan ti ambho naṭṭhaputta purisa, etassa naṭṭhaphālassa phālaṃ dehi. "
491269,111,1171,72,95,1,119,19,"Mā te puttamahāsi {phālanaṭṭho}ti sace hissa phālaṃ na dassasi, puttaṃ te harissati, taṃ te esa mā haratu, phālamassa dehīti."
491270,111,1171,96,109,1,32,7,"‘‘ Demi, sāmi, sace me puttaṃ detī’’ ti."
