491319,111,1192,2,7,1,24,2,[ 220]10. Dhammadhajajātakavaṇṇanā 
491320,111,1193,2,14,1,102,11,Sukhaṃ {jīvitarūposī}ti idaṃ satthā veḷuvane viharanto devadattassa vadhāya parisakkanaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
491321,111,1193,15,42,1,140,19,"Tadā hi satthā‘‘ na, bhikkhave, idāneva, pubbepi devadatto mayhaṃ vadhāya parisakkiyeva, santāsamattampi pana kātuṃ nāsakkhī’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
491322,111,1194,2,15,1,80,11,"Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ yasapāṇi nāma rājā rajjaṃ kāresi, kāḷako nāmassa senāpati ahosi. "
491323,111,1194,16,30,1,111,13,"Tadā bodhisatto tasseva purohito ahosi nāmena dhammadhajo nāma, rañño pana sīsappasādhanakappako chattapāṇi nāma. "
491324,111,1194,31,49,1,135,16,"Rājā dhammena rajjaṃ kāreti, senāpati panassa vinicchayaṃ karonto lañjaṃ khādati parapiṭṭhimaṃsiko, lañjaṃ gahetvā assāmike sāmike karoti. "
491325,111,1194,50,91,1,309,34,"Athekadivasaṃ vinicchaye parājito manusso bāhā paggayha kandanto vinicchayā nikkhanto rājupaṭṭhānaṃ gacchantaṃ bodhisattaṃ disvā tassa pādesu patitvā‘‘ tumhādisesu nāma, sāmi, rañño atthañca dhammañca anusāsantesu kāḷakasenāpati lañjaṃ gahetvā assāmike sāmike karotī’’ ti attano parājitabhāvaṃ bodhisattassa kathesi. "
491326,111,1194,92,111,1,105,13,"Bodhisatto kāruññaṃ uppādetvā ‘‘ ehi bhaṇe, aḍḍaṃ te vinicchinissāmī’’ ti taṃ gahetvā vinicchayaṭṭhānaṃ agamāsi. "
491327,111,1194,112,122,1,83,9,"Mahājano sannipati, bodhisatto taṃ aḍḍaṃ paṭivinicchinitvā sāmikaññeva sāmikaṃ akāsi. "
491328,111,1195,2,10,1,45,7,"Mahājano sādhukāraṃ adāsi, so saddo mahā ahosi. "
491329,111,1195,11,23,1,41,8,Rājā taṃ sutvā‘‘ kiṃ saddo nāmeso’’ ti pucchi.
491330,111,1195,24,38,1,83,8,"‘‘ Deva, dhammadhajapaṇḍitena dubbinicchito aḍḍo suvinicchito, tatresa sādhukārasaddo’’ ti. "
491331,111,1195,39,54,1,78,11,Rājā tuṭṭho bodhisattaṃ pakkosāpetvā‘‘ aḍḍo kira te ācariya vinicchito’’ ti pucchi.
491332,111,1195,55,100,1,249,30,"‘‘ Āma, mahārāja, kāḷakena dubbinicchitaṃ aḍḍaṃ vinicchinin’’ ti vutte‘‘ ito dāni paṭṭhāya tumheva aḍḍaṃ vinicchinatha, mayhañca kaṇṇasukhaṃ bhavissati lokassa ca vuḍḍhī’’ ti vatvā anicchantampi taṃ‘‘ sattānuddayāya vinicchaye nisīdathā’’ ti yācitvā sampaṭicchāpesi. "
491333,111,1195,101,110,1,69,8,"Tato paṭṭhāya bodhisatto vinicchaye nisīdati, sāmikeyeva sāmike karoti. "
491334,111,1196,2,27,1,177,20,"Kāḷako tato paṭṭhāya lañjaṃ alabhanto lābhato parihāyitvā bodhisattassa āghātaṃ bandhitvā‘‘ mahārāja, dhammadhajapaṇḍito tava rajjaṃ patthetī’’ ti bodhisattaṃ rañño antare paribhindi. "
491335,111,1196,28,51,1,115,16,"Rājā asaddahanto‘‘ mā evaṃ avacā’’ ti paṭikkhipitvā puna tena‘‘ sace me na saddahatha, tassāgamanakāle vātapānena oloketha. "
491336,111,1196,52,85,1,172,22,Athānena sakalanagarassa attano hatthe katabhāvaṃ passissathā’’ ti vutte rājā tassa aḍḍakārakaparisaṃ disvā‘‘ etasseva parisā’’ ti saññāya bhijjitvā‘‘ kiṃ karoma senāpatī’’ ti pucchi.
491337,111,1196,86,97,1,28,5,"‘‘ Deva, etaṃ māretuṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti ."
491338,111,1196,98,107,1,42,5,‘‘ Oḷārikadosaṃ apassantā kathaṃ māressāmā’’ ti?
491339,111,1196,108,115,1,16,3,‘‘ Attheko upāyo’’ ti.
491340,111,1196,116,122,1,13,2,‘‘ Katarūpāyo’’ ti.
491341,111,1196,123,138,1,77,11,‘‘ Asayhamassa kammaṃ āropetvā taṃ kātuṃ asakkontaṃ taṃ tena dosena māressāmā’’ ti.
491342,111,1196,139,147,1,24,4,‘‘ Kiṃ pana asayhakamman’’ ti?
491343,111,1196,148,162,1,97,11,"‘‘ Mahārāja, uyyānaṃ nāma sārabhūmiyaṃ ropitaṃ paṭijaggiyamānaṃ tīhi catūhi saṃvaccharehi phalaṃ deti. "
491344,111,1196,163,182,1,99,15,"Tumhe taṃ pakkosāpetvā‘ sve uyyānaṃ kīḷissāma, uyyānaṃ me māpehī’ ti vadatha, so māpetuṃ na sakkhissati. "
