491506,111,1253,2,7,1,19,2,[ 221]1. Kāsāvajātakavaṇṇanā 
491507,111,1254,2,13,1,79,10,Anikkasāvo kāsāvan ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto devadattaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
491508,111,1254,14,18,1,32,4,Vatthu pana rājagahe samuṭṭhitaṃ. 
491509,111,1254,19,27,1,77,8,Ekasmiṃ samaye dhammasenāpati pañcahi bhikkhusatehi saddhiṃ veḷuvane viharati. 
491510,111,1254,28,35,1,71,7,Devadattopi attano anurūpāya dussīlaparisāya parivuto gayāsīse viharati. 
491511,111,1254,36,43,1,67,7,Tasmiṃ samaye rājagahavāsino chandakaṃ saṅgharitvā dānaṃ sajjayiṃsu. 
491512,111,1254,44,61,1,112,13,Atheko vohāratthāya āgatavāṇijo imaṃ sāṭakaṃ vissajjetvā‘‘ mampi pattikaṃ karothā’’ ti mahagghaṃ gandhakāsāvaṃ adāsi. 
491513,111,1254,62,71,1,82,8,"Nāgarā mahādānaṃ pavattayiṃsu, sabbaṃ chandakena saṅkaḍḍhitaṃ kahāpaṇeheva niṭṭhāsi. "
491514,111,1254,72,76,1,23,4,So sāṭako atireko ahosi. 
491515,111,1254,77,84,1,53,5,Mahājano sannipatitvā‘‘ ayaṃ gandhakāsāvasāṭako atireko. 
491516,111,1254,85,98,1,70,9,"Kassa naṃ dema, kiṃ sāriputtattherassa, udāhu devadattassā’’ ti mantayiṃsu. "
491517,111,1255,2,10,1,37,4,Tattheke ‘‘ sāriputtattherassā’’ ti āhaṃsu. 
491518,111,1255,11,41,1,205,21,"Apare‘‘ sāriputtatthero katipāhaṃ vasitvā yathāruci pakkamissati , devadattatthero pana nibaddhaṃ amhākaṃ nagarameva upanissāya viharati, maṅgalāmaṅgalesu ayameva amhākaṃ avassayo, devadattassa dassāmā’’ ti āhaṃsu. "
491519,111,1255,42,59,1,101,12,"Sambahulikaṃ karontesupi‘‘ devadattassa dassāmā’’ ti vattāro bahutarā ahesuṃ, atha naṃ devadattassa adaṃsu. "
491520,111,1255,60,70,1,95,10,Devadatto tassa dasā chindāpetvā ovaṭṭikaṃ sibbāpetvā rajāpetvā suvaṇṇapaṭṭavaṇṇaṃ katvā pārupi. 
491521,111,1255,71,99,1,192,22,"Tasmiṃ kāle tiṃsamattā bhikkhū rājagahā nikkhamitvā sāvatthiṃ gantvā satthāraṃ vanditvā katapaṭisanthārā taṃ pavattiṃ ārocetvā‘‘ evaṃ, bhante, attano ananucchavikaṃ arahaddhajaṃ pārupī’’ ti ārocesuṃ. "
491522,111,1255,100,122,1,122,15,"Satthā‘‘ na, bhikkhave, devadatto idāneva attano ananurūpaṃ arahaddhajaṃ paridahati, pubbepi paridahiyevā’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
491523,111,1256,2,17,1,173,15,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto himavantapadese hatthikule nibbattitvā vayappatto asītisahassamattavāraṇaparivāro yūthapati hutvā araññāyatane vasati. 
