491557,111,1271,2,13,1,79,9,Idaṃ {tadācariyavaco}ti idaṃ satthā veḷuvane viharanto devadattaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
491558,111,1271,14,19,1,56,5,Ekadivasañhi bhikkhū dhammasabhāyaṃ kathaṃ samuṭṭhāpesuṃ–
491559,111,1271,20,45,1,163,17,"‘‘ āvuso, devadatto nāma kakkhaḷo pharuso sāhasiko sammāsambuddhe abhimāre payojesi, silaṃ pavijjhi, nāḷāgiriṃ payojesi, khantimettānuddayamattampissa tathāgate natthī’’ ti. "
491560,111,1271,46,89,1,190,26,"Satthā āgantvā‘‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ imāya nāmā’’ ti vutte‘‘ na, bhikkhave, idāneva, pubbepi devadatto kakkhaḷo pharuso nikkāruṇikoyevā’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
491561,111,1272,2,18,1,142,15,"Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto himavantapadese mahānandiyo nāma vānaro ahosi, kaniṭṭhabhātiko panassa cūḷanandiyo nāma. "
491562,111,1272,19,27,1,93,8,Te ubhopi asītisahassavānaraparivārā himavantapadese andhamātaraṃ paṭijaggantā vāsaṃ kappesuṃ. 
491563,111,1272,28,38,1,87,10,Te mātaraṃ sayanagumbe ṭhapetvā araññaṃ pavisitvā madhurāni phalāphalāni mātuyā pesenti. 
491564,111,1272,39,50,1,73,9,"Āharaṇakavānarā tassā na denti, sā khudāpīḷitā aṭṭhicammāvasesā kisā ahosi. "
491565,111,1272,51,55,1,23,4,Atha naṃ bodhisatto āha–
491566,111,1272,56,72,1,71,9,"‘‘ mayaṃ, amma, tumhākaṃ madhuraphalāphalāni pesema, tumhe kasmā milāyathā’’ ti."
491567,111,1272,73,82,1,21,4,"‘‘ Tāta, nāhaṃ labhāmī’’ ti. "
491568,111,1272,83,86,1,18,2,Bodhisatto cintesi –
491569,111,1272,87,103,1,86,11,"‘‘ mayi yūthaṃ pariharante mātā me nassissati, yūthaṃ pahāya mātaraṃyeva paṭijaggissāmī’’ ti. "
491570,111,1272,104,122,1,87,12,"So cūḷanandiyaṃ pakkositvā‘‘ tāta, tvaṃ yūthaṃ parihara, ahaṃ mātaraṃ paṭijaggissāmī’’ ti āha. "
491571,111,1272,123,141,1,95,12,"Sopi naṃ‘‘ bhātika, mayhaṃ yūthapariharaṇena kammaṃ natthi, ahampi mātarameva paṭijaggissāmī’’ ti āha. "
491572,111,1272,142,159,1,137,17,Iti te ubhopi ekacchandā hutvā yūthaṃ pahāya mātaraṃ gahetvā himavantā oruyha paccante nigrodharukkhe vāsaṃ kappetvā mātaraṃ paṭijaggiṃsu. 
491573,111,1273,2,19,1,136,13,Atheko bārāṇasivāsī brāhmaṇamāṇavo takkasilāyaṃ disāpāmokkhassa ācariyassa santike sabbasippāni uggaṇhitvā‘‘ gamissāmī’’ ti ācariyaṃ āpucchi. 
491574,111,1273,20,59,1,267,29,"Ācariyo aṅgavijjānubhāvena tassa kakkhaḷapharusasāhasikabhāvaṃ ñatvā‘‘ tāta, tvaṃ kakkhaḷo pharuso sāhasiko, evarūpānaṃ na sabbakālaṃ ekasadisameva ijjhati, mahāvināsaṃ mahādukkhaṃ pāpuṇissasi, mā tvaṃ kakkhaḷo hohi, pacchānutāpanakāraṇaṃ kammaṃ mā karī’’ ti ovaditvā uyyojesi. "
491575,111,1273,60,97,1,300,32,"So ācariyaṃ vanditvā bārāṇasiṃ gantvā gharāvāsaṃ gahetvā aññehi sippehi jīvikaṃ kappetuṃ asakkonto‘‘ dhanukoṭiṃ nissāya jīvissāmi, luddakammaṃ katvā jīvikaṃ kappessāmī’’ ti bārāṇasito nikkhamitvā paccantagāmake vasanto dhanukalāpasannaddho araññaṃ pavisitvā nānāmige māretvā maṃsavikkayena jīvikaṃ kappesi. "
491576,111,1273,98,119,1,153,17,So ekadivasaṃ araññe kiñci alabhitvā āgacchanto aṅgaṇapariyante ṭhitaṃ nigrodharukkhaṃ disvā‘‘ api nāmettha kiñci bhaveyyā’’ ti nigrodharukkhābhimukho pāyāsi. 
491577,111,1274,2,28,1,165,22,Tasmiṃ khaṇe ubhopi te bhātaro mātaraṃ phalāni khādāpetvā purato katvā viṭapabbhantare nisinnā taṃ āgacchantaṃ disvā‘‘ kiṃ no mātaraṃ karissatī’’ ti sākhantare nilīyiṃsu. 
491578,111,1274,29,41,1,95,12,Sopi kho sāhasikapuriso rukkhamūlaṃ āgantvā taṃ tesaṃ mātaraṃ jarādubbalaṃ andhaṃ disvā cintesi–
491579,111,1274,42,55,1,72,9,‘‘ kiṃ me tucchahatthagamanena imaṃ makkaṭiṃ vijjhitvā gahetvā gamissāmī’’ ti. 
491580,111,1274,56,62,1,36,5,So tassā vijjhanatthāya dhanuṃ gaṇhi. 
491581,111,1274,63,123,1,337,45,"Taṃ disvā bodhisatto‘‘ tāta cūḷanandiya, eso me puriso mātaraṃ vijjhitukāmo, ahamassā jīvitadānaṃ dassāmi, tvaṃ mamaccayena mātaraṃ paṭijaggeyyāsī’’ ti vatvā sākhantarā nikkhamitvā‘‘ bho purisa, mā me mātaraṃ vijjhi, esā andhā jarādubbalā, ahamassā jīvitadānaṃ demi, tvaṃ etaṃ amāretvā maṃ mārehī’’ ti tassa paṭiññaṃ gahetvā sarassa āsannaṭṭhāne nisīdi. "
491582,111,1274,124,135,1,86,10,So nikkaruṇo bodhisattaṃ vijjhitvā pātetvā mātarampissa vijjhituṃ puna dhanuṃ sannayhi. 
491583,111,1274,136,196,1,348,47,"Taṃ disvā cūḷanandiyo‘‘ ayaṃ me mātaraṃ vijjhitukāmo, ekadivasampi kho me mātā jīvamānā laddhajīvitāyeva nāma hoti, jīvitadānamassā dassāmī’’ ti sākhantarā nikkhamitvā‘‘ bho purisa, mā me mātaraṃ vijjhi, ahamassā jīvitadānaṃ dammi, tvaṃ maṃ vijjhitvā amhe dve bhātike gahetvā amhākaṃ mātu jīvitadānaṃ dehī’’ ti tassa paṭiññaṃ gahetvā sarassa āsannaṭṭhāne nisīdi. "
491584,111,1274,197,219,1,141,18,So tampi vijjhitvā pātetvā‘‘ ayaṃ makkaṭī ghare dārakānaṃ bhavissatī’’ ti mātarampi tesaṃ vijjhitvā pātetvā tayopi kājenādāya gehābhimukho pāyāsi. 
491585,111,1275,2,17,1,122,14,"Athassa pāpapurisassa gehe asani patitvā bhariyañca dve dārake ca geheneva saddhiṃ jhāpesi, piṭṭhivaṃsathūṇamattaṃ avasissi. "
491586,111,1275,18,27,1,63,9,Athassa naṃ gāmadvāreyeva eko puriso disvā taṃ pavattiṃ ārocesi. 
491587,111,1275,28,46,1,146,17,So puttadārasokena abhibhūto tasmiṃyeva ṭhāne maṃsakājañja dhanuñca chaḍḍetvā vatthaṃ pahāya naggo bāhā paggayha paridevamāno gantvā gharaṃ pāvisi. 
491588,111,1275,47,63,1,95,14,"Athassa sā thūṇā bhijjitvā sīse patitvā sīsaṃ bhindi, pathavī vivaraṃ adāsi, avīcito jālā uṭṭhahi. "
491589,111,1275,64,86,1,147,17,So pathaviyā giliyamāno ācariyassa ovādaṃ saritvā‘‘ imaṃ vata kāraṇaṃ disvā pārāsariyabrāhmaṇo mayhaṃ ovādamadāsī’’ ti paridevamāno imaṃ gāthādvayamāha– 
491590,111,1276,2,4,1,0,0,143.
491591,111,1277,2,9,1,40,5,"‘ ‘ Idaṃ tadācariyavaco, pārāsariyo yadabravi; "
491592,111,1278,2,12,1,48,9,"Māsu tvaṃ akari pāpaṃ, yaṃ tvaṃ pacchā kataṃ tape. "
491593,111,1279,2,4,1,0,0,144.
491594,111,1280,2,11,1,38,7,"‘ ‘ Yāni karoti puriso, tāni attani passati; "
491595,111,1281,2,8,1,40,5,"Kalyāṇakārī kalyāṇaṃ, pāpakārī ca pāpakaṃ; "
491596,111,1282,2,12,1,45,7,"Yādisaṃ vapate bījaṃ, tādisaṃ harate phalan’’ ti. "
491597,111,1283,2,8,1,40,5,Tassattho – yaṃ pārāsariyo brāhmaṇo abravi–
491598,111,1283,9,29,1,86,14,"‘‘ māsu tvaṃ pāpaṃ akarī, yaṃ kataṃ pacchā tvaññeva tapeyyā’’ ti, idaṃ taṃ ācariyassa vacanaṃ. "
491599,111,1283,30,42,1,97,11,"Yāni kāyavacīmanodvārehi kammāni puriso karoti, tesaṃ vipākaṃ paṭilabhanto tāniyeva attani passati. "
491600,111,1283,43,54,1,100,10,"Kalyāṇakammakārī kalyāṇaṃ phalamanubhoti, pāpakārī ca pāpakameva hīnaṃ lāmakaṃ aniṭṭhaphalaṃ anubhoti. "
491601,111,1283,55,71,1,122,14,"Lokasmimpi hi yādisaṃ vapate bījaṃ, tādisaṃ harate phalaṃ, bījānurūpaṃ bījānucchavikameva phalaṃ harati gaṇhāti anubhavatīti. "
491602,111,1283,72,79,1,62,7,Iti so paridevanto pathaviṃ pavisitvā avīcimahāniraye nibbatti. 
491603,111,1284,2,26,1,135,16,"Satthā ‘‘ na, bhikkhave, devadatto idāneva, pubbepi kakkhaḷo pharuso nikkāruṇikoyevā’’ ti vatvā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–"
491604,111,1284,27,51,1,143,16,"‘‘ tadā luddakapuriso devadatto ahosi, disāpāmokkho ācariyo sāriputto, cūḷanandiyo ānando, mātā mahāpajāpatigotamī, mahānandiyo pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
491605,111,1285,2,4,1,31,2,Cūḷanandiyajātakavaṇṇanā dutiyā.
491606,111,1287,2,7,1,23,2,[ 223]3. Puṭabhattajātakavaṇṇanā 
491607,111,1288,2,16,1,97,13,Name namantassa bhaje bhajantan ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ekaṃ kuṭumbikaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
491608,111,1288,17,25,1,83,8,Sāvatthinagaravāsī kireko kuṭumbiko ekena janapadakuṭumbikena saddhiṃ vohāraṃ akāsi. 
491609,111,1288,26,35,1,60,8,So attano bhariyaṃ ādāya tassa dhāraṇakassa santikaṃ agamāsi. 
491610,111,1288,36,54,1,90,13,"Dhāraṇako‘‘ dātuṃ na sakkomī’’ ti na kiñci adāsi, itaro kujjhitvā bhattaṃ abhuñjitvāva nikkhami. "
491611,111,1288,55,72,1,111,13,Atha naṃ antarāmagge chātajjhattaṃ disvā maggapaṭipannā purisā‘‘ bhariyāyapi datvā bhuñjāhī’’ ti bhattapuṭaṃ adaṃsu. 
491612,111,1288,73,110,1,195,26,"So taṃ gahetvā tassā adātukāmo hutvā‘‘ bhadde, idaṃ corānaṃ tiṭṭhanaṭṭhānaṃ, tvaṃ purato yāhī’’ ti uyyojetvā sabbaṃ bhattaṃ bhuñjitvā tucchapuṭaṃ dassetvā‘‘ bhadde, abhattakaṃ tucchapuṭameva adaṃsū’’ ti āha. "
491613,111,1288,111,118,1,58,7,Sā tena ekakeneva bhuttabhāvaṃ ñatvā domanassappattā ahosi. 
491614,111,1288,119,132,1,83,9,Te ubhopi jetavanapiṭṭhivihārena gacchantā‘‘ pānīyaṃ pivissāmā’’ ti jetavanaṃ pavisiṃsu. 
491615,111,1289,2,19,1,146,16,"Satthāpi tesaññeva āgamanaṃ olokento maggaṃ gahetvā ṭhitaluddako viya gandhakuṭichāyāya nisīdi, te satthāraṃ disvā upasaṅkamitvā vanditvā nisīdiṃsu. "
491616,111,1289,20,40,1,93,14,"Satthā tehi saddhiṃ paṭisanthāraṃ katvā‘‘ kiṃ, upāsike, ayaṃ te bhattā hitakāmo sasneho’’ ti pucchi."
491617,111,1289,41,69,1,150,20,"‘‘ Bhante, ahaṃ etassa sasnehā, ayaṃ pana mayhaṃ nisneho, tiṭṭhantu aññepi divasā, ajjevesa antarāmagge puṭabhattaṃ labhitvā mayhaṃ adatvā attanāva bhuñjī’’ ti."
491618,111,1289,70,83,1,69,9,"‘‘ Upāsike, niccakālampi tvaṃ etassa hitakāmā sasnehā, ayaṃ pana nisnehova. "
491619,111,1289,84,104,1,108,17,"Yadā pana paṇḍite nissāya tava guṇe jānāti, tadā te sabbissariyaṃ niyyādetī’’ ti vatvā tāya yācito atītaṃ āhari. "
491620,111,1290,2,15,1,121,12,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto amaccakule nibbattitvā vayappatto tassa atthadhammānusāsako ahosi. 
491621,111,1290,16,30,1,65,10,Atha rājā‘‘ padubbheyyāpi me ayan’’ ti attano puttaṃ āsaṅkanto nīhari. 
491622,111,1290,31,41,1,78,10,So attano bhariyaṃ gahetvā nagarā nikkhamma ekasmiṃ kāsikagāmake vāsaṃ kappesi. 
491623,111,1290,42,74,1,194,23,So aparabhāge pitu kālakatabhāvaṃ sutvā‘‘ kulasantakaṃ rajjaṃ gaṇhissāmī’’ ti bārāṇasiṃ paccāgacchanto antarāmagge‘‘ bhariyāyapi datvā bhuñjāhī’’ ti bhattapuṭaṃ labhitvā tassā adatvā sayameva taṃ bhuñji. 
491624,111,1290,75,87,1,51,7,Sā‘‘ kakkhaḷo vatāyaṃ puriso’’ ti domanassappattā ahosi. 
491625,111,1290,88,121,1,160,24,"So bārāṇasiyaṃ rajjaṃ gahetvā taṃ aggamahesiṭṭhāne ṭhapetvā‘‘ ettakameva etissā alan’’ ti na aññaṃ sakkāraṃ vā sammānaṃ vā karoti,‘‘ kathaṃ yāpesī’’ tipi naṃ na pucchati. "
491626,111,1291,2,4,1,18,2,Bodhisatto cintesi–
491627,111,1291,5,65,1,305,42,"‘‘ ayaṃ devī rañño bahūpakārā sasnehā, rājā panetaṃ kismiñci na maññati, sakkārasammānamassā kāressāmī’’ ti taṃ upasaṅkamitvā upacāraṃ katvā ekamantaṃ ṭhatvā‘‘ kiṃ, tātā’’ ti vutte‘‘ kathaṃ samuṭṭhāpetuṃ mayaṃ, devi, tumhe upaṭṭhahāma, kiṃ nāma mahallakānaṃ pitūnaṃ vatthakhaṇḍaṃ vā bhattapiṇḍaṃ vā dātuṃ na vaṭṭatī’’ ti āha."
491628,111,1291,66,91,1,113,19,"‘‘ Tāta, ahaṃ attanāva kiñci na labhāmi, tumhākaṃ kiṃ dassāmi, nanu labhanakāle adāsiṃ, idāni pana me rājā na kiñci deti. "
491629,111,1291,92,110,1,124,15,"Tiṭṭhatu aññaṃ dānaṃ, rajjaṃ gaṇhituṃ āgacchanto antarāmagge bhattapuṭaṃ labhitvā bhattamattampi me adatvā attanāva bhuñjī’’ ti."
491630,111,1291,111,126,1,57,9,"‘‘ Kiṃ pana, amma, rañño santike evaṃ kathetuṃ sakkhissathā’’ ti?"
491631,111,1291,127,135,1,19,3,"‘‘ Sakkhissāmi, tātā’’ ti."
491632,111,1291,136,164,1,166,24,‘‘ Tena hi ajjeva mama rañño santike ṭhitakāle mayi pucchante evaṃ kathetha ajjeva vo guṇaṃ jānāpessāmī’’ ti evaṃ vatvā bodhisatto purimataraṃ gantvā rañño santike aṭṭhāsi. 
491633,111,1291,165,170,1,32,5,Sāpi gantvā rañño samīpe aṭṭhāsi. 
491634,111,1292,2,27,1,126,19,"Atha naṃ bodhisatto‘‘ amma, tumhe ativiya kakkhaḷā, kiṃ nāma pitūnaṃ vatthakhaṇḍaṃ vā bhattapiṇḍamattaṃ vā dātuṃ na vaṭṭatī’’ ti āha."
491635,111,1292,28,45,1,67,11,"‘‘ Tāta, ahameva rañño santikā kiñci na labhāmi, tumhākaṃ kiṃ dassāmī’’ ti?"
491636,111,1292,46,55,1,36,5,‘‘ Nanu aggamahesiṭṭhānaṃ te laddhan’’ ti?
491637,111,1292,56,87,1,167,23,"‘‘ Tāta, kismiñci sammāne asati aggamahesiṭṭhānaṃ kiṃ karissati, idāni me tumhākaṃ rājā kiṃ dassati, so antarāmagge bhattapuṭaṃ labhitvā tato kiñci adatvā sayameva bhuñjī’’ ti. "
491638,111,1292,88,99,1,39,6,"Bodhisatto‘‘ evaṃ kira, mahārājā’’ ti pucchi. "
491639,111,1292,100,102,1,15,2,Rājā adhivāsesi. 
491640,111,1292,103,121,1,102,14,"Bodhisatto tassa adhivāsanaṃ viditvā‘‘ tena hi, amma, rañño appiyakālato paṭṭhāya kiṃ tumhākaṃ idha vāsena. "
491641,111,1292,122,158,1,223,28,"Lokasmiñhi appiyasampayogo ca dukkho, tumhākaṃ idha vāse sati rañño appiyasampayogova dukkhaṃ bhavissati, ime sattā nāma bhajante bhajanti, abhajanabhāvaṃ ñatvā aññattha gantabbaṃ, mahanto lokasannivāso’’ ti vatvā imā gāthā avoca– "
491642,111,1293,2,4,1,0,0,145.
491643,111,1294,2,12,1,62,8,"‘ ‘ Name namantassa bhaje bhajantaṃ, kiccānukubbassa kareyya kiccaṃ; "
491644,111,1295,2,9,1,61,6,"Nānatthakāmassa kareyya atthaṃ, asambhajantampi na sambhajeyya. "
491645,111,1296,2,4,1,0,0,146.
491646,111,1297,2,13,1,60,9,"‘ ‘ Caje cajantaṃ vanathaṃ na kayirā, apetacittena na sambhajeyya; "
491647,111,1298,2,15,1,64,10,"Dijo dumaṃ khīṇaphalanti ñatvā, aññaṃ samekkheyya mahā hi loko’’ ti. "
491648,111,1299,2,14,1,78,11,"Tattha name namantassa bhaje bhajantan ti yo attano namati, tasseva paṭinameyya. "
491649,111,1299,15,21,1,29,5,"Yo ca bhajati, tameva bhajeyya. "
491650,111,1299,22,32,1,105,10,Kiccānukubbassa kareyya kiccan ti attano uppannakiccaṃ anukubbantasseva tassapi uppannakiccaṃ paṭikareyya. 
491651,111,1299,33,48,1,103,13,"Caje cajantaṃ vanathaṃ na {kayirā}ti attānaṃ jahantaṃ jaheyyeva, tasmiṃ taṇhāsaṅkhātaṃ vanathaṃ na kareyya. "
491652,111,1299,49,53,1,47,3,{Apetacittenā}ti vigatacittena vipallatthacittena. 
491653,111,1299,54,61,1,53,6,Na {sambhajeyyā}ti tathārūpena saddhiṃ na samāgaccheyya. 
491654,111,1299,62,89,1,153,22,"Dijo duman ti yathā sakuṇo pubbe phalitampi rukkhaṃ phale khīṇe‘‘ khīṇaphalo ayan’’ ti ñatvā taṃ chaḍḍetvā aññaṃ samekkhati pariyesati, evaṃ aññaṃ samekkheyya. "
491655,111,1299,90,101,1,63,10,"Mahā hi esa loko, atha tumhe sasnehaṃ ekaṃ purisaṃ labhissathāti. "
491656,111,1300,2,8,1,49,6,Taṃ sutvā bārāṇasirājā deviyā sabbissariyaṃ adāsi. 
491657,111,1300,9,14,1,41,5,Tato paṭṭhāya samaggā sammodamānā vasiṃsu. 
491658,111,1301,2,17,1,133,13,"Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā saccāni pakāsetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi, saccapariyosāne dve jayampatikā sotāpattiphale patiṭṭhahiṃsu."
491659,111,1301,18,34,1,79,11,"‘‘ Tadā jayampatikā ime dve jayampatikā ahesuṃ, paṇḍitāmacco pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
