491661,111,1304,2,7,1,21,2,[ 224]4. Kumbhilajātakavaṇṇanā 
491662,111,1305,2,15,1,81,10,Yassete caturo {dhammā}ti idaṃ satthā veḷuvane viharanto devadattaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
491663,111,1306,2,4,1,0,0,147.
491664,111,1307,2,11,1,42,7,"‘ ‘ Yassete caturo dhammā, vānarinda yathā tava; "
491665,111,1308,2,10,1,46,7,"Saccaṃ dhammo dhiti cāgo, diṭṭhaṃ so ativattati. "
491666,111,1309,2,4,1,0,0,148.
491667,111,1310,2,11,1,42,7,"‘ ‘ Yassa cete na vijjanti, guṇā paramabhaddakā; "
491668,111,1311,2,13,1,50,8,"Saccaṃ dhammo dhiti cāgo, diṭṭhaṃ so nātivattatī’’ ti. "
491669,111,1312,2,21,1,141,17,"Tattha guṇā {paramabhaddakā}ti yassa ete paramabhaddakā cattāro rāsaṭṭhena piṇḍaṭṭhena guṇā na vijjanti, so paccāmittaṃ atikkamituṃ na sakkotīti. "
491670,111,1312,22,29,1,75,7,Sesamettha sabbaṃ heṭṭhā kumbhilajātake vuttanayameva saddhiṃ samodhānenāti. 
491671,111,1313,2,4,1,30,2,Kumbhilajātakavaṇṇanā catutthā.
491672,111,1315,2,7,1,24,2,[ 225]5. Khantivaṇṇajātakavaṇṇanā 
491673,111,1316,2,15,1,83,11,"Atthi me puriso, {devā}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto kosalarājānaṃ ārabbha kathesi. "
491674,111,1316,16,22,1,47,6,Tassa kireko bahūpakāro amacco antepure padussi. 
491675,111,1316,23,35,1,55,8,Rājā‘‘ upakārako me’’ ti ñatvāpi adhivāsetvā satthu ārocesi. 
491676,111,1316,36,53,1,87,11,"Satthā‘‘ porāṇakarājānopi, mahārāja, evaṃ adhivāsesuṃyevā’’ ti vatvā tena yācito atītaṃ āhari. "
491677,111,1317,2,18,1,116,15,"Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente eko amacco tassa antepure padussi, amaccassāpi sevako tassa gehe padussi. "
491678,111,1317,19,54,1,190,27,"So tassa aparādhaṃ adhivāsetuṃ asakkonto taṃ ādāya rañño santikaṃ gantvā‘‘ deva, eko me upaṭṭhāko sabbakiccakārako , so mayhaṃ gehe padussi, tassa kiṃ kātuṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti pucchanto paṭhamaṃ gāthamāha– "
