491682,111,1321,2,14,1,68,9,Tattha tassa {cekoparādhatthī}ti tassa ca purisassa eko aparādho atthi. 
491683,111,1321,15,43,1,153,21,"Tattha tvaṃ kinti {maññasī}ti tattha tassa purisassa aparādhe tvaṃ‘‘ kiṃ kātabban’’ ti maññasi, yathā te cittaṃ uppajjati, tadanurūpamassa daṇḍaṃ paṇehīti dīpeti. "
