491909,111,1419,36,85,1,228,31,"Satthā āgantvā‘‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ imāya nāmā’’ ti vutte‘‘ na, bhikkhave, devadatto idāneva ācariyaṃ paccakkhāya mama paṭipakkho hutvā mahāvināsaṃ patto, pubbepi pattoyevā’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
491910,111,1420,2,14,1,125,12,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto hatthācariyakule nibbattitvā vayappatto hatthisippe nipphattiṃ pāpuṇi. 
