491914,111,1420,46,57,1,38,5,"‘‘ ācariya , ahaṃ rājānaṃ upaṭṭhahissāmī’’ ti. "
491915,111,1420,58,70,1,45,7,"Bodhisatto‘‘ sādhu, tātā’’ ti gantvā rañño ārocesi–"
