492008,111,1452,14,27,1,126,11,"Naccagītāsu kusalā naccagītāni payojesuṃ, pokkharaṇiyaṃ macchakacchapā gītasaddalolatāya sannipatitvā raññāva saddhiṃ gacchanti. "
492009,111,1452,28,47,1,108,15,Rājā tālakkhandhappamāṇaṃ macchaghaṭaṃ disvā‘‘ kiṃ nu kho ime macchā mayā saddhiṃyeva carantī’’ ti amacce pucchi. 
