492013,111,1452,80,90,1,72,8,"Macchā bhattavelāya ekacce āgacchanti, ekacce nāgacchanti, bhattaṃ nassati. "
492014,111,1452,91,94,1,24,3,Rañño tamatthaṃ ārocesuṃ. 
492015,111,1452,95,112,1,103,13,Rājā‘‘ ito paṭṭhāya sattavelāya bheriṃ paharitvā bherisaññāya macchesu sannipatitesu bhattaṃ dethā’’ ti āha. 
492016,111,1452,113,122,1,84,9,Tato paṭṭhāya bhattakammiko bheriṃ paharāpetvā sannipatitānaṃ macchānaṃ bhattaṃ deti. 
492017,111,1452,123,127,1,40,4,Tepi bherisaññāya sannipatitvā bhuñjanti. 
492018,111,1453,2,11,1,69,9,Tesu evaṃ sannipatitvā bhuñjantesu eko suṃsumāro āgantvā macche khādi. 
492019,111,1453,12,15,1,27,3,Bhattakammiko rañño ārocesi. 
492020,111,1453,16,33,1,82,11,Rājā taṃ sutvā‘‘ suṃsumāraṃ macchānaṃ khādanakāle vikaṇṇakena vijjhitvā gaṇhā’’ ti āha . 
492021,111,1453,34,55,1,114,16,"So‘‘ sādhū’’ ti gantvā nāvāya ṭhatvā macche khādituṃ āgataṃ suṃsumāraṃ vikaṇṇakena pahari, taṃ tassa antopiṭṭhiṃ pāvisi. "
492022,111,1453,56,62,1,42,6,So vedanāppatto hutvā taṃ gahetvāva palāyi. 
492023,111,1453,63,71,1,70,8,Bhattakammiko tassa viddhabhāvaṃ ñatvā taṃ ālapanto paṭhamaṃ gāthamāha– 
492024,111,1454,2,4,1,0,0,165.
492025,111,1455,2,13,1,61,9,"‘ ‘ Kāmaṃ yahiṃ icchasi tena gaccha, viddhosi mammamhi vikaṇṇakena; "
492026,111,1456,2,13,1,58,8,"Hatosi bhattena suvāditena, lolo ca macche anubandhamāno’’ ti. "
492027,111,1457,2,6,1,24,4,Tattha kāman ti ekaṃsena. 
492028,111,1457,7,17,1,56,8,"Yahiṃ icchasi tena {gacchā}ti yasmiṃ icchasi, tasmiṃ gaccha. "
492029,111,1457,18,21,1,22,2,{Mammamhī}ti mammaṭṭhāne. 
492030,111,1457,22,25,1,30,2,{Vikaṇṇakenā}ti vikaṇṇakasallena. 
492031,111,1457,26,54,1,212,25,"Hatosi bhattena suvāditena, lolo ca macche {anubandhamāno}ti tvaṃ bherivāditasaññāya bhatte dīyamāne lolo hutvā khādanatthāya macche anubandhamāno tena savāditena bhattena hato, gataṭṭhānepi te jīvitaṃ natthīti attho. "
