492035,111,1460,2,10,1,52,6,"‘ ‘ Evampi lokāmisaṃ opatanto, vihaññatī cittavasānuvattī; "
492036,111,1461,2,13,1,60,8,"So haññatī ñātisakhāna majjhe, macchānugo soriva suṃsumāro’’ ti. "
492037,111,1462,2,7,1,34,5,Tattha lokāmisan ti pañca kāmaguṇā. 
492038,111,1462,8,24,1,70,11,"Te hi loko iṭṭhato kantato manāpato gaṇhāti, tasmā‘‘ lokāmisan’’ ti vuccati. "
492039,111,1462,25,59,1,276,31,"{Opatanto}ti taṃ lokāmisaṃ anupatanto kilesavasena cittavasānuvattī puggalo vihaññati kilamati, so {haññatī}ti so evarūpo puggalo ñātīnañca sakhānañca majjhe so vikaṇṇakena viddho macchānugo suṃsumāro viya pañca kāmaguṇe manāpāti gahetvā haññati kilamati mahāvināsaṃ pāpuṇātiyevāti. "
492040,111,1463,2,17,1,137,13,"Evaṃ satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā saccāni pakāsetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi, saccapariyosāne ukkaṇṭhitabhikkhu sotāpattiphale patiṭṭhahi."
492041,111,1463,18,34,1,80,10,"‘‘ Tadā suṃsumāro devadatto, macchā buddhaparisā, bārāṇasirājā pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
492042,111,1464,2,4,1,29,2,Vikaṇṇakajātakavaṇṇanā tatiyā.
492043,111,1466,2,7,1,21,2,[ 234]4. Asitābhūjātakavaṇṇanā 
492044,111,1467,2,14,1,87,10,Tvameva {dānimakarā}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto aññataraṃ kumārikaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
492045,111,1467,15,30,1,137,14,"Sāvatthiyaṃ kirekasmiṃ dvinnaṃ aggasāvakānaṃ upaṭṭhākakule ekā kumārikā abhirūpā sobhaggappattā, sā vayappattā samānajātikaṃ kulaṃ agamāsi. "
492046,111,1467,31,38,1,58,7,Sāmiko taṃ kismiñci amaññamāno aññattha cittavasena carati. 
492047,111,1467,39,54,1,119,15,Sā tassa taṃ attani anādarataṃ agaṇetvā dve aggasāvake nimantetvā dānaṃ datvā dhammaṃ suṇantī sotāpattiphale patiṭṭhahi. 
492048,111,1467,55,83,1,178,21,"Sā tato paṭṭhāya maggaphalasukhena vītināmayamānā‘‘ sāmikopi maṃ na icchati, gharāvāsena me kammaṃ natthi, pabbajissāmī’’ ti cintetvā mātāpitūnaṃ ācikkhitvā pabbajitvā arahattaṃ pāpuṇi. "
492049,111,1467,84,90,1,37,6,Tassā sā kiriyā bhikkhūsu pākaṭā jātā. 
492050,111,1467,91,96,1,57,5,Athekadivasaṃ bhikkhū dhammasabhāyaṃ kathaṃ samuṭṭhāpesuṃ–
492051,111,1467,97,128,1,216,24,"‘‘ āvuso, asukakulassa dhītā atthagavesikā sāmikassa anicchabhāvaṃ ñatvā aggasāvakānaṃ dhammaṃ sutvā sotāpattiphale patiṭṭhāya puna mātāpitaro āpucchitvā pabbajitvā arahattaṃ pattā, evaṃ atthagavesikā, āvuso sā kumārikā’’ ti. "
492052,111,1467,129,171,1,191,25,"Satthā āgantvā‘‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ imāya nāmā’’ ti vutte‘‘ na, bhikkhave, idānevesā kuladhītā atthagavesikā, pubbepi atthagavesikāyevā’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
492053,111,1468,2,18,1,147,16,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto isipabbajjaṃ pabbajitvā abhiññā ca samāpattiyo ca nibbattetvā himavantapadese vāsaṃ kappesi. 
492054,111,1468,19,30,1,115,11,Tadā bārāṇasirājā attano puttassa brahmadattakumārassa parivārasampattiṃ disvā uppannāsaṅko puttaṃ raṭṭhā pabbājesi. 
492055,111,1468,31,45,1,118,13,So asitābhuṃ nāma attano deviṃ ādāya himavantaṃ pavisitvā macchamaṃsaphalāphalāni khādanto paṇṇasālāya nivāsaṃ kappesi. 
492056,111,1468,46,64,1,108,14,So ekaṃ kinnariṃ disvā paṭibaddhacitto‘‘ imaṃ pajāpatiṃ karissāmī’’ ti asitābhuṃ agaṇetvā tassā anupadaṃ agamāsi. 
492057,111,1468,65,106,1,297,36,"Sā taṃ kinnariṃ anubandhamānaṃ disvā‘‘ ayaṃ maṃ agaṇetvā kinnariṃ anubandhati, kiṃ me iminā’’ ti virattacittā hutvā bodhisattaṃ upasaṅkamitvā vanditvā attano kasiṇaparikammaṃ kathāpetvā kasiṇaṃ olokentī abhiññā ca samāpattiyo ca nibbattetvā bodhisattaṃ vanditvā āgantvā attano paṇṇasālāya dvāre aṭṭhāsi. "
492058,111,1468,107,118,1,112,11,Brahmadattopi kinnariṃ anubandhanto vicaritvā tassā gatamaggampi adisvā chinnāso hutvā paṇṇasālābhimukhova āgato. 
492059,111,1468,119,144,1,154,20,"Asitābhū taṃ āgacchantaṃ disvā vehāsaṃ abbhuggantvā maṇivaṇṇe gaganatale ṭhitā‘‘ ayyaputta, taṃ nissāya mayā idaṃ jhānasukhaṃ laddhan’’ ti vatvā imaṃ gāthamāha– "
492060,111,1469,2,4,1,0,0,167.
492061,111,1470,2,12,1,40,7,"‘ ‘ Tvameva dānimakara, yaṃ kāmo byagamā tayi; "
492062,111,1471,2,10,1,46,5,"Soyaṃ appaṭisandhiko, kharachinnaṃva renukan’’ ti. "
492063,111,1472,2,18,1,96,12,"Tattha tvameva {dānimakarā}ti, ayyaputta, maṃ pahāya kinnariṃ anubandhanto tvaññeva idāni idaṃ akara. "
492064,111,1472,19,39,1,127,18,"Yaṃ kāmo byagamā {tayī}ti yaṃ mama tayi kāmo vigato vikkhambhanappahānena pahīno, yassa pahīnattā ahaṃ imaṃ visesaṃ pattāti dīpeti. "
492065,111,1472,40,53,1,84,11,"Soyaṃ {appaṭisandhiko}ti so pana kāmo idāni appaṭisandhiko jāto, na sakkā paṭisandhituṃ. "
492066,111,1472,54,64,1,74,9,"Kharachinnaṃva renukan ti kharo vuccati kakaco, renukaṃ vuccati hatthidanto. "
492067,111,1472,65,92,1,198,25,"Yathā kakacena chinno hatthidanto appaṭisandhiko hoti, na puna purimanayena allīyati, evaṃ puna mayhaṃ tayā saddhiṃ cittassa ghaṭanaṃ nāma natthīti vatvā tassa passantasseva uppatitvā aññattha agamāsi. "
492068,111,1473,2,8,1,48,6,So tassā gatakāle paridevamāno dutiyaṃ gāthamāha– 
492069,111,1474,2,4,1,0,0,168.
492070,111,1475,2,10,1,38,5,"‘ ‘ Atricchaṃ atilobhena , atilobhamadena ca; "
492071,111,1476,2,11,1,41,6,"Evaṃ hāyati atthamhā, ahaṃva asitābhuyā’’ ti. "
492072,111,1477,2,17,1,128,13,"Tattha atricchaṃ {atilobhenā}ti atricchā vuccati atra atra icchāsaṅkhātā apariyantataṇhā, atilobho vuccati atikkamitvā pavattalobho. "
492073,111,1477,18,26,1,67,7,Atilobhamadena {cā}ti purisamadaṃ uppādanato atilobhamado nāma jāyati. 
492074,111,1477,27,47,1,147,18,"Idaṃ vuttaṃ hoti– atricchāvasena atricchamāno puggalo atilobhena ca atilobhamadena ca yathā ahaṃ asitābhuyā rājadhītāya parihīno, evaṃ atthā hāyatīti. "
492075,111,1478,2,15,1,89,13,Iti so imāya gāthāya paridevitvā araññe ekakova vasitvā pitu accayena gantvā rajjaṃ gaṇhi. 
492076,111,1479,2,8,1,54,6,Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–
492077,111,1479,9,28,1,80,14,"‘‘ tadā rājaputto ca rājadhītā ca ime dve janā ahesuṃ, tāpaso pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
492078,111,1480,2,4,1,30,2,Asitābhūjātakavaṇṇanā catutthā.
492079,111,1482,2,7,1,24,2,[ 235]5. Vacchanakhajātakavaṇṇanā 
492080,111,1483,2,15,1,83,10,Sukhā gharā {vacchanakhā}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto rojamallaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
492081,111,1483,16,20,1,35,4,So kirāyasmato ānandassa gihisahāyo. 
492082,111,1483,21,32,1,86,10,"So ekadivasaṃ āgamanatthāya therassa sāsanaṃ pāhesi, thero satthāraṃ āpucchitvā agamāsi. "
492083,111,1483,33,71,1,268,31,"So theraṃ nānaggarasabhojanaṃ bhojetvā ekamantaṃ nisinno therena saddhiṃ paṭisanthāraṃ katvā theraṃ gihibhogehi pañcahi kāmaguṇehi nimantento‘‘ bhante ānanda, mama gehe pahūtaṃ saviññāṇakaaviññāṇakaratanaṃ, idaṃ majjhe bhinditvā tuyhaṃ dammi, ehi ubho agāraṃ ajjhāvasāmā’’ ti. "
492084,111,1483,72,129,1,254,36,"Thero tassa kāmaguṇesu ādīnavaṃ kathetvā uṭṭhāyāsanā vihāraṃ gantvā‘‘ diṭṭho te, ānanda, rojo’’ ti satthārā pucchito‘‘ āma, bhante’’ ti vatvā‘‘ kimassa kathesī’’ ti vutte‘‘ bhante, maṃ rojo gharāvāsena nimantesi, athassāhaṃ gharāvāse ceva kāmaguṇesu ca ādīnavaṃ kathesin’’ ti. "
492085,111,1483,130,155,1,127,18,"Satthā‘‘ na kho, ānanda, rojo mallo idāneva pabbajite gharāvāsena nimantesi, pubbepi nimantesiyevā’’ ti vatvā tena yācito atītaṃ āhari. "
492086,111,1484,2,27,1,253,24,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto aññatarasmiṃ nigamagāme brāhmaṇakule nibbattitvā vayappatto isipabbajjaṃ pabbajitvā himavantapadese ciraṃ vasitvā loṇambilasevanatthāya bārāṇasiṃ patvā rājuyyāne vasitvā punadivase bārāṇasiṃ pāvisi. 
492087,111,1484,28,43,1,135,15,Athassa bārāṇasiseṭṭhi ācāravihāre pasīditvā gehaṃ netvā bhojetvā uyyāne vasanatthāya paṭiññaṃ gahetvā taṃ paṭijagganto uyyāne vasāpesi. 
492088,111,1484,44,48,1,34,4,Te aññamaññaṃ uppannasinehā ahesuṃ. 
492089,111,1485,2,8,1,70,6,Athekadivasaṃ bārāṇasiseṭṭhi bodhisatte pemavissāsavasena evaṃ cintesi–
492090,111,1485,9,31,1,147,17,"‘‘ pabbajjā nāma dukkhā, mama sahāyaṃ vacchanakhaparibbājakaṃ uppabbājetvā sabbaṃ vibhavaṃ majjhe bhinditvā tassa datvā dvepi samaggavāsaṃ vasissāmā’’ ti. "
492091,111,1485,32,63,1,202,24,"So ekadivasaṃ bhattakiccapariyosāne tena saddhiṃ madhurapaṭisanthāraṃ katvā‘‘ bhante vacchanakha, pabbajjā nāma dukkhā, sukho gharāvāso, ehi ubho samaggā kāme paribhuñjantā vasāmā’’ ti vatvā paṭhamaṃ gāthamāha– "
492092,111,1486,2,4,1,0,0,169.
492093,111,1487,2,11,1,43,6,"‘ ‘ Sukhā gharā vacchanakha, sahiraññā sabhojanā; "
492094,111,1488,2,12,1,47,7,"Yattha bhutvā pivitvā ca, sayeyyātha anussuko’’ ti. "
492095,111,1489,2,7,1,38,3,Tattha {sahiraññā}ti sattaratanasampannā. 
492096,111,1489,8,11,1,34,2,{Sabhojanā}ti bahukhādanīyabhojanīyā. 
492097,111,1489,12,26,1,118,13,Yattha bhutvā pivitvā {cā}ti yesu sahiraññabhojanesu gharesu nānaggarasāni bhojanāni paribhuñjitvā nānāpānāni ca pivitvā. 
492098,111,1489,27,41,1,106,12,"Sayeyyātha {anussuko}ti yesu alaṅkatasirisayanapiṭṭhe anussuko hutvā sayeyyāsi, te gharā nāma ativiya sukhāti. "
492099,111,1490,2,35,1,193,25,"Athassa taṃ sutvā bodhisatto‘‘ mahāseṭṭhi, tvaṃ aññāṇatāya kāmagiddho hutvā gharāvāsassa guṇaṃ, pabbajjāya ca aguṇaṃ kathesi, gharāvāsassa te aguṇaṃ kathessāmi, suṇāhi dānī’’ ti vatvā dutiyaṃ gāthamāha– "
492100,111,1491,2,4,1,0,0,170.
492101,111,1492,2,11,1,40,6,"‘ ‘ Gharā nānīhamānassa, gharā nābhaṇato musā; "
492102,111,1493,2,7,1,40,4,"Gharā nādinnadaṇḍassa, paresaṃ anikubbato; "
492103,111,1494,2,12,1,54,7,"Evaṃ chiddaṃ durabhisambhavaṃ, ko gharaṃ paṭipajjatī’’ ti. "
492104,111,1495,2,18,1,139,14,"Tattha gharā {nānīhamānassā}ti niccakālaṃ kasigorakkhādikaraṇena anīhamānassa avāyamantassa gharā nāma natthi, gharāvāso na patiṭṭhātīti attho. "
492105,111,1495,19,29,1,95,9,Gharā nābhaṇato {musā}ti khettavatthuhiraññasuvaṇṇādīnaṃ atthāya amusābhaṇatopi gharā nāma natthi. 
492106,111,1495,30,46,1,132,12,"Gharā nādinnadaṇḍassa, paresaṃ {anikubbato}ti {nādinnadaṇḍassā}ti aggahitadaṇḍassa, nikkhittadaṇḍassa paresaṃ anikubbato gharā nāma natthi. "
492107,111,1495,47,64,1,170,16,"Yo pana ādinnadaṇḍo hutvā paresaṃ dāsakammakarādīnaṃ tasmiṃ tasmiṃ aparādhe aparādhānurūpaṃ vadhabandhanachedanatāḷanādivasena karoti, tasseva gharāvāso saṇṭhahatīti attho. "
492108,111,1495,65,108,1,315,36,"Evaṃ chiddaṃ durabhisambhavaṃ, ko gharaṃ {paṭipajjatī}ti taṃ dāni evaṃ etesaṃ īhanādīnaṃ akaraṇe sati tāya tāya parihāniyā chiddaṃ karaṇepi sati niccameva kātabbato durabhisambhavaṃ durārādhanīyaṃ, niccaṃ karontassapi vā durabhisambhavameva duppūraṃ gharāvāsaṃ‘‘ ahaṃ nipparitasso hutvā ajjhāvasissāmī’’ ti ko paṭipajjatīti. "
492109,111,1496,2,9,1,61,7,Evaṃ mahāsatto gharāvāsassa dosaṃ kathetvā uyyānameva agamāsi. 
492110,111,1497,2,9,1,54,6,Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–
492111,111,1497,10,25,1,82,10,"‘‘ tadā bārāṇasiseṭṭhi rojo mallo ahosi, vacchanakhaparibbājako pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
492112,111,1498,2,4,1,32,2,Vacchanakhajātakavaṇṇanā pañcamā.
492113,111,1500,2,7,1,17,2,[ 236]6. Bakajātakavaṇṇanā 
492114,111,1501,2,15,1,92,11,Bhaddako vatayaṃ {pakkhī}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ekaṃ kuhakabhikkhuṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
492115,111,1501,16,37,1,98,14,"Tañhi satthā ānetvā dassitaṃ disvā‘‘ na, bhikkhave, idāneva, pubbepesa kuhakoyevā’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
492116,111,1502,2,16,1,115,13,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto himavantapadese ekasmiṃ sare maccho hutvā mahāparivāro vasi. 
492117,111,1502,17,39,1,145,18,Atheko bako‘‘ macche khādissāmī’’ ti sarassa āsannaṭṭhāne sīsaṃ pātetvā pakkhe pasāretvā mandamando macche olokento aṭṭhāsi tesaṃ pamādaṃ āgamayamāno. 
492118,111,1502,40,49,1,77,9,Tasmiṃ khaṇe bodhisatto macchagaṇaparivuto gocaraṃ gaṇhanto taṃ ṭhānaṃ pāpuṇi. 
492119,111,1502,50,56,1,48,6,Macchagaṇo taṃ bakaṃ passitvā paṭhamaṃ gāthamāha– 
492120,111,1503,2,4,1,0,0,171.
492121,111,1504,2,10,1,43,6,"‘ ‘ Bhaddako vatayaṃ pakkhī, dijo kumudasannibho; "
492122,111,1505,2,10,1,44,5,"Vūpasantehi pakkhehi, mandamandova jhāyatī’’ ti. "
492123,111,1506,2,14,1,88,11,Tattha mandamandova {jhāyatī}ti abalabalo viya hutvā kiñci ajānanto viya ekakova jhāyatīti. 
492124,111,1507,2,8,1,46,6,Atha naṃ bodhisatto oloketvā dutiyaṃ gāthamāha– 
492125,111,1508,2,4,1,0,0,172.
