492231,111,1562,13,43,1,243,23,"Devadatte satthari āghātaṃ bandhitvā navamāsaccayena jetavanadvārakoṭṭhake pathaviyaṃ nimugge jetavanavāsino ca sakalaraṭṭhavāsino ca‘‘ buddhapaṭikaṇṭako devadatto pathaviyā gilito, nihatapaccāmitto dāni sammāsambuddho jāto’’ ti tuṭṭhahaṭṭhā ahesuṃ. "
492232,111,1562,44,54,1,104,10,Tesaṃ kathaṃ sutvā paramparaghosena sakalajambudīpavāsino yakkhabhūtadevagaṇā ca tuṭṭhahaṭṭhā eva ahesuṃ. 
