492255,111,1569,25,85,1,380,53,"Piṅgalarājā hi pāsādā otaranto ca ārohanto ca kammāramuṭṭhikāya paharanto viya mayhaṃ sīse aṭṭhaṭṭha khaṭake deti, so paralokaṃ gantvāpi mama sīse dadamāno viya nirayapālānampi yamassapi sīle khaṭake dassati, atha naṃ te‘ ativiya ayaṃ amhe bādhatī’ ti puna idheva ānetvā vissajjeyyuṃ, atha me so punapi sīse khaṭake dadeyyāti bhayenāhaṃ rodāmī’’ ti imamatthaṃ pakāsento dutiyaṃ gāthamāha– "
