492331,111,1600,49,74,1,153,23,"Siṅgālo viya dāṭhinan ti yathā siṅgālo dāṭhīnaṃ mahā ahosi, evaṃ mahā hoti, atha so siṅgālo viya pamādaṃ āpajjitvā taṃ parivāraṃ nissāya vināsaṃ pāpuṇātīti."
