492600,111,1699,17,27,1,60,9,Deti dānaṃ {asaññato}ti asaññato dussīlo evaṃ katvā dānaṃ deti. 
492601,111,1699,28,44,1,132,14,"Edisaṃ bhattaṃ bhuñjamāno, sa pāpena {upalippatī}ti edisaṃ uddissakatabhattaṃ bhuñjamāno so samaṇopi pāpena upalippati saṃyujjatiyevāti. "
