492612,111,1709,2,13,1,85,10,Addhā pādañjalī {sabbe}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto lāḷudāyītheraṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
492613,111,1709,14,26,1,92,11,"Ekasmiñhi divase dve aggasāvakā pañhaṃ vinicchinanti, bhikkhū pañhaṃ suṇantā there pasaṃsanti. "
492614,111,1709,27,43,1,84,12,Lāḷudāyīthero pana parisantare nisinno‘‘ ete amhehi samaṃ kiṃ jānantī’’ ti oṭṭhaṃ bhañji. 
492615,111,1709,44,52,1,48,7,"Taṃ disvā therā uṭṭhāya pakkamiṃsu, parisā bhijji. "
492616,111,1709,53,57,1,43,4,Dhammasabhāyaṃ bhikkhū kathaṃ samuṭṭhāpesuṃ–
492617,111,1709,58,71,1,56,8,"‘‘ āvuso lāḷudāyī, dve aggasāvake garahitvā oṭṭhaṃ bhañjī’’ ti. "
492618,111,1709,72,98,1,128,19,"Taṃ sutvā satthā‘‘ na, bhikkhave, idāneva, pubbepi lāḷudāyī ṭhapetvā oṭṭhabhañjanaṃ tato uttari aññaṃ na jānātī’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
492619,111,1710,2,14,1,94,10,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto tassa atthadhammānusāsako amacco ahosi. 
492620,111,1710,15,22,1,55,7,Rañño pādañjalī nāma putto lālo dandhaparisakkano ahosi. 
492621,111,1710,23,26,1,26,3,Aparabhāge rājā kālamakāsi. 
492622,111,1710,27,43,1,99,12,Amaccā rañño matakiccāni katvā‘‘ taṃ rajje abhisiñcissāmā’’ ti mantayamānā rājaputtaṃ pādañjaliṃ āhaṃsu. 
492623,111,1710,44,60,1,89,11,"Bodhisatto pana‘‘ ayaṃ kumāro lālo dandhaparisakkano, pariggahetvā naṃ abhisiñcissāmā’’ ti āha. "
492624,111,1710,61,72,1,97,11,Amaccā vinicchayaṃ sajjetvā kumāraṃ samīpe nisīdāpetvā aḍḍaṃ vinicchinantā na sammā vinicchiniṃsu. 
