492634,111,1715,2,23,1,122,15,"Te aparasmimpi divase vinicchayaṃ sajjetvā aññaṃ aḍḍaṃ suṭṭhu vinicchinitvā‘‘ kīdisaṃ, deva, suṭṭhu vinicchinitan’’ ti pucchiṃsu. "
