492649,111,1724,55,61,1,48,6,Te attano attano adhigatavisesaṃ satthu ārocesuṃ. 
492650,111,1724,62,66,1,39,4,Athekassa bhikkhuno parivitakko udapādi–
492651,111,1724,67,83,1,74,10,"‘‘ imesaṃ kammaṭṭhānāni nānā, nibbānaṃ ekaṃ, kathaṃ sabbehi arahattaṃ pattan’’ ti. "
492652,111,1724,84,87,1,19,3,So satthāraṃ pucchi. 
492653,111,1724,88,118,1,127,18,"Satthā‘‘ kiṃ te, bhikkhu, kiṃsukadiṭṭhabhātikehi nānattan’’ ti vatvā‘‘ idaṃ no, bhante, kāraṇaṃ kathethā’’ ti bhikkhūhi yācito atītaṃ āhari. "
492654,111,1725,2,12,1,71,9,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente tassa cattāro puttā ahesuṃ. 
492655,111,1725,13,33,1,101,13,"Te ekadivasaṃ sārathiṃ pakkosetvā‘‘ mayaṃ, samma, kiṃsukaṃ daṭṭhukāmā, kiṃsukarukkhaṃ no dassehī’’ ti āhaṃsu. "
492656,111,1725,34,63,1,159,20,"Sārathi‘‘ sādhu, dassessāmī’’ ti vatvā catunnampi ekato adassetvā jeṭṭharājaputtaṃ tāva rathe nisīdāpetvā araññaṃ netvā‘‘ ayaṃ kiṃsuko’’ ti khāṇukakāle kiṃsukaṃ dassesi. "
492657,111,1725,64,72,1,68,6,"Aparassa bahalapalāsakāle, aparassa pupphitakāle, aparassa phalitakāle. "
492658,111,1725,73,88,1,86,11,Aparabhāge cattāropi bhātaro ekato nisinnā‘‘ kiṃsuko nāma kīdiso’’ ti kathaṃ samuṭṭhāpesuṃ. 
492659,111,1725,89,99,1,37,6,Tato eko‘‘ seyyāthāpi jhāmathūṇo’’ ti āha. 
492660,111,1725,100,126,1,96,12,"Dutiyo‘‘ seyyathāpi nigrodharukkho’’ ti, tatiyo‘‘ seyyathāpi maṃsapesī’’ ti, catuttho‘‘ seyyathāpi sirīso’’ ti. "
492661,111,1725,127,158,1,161,22,"Te aññamaññassa kathāya aparituṭṭhā pitu santikaṃ gantvā‘‘ deva, kiṃsuko nāma kīdiso’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ tumhehi kiṃ kathitan’’ ti vutte attanā kathitanīhāraṃ rañño kathesuṃ. "
492662,111,1725,159,197,1,195,28,"Rājā‘‘ catūhipi tumhehi kiṃsuko diṭṭho, kevalaṃ vo kiṃsukassa dassento sārathi‘ imasmiṃ kāle kiṃsuko kīdiso , imasmiṃ kīdiso’ ti vibhajitvā na pucchito, tena vo kaṅkhā uppannā’’ ti vatvā paṭhamaṃ gāthamāha– "
