492700,111,1747,2,13,1,57,9,"‘ ‘ Nanu maṃ suhadayoti maññasi, yañca maṃ hanasi veḷuyaṭṭhiyā; "
492701,111,1748,2,12,1,57,7,"Pakkambavane ramāmase, gaccha tvaṃ gharakaṃ yathāsukhan’’ ti. "
492702,111,1749,2,28,1,103,16,"Tattha nanu maṃ suhadayoti {maññasī}ti nanu tvaṃ maṃ‘‘ suhadayo’’ ti maññasi,‘‘ suhadayo ayan’’ ti maññasīti attho. "
492703,111,1749,29,46,1,109,14,"Yañca maṃ hanasi {veḷuyaṭṭhiyā}ti yaṃ maṃ evaṃ atimaññasi, yañca veḷupesikāya hanasi, tenāhaṃ nāgacchāmīti dīpeti. "
