492814,111,1798,41,46,1,60,4,Nāpi {morūpasevinā}ti morapattagijjhapattādīhi akatūpasevanena. 
492815,111,1798,47,56,1,64,8,Tenamhi hadaye {viddho}ti tena kilesakaṇḍenāhaṃ hadaye viddho amhi. 
492816,111,1798,57,62,1,56,4,{Sabbaṅgaparidāhinā}ti sabbāni aṅgāni paridahanasamatthena. 
492817,111,1798,63,78,1,115,14,"Mahārāja, tena hi kilesakaṇḍena hadaye viddhakālato paṭṭhāya mama aggi padittāniva sabbāni aṅgāni ḍayhantīti dasseti. "
492818,111,1799,2,10,1,54,7,Āvedhañca na {passāmī}ti viddhaṭṭhāne vaṇañca na passāmi. 
492819,111,1799,11,24,1,80,11,"Yato {ruhiramassave}ti yato me āvedhato lohitaṃ pagghareyya, taṃ na passāmīti attho. "
492820,111,1799,25,42,1,106,15,"Yāva ayoniso cittan ti ettha {yāvā}ti daḷhatthe nipāto, ativiya daḷhaṃ katvā ayoniso cittaṃ vaḍḍhitanti attho. "
492821,111,1799,43,52,1,64,9,Sayaṃ me dukkhamābhatan ti attanāva mayā attano dukkhaṃ ānītanti. 
492822,111,1800,2,79,1,459,59,"Evaṃ bodhisatto imāhi tīhi gāthāhi rañño dhammaṃ desetvā rājānaṃ paṇṇasālato bahi katvā kasiṇaparikammaṃ katvā naṭṭhaṃ jhānaṃ uppādetvā paṇṇasālāya nikkhamitvā ākāse nisinno rājānaṃ ovaditvā‘‘ mahārāja, ahaṃ himavantameva gamissāmī’’ ti vatvā‘‘ na sakkā, bhante, gantun’’ ti vuccamānopi‘‘ mahārāja, mayā idha vasantena evarūpo vippakāro patto, idāni na sakkā idha vasitun’’ ti rañño yācantasseva ākāse uppatitvā himavantaṃ gantvā tattha yāvatāyukaṃ ṭhatvā brahmalokūpago ahosi. "
492823,111,1801,2,16,1,126,12,"Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā saccāni pakāsetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi, saccapariyosāne ukkaṇṭhitabhikkhu arahatte patiṭṭhahi. "
