492827,111,1804,2,7,1,23,2,[ 252]2. Tilamuṭṭhijātakavaṇṇanā 
492828,111,1805,2,17,1,97,13,Ajjāpi me taṃ {manasī}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto aññataraṃ kodhanaṃ bhikkhuṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
492829,111,1805,18,37,1,125,15,"Aññataro kira, bhikkhu, kodhano ahosi upāyāsabahulo, appampi vutto samāno kuppi abhisajji, kopañca dosañca appaccayañca pātvākāsi. "
492830,111,1805,38,43,1,57,5,Athekadivasaṃ bhikkhū dhammasabhāyaṃ kathaṃ samuṭṭhāpesuṃ–
492831,111,1805,44,71,1,186,21,"‘‘ āvuso, asuko nāma bhikkhu kodhano upāyāsabahulo uddhane pakkhittaloṇaṃ viya taṭataṭāyanto vicarati, evarūpe nikkodhane buddhasāsane pabbajito samāno kodhamattampi niggaṇhituṃ na sakkotī’’ ti. "
492832,111,1805,72,122,1,212,32,"Satthā tesaṃ kathaṃ sutvā ekaṃ bhikkhuṃ pesetvā taṃ bhikkhuṃ pakkosāpetvā‘‘ saccaṃ kira tvaṃ, bhikkhu, kodhano’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ saccaṃ, bhante’’ ti vutte‘‘ na, bhikkhave, idāneva, pubbepi ayaṃ kodhano ahosī’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
492833,111,1806,2,12,1,85,10,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente tassa putto brahmadattakumāro nāma ahosi. 
492834,111,1806,13,63,1,359,38,"Porāṇakarājāno ca attano putte‘‘ evaṃ ete nihatamānadappā sītuṇhakkhamā lokacārittaññū ca bhavissantī’’ ti attano nagare disāpāmokkhaācariye vijjamānepi sippuggahaṇatthāya dūre tiroraṭṭhaṃ pesenti, tasmā sopi rājā soḷasavassuddesikaṃ puttaṃ pakkosāpetvā ekapaṭalikaupāhanā ca paṇṇacchattañca kahāpaṇasahassañca datvā‘‘ tāta, takkasilaṃ gantvā sippaṃ uggaṇhā’’ ti pesesi. "
492835,111,1806,64,103,1,283,34,"So‘‘ sādhū’’ ti mātāpitaro vanditvā nikkhamitvā anupubbena takkasilaṃ patvā ācariyassa gehaṃ pucchitvā ācariye māṇavakānaṃ sippaṃ vācetvā uṭṭhāya gharadvāre caṅkamante gehaṃ gantvā yasmiṃ ṭhāne ṭhito ācariyaṃ addasa, tattheva upāhanā omuñcitvā chattañca apanetvā ācariyaṃ vanditvā aṭṭhāsi. "
492836,111,1806,104,110,1,52,6,So tassa kilantabhāvaṃ ñatvā āgantukasaṅgahaṃ kāresi. 
492837,111,1806,111,138,1,126,17,"Kumāro bhuttabhojano thokaṃ vissamitvā ācariyaṃ upasaṅkamitvā vanditvā aṭṭhāsi,‘‘ kuto āgatosi, tātā’’ ti ca vutte‘‘ bārāṇasito’’ ti āha."
492838,111,1806,139,146,1,16,3,‘‘ Kassa puttosī’’ ti?
492839,111,1806,147,153,1,16,2,‘‘ Bārāṇasirañño’’ ti.
492840,111,1806,154,160,1,19,2,‘‘ Kenatthenāgatosī’’ ti?
492841,111,1806,161,168,1,23,3,‘‘ Sippaṃ uggaṇhatthāyā’’ ti.
492842,111,1806,169,182,1,62,8,"‘‘ Kiṃ te ācariyabhāgo ābhato, udāhu dhammantevāsiko hotukāmosī’’ ti? "
492843,111,1806,183,199,1,86,11,So‘‘ ācariyabhāgo me ābhato’’ ti vatvā ācariyassa pādamūle sahassatthavikaṃ ṭhapetvā vandi. 
492844,111,1807,2,18,1,137,15,"Dhammantevāsikā divā ācariyassa kammaṃ katvā rattiṃ sippaṃ uggaṇhanti, ācariyabhāgadāyakā gehe jeṭṭhaputtā viya hutvā sippameva uggaṇhanti. "
492845,111,1807,19,27,1,75,8,Tasmā sopi ācariyo sallahukena subhanakkhattena kumārassa sippaṃ paṭṭhapesi. 
492846,111,1807,28,36,1,72,8,Kumāropi sippaṃ uggaṇhanto ekadivasaṃ ācariyena saddhiṃ nhāyituṃ agamāsi. 
492847,111,1807,37,46,1,70,9,Athekā mahallikā itthī tilāni sete katvā pattharitvā rakkhamānā nisīdi. 
492848,111,1807,47,69,1,122,17,"Kumāro setatile disvā khāditukāmo hutvā ekaṃ tilamuṭṭhiṃ gahetvā khādi, mahallikā‘‘ taṇhāluko eso’’ ti kiñci avatvā tuṇhī ahosi. "
492849,111,1807,70,82,1,63,11,"So punadivasepi tāya velāya tatheva akāsi, sāpi naṃ na kiñci āha. "
492850,111,1807,83,103,1,127,15,"Itaro tatiyadivasepi tathevākāsi, tadā mahallikā‘‘ disāpāmokkho ācariyo attano antevāsikehi maṃ vilumpāpetī’’ ti bāhā paggayha kandi. "
492851,111,1807,104,117,1,42,7,"Ācariyo nivattitvā‘‘ kiṃ etaṃ , ammā’’ ti pucchi."
492852,111,1807,118,147,1,139,21,"‘‘ Sāmi, antevāsiko te mayā katānaṃ setatilānaṃ ajjekaṃ muṭṭhiṃ khādi, hiyyo ekaṃ, pare ekaṃ, nanu evaṃ khādanto mama santakaṃ sabbaṃ nāsessatī’’ ti."
492853,111,1807,148,161,1,34,7,"‘‘ Amma, mā rodi, mūlaṃ te dāpessāmī’’ ti."
492854,111,1807,162,185,1,85,15,"‘‘ Na me, sāmi, mūlenattho, yathā panesa kumāro puna evaṃ na karoti, tathā taṃ sikkhāpehī’’ ti. "
492855,111,1807,186,218,1,155,23,"Ācariyo‘‘ tena hi passa, ammā’’ ti dvīhi māṇavehi taṃ kumāraṃ dvīsu hatthesu gāhāpetvā veḷupesikaṃ gahetvā‘‘ puna evarūpaṃ mā akāsī’’ ti tikkhattuṃ piṭṭhiyaṃ pahari. "
492856,111,1807,219,229,1,88,10,Kumāro ācariyassa kujjhitvā rattāni akkhīni katvā pādapiṭṭhito yāva kesamatthakā olokesi. 
492857,111,1807,230,234,1,38,4,Sopissa kujjhitvā olokitabhāvaṃ aññāsi. 
492858,111,1807,235,278,1,256,32,"Kumāro sippaṃ niṭṭhāpetvā‘‘ anuyogaṃ datvā mārāpetabbo esa mayā’’ ti tena katadosaṃ hadaye ṭhapetvā gamanakāle ācariyaṃ vanditvā‘‘ yadāhaṃ, ācariya, bārāṇasirajjaṃ patvā tumhākaṃ santikaṃ pesessāmi, tadā tumhe āgaccheyyāthā’’ ti sasineho viya paṭiññaṃ gahetvā pakkāmi. "
492859,111,1808,2,10,1,53,7,So bārāṇasiṃ patvā mātāpitaro vanditvā sippaṃ dassesi. 
492860,111,1808,11,28,1,93,12,"Rājā‘‘ jīvamānena me putto diṭṭho, jīvamānovassa rajjasiriṃ passāmī’’ ti puttaṃ rajje patiṭṭhāpesi. "
492861,111,1808,29,48,1,126,14,So rajjasiriṃ anubhavamāno ācariyena katadosaṃ saritvā uppannakodho‘‘ mārāpessāmi nan’’ ti pakkosanatthāya ācariyassa dūtaṃ pāhesi. 
492862,111,1808,49,84,1,183,23,Ācariyo‘‘ taruṇakāle naṃ saññāpetuṃ na sakkhissāmī’’ ti agantvā tassa rañño majjhimavayakāle‘‘ idāni naṃ saññāpetuṃ sakkhissāmī’’ ti gantvā rājadvāre ṭhatvā‘‘ takkasilācariyo āgato’’ ti ārocāpesi. 
492863,111,1808,85,133,1,275,38,"Rājā tuṭṭho brāhmaṇaṃ pakkosāpetvā taṃ attano santikaṃ āgataṃ disvāva kodhaṃ uppādetvā rattāni akkhīni katvā amacce āmantetvā‘‘ bho, ajjāpi me ācariyena pahaṭaṭṭhānaṃ rujjati, ācariyo nalāṭena maccuṃ ādāya‘ marissāmī’ ti āgato, ajjassa jīvitaṃ natthī’’ ti vatvā purimā dve gāthā avoca– "
