492871,111,1815,13,34,1,136,19,"Yaṃ maṃ tvaṃ tilamuṭṭhiyā kāraṇā anutāḷayi, anutāḷento ca maṃ bāhāya gahetvā anutāḷayi, taṃ anutāḷanaṃ ajjāpi me manasīti ayañhettha attho. "
