492873,111,1815,46,55,1,63,8,Yenāsi {brāhmaṇāgato}ti yasmā brāhmaṇa idha mama santikaṃ āgatosi. 
492874,111,1815,56,71,1,79,13,"Yaṃ maṃ bāhā {gahetvānā}ti yaṃ mama bāhā gahetvā, yaṃ maṃ bāhāya gahetvātipi attho. "
