492912,111,1832,22,37,1,62,10,"‘‘ Tadā rājā kodhano bhikkhu ahosi, ācariyo pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
492913,111,1833,2,4,1,30,2,Tilamuṭṭhijātakavaṇṇanā dutiyā.
492914,111,1835,2,7,1,23,2,[ 253]3. Maṇikaṇṭhajātakavaṇṇanā 
492915,111,1836,2,19,1,104,12,Mamannapānan ti idaṃ satthā āḷaviṃ nissāya aggāḷave cetiye viharanto kuṭikārasikkhāpadaṃ( pārā.342) ārabbha kathesi. 
492916,111,1836,20,40,1,139,15,"Āḷavakā hi bhikkhū saññācikāya kuṭiyo kārayamānā yācanabahulā viññattibahulā vihariṃsu‘‘ purisaṃ detha, purisatthakaraṃ dethā’’ tiādīni vadantā. "
492917,111,1836,41,52,1,96,10,Manussā upaddutā yācanāya upaddutā viññattiyā bhikkhū disvā ubbijjiṃsupi uttasiṃsupi palāyiṃsupi. 
492918,111,1836,53,65,1,101,11,"Athāyasmā mahākassapo āḷaviṃ upasaṅkamitvā piṇḍāya pāvisi, manussā therampi disvā tatheva paṭipajjiṃsu. "
492919,111,1836,66,101,1,245,27,"So pacchābhattaṃ piṇḍapātapaṭikkanto bhikkhū āmantetvā‘‘ pubbāyaṃ, āvuso, āḷavī sulabhapiṇḍā, idāni kasmā dullabhapiṇḍā jātā’’ ti pucchitvā taṃ kāraṇaṃ sutvā bhagavati āḷaviṃ āgantvā aggāḷavacetiye viharante bhagavantaṃ upasaṅkamitvā etamatthaṃ ārocesi. "
492920,111,1836,102,111,1,78,8,Satthā etasmiṃ kāraṇe bhikkhusaṅghaṃ sannipātāpetvā āḷavake bhikkhū paṭipucchi –
492921,111,1836,112,126,1,57,8,"‘‘ saccaṃ kira tumhe, bhikkhave, saññācikāya kuṭiyo kārethā’’ ti."
492922,111,1836,127,169,1,244,30,"‘‘ Saccaṃ, bhante’’ ti vutte te bhikkhū garahitvā‘‘ bhikkhave, yācanā nāmesā sattaratanaparipuṇṇe nāgabhavane vasantānaṃ nāgānampi amanāpā, pageva manussānaṃ, yesaṃ ekaṃ kahāpaṇakaṃ uppādentānaṃ pāsāṇato maṃsaṃ uppāṭanakālo viya hotī’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
492923,111,1837,2,11,1,89,9,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto mahāvibhave brāhmaṇakule nibbatti. 
492924,111,1837,12,23,1,93,11,Tassa ādhāvitvā paridhāvitvā vicaraṇakāle aññopi puññavā satto tassa mātu kucchismiṃ nibbatti. 
492925,111,1837,24,37,1,129,13,Te ubhopi bhātaro vayappattā mātāpitūnaṃ kālakiriyāya saṃviggahadayā isipabbajjaṃ pabbajitvā gaṅgātīre paṇṇasālaṃ māpetvā vasiṃsu. 
492926,111,1837,38,46,1,67,7,"Tesu jeṭṭhassa uparigaṅgāya paṇṇasālā ahosi, kaniṭṭhassa adhogaṅgāya. "
492927,111,1837,47,73,1,234,24,"Athekadivasaṃ maṇikaṇṭho nāma nāgarājā nāgabhavanā nikkhamitvā gaṅgātīre māṇavakavesena vicaranto kaniṭṭhassa assamaṃ gantvā vanditvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi, te aññamaññaṃ sammodanīyakathaṃ kathetvā vissāsikā ahesuṃ, vinā vattituṃ nāsakkhiṃsu. "
492928,111,1837,74,105,1,308,31,Maṇikaṇṭho abhiṇhaṃ kaniṭṭhatāpasassa santikaṃ āgantvā kathāsallāpena nisīditvā gamanakāle tāpase sinehena attabhāvaṃ vijahitvā bhogehi tāpasaṃ parikkhipanto parissajitvā uparimuddhani mahantaṃ phaṇaṃ dhāretvā thokaṃ vasitvā taṃ sinehaṃ vinodetvā sarīraṃ viniveṭhetvā tāpasaṃ vanditvā sakaṭṭhānameva gacchati. 
492929,111,1837,106,115,1,87,9,Tāpaso tassa bhayena kiso ahosi lūkho dubbaṇṇo uppaṇḍuppaṇḍukajāto dhamanisanthatagatto. 
492930,111,1838,2,8,1,36,5,So ekadivasaṃ bhātu santikaṃ agamāsi. 
492931,111,1838,9,13,1,18,4,Atha naṃ so pucchi–
492932,111,1838,14,29,1,78,9,"‘‘ kissa, tvaṃ bho, kiso lūkho dubbaṇṇo uppaṇḍuppaṇḍukajāto dhamanisanthatagatto’’ ti. "
492933,111,1838,30,86,1,232,36,"So tassa taṃ pavattiṃ ārocetvā‘‘ kiṃ pana, tvaṃ bho, tassa nāgarājassa āgamanaṃ icchasi, na icchasī’’ ti puṭṭho‘‘ na icchāmī’’ ti vatvā‘‘ so pana nāgarājā tava santikaṃ āgacchanto kiṃ piḷandhanaṃ piḷandhitvā āgacchatī’’ ti vutte‘‘ maṇiratanan’’ ti āha. "
492934,111,1838,87,113,1,137,21,"Tena hi tvaṃ tasmiṃ nāgarāje tava santikaṃ āgantvā anisinneyeva‘‘ maṇiṃ me dehī’’ ti yāca, evaṃ so nāgo taṃ bhogehi aparikkhipitvāva gamissati. "
492935,111,1838,114,136,1,170,20,"Punadivase assamapadadvāre ṭhatvā āgacchantameva naṃ yāceyyāsi, tatiyadivase gaṅgātīre ṭhatvā udakā ummujjantameva naṃ yāceyyāsi, evaṃ so tava santikaṃ puna na āgamissatīti. "
492936,111,1839,2,33,1,166,21,"Tāpaso ‘‘ sādhū’’ ti paṭissuṇitvā attano paṇṇasālaṃ gantvā punadivase nāgarājānaṃ āgantvā ṭhitamattameva‘‘ etaṃ attano piḷandhanamaṇiṃ me dehī’’ ti yāci, so anisīditvāva palāyi. "
492937,111,1839,34,55,1,121,16,"Atha naṃ dutiyadivase assamapadadvāre ṭhatvā āgacchantameva‘‘ hiyyo me maṇiratanaṃ nādāsi, ajja dānaṃ laddhuṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti āha. "
492938,111,1839,56,60,1,36,4,Nāgo assamapadaṃ apavisitvāva palāyi. 
492939,111,1839,61,82,1,109,16,"Tatiyadivase udakato ummujjantameva naṃ‘‘ ajja me tatiyo divaso yācantassa, dehi dāni me etaṃ maṇiratanan’’ ti āha. "
492940,111,1839,83,91,1,59,8,Nāgarājā udake ṭhatvāva tāpasaṃ paṭikkhipanto dve gāthā āha– 
492941,111,1840,2,4,1,0,0,7.
492942,111,1841,2,11,1,55,7,"‘ ‘ Mamannapānaṃ vipulaṃ uḷāraṃ, uppajjatīmassa maṇissa hetu; "
492943,111,1842,2,12,1,56,9,"Taṃ te na dassaṃ atiyācakosi, na cāpi te assamamāgamissaṃ. "
492944,111,1843,2,4,1,0,0,8.
492945,111,1844,2,11,1,53,7,"‘ ‘ Susū yathā sakkharadhotapāṇī, tāsesimaṃ selaṃ yācamāno; "
492946,111,1845,2,15,1,59,10,"Taṃ te na dassaṃ atiyācakosi, na cāpi te assamamāgamissan’’ ti. "
492947,111,1846,2,10,1,84,7,Tattha mamannapānan ti mama yāgubhattādidibbabhojanaṃ aṭṭhapānakabhedañca dibbapānaṃ. 
492948,111,1846,11,14,1,15,3,Vipulan ti bahu. 
492949,111,1846,15,19,1,25,4,Uḷāran ti seṭṭhaṃ paṇītaṃ. 
492950,111,1846,20,26,1,25,5,Taṃ {te}ti taṃ maṇiṃ tuyhaṃ. 
492951,111,1846,27,43,1,123,14,{Atiyācakosī}ti kālañca pamāṇañca atikkamitvā ajja tīṇi divasāni mayhaṃ piyaṃ manāpaṃ maṇiratanaṃ yācamāno atikkamma yācakosi. 
492952,111,1846,44,56,1,57,10,"Na cāpi {te}ti na kevalaṃ na dassaṃ, assamampi te nāgamissaṃ. "
492953,111,1846,57,64,1,42,6,Susū {yathā}ti yathā nāma yuvā taruṇamanusso. 
492954,111,1846,65,73,1,69,6,"{Sakkharadhotapāṇī}ti sakkharāya dhotapāṇi, telena pāsāṇe dhotaasihattho. "
492955,111,1846,74,97,1,138,18,Tāsesimaṃ selaṃ {yācamāno}ti imaṃ maṇiṃ yācanto tvaṃ kañcanatharukhaggaṃ abbāhitvā‘‘ sīsaṃ te chindāmī’’ ti vadanto taruṇapuriso viya maṃ tāsesi. 
492956,111,1847,2,13,1,84,11,Evaṃ vatvā so nāgarājā udake nimujjitvā attano nāgabhavanameva gantvā na paccāgañchi. 
492957,111,1847,14,28,1,139,14,Atha so tāpaso tassa dassanīyassa nāgarājassa adassanena bhiyyosomattāya kiso ahosi lūkho dubbaṇṇo uppaṇḍuppaṇḍukajāto dhamanisanthatagatto. 
492958,111,1847,29,87,1,307,40,"Atha jeṭṭhatāpaso‘‘ kaniṭṭhassa pavattiṃ jānissāmī’’ ti tassa santikaṃ āgantvā taṃ bhiyyosomattāya paṇḍuroginaṃ disvā‘‘ kiṃ nu kho, bho, tvaṃ bhiyyosomattāya paṇḍurogī jāto’’ ti vatvā‘‘ tassa dassanīyassa nāgarājassa adassanenā’’ ti sutvā‘‘ ayaṃ tāpaso nāgarājānaṃ vinā vattituṃ na sakkotī’’ ti sallakkhetvā tatiyaṃ gāthamāha– "
492959,111,1848,2,4,1,0,0,9.
492960,111,1849,2,15,1,53,10,"‘ ‘ Na taṃ yāce yassa piyaṃ jigīse, desso hoti atiyācanāya; "
492961,111,1850,2,12,1,58,7,"Nāgo maṇiṃ yācito brāhmaṇena, adassanaṃyeva tadajjhagamā’’ ti. "
492962,111,1851,2,11,1,43,8,Tattha na taṃ {yāce}ti taṃ bhaṇḍaṃ na yāceyya. 
492963,111,1851,12,22,1,64,9,Yassa piyaṃ {jigīse}ti yaṃ bhaṇḍaṃ assa puggalassa piyanti jāneyya. 
492964,111,1851,23,28,1,24,4,Desso {hotī}ti appiyo hoti. 
492965,111,1851,29,37,1,70,7,{Atiyācanāyā}ti pamāṇaṃ atikkamitvā varabhaṇḍaṃ yācanto tāya atiyācanāya. 
492966,111,1851,38,45,1,62,6,Adassanaṃyeva {tadajjhagamā}ti tato paṭṭhāya adassanameva gatoti. 
492967,111,1852,2,21,1,96,15,Evaṃ pana taṃ vatvā‘‘ ito dāni paṭṭhāya mā socī’’ ti samassāsetvā jeṭṭhabhātā attano assamameva gato. 
492968,111,1852,22,34,1,94,11,Athāparabhāge te dvepi bhātaro abhiññā ca samāpattiyo ca nibbattetvā brahmalokaparāyaṇā ahesuṃ. 
492969,111,1853,2,29,1,171,19,"Satthā ‘‘ evaṃ, bhikkhave, sattaratanaparipuṇṇe nāgabhavane vasantānaṃ nāgānampi yācanā nāma amanāpā, kimaṅgaṃ pana manussānan’’ ti imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–"
492970,111,1853,30,44,1,56,9,"‘‘ tadā kaniṭṭho ānando ahosi, jeṭṭho pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
492971,111,1854,2,4,1,30,2,Maṇikaṇṭhajātakavaṇṇanā tatiyā.
492972,111,1856,2,7,1,34,2,[ 254]4. Kuṇḍakakucchisindhavajātakavaṇṇanā 
492973,111,1857,2,12,1,88,10,Bhutvā tiṇaparighāsan ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto sāriputtattheraṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
492974,111,1857,13,35,1,180,18,Ekasmiñhi samaye sammāsambuddhe sāvatthiyaṃ vassaṃ vasitvā cārikaṃ caritvā puna paccāgate manussā‘‘ āgantukasakkāraṃ karissāmā’’ ti buddhappamukhassa bhikkhusaṅghassa mahādānaṃ dadanti. 
492975,111,1857,36,54,1,119,16,"Vihāre ekaṃ dhammaghosakabhikkhuṃ ṭhapesuṃ, so ye ye āgantvā yattake bhikkhū icchanti, tesaṃ tesaṃ bhikkhū vicāretvā deti. "
492976,111,1858,2,28,1,182,22,Athekā duggatamahallikā itthī ekameva paṭivīsaṃ sajjetvā tesaṃ tesaṃ manussānaṃ bhikkhūsu vicāretvā dinnesu ussūre dhammaghosakassa santikaṃ āgantvā‘‘ mayhaṃ ekaṃ bhikkhuṃ dethā’’ ti āha. 
492977,111,1858,29,50,1,101,15,"So‘‘ mayā sabbe bhikkhū vicāretvā dinnā, sāriputtatthero pana vihāreyeva, tvaṃ tassa bhikkhaṃ dehī’’ ti āha. "
492978,111,1858,51,71,1,128,15,Sā‘‘ sādhū’’ ti tuṭṭhacittā jetavanadvārakoṭṭhake ṭhatvā therassa āgatakāle vanditvā hatthato pattaṃ gahetvā gharaṃ netvā nisīdāpesi.
492979,111,1858,72,88,1,95,12,‘‘ Ekāya kira mahallikāya dhammasenāpati attano ghare nisīdāpito’’ ti bahūni saddhāni kulāni assosuṃ. 
492980,111,1858,89,120,1,211,27,Tesu rājā passenadī kosalo taṃ pavattiṃ sutvā tassā sāṭakena ceva sahassatthavikāya ca saddhiṃ bhattabhājanāni pahiṇi‘‘ mayhaṃ ayyaṃ parivisamānā imaṃ sāṭakaṃ nivāsetvā ime kahāpaṇe vaḷañjetvā theraṃ parivisatū’’ ti. 
492981,111,1858,121,133,1,80,10,"Yathā ca rājā, evaṃ anāthapiṇḍiko cūḷaanāthapiṇḍiko visākhā ca mahāupāsikā pahiṇi. "
492982,111,1858,134,143,1,89,9,Aññānipi pana kulāni ekasatadvisatādivasena attano attano balānurūpena kahāpaṇe pahiṇiṃsu. 
492983,111,1858,144,150,1,51,6,Evaṃ ekāheneva sā mahallikā satasahassamattaṃ labhi. 
492984,111,1858,151,170,1,172,18,Thero pana tāya dinnayāgumeva pivitvā tāya katakhajjakameva pakkabhattameva ca paribhuñjitvā anumodanaṃ katvā taṃ mahallikaṃ sotāpattiphale patiṭṭhāpetvā vihārameva agamāsi. 
492985,111,1859,2,7,1,56,5,Dhammasabhāyaṃ bhikkhū therassa guṇakathaṃ samuṭṭhāpesuṃ–
492986,111,1859,8,19,1,78,7,"‘‘ āvuso, dhammasenāpati mahallikagahapatāniṃ duggatabhāvato mocesi, patiṭṭhā ahosi. "
492987,111,1859,20,27,1,44,5,Tāya dinnamāhāraṃ ajigucchanto paribhuñjī’’ ti. 
492988,111,1859,28,82,1,264,36,"Satthā āgantvā‘‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ imāya nāmā’’ ti vutte‘‘ na, bhikkhave, sāriputto idāneva etissā mahallikāya avassayo jāto, na ca idāneva tāya dinnaṃ āhāraṃ ajigucchanto paribhuñjati, pubbepi paribhuñjiyevā’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
492989,111,1860,2,11,1,91,9,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto uttarāpathe assavāṇijakule nibbatti. 
492990,111,1860,12,19,1,75,7,Uttarāpathajanapadato pañcasatā assavāṇijā asse bārāṇasiṃ ānetvā vikkiṇanti. 
492991,111,1860,20,26,1,68,6,Aññataropi assavāṇijo pañcaassasatāni ādāya bārāṇasimaggaṃ paṭipajji. 
492992,111,1860,27,40,1,92,12,"Antarāmagge ca bārāṇasito avidūre eko nigamagāmo atthi, tattha pubbe mahāvibhavo seṭṭhi ahosi. "
492993,111,1860,41,60,1,120,16,"Tassa mahantaṃ nivesanaṃ, taṃ pana kulaṃ anukkamena parikkhayaṃ gataṃ, ekāva mahallikā avasiṭṭhā, sā tasmiṃ nivesane vasati. "
492994,111,1860,61,81,1,113,16,Atha so assavāṇijo taṃ nigamagāmaṃ patvā‘‘ vetanaṃ dassāmī’’ ti tassā nivesane nivāsaṃ gaṇhitvā asse ekamante ṭhapesi. 
492995,111,1860,82,87,1,61,5,Taṃdivasamevassa ekissā ājānīyāvaḷavāya gabbhavuṭṭhānaṃ ahosi. 
492996,111,1860,88,106,1,87,14,So dve tayo divase vasitvā asse balaṃ gāhāpetvā‘‘ rājānaṃ passissāmī’’ ti asse ādāya pāyāsi. 
492997,111,1860,107,146,1,144,23,"Atha naṃ mahallikā‘‘ gehavetanaṃ dehī’’ ti vatvā‘‘ sādhu, amma, demī’’ ti vutte‘‘ tāta, vetanaṃ me dadamāno imampi assapotakaṃ vetanato khaṇḍetvā dehī’’ ti āha. "
492998,111,1860,147,152,1,26,4,Vāṇijo tathā katvā pakkāmi. 
492999,111,1860,153,162,1,107,9,Sā tasmiṃ assapotake puttasinehaṃ paccupaṭṭhapetvā avassāvanajhāmakabhattavighāsatiṇāni datvā taṃ paṭijaggi. 
493000,111,1861,2,12,1,84,10,Athāparabhāge bodhisatto pañca assasatāni ādāya āgacchanto tasmiṃ gehe nivāsaṃ gaṇhi. 
493001,111,1861,13,22,1,101,9,Kuṇḍakakhādakassa sindhavapotakassa ṭhitaṭṭhānato gandhaṃ ghāyitvā ekaassopi gehaṃ pavisituṃ nāsakkhi. 
493002,111,1861,23,26,1,28,3,Bodhisatto mahallikaṃ pucchi–
493003,111,1861,27,40,1,37,7,"‘‘ amma, kacci imasmiṃ gehe asso atthī’’ ti ."
493004,111,1861,41,64,1,96,16,"‘‘ Tāta, añño asso nāma natthi, ahaṃ pana puttaṃ katvā ekaṃ assapotakaṃ paṭijaggāmi, so ettha atthī’’ ti."
493005,111,1861,65,74,1,16,4,"‘‘ Kahaṃ so, ammā’’ ti?"
493006,111,1861,75,84,1,20,4,"‘‘ Carituṃ gato, tātā’’ ti."
493007,111,1861,85,95,1,30,5,"‘‘ Kāya velāya āgamissati, ammā’’ ti?"
493008,111,1861,96,104,1,15,3,"‘‘ Sāyanhe, tātā’’ ti. "
493009,111,1861,105,113,1,65,8,Bodhisatto tassa āgamanaṃ paṭimānento asse bahi ṭhapetvāva nisīdi. 
493010,111,1861,114,118,1,41,4,Sindhavapotakopi vicaritvā kāleyeva āgami. 
493011,111,1861,119,139,1,139,15,"Bodhisatto kuṇḍakakucchisindhavapotakaṃ disvā lakkhaṇāni samānetvā‘‘ ayaṃ sindhavo anaggho, mahallikāya mūlaṃ datvā gahetuṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti cintesi. "
493012,111,1861,140,146,1,62,6,Sindhavapotakopi gehaṃ pavisitvā attano vasanaṭṭhāneyeva ṭhito. 
493013,111,1861,147,154,1,46,7,Tasmiṃ khaṇe te assā gehaṃ pavisituṃ sakkhiṃsu. 
493014,111,1862,2,22,1,111,15,"Bodhisatto dvīhatīhaṃ vasitvā asse santappetvā gacchanto‘‘ amma, imaṃ assapotakaṃ mūlaṃ gahetvā mayhaṃ dehī’’ ti āha."
493015,111,1862,23,37,1,47,8,"‘‘ Kiṃ vadesi, tāta, puttaṃ vikkiṇantā nāma atthī’’ ti."
493016,111,1862,38,50,1,44,7,"‘‘ Amma, tvaṃ etaṃ kiṃ khādāpetvā paṭijaggasī’’ ti?"
493017,111,1862,51,65,1,101,9,"‘‘ Odanakañjikañca jhāmakabhattañca vighāsatiṇañca khādāpetvā kuṇḍakayāguñca pāyetvā paṭijaggāmi, tātā’’ ti."
493018,111,1862,66,85,1,116,12,"‘‘ Amma, ahaṃ etaṃ labhitvā piṇḍarasabhojanaṃ bhojessāmi, ṭhitaṭṭhāne celavitānaṃ pasāretvā attharaṇapiṭṭhe ṭhapessāmī’’ ti."
493019,111,1862,86,104,1,69,12,"‘‘ Tāta, evaṃ sante mama putto ca sukhaṃ anubhavatu, taṃ gahetvā gacchā’’ ti. "
