493071,111,1883,2,21,1,122,15,Yāva so {mattamaññāsī}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ekaṃ atibahuṃ bhuñjitvā ajīraṇena kālakataṃ bhikkhuṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
493072,111,1883,22,31,1,80,9,Tasmiṃ kira evaṃ kālakate dhammasabhāyaṃ bhikkhū tassa aguṇakathaṃ samuṭṭhāpesuṃ–
493073,111,1883,32,50,1,106,13,"‘‘ āvuso, asuko nāma bhikkhu attano kucchippamāṇaṃ ajānitvā atibahuṃ bhuñjitvā jīrāpetuṃ asakkonto kālakato’’ ti. "
493074,111,1883,51,92,1,176,24,"Satthā āgantvā‘‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ imāya nāmā’’ ti vutte‘‘ na, bhikkhave, idāneva, pubbepesa atibhojanapaccayeneva mato’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
493075,111,1884,2,18,1,171,16,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto himavantapadese sukayoniyaṃ nibbattitvā anekānaṃ sukasahassānaṃ samuddānugate himavantapadese vasantānaṃ rājā ahosi. 
