493123,111,1909,2,4,1,25,2,Sukajātakavaṇṇanā pañcamā.
493124,111,1911,2,7,1,23,2,[ 256]6. Jarūdapānajātakavaṇṇanā 
493125,111,1912,2,13,1,92,10,Jarūdapānaṃ {khaṇamānā}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto sāvatthivāsino vāṇije ārabbha kathesi. 
493126,111,1912,14,55,1,305,34,"Te kira sāvatthiyaṃ bhaṇḍaṃ gahetvā sakaṭāni pūretvā vohāratthāya gamanakāle tathāgataṃ nimantetvā saraṇāni gahetvā sīlesu patiṭṭhāya satthāraṃ vanditvā‘‘ mayaṃ, bhante, vohāratthāya dīghamaggaṃ gamissāma, bhaṇḍaṃ vissajjetvā siddhippattā sotthinā paccāgantvā pana tumhe vandissāmā’’ ti vatvā maggaṃ paṭipajjiṃsu. "
493127,111,1912,56,85,1,155,20,"Te kantāramagge purāṇaudapānaṃ disvā‘‘ imasmiṃ udapāne pānīyaṃ natthi, mayañca pipāsitā, khaṇissāma nan’’ ti khaṇantā paṭipāṭiyā bahuṃ ayaṃ… pe… veḷuriyaṃ labhiṃsu. "
493128,111,1912,86,99,1,90,11,Te teneva santuṭṭhā hutvā tesaṃ ratanānaṃ sakaṭāni pūretvā sotthinā sāvatthiṃ paccāgamiṃsu. 
493129,111,1912,100,125,1,172,21,Te ābhataṃ dhanaṃ paṭisāmetvā mayaṃ‘‘ siddhippattā bhattaṃ dassāmā’’ ti tathāgataṃ nimantetvā dānaṃ datvā vanditvā ekamantaṃ nisinnā attano dhanassa laddhākāraṃ satthu ārocesuṃ. 
493130,111,1912,126,158,1,212,27,"Satthā‘‘ tumhe kho upāsakā tena dhanena santuṭṭhā hutvā pamāṇaññutāya dhanañca jīvitañca alabhittha, porāṇakā pana asantuṭṭhā amattaññuno paṇḍitānaṃ vacanaṃ akatvā jīvikkhayaṃ pattā’’ ti vatvā tehi yācito atītaṃ āhari. "
493131,111,1913,2,14,1,126,12,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto bārāṇasiyaṃ vāṇijakule nibbattitvā vayappatto satthavāhajeṭṭhako ahosi. 
493132,111,1913,15,30,1,114,15,So bārāṇasiyaṃ bhaṇḍaṃ gahetvā sakaṭāni pūretvā bahū vāṇije ādāya tameva kantāraṃ paṭipanno tameva udapānaṃ addasa. 
493133,111,1913,31,48,1,94,13,Tattha te vāṇijā‘‘ pānīyaṃ pivissāmā’’ ti taṃ udapānaṃ khaṇantā paṭipāṭiyā bahūni ayādīni labhiṃsu. 
493134,111,1913,49,68,1,121,15,Te bahumpi ratanaṃ labhitvā tena asantuṭṭhā‘‘ aññampi ettha ito sundarataraṃ bhavissatī’’ ti bhiyyosomattāya taṃ khaṇiṃsuyeva. 
493135,111,1913,69,73,1,22,4,Atha bodhisatto te āha–
