493223,111,1952,184,198,1,35,8,"‘‘ Tena hi ayaṃ te rājadūto, ehī’’ ti āha. "
493224,111,1952,199,237,1,172,27,"Tesu hi janapadesu yaṃkiñci sakkharaṃ vā kapālakhaṇḍaṃ vā ukkhipitvā‘‘ ayaṃ te rājadūto, ehī’’ ti vutte yo na gacchati, tassa rājāṇaṃ karoti, tasmā so‘‘ rājadūto’’ ti sutvāva nikkhami. "
493225,111,1953,2,33,1,180,24,"So tena saddhiṃ rājakulaṃ gacchanto ekaṃ sahāyakassa vasanagāmaṃ patvā‘‘ bho, atichātomhi, yāva gāmaṃ pavisitvā āhārakiccaṃ katvā āgacchāmi, tāva idheva hohī’’ ti vatvā sahāyagehaṃ pāvisi. "
493226,111,1953,34,69,1,216,26,"Sahāyo panassa gehe natthi, sahāyikā disvā‘‘ sāmi, pakkāhāro natthi, muhuttaṃ adhivāsehi, idāneva pacitvā dassāmī’’ ti nisseṇiyā vegena taṇḍulakoṭṭhakaṃ abhiruhantī bhūmiyaṃ pati, taṅkhaṇaññeva tassā sattamāsiko gabbho patito. "
493227,111,1953,70,97,1,130,21,"Tasmiṃ khaṇe tassā sāmiko āgantvā taṃ disvā‘‘ tvaṃ me bhariyaṃ paharitvā gabbhaṃ pātesi, ayaṃ te rājadūto, ehī’’ ti taṃ gahetvā nikkhami. "
493228,111,1953,98,106,1,53,8,Tato paṭṭhāya dve janā gāmaṇiṃ majjhe katvā gacchanti. 
493229,111,1954,2,16,1,95,12,"Athekasmiṃ gāmadvāre eko assagopako assaṃ nivattetuṃ na sakkoti, assopi tesaṃ santikena gacchati. "
493230,111,1954,17,35,1,102,13,"Assagopako gāmaṇicandaṃ disvā‘‘ mātula gāmaṇicanda, etaṃ tāva assaṃ kenacideva paharitvā nivattehī’’ ti āha. "
493231,111,1954,36,49,1,86,12,"So ekaṃ pāsāṇaṃ gahetvā khipi, pāsāṇo assassa pāde paharitvā eraṇḍadaṇḍakaṃ viya bhindi. "
493232,111,1954,50,69,1,79,14,"Atha naṃ assagopako‘‘ tayā me assassa pādo bhinno, ayaṃ te rājadūto’’ ti vatvā gaṇhi. "
493233,111,1955,2,7,1,31,5,So tīhi janehi nīyamāno cintesi–
493234,111,1955,8,36,1,134,19,"‘‘ ime maṃ rañño dassessanti, ahaṃ goṇamūlampi dātuṃ na sakkomi, pageva gabbhapātanadaṇḍaṃ, assamūlaṃ pana kuto labhissāmi, mataṃ me seyyo’’ ti. "
493235,111,1955,37,56,1,144,18,"So gacchanto antarāmagge aṭaviyaṃ maggasamīpeyeva ekaṃ ekato papātaṃ pabbataṃ addasa, tassa chāyāya dve pitāputtā naḷakārā ekato kilañjaṃ cinanti. "
