493308,111,1971,2,3,1,6,1,Kathaṃ ? 
493309,111,1971,4,34,1,206,26,"Paṭhamaṃ tāva sāsanaṃ sutvā‘‘ pubbe tesaṃ vasanaṭṭhāne velaṃ jānitvā vassanakukkuṭo ahosi, tesaṃ tena saddena uṭṭhāya mante gahetvā sajjhāyaṃ karontānaññeva aruṇo uggacchati, tena tesaṃ gahitagahitaṃ na nassati. "
493310,111,1971,35,82,1,310,39,"Idāni pana nesaṃ vasanaṭṭhāne avelāya vassanakakukkuṭo atthi, so atirattiṃ vā vassati atipabhāte vā, atirattiṃ vassantassa tassa saddena uṭṭhāya mante gahetvā niddābhibhūtā sajjhāyaṃ akatvāva puna sayanti , atipabhāte vassantassa saddena uṭṭhāya sajjhāyituṃ na labhanti, tena tesaṃ gahitagahitaṃ na paññāyatī’’ ti āha. "
493311,111,1972,2,13,1,80,9,Dutiyaṃ sutvā‘‘ te pubbe samaṇadhammaṃ karontā kasiṇaparikamme yuttapayuttā ahesuṃ. 
493312,111,1972,14,37,1,202,21,"Idāni pana samaṇadhammaṃ vissajjetvā akattabbesu yuttapayuttā ārāme uppannāni phalāphalāni upaṭṭhākānaṃ datvā piṇḍapaṭipiṇḍakena micchājīvena jīvikaṃ kappenti, tena nesaṃ phalāphalāni na madhurāni jātāni. "
493313,111,1972,38,53,1,112,14,"Sace pana te pubbe viya puna samaṇadhamme yuttapayuttā bhavissanti, puna tesaṃ phalāphalāni madhurāni bhavissanti. "
493314,111,1972,54,69,1,86,12,"Te tāpasā rājakulānaṃ paṇḍitabhāvaṃ na jānanti, samaṇadhammaṃ tesaṃ kātuṃ vadehī’’ ti āha. "
493315,111,1973,2,17,1,83,12,"Tatiyaṃ sutvā‘‘ te nāgarājāno aññamaññaṃ kalahaṃ karonti, tena taṃ udakaṃ āvilaṃ jātaṃ. "
493316,111,1973,18,32,1,70,11,"Sace te pubbe viya samaggā bhavissanti, puna pasannaṃ bhavissatī’’ ti āha. "
493317,111,1974,2,18,1,111,13,"Catutthaṃ sutvā‘‘ sā rukkhadevatā pubbe aṭaviyaṃ paṭipanne manusse rakkhati, tasmā nānappakāraṃ balikammaṃ labhati. "
493318,111,1974,19,29,1,57,9,"Idāni pana ārakkhaṃ na karoti, tasmā balikammaṃ na labhati. "
493319,111,1974,30,39,1,65,8,"Sace pubbe viya ārakkhaṃ karissati, puna lābhaggappattā bhavissati. "
493320,111,1974,40,55,1,89,12,"Sā rājūnaṃ atthibhāvaṃ na jānāti, tasmā aṭaviāruḷhamanussānaṃ ārakkhaṃ kātuṃ vadehī’’ ti āha. "
493321,111,1975,2,28,1,144,20,"Pañcamaṃ sutvā‘‘ yasmiṃ vammikapāde nisīditvā so tittiro manāpaṃ vassati, tassa heṭṭhā mahantī nidhikumbhi atthi, taṃ uddharitvā tvaṃ gaṇhāhī’’ ti āha. "
493322,111,1976,2,46,1,266,36,"Chaṭṭhaṃ sutvā‘‘ yassa rukkhassa mūle so migo tiṇāni khādituṃ sakkoti, tassa rukkhassa upari mahantaṃ bhamaramadhu atthi, so madhumakkhitesu tiṇesu paluddho aññāni khādituṃ na sakkoti, tvaṃ taṃ madhupaṭalaṃ haritvā aggamadhuṃ amhākaṃ pahiṇa, sesaṃ attanā paribhuñjā’’ ti āha. "
493323,111,1977,2,38,1,244,30,"Sattamaṃ sutvā‘‘ yasmiṃ vammike so sappo vasati, tassa heṭṭhā mahantī nidhikumbhi atthi, so taṃ rakkhamāno vasanto nikkhamanakāle dhanalobhena sarīraṃ sithilaṃ katvā lagganto nikkhamati, gocaraṃ gahetvā dhanasinehena alagganto vegena sahasā pavisati. "
493324,111,1977,39,48,1,47,7,Taṃ nidhikumbhiṃ uddharitvā tvaṃ gaṇhāhī’’ ti āha. 
493325,111,1978,2,19,1,107,13,Aṭṭhamaṃ sutvā‘‘ tassā taruṇitthiyā sāmikassa ca mātāpitūnañca vasanagāmānaṃ antare ekasmiṃ gāmake jāro atthi. 
493326,111,1978,20,58,1,249,33,"Sā taṃ saritvā tasmiṃ sinehena sāmikassa gehe vasituṃ asakkontī‘ mātāpitaro passissāmī’ ti jārassa gehe katipāhaṃ vasitvā mātāpitūnaṃ gehaṃ gacchati, tattha katipāhaṃ vasitvā puna jāraṃ saritvā‘ sāmikassa gehaṃ gamissāmī’ ti puna jārasseva gehaṃ gacchati. "
493327,111,1978,59,69,1,73,9,Tassā itthiyā rājūnaṃ atthibhāvaṃ ācikkhitvā‘ sāmikasseva kira gehe vasatu. 
493328,111,1978,70,90,1,89,15,"Sace taṃ rājā gaṇhāpeti, jīvitaṃ te natthi, appamādaṃ kātuṃ vaṭṭatī’ ti tassā kathehī’’ ti āha. "
493329,111,1979,2,24,1,131,19,"Navamaṃ sutvā‘‘ sā gaṇikā pubbe ekassa hatthato bhatiṃ gahetvā taṃ ajīrāpetvā aññassa hatthato na gaṇhāti, tenassā pubbe bahuṃ uppajji. "
493330,111,1979,25,53,1,197,25,"Idāni pana attano dhammataṃ vissajjetvā ekassa hatthato gahitaṃ ajīrāpetvāva aññassa hatthato gaṇhāti, purimassa okāsaṃ akatvā pacchimassa karoti, tenassā bhati na uppajjati, na keci naṃ upasaṅkamanti. "
493331,111,1979,54,61,1,52,6,"Sace attano dhamme ṭhassati, pubbasadisāva bhavissati. "
493332,111,1979,62,70,1,39,6,Attano dhamme ṭhātumassā kathehī’’ ti āha. 
493333,111,1980,2,31,1,194,24,"Dasamaṃ sutvā‘‘ so gāmabhojako pubbe dhammena samena aḍḍaṃ vinicchini, tena manussānaṃ piyo ahosi manāpo, sampiyāyamānā cassa manussā bahupaṇṇākāraṃ āhariṃsu, tena abhirūpo dhanavā yasasampanno ahosi. "
493334,111,1980,32,46,1,106,13,"Idāni pana lañjavittako hutvā adhammena aḍḍaṃ vinicchinati, tena duggato kapaṇo hutvā paṇḍurogena abhibhūto. "
493335,111,1980,47,57,1,74,9,"Sace pubbe viya dhammena aḍḍaṃ vinicchinissati, puna pubbasadiso bhavissati. "
493336,111,1980,58,72,1,78,11,"So rañño atthibhāvaṃ na jānāti, dhammena aḍḍaṃ vinicchinitumassa kathehī’’ ti āha. "
493337,111,1981,2,31,1,216,27,"Iti so gāmaṇicando imāni ettakāni sāsanāni rañño ārocesi, rājā attano paññāya sabbānipi tāni sabbaññubuddho viya byākaritvā gāmaṇicandassa bahuṃ dhanaṃ datvā tassa vasanagāmaṃ brahmadeyyaṃ katvā tasseva datvā uyyojesi. "
493338,111,1981,32,83,1,459,49,So nagarā nikkhamitvā bodhisattena dinnasāsanaṃ brāhmaṇamāṇavakānañca tāpasānañca nāgarājassa ca rukkhadevatāya ca ārocetvā tittirassa vasanaṭṭhānato nidhiṃ gahetvā migassa tiṇakhādanaṭṭhāne rukkhato bhamaramadhuṃ gahetvā rañño madhuṃ pesetvā sappassa vasanaṭṭhāne vammikaṃ khaṇitvā nidhiṃ gahetvā taruṇitthiyā ca gaṇikāya ca gāmabhojakassa ca rañño kathitaniyāmeneva sāsanaṃ ārocetvā mahantena yasena attano gāmakaṃ gantvā yāvatāyukaṃ ṭhatvā yathākammaṃ gato. 
493339,111,1981,84,92,1,80,8,Ādāsamukharājāpi dānādīni puññāni katvā jīvitapariyosāne saggapuraṃ pūrento gato. 
