493477,111,2031,42,71,1,309,27,"Bhuñjanto pana antogehe na bhuñjati, attano bhojanavidhānaṃ olokentaṃ mahājanaṃ puññaṃ kāretukāmatāya rājadvāre ratanamaṇḍapaṃ kāretvā bhojanavelāya taṃ alaṅkarāpetvā kañcanamaye samussitasetacchatte rājapallaṅke nisīditvā khattiyakaññāhi parivuto satasahassagghanikāya suvaṇṇapātiyā sabbarasabhojanaṃ bhuñjati. "
493478,111,2031,72,111,1,222,28,"Atheko lolapuriso tassa bhojanavidhānaṃ oloketvā taṃ bhojanaṃ bhuñjitukāmo hutvā pipāsaṃ sandhāretuṃ asakkonto‘‘ attheko upāyo’’ ti gāḷhaṃ nivāsetvā hatthe ukkhipitvā‘‘ bho, ahaṃ dūto, dūto’’ ti uccāsaddaṃ karonto rājānaṃ upasaṅkami. "
