493550,111,2077,24,84,1,394,47,"So dhītarañca bhāgineyyañca dvepi antonivesane posento ekadivasaṃ amaccehi saddhiṃ nisinno‘‘ mamaccayena mayhaṃ bhāgineyyo rājā bhavissati, dhītāpi me tassa aggamahesī bhavissatī’’ ti vatvā aparabhāge bhāgineyyassa vayappattakāle puna amaccehi saddhiṃ nisinno‘‘ mayhaṃ bhāgineyyassa aññassa rañño dhītaraṃ ānessāma, mayhaṃ dhītarampi aññasmiṃ rājakule dassāma, evaṃ no ñātakā bahutarā bhavissantī’’ ti āha. "
