493619,111,2108,2,7,1,26,2,[ 263]3. Cūḷapalobhanajātakavaṇṇanā 
493620,111,2109,2,15,1,97,11,Abhijjamāne vārismin ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ekaṃ ukkaṇṭhitabhikkhumeva ārabbha kathesi. 
493621,111,2109,16,57,1,187,25,"Tañhi satthā dhammasabhaṃ ānītaṃ‘‘ saccaṃ kira, tvaṃ bhikkhu, ukkaṇṭhitosī’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ saccaṃ, bhante’’ ti vutte‘‘ bhikkhu, itthiyo nāmetā porāṇake suddhasattepi saṃkilesesun’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
493622,111,2110,2,18,1,94,12,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatto rājā aputtako hutvā attano itthiyo‘‘ puttapatthanaṃ karothā’’ ti āha. 
493623,111,2110,19,22,1,18,3,Tā putte patthenti. 
493624,111,2110,23,32,1,80,9,Evaṃ addhāne gate bodhisatto brahmalokā cavitvā aggamahesiyā kucchismiṃ nibbatti. 
493625,111,2110,33,39,1,57,6,Taṃ jātamattaṃ nhāpetvā thaññapāyanatthāya dhātiyā adaṃsu. 
493626,111,2110,40,48,1,42,7,"So pāyamāno rodati, atha naṃ aññissā adaṃsu. "
493627,111,2110,49,53,1,34,4,Mātugāmahatthagato neva tuṇhī hoti. 
493628,111,2110,54,64,1,69,9,"Atha naṃ ekassa pādamūlikassa adaṃsu, tena gahitamattoyeva tuṇhī ahosi. "
493629,111,2110,65,72,1,42,6,Tato paṭṭhāya purisāva taṃ gahetvā caranti. 
493630,111,2110,73,84,1,72,10,"Thaññaṃ pāyentā duhitvā vā pāyenti, sāṇiantarena vā thanaṃ mukhe ṭhapenti. "
493631,111,2110,85,90,1,43,4,Tenassa {anitthigandhakumāro}ti nāmaṃ kariṃsu. 
493632,111,2110,91,99,1,65,8,Tassa aparāparaṃ vaddhamānassapi mātugāmaṃ nāma dassetuṃ na sakkā. 
493633,111,2110,100,106,1,60,6,Tenassa rājā visuṃyeva nisajjādiṭṭhānāni jhānāgārañca kāresi. 
493634,111,2111,2,6,1,34,4,So tassa soḷasavassikakāle cintesi–
493635,111,2111,7,32,1,112,18,"‘‘ mayhaṃ añño putto natthi, ayaṃ pana kumāro kāme na paribhuñjati, rajjampi na icchissati, dulladdho vata me putto’’ ti. "
493636,111,2111,33,61,1,163,22,"Atha naṃ ekā naccagītavāditakusalā purise paricaritvā attano vase kātuṃ paṭibalā taruṇanāṭakitthī upasaṅkamitvā‘‘ deva, kiṃ nu cintesī’’ ti āha, rājā taṃ kāraṇaṃ ācikkhi."
493637,111,2111,62,77,1,54,8,"‘‘ Hotu, deva , ahaṃ taṃ palobhetvā kāmarasaṃ jānāpessāmī’’ ti."
493638,111,2111,78,96,1,95,12,"‘‘ Sace me puttaṃ anitthigandhakumāraṃ palobhetuṃ sakkissasi, so rājā bhavissati, tvaṃ aggamahesī’’ ti. "
493639,111,2111,97,113,1,78,11,"Sā‘‘ mameso bhāro, tumhe mā cintayitthā’’ ti vatvā ārakkhamanusse upasaṅkamitvā āha–"
493640,111,2111,114,124,1,83,8,‘‘ ahaṃ paccūsasamaye āgantvā ayyaputtassa sayanaṭṭhāne bahijhānāgāre ṭhatvā gāyissāmi. 
493641,111,2111,125,134,1,55,7,"Sace so kujjhati, mayhaṃ katheyyātha, ahaṃ apagacchissāmi. "
493642,111,2111,135,144,1,36,6,"Sace suṇāti, vaṇṇaṃ me katheyyāthā’’ ti. "
493643,111,2111,145,153,1,26,4,Te‘‘ sādhū’’ ti sampaṭicchiṃsu. 
493644,111,2112,2,64,1,445,52,"Sāpi paccūsakāle tasmiṃ padese ṭhatvā tantissarena gītassaraṃ, gītassarena tantissaraṃ anatikkamitvā madhurena saddena gāyi, kumāro suṇantova nipajji, punadivase ca āsannaṭṭhāne ṭhatvā gāyituṃ āṇāpesi, punadivase jhānāgāre ṭhatvā gāyituṃ āṇāpesi, punadivase attano samīpe ṭhatvāti evaṃ anukkameneva taṇhaṃ uppādetvā lokadhammaṃ sevitvā kāmarasaṃ ñatvā‘‘ mātugāmaṃ nāma aññesaṃ na dassāmī’’ ti asiṃ gahetvā antaravīthiṃ otaritvā purise anubandhanto vicari. "
493645,111,2112,65,74,1,65,9,Atha naṃ rājā gāhāpetvā tāya kumārikāya saddhiṃ nagarā nīharāpesi. 
493646,111,2112,75,92,1,138,16,"Ubhopi araññaṃ pavisitvā adhogaṅgaṃ gantvā ekasmiṃ passe gaṅgaṃ, ekasmiṃ samuddaṃ katvā ubhinnamantare assamapadaṃ māpetvā vāsaṃ kappayiṃsu. "
493647,111,2112,93,103,1,92,9,"Kumārikā paṇṇasālāyaṃ nisīditvā kandamūlādīni pacati, bodhisatto araññato phalāphalaṃ āharati. "
493648,111,2113,2,17,1,133,14,Athekadivasaṃ tasmiṃ phalāphalatthāya gate samuddadīpakā eko tāpaso bhikkhācāratthāya ākāsena gacchanto dhūmaṃ disvā assamapade otari. 
493649,111,2113,18,37,1,116,14,"Atha naṃ sā‘‘ nisīda, yāva paccatī’’ ti nisīdāpetvā itthikuttena palobhetvā jhānā cāvetvā brahmacariyamassa antaradhāpesi. "
493650,111,2113,38,55,1,142,16,So pakkhacchinnakāko viya hutvā taṃ jahituṃ asakkonto sabbadivasaṃ tattheva ṭhatvā bodhisattaṃ āgacchantaṃ disvā vegena samuddābhimukho palāyi. 
