493676,111,2128,46,79,1,236,28,"So assamaṃ gantvā taṃ itthiṃ manussapathaṃ netvā‘‘ gaccha, tvan’’ ti uyyojetvā araññaṃ pavisitvā manuññe bhūmibhāge assamaṃ māpetvā isipabbajjaṃ pabbajitvā kasiṇaparikammaṃ katvā abhiññā ca samāpattiyo ca nibbattetvā brahmalokaparāyaṇo ahosi. "
