493680,111,2132,2,7,1,23,2,[ 264]4. Mahāpanādajātakavaṇṇanā 
493681,111,2133,2,14,1,93,11,Panādo nāma so {rājā}ti idaṃ satthā gaṅgātīre nisinno bhaddajittherassānubhāvaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
493682,111,2133,15,42,1,213,22,Ekasmiñhi samaye satthā sāvatthiyaṃ vassaṃ vasitvā‘‘ bhaddajikumārassa saṅgahaṃ karissāmī’’ ti bhikkhusaṅghaparivuto cārikaṃ caramāno bhaddiyanagaraṃ patvā jātiyāvane tayo māse vasi kumārassa ñāṇaparipākaṃ āgamayamāno. 
493683,111,2133,43,48,1,71,5,Bhaddajikumāro mahāyaso asītikoṭivibhavassa bhaddiyaseṭṭhino ekaputtako. 
493684,111,2133,49,56,1,50,7,Tassa tiṇṇaṃ utūnaṃ anucchavikā tayo pāsādā ahesuṃ. 
