493687,111,2133,72,89,1,118,12,"Tasmiṃ khaṇe‘‘ kumārassa yasaṃ passissāmā’’ ti sakalanagaraṃ saṅkhubhi, pāsādantare cakkāticakkāni mañcātimañcāni bandhanti. "
