493689,111,2134,17,42,1,193,20,"Nāgarā‘‘ bhante, sve gamissathā’’ ti satthāraṃ nimantetvā dutiyadivase buddhappamukhassa bhikkhusaṅghassa mahādānaṃ sajjetvā nagaramajjhe maṇḍapaṃ katvā alaṅkaritvā āsanāni paññapetvā kālaṃ ārocesuṃ. "
