493790,111,2174,2,7,1,28,2,[ 266]6. Vātaggasindhavajātakavaṇṇanā 
493791,111,2175,2,16,1,101,12,Yenāsi kisiyā {paṇḍū}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto sāvatthiyaṃ aññataraṃ kuṭumbikaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
493792,111,2175,17,34,1,148,16,"Sāvatthiyaṃ kirekā abhirūpā itthī ekaṃ abhirūpaṃ kuṭumbikaṃ disvā paṭibaddhacittā ahosi, sakalasarīraṃ jhāyamāno viyassā abbhantare kilesaggi uppajji. "
493793,111,2175,35,51,1,99,13,"Sā neva kāyassādaṃ labhi, na cittassādaṃ, bhattampissā na rucci, kevalaṃ mañcakaaṭaniṃ gahetvā nipajji. "
493794,111,2175,52,59,1,45,7,Atha naṃ upaṭṭhāyikā ca sahāyikā ca pucchiṃsu–
493795,111,2175,60,77,1,73,12,"‘‘ kiṃ nu kho tvaṃ kampamānacittā aṭaniṃ gahetvā nipannā, kiṃ te aphāsukan’’ ti. "
493796,111,2175,78,87,1,65,9,Sā ekaṃ dve vāre akathetvā punappunaṃ vuccamānā tamatthaṃ ārocesi. 
493797,111,2175,88,116,1,153,21,"Atha naṃ tā samassāsetvā‘‘ tvaṃ mā cintayi, mayaṃ taṃ ānessāmā’’ ti vatvā gantvā kuṭumbikena saddhiṃ mantesuṃ, so paṭikkhipitvā punappunaṃ vuccamāno adhivāsesi. "
493798,111,2175,117,131,1,77,10,Tā‘‘ asukadivase asukavelāyaṃ āgacchā’’ ti paṭiññaṃ gahetvā gantvā tassā ārocesuṃ. 
493799,111,2175,132,145,1,117,13,Sā attano sayanagabbhaṃ sajjetvā attānaṃ alaṅkaritvā sayanapiṭṭhe nisinnā tasmiṃ āgantvā sayanekadese nisinne cintesi–
493800,111,2175,146,177,1,181,23,"‘‘ sacāhaṃ imassa garukaṃ akatvā idāneva okāsaṃ karissāmi, issariyaṃ me parihāyissati, āgatadivaseyeva okāsakaraṇaṃ nāma akāraṇaṃ, ajja na maṅkuṃ katvā aññasmiṃ divase okāsaṃ karissāmī’’ ti. "
