493847,111,2197,2,7,1,22,2,[ 267]7. Kakkaṭakajātakavaṇṇanā 
493848,111,2198,2,15,1,76,10,Siṅgī {migo}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto aññataraṃ itthiṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
493849,111,2198,16,31,1,145,15,Sāvatthiyaṃ kireko kuṭumbiko attano bhariyaṃ gahetvā uddhārasodhanatthāya janapadaṃ gantvā uddhāraṃ sodhetvā āgacchanto antarāmagge corehi gahito. 
493850,111,2198,32,44,1,97,11,"Bhariyā panassa abhirūpā pāsādikā dassanīyā, corajeṭṭhako tassā sinehena kuṭumbikaṃ māretuṃ ārabhi. "
493851,111,2198,45,69,1,136,19,"Sā pana itthī sīlavatī ācārasampannā patidevatā, sā corajeṭṭhakassa pādesu nipatitvā‘‘ sāmi, sace mayi sineho atthi, mā mayhaṃ sāmikaṃ mārehi. "
493852,111,2198,70,99,1,164,24,"Sace māresi, ahampi visaṃ vā khāditvā nāsavātaṃ vā sannirumbhitvā marissāmi, tayā pana saddhiṃ na gamissāmi, mā me akāraṇena sāmikaṃ mārehī’’ ti yācitvā taṃ vissajjāpesi. "
493853,111,2198,100,122,1,175,18,Te ubhopi sotthinā sāvatthiṃ patvā jetavanapiṭṭhivihārena gacchantā‘‘ vihāraṃ pavisitvā satthāraṃ vandissāmā’’ ti gandhakuṭipariveṇaṃ gantvā satthāraṃ vanditvā ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃsu. 
493854,111,2198,123,142,1,75,10,"Te satthārā‘‘ kahaṃ gatattha, upāsakā’’ ti puṭṭhā‘‘ uddhārasodhanatthāyā’’ ti āhaṃsu."
493855,111,2198,143,155,1,58,8,‘‘ Antarāmagge pana ārogyena āgatatthā’’ ti vutte kuṭumbiko āha–
493856,111,2198,156,181,1,125,17,"‘‘ antarāmagge no, bhante, corā gaṇhiṃsu, tatresā maṃ māriyamānaṃ corajeṭṭhakaṃ yācitvā mocesi, imaṃ nissāya mayā jīvitaṃ laddhan’’ ti. "
493857,111,2198,182,208,1,129,18,"Satthā‘‘ na, upāsaka, idānevetāya evaṃ tuyhaṃ jīvitaṃ dinnaṃ, pubbepi paṇḍitānampi jīvitaṃ adāsiyevā’’ ti vatvā tena yācito atītaṃ āhari. "
493858,111,2199,2,13,1,104,10,"Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente himavante mahāudakarahado, tattha mahāsuvaṇṇakakkaṭako ahosi. "
493859,111,2199,14,24,1,48,6,So tassa nivāsabhāvena‘‘ kuḷīradaho’’ ti paññāyittha. 
493860,111,2199,25,34,1,72,8,"Kakkaṭako mahā ahosi khalamaṇḍalappamāṇo, hatthī gahetvā vadhitvā khādati. "
493861,111,2199,35,45,1,65,9,Hatthī tassa bhayena tattha otaritvā gocaraṃ gaṇhituṃ na sakkonti. 
493862,111,2199,46,57,1,115,11,Tadā bodhisatto kuḷīradahaṃ upanissāya vasamānaṃ hatthiyūthajeṭṭhakaṃ paṭicca kareṇuyā kucchismiṃ paṭisandhiṃ gaṇhi. 
493863,111,2199,58,74,1,96,12,Athassa mātā‘‘ gabbhaṃ rakkhissāmī’’ ti aññaṃ pabbatappadesaṃ gantvā gabbhaṃ rakkhitvā puttaṃ vijāyi. 
493864,111,2199,75,86,1,93,10,So anukkamena viññutaṃ patto mahāsarīro thāmasampanno sobhaggappatto añjanapabbato viya ahosi. 
493865,111,2199,87,120,1,189,24,"So ekāya kareṇuyā saddhiṃ saṃvāsaṃ kappetvā‘‘ kakkaṭakaṃ gaṇhissāmī’’ ti attano bhariyañca mātarañca ādāya taṃ hatthiyūthaṃ upasaṅkamitvā pitaraṃ passitvā‘‘ tāta, ahaṃ kakkaṭakaṃ gaṇhissāmī’’ ti āha. "
493866,111,2199,121,144,1,90,14,"Atha naṃ pitā‘‘ na sakkhissasi, tātā’’ ti vāretvā punappunaṃ vadantaṃ‘‘ tvaññeva jānissasī’’ ti āha. "
493867,111,2200,2,57,1,324,40,"So kuḷīradahaṃ upanissāya vasante sabbavāraṇe sannipātetvā sabbehi saddhiṃ dahasamīpaṃ gantvā‘‘ kiṃ so kakkaṭako otaraṇakāle gaṇhāti, udāhu gocaraṃ gaṇhanakāle, udāhu uttaraṇakāle’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ uttaraṇakāle’’ ti sutvā‘‘ tena hi tumhe kuḷīradahaṃ otaritvā yāvadatthaṃ gocaraṃ gahetvā paṭhamaṃ uttaratha, ahaṃ pacchato bhavissāmī’’ ti āha. "
493868,111,2200,58,61,1,20,3,Vāraṇā tathā kariṃsu. 
493869,111,2200,62,80,1,157,17,"Kuḷīro pacchato uttarantaṃ bodhisattaṃ mahāsaṇḍāsena kammāro lohasalākaṃ viya aḷadvayena pāde daḷhaṃ gaṇhi, kareṇukā bodhisattaṃ avijahitvā samīpeyeva aṭṭhāsi. "
493870,111,2200,81,94,1,98,12,"Bodhisatto ākaḍḍhanto kuḷīraṃ cāletuṃ nāsakkhi, kuḷīro pana taṃ ākaḍḍhanto attano abhimukhaṃ karoti. "
493871,111,2200,95,114,1,170,17,"So maraṇabhayatajjito baddharavaṃ ravi, sabbe vāraṇā maraṇabhayatajjitā koñcanādaṃ katvā muttakarīsaṃ cajamānā palāyiṃsu, kareṇukāpissa saṇṭhātuṃ asakkontī palāyituṃ ārabhi. "
493872,111,2201,2,13,1,82,10,Atha naṃ so attano baddhabhāvaṃ saññāpetvā tassā apalāyanatthaṃ paṭhamaṃ gāthamāha– 
