493905,111,2217,2,7,1,24,2,[ 268]8. Ārāmadūsakajātakavaṇṇanā 
493906,111,2218,2,13,1,99,11,Yo ve sabbasametānan ti idaṃ satthā dakkhiṇāgirijanapade aññataraṃ uyyānapālaputtaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
