494024,111,2285,2,13,1,84,10,Sabbehi kira {ñātīhī}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto kākolūkakalahaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
494025,111,2285,14,33,1,147,18,"Tasmiñhi kāle kākā divā ulūke khādanti, ulūkā sūriyatthaṅgamanato paṭṭhāya tattha tattha sayitānaṃ kākānaṃ sīsāni chinditvā te jīvitakkhayaṃ pāpenti. "
494026,111,2285,34,48,1,164,14,Athekassa bhikkhuno jetavanapaccante ekasmiṃ pariveṇe vasantassa sammajjanakāle rukkhato patitāni sattaṭṭhanāḷimattānipi bahutarānipi kākasīsāni chaḍḍetabbāni honti. 
494027,111,2285,49,53,1,31,4,So tamatthaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ ārocesi. 
494028,111,2285,54,58,1,43,4,Bhikkhū dhammasabhāyaṃ kathaṃ samuṭṭhāpesuṃ–
494029,111,2285,59,79,1,104,13,"‘‘ āvuso, amukassa kira bhikkhuno vasanaṭṭhāne divase divase ettakāni nāma kākasīsāni chaḍḍetabbāni hontī’’ ti. "
494030,111,2285,80,135,1,246,33,"Satthā āgantvā‘‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā’’ ti pucchi, bhikkhū‘‘ imāya nāmā’’ ti vatvā‘‘ kadā paṭṭhāya pana, bhante, kākānañca ulūkānañca aññamaññaṃ veraṃ uppannan’’ ti pucchiṃsu, satthā‘‘ paṭhamakappikakālato paṭṭhāyā’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
494031,111,2286,2,30,1,245,26,"Atīte paṭhamakappikā manussā sannipatitvā ekaṃ abhirūpaṃ sobhaggappattaṃ ācārasampannaṃ sabbākāraparipuṇṇaṃ purisaṃ gahetvā rājānaṃ kariṃsu, catuppadāpi sannipatitvā ekaṃ sīhaṃ rājānaṃ akaṃsu, mahāsamudde macchā ānandaṃ nāma macchaṃ rājānaṃ akaṃsu. "
494032,111,2286,31,48,1,125,14,"Tato sakuṇagaṇā himavantapadese ekasmiṃ piṭṭhipāsāṇe sannipatitvā‘‘ manussesu rājā paññāyati, tathā catuppadesu ceva macchesu ca. "
494033,111,2286,49,72,1,144,18,"Amhākaṃ panantare rājā nāma natthi, appatissavāso nāma na vaṭṭati, amhākampi rājānaṃ laddhuṃ vaṭṭati, ekaṃ rājaṭṭhāne ṭhapetabbayuttakaṃ jānāthā’’ ti. "
494034,111,2286,73,89,1,76,12,Te tādisaṃ sakuṇaṃ olokayamānā ekaṃ ulūkaṃ rocetvā‘‘ ayaṃ no ruccatī’’ ti āhaṃsu. 
494035,111,2286,90,96,1,62,6,Atheko sakuṇo sabbesaṃ ajjhāsayaggahaṇatthaṃ tikkhattuṃ sāvesi. 
494036,111,2286,97,145,1,337,41,"Tassa sāventassa dve sāvanā adhivāsetvā tatiyasāvanāya eko kāko uṭṭhāya‘‘ tiṭṭha tāvetassa imasmiṃ rājābhisekakāle evarūpaṃ mukhaṃ bhavati, kuddhassa kīdisaṃ bhavissati, iminā hi kuddhena olokitā mayaṃ tattakapāle pakkhittaloṇaṃ viya tattha tattheva bhijjissāma, imaṃ rājānaṃ kātuṃ mayhaṃ na ruccatī’’ ti imamatthaṃ pakāsetuṃ paṭhamaṃ gāthamāha– "
494037,111,2287,2,4,1,0,0,58.
494038,111,2288,2,13,1,38,7,"‘ ‘ Sabbehi kira ñātīhi, kosiyo issaro kato; "
494039,111,2289,2,10,1,44,5,"Sace ñātīhanuññāto, bhaṇeyyāhaṃ ekavācikan’’ ti. "
494040,111,2290,2,12,1,48,8,"Tassattho – yā esā sāvanā vattati, taṃ sutvā vadāmi. "
494041,111,2290,13,22,1,58,9,Sabbehi kira imehi samāgatehi ñātīhi ayaṃ kosiyo rājā kato. 
494042,111,2290,23,34,1,83,10,"Sace panāhaṃ ñātīhi anuññāto bhaveyyaṃ, ettha vattabbaṃ ekavācikaṃ kiñci bhaṇeyyanti. "
494043,111,2291,2,9,1,47,6,Atha naṃ anujānantā sakuṇā dutiyaṃ gāthamāhaṃsu– 
