494045,111,2293,2,11,1,45,7,"‘ ‘ Bhaṇa samma anuññāto, atthaṃ dhammañca kevalaṃ; "
494046,111,2294,2,12,1,47,7,"Santi hi daharā pakkhī, paññavanto jutindharā’’ ti. "
494047,111,2295,2,24,1,100,15,"Tattha bhaṇa, samma, {anuññāto}ti, samma, vāyasa tvaṃ amhehi sabbehi anuññāto, yaṃ te bhaṇitabbaṃ, taṃ bhaṇa. "
494048,111,2295,25,36,1,90,11,Atthaṃ dhammañca kevalan ti bhaṇanto ca kāraṇañceva paveṇiāgatañca vacanaṃ amuñcitvā bhaṇa. 
494049,111,2295,37,47,1,88,9,Paññavanto {jutindharā}ti paññāsampannā ceva ñāṇobhāsadharā ca daharāpi pakkhino atthiyeva. 
