494053,111,2299,2,12,1,51,7,"Akkuddhassa mukhaṃ passa, kathaṃ kuddho karissatī’’ ti. "
494054,111,2300,2,20,1,120,15,"Tassattho – bhaddaṃ tumhākaṃ hotu, yaṃ panetaṃ tikkhattuṃ sāvanavācāya ulūkassa abhisecanaṃ karīyati, etaṃ mayhaṃ na ruccati. "
494055,111,2300,21,41,1,138,18,"Etassa hi idāni tuṭṭhacittassa akkuddhassa mukhaṃ passatha, kuddho panāyaṃ kathaṃ karissatīti na jānāmi, sabbathāpi etaṃ mayhaṃ na ruccatīti. "
494056,111,2301,2,25,1,105,17,"So evaṃ vatvā‘‘ mayhaṃ na ruccati, mayhaṃ na ruccatī’’ ti viravanto ākāse uppati, ulūkopi naṃ uṭṭhāya anubandhi. "
