494171,111,2360,2,10,1,38,6,"‘ ‘ Ahaṃ kapismi dummedho, anāmāsāni āmasiṃ; "
494172,111,2361,2,14,1,54,9,"Tvaṃ maṃ mocaya bhaddaṃ te, mutto gaccheyya pabbatan’’ ti. "
494173,111,2362,2,14,1,80,11,Tattha ahaṃ kapismi {dummedho}ti bhaddaṃ te ahaṃ asmi dummedho capalacitto makkaṭo. 
494174,111,2362,15,20,1,47,5,Anāmāsāni āmasin ti anāmasitabbaṭṭhānāni āmasiṃ. 
494175,111,2362,21,38,1,92,15,"Tvaṃ maṃ mocaya bhaddaṃ {te}ti tvaṃ dayālu anukampako maṃ imamhā dukkhā mocehi, bhaddaṃ te hotu. "
494176,111,2362,39,57,1,134,17,"Mutto gaccheyya pabbatan ti sohaṃ tavānubhāvena imamhā byasanā mutto pabbatameva gaccheyyaṃ, na te puna cakkhupathe attānaṃ dasseyyanti. "
494177,111,2363,2,10,1,75,8,Bodhisatto tasmiṃ kāruññena kacchapena saddhiṃ sallapanto tatiyaṃ gāthamāha– 
