494180,111,2366,2,12,1,48,7,"Muñca kassapa koṇḍaññaṃ, kataṃ methunakaṃ tayā’’ ti. "
494181,111,2367,2,17,1,123,11,"Tassattho – kacchapā nāma kassapagottā honti, makkaṭā koṇḍaññagottā, kassapakoṇḍaññānañca aññamaññaṃ āvāhavivāhasambandho atthi. "
494182,111,2367,18,46,1,222,23,"Addhā tayidaṃ lolena dussīlamakkaṭena tayā saddhiṃ, tayā ca dussīlena iminā makkaṭena saddhiṃ gottasadisatāsaṅkhātassa methunadhammassa anucchavikaṃ dussīlyakammasaṅkhātampi methunakaṃ kataṃ, tasmā muñca, kassapa, koṇḍaññan ti. "
494183,111,2368,2,11,1,79,9,Kacchapo bodhisattassa vacanaṃ sutvā kāraṇena pasanno vānarassa aṅgajātaṃ muñci. 
