494190,111,2372,2,7,1,17,2,[ 274]4. Lolajātakavaṇṇanā 
494191,111,2373,2,14,1,87,11,Kāyaṃ balākā {sikhinī}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ekaṃ lolabhikkhuṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
494192,111,2373,15,48,1,202,26,"Tañhi dhammasabhaṃ ānītaṃ satthā‘‘ na tvaṃ bhikkhu idāneva lolo, pubbepi loloyeva, lolatāyeva ca jīvitakkhayaṃ patto, taṃ nissāya porāṇakapaṇḍitāpi attano vasanaṭṭhānā paribāhirā ahesun’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
494193,111,2374,2,13,1,115,11,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bārāṇasiseṭṭhino mahānase bhattakārako puññatthāya nīḷapacchiṃ ṭhapesi. 
494194,111,2374,14,21,1,64,7,Tadā bodhisatto pārāvatayoniyaṃ nibbattitvā tattha vāsaṃ kappesi. 
494195,111,2374,22,63,1,278,32,Atheko lolakāko mahānasamatthakena gacchanto nānappakāraṃ macchamaṃsavikatiṃ disvā pipāsābhibhūto‘‘ kaṃ nu kho nissāya sakkā bhaveyyaṃ okāsaṃ laddhun’’ ti cintetvā bodhisattaṃ disvā‘‘ imaṃ nissāya sakkā’’ ti sanniṭṭhānaṃ katvā tassa gocarāya araññagamanakāle piṭṭhito piṭṭhito anubandhi. 
494196,111,2374,64,88,1,97,16,"Atha naṃ bodhisatto‘‘ mayaṃ kho, kāka, aññagocarā, tvampi aññagocaro, kiṃ nu kho maṃ anubandhasī’’ ti āha."
494197,111,2374,89,110,1,97,13,"‘‘ Tumhākaṃ, sāmi, kiriyā mayhaṃ ruccati, ahampi tumhehi samānagocaro hutvā tumhe upaṭṭhātuṃ icchāmī’’ ti. "
494198,111,2374,111,113,1,22,2,Bodhisatto sampaṭicchi. 
494199,111,2374,114,151,1,253,31,"So tena saddhiṃ gocarabhūmiyaṃ ekagocaraṃ caranto viya osakkitvā gomayarāsiṃ viddhaṃsetvā pāṇake khāditvā kucchipūraṃ katvā bodhisattaṃ upasaṅkamitvā‘‘ tumhe ettakaṃ kālaṃ caratheva, nanu bhojane nāma pamāṇaṃ ñātuṃ vaṭṭati, etha nātisāyameva gacchāmā’’ ti āha. "
494200,111,2374,152,157,1,42,5,Bodhisatto taṃ ādāya vasanaṭṭhānaṃ agamāsi. 
494201,111,2374,158,173,1,90,11,Bhattakārako‘‘ amhākaṃ pārāvato sahāyaṃ gahetvā āgato’’ ti kākassāpi ekaṃ thusapacchiṃ ṭhapesi. 
494202,111,2374,174,179,1,42,5,Kākopi catūhapañcāhaṃ teneva nīhārena vasi. 
494203,111,2375,2,16,1,123,12,"Athekadivasaṃ seṭṭhino bahumacchamaṃsaṃ āhariyittha, kāko taṃ disvā lobhābhibhūto paccūsakālato paṭṭhāya nitthunanto nipajji. "
494204,111,2375,17,33,1,69,10,"Atha naṃ punadivase bodhisatto‘‘ ehi, samma, gocarāya pakkamissāmā’’ ti āha."
494205,111,2375,34,45,1,43,6,"‘‘ Tumhe gacchatha, mayhaṃ ajiṇṇāsaṅkā atthī’’ ti."
494206,111,2375,46,79,1,182,23,"‘‘ Samma, kākānaṃ ajīrako nāma natthi, dīpavaṭṭimattameva hi tumhākaṃ kucchiyaṃ thokaṃ tiṭṭhati, sesaṃ ajjhohaṭamattameva jīrati, mama vacanaṃ karohi, mā etaṃ macchamaṃsaṃ disvā evamakāsī’’ ti."
494207,111,2375,80,93,1,49,7,"‘‘ Sāmi, kiṃ nāmetaṃ kathetha, ajiṇṇāsaṅkāva mayhan’’ ti."
494208,111,2375,94,107,1,57,9,‘‘ Tena hi appamatto hohī’’ ti taṃ ovaditvā bodhisatto pakkāmi. 
494209,111,2376,2,10,1,95,8,Bhattakārakopi nānāmacchamaṃsavikatiyo sampādetvā sarīrato sedaṃ apanento mahānasadvāre aṭṭhāsi. 
494210,111,2376,11,25,1,72,10,Kāko‘‘ ayaṃ idāni kālo maṃsaṃ khāditun’’ ti gantvā rasakaroṭimatthake nisīdi. 
494211,111,2376,26,70,1,320,35,"Bhattakārako‘‘ kirī’’ ti saddaṃ sutvā nivattitvā olokento kākaṃ disvā pavisitvā taṃ gahetvā sakalasarīralomaṃ luñcitvā matthake cūḷaṃ ṭhapetvā siṅgīveramaricādīni pisitvā takkena āloḷetvā‘‘ tvaṃ amhākaṃ seṭṭhino macchamaṃsaṃ ucchiṭṭhakaṃ karosī’’ ti sakalasarīramassa makkhetvā khipitvā nīḷapacchiyaṃ pātesi, balavavedanā uppajji. "
494212,111,2376,71,81,1,88,10,Bodhisatto gocarabhūmito āgantvā taṃ nitthunantaṃ disvā davaṃ karonto paṭhamaṃ gāthamāha– 
