494214,111,2378,2,10,1,40,6,"‘ ‘ Kāyaṃ balākā sikhinī, corī laṅghipitāmahā; "
494215,111,2379,2,13,1,44,8,"Oraṃ balāke āgaccha, caṇḍo me vāyaso sakhā’’ ti. "
494216,111,2380,2,28,1,160,20,Tattha kāyaṃ balākā {sikhinī}ti taṃ kākaṃ tassa bahalatakkena makkhitasarīrasetavaṇṇattā matthake ca sikhāya ṭhapitattā‘‘ kā esā balākā sikhinī’’ ti pucchanto ālapati. 
494217,111,2380,29,47,1,90,12,"{Corī}ti kulassa ananuññāya kulagharaṃ, kākassa vā aruciyā pacchiṃ paviṭṭhattā‘‘ corī’’ ti vadati. "
494218,111,2380,48,69,1,147,18,"{Laṅghipitāmahā}ti laṅghī vuccati ākāse laṅghanato megho, balākā ca nāma meghasaddena gabbhaṃ gaṇhantīti meghasaddo balākānaṃ pitā, megho pitāmaho hoti. "
494219,111,2380,70,77,1,24,3,Tenāha‘‘ laṅghipitāmahā’’ ti. 
494220,111,2380,78,88,1,42,7,"Oraṃ balāke {āgacchā}ti, ambho balāke, ito ehi. "
494221,111,2380,89,127,1,230,32,"Caṇḍo me vā yaso {sakhā}ti mayhaṃ sakhā pacchisāmiko vāyaso caṇḍo pharuso , so āgato taṃ disvā kaṇayasadisena tuṇḍena koṭṭetvā jīvitakkhayaṃ pāpeyya, tasmā yāva vāyaso nāgacchati, tāva pacchito otaritvā ito ehi, sīghaṃ palāyassūti vadati. "
