494265,111,2411,2,7,1,23,2,[ 276]6. Kurudhammajātakavaṇṇanā 
494266,111,2412,2,14,1,97,11,Tava saddhañca {sīlañcā}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ekaṃ haṃsaghātakabhikkhuṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
494267,111,2412,15,25,1,89,9,Sāvatthivāsino dve sahāyakā bhikkhū pabbajitvā laddhūpasampadā yebhuyyena ekato vicaranti. 
494268,111,2412,26,44,1,142,17,"Te ekadivasaṃ aciravatiṃ gantvā nhatvā vālukapuline ātapaṃ tappamānā sāraṇīyakathaṃ kathentā aṭṭhaṃsu, tasmiṃ khaṇe dve haṃsā ākāsena gacchanti. "
494269,111,2412,45,70,1,114,15,"Atheko daharabhikkhu sakkharaṃ gahetvā‘‘ ekassa haṃsapotakassa akkhiṃ paharissāmī’’ ti āha, itaro‘‘ na sakkhissasī’’ ti āha."
494270,111,2412,71,84,1,60,8,"‘‘ Tiṭṭhatu imasmiṃ passe akkhi, parapasse akkhiṃ paharissāmī’’ ti."
494271,111,2412,85,93,1,28,4,‘‘ Idampi na sakkhissasiyevā’’ ti.
494272,111,2412,94,108,1,75,10,‘‘ Tena hi upadhārehī’’ ti tiyaṃsaṃ sakkharaṃ gahetvā haṃsassa pacchābhāge khipi. 
494273,111,2412,109,125,1,137,15,"Haṃso sakkharasaddaṃ sutvā nivattitvā olokesi, atha naṃ itaro vaṭṭasakkharaṃ gahetvā parapasse akkhimhi paharitvā orimakkhinā nikkhamāpesi. "
