494346,111,2435,2,38,1,307,31,"Evaṃ hatthikkhandhavaragatova mahāsatto vācāya datvā puna hatthikkhandhā oruyha‘‘ sace analaṅkataṭṭhānaṃ atthi, alaṅkaritvā dassāmī’’ ti vatvā tikkhattuṃ padakkhiṇaṃ karonto upadhāretvā analaṅkataṭṭhānaṃ adisvā tassa soṇḍaṃ brāhmaṇānaṃ hatthesu ṭhapetvā suvaṇṇabhiṅkārena pupphagandhavāsitaṃ udakaṃ pātetvā adāsi. "
494347,111,2435,39,57,1,137,16,"Brāhmaṇā saparivāraṃ nāgaṃ sampaṭicchitvā hatthipiṭṭhe nisinnā dantapuraṃ gantvā hatthiṃ rañño adaṃsu, hatthimhi āgatepi devo na vassateva. "
494348,111,2435,58,126,1,393,51,"Rājā‘‘ kiṃ nu kho kāraṇan’’ ti uttariṃ pucchanto‘‘ dhanañcayakorabyarājā kurudhammaṃ rakkhati, tenassa raṭṭhe anvaḍḍhamāsaṃ anudasāhaṃ devo vassati, rañño guṇānubhāvo cesa, imassa pana tiracchānagatassa guṇā hontāpi kittakā bhaveyyun’’ ti sutvā‘‘ tena hi yathālaṅkatameva saparivāraṃ hatthiṃ patinetvā rañño datvā yaṃ so kurudhammaṃ rakkhati, taṃ suvaṇṇapaṭṭe likhitvā ānethā’’ ti brāhmaṇe ca amacce ca pesesi. "
494349,111,2435,127,164,1,212,29,"Te gantvā rañño hatthiṃ niyyādetvā‘‘ deva, imasmiṃ hatthimhi gatepi amhākaṃ raṭṭhe devo na vassati, tumhe kira kurudhammaṃ nāma rakkhatha, amhākampi rājā taṃ rakkhitukāmo imasmiṃ suvaṇṇapaṭṭe likhitvā ānethā’’ ti pesesi."
494350,111,2435,165,173,1,23,4,‘‘ Detha no kurudhamman’’ ti.
494351,111,2435,174,205,1,145,23,"‘‘ Tātā, saccāhaṃ etaṃ kurudhammaṃ rakkhāmi, idāni pana me tattha kukkuccaṃ atthi, na me so kurudhammo cittaṃ ārādheti, tasmā tumhākaṃ dātuṃ na sakkā’’ ti. "
494352,111,2436,2,9,1,42,7,Kasmā pana taṃ sīlaṃ rājānaṃ na ārādhetīti? 
494353,111,2436,10,38,1,237,27,"Tadā kira rājūnaṃ tatiye tatiye saṃvacchare kattikamāse pavatto chaṇo nāma hoti, taṃ chaṇaṃ kīḷantā rājāno sabbālaṅkārapaṭimaṇḍitā devavesaṃ gahetvā cittarājassa nāma yakkhassa santike ṭhatvā catuddisā pupphapaṭimaṇḍite cittasare khipanti. "
494354,111,2436,39,62,1,185,23,Ayampi rājā taṃ khaṇaṃ kīḷanto ekissā taḷākapāḷiyā cittarājassa yakkhassa santike ṭhatvā catuddisā cittasare khipitvā tesu sesadisāgate tayo sare disvā udakapiṭṭhe khittasaraṃ na addasa. 
494355,111,2436,63,87,1,135,19,"Rañño‘‘ kacci nu kho mayā khitto saro macchasarīre patito’’ ti kukkuccaṃ ahosi pāṇātipātakammena sīlabhedaṃ ārabbha, tasmā sīlaṃ na ārādheti. "
494356,111,2436,88,90,1,10,2,So evamāha–
494357,111,2436,91,112,1,98,14,"‘‘ tātā, mayhaṃ kurudhamme kukkuccaṃ atthi, mātā pana me surakkhitaṃ rakkhati, tassā santike gaṇhathā’’ ti."
494358,111,2436,113,141,1,125,19,"‘‘ Mahārāja, tumhākaṃ‘ pāṇaṃ vadhissāmī’ ti cetanā natthi, taṃ vinā pāṇātipāto nāma na hoti, detha no attanā rakkhitaṃ kurudhamman’’ ti."
494359,111,2436,142,152,1,42,6,‘‘ Tena hi likhathā’’ ti suvaṇṇapaṭṭe likhāpesi–
494360,111,2436,153,198,1,187,30,"‘‘ pāṇo na hantabbo, adinnaṃ nādātabbaṃ , kāmesu micchā na caritabbaṃ, musā na bhaṇitabbaṃ , majjaṃ na pātabban’’ ti likhāpetvā ca pana‘‘ evaṃ santepi neva maṃ ārādheti, mātu me santike gaṇhathā’’ ti āha. "
494361,111,2437,2,24,1,105,16,"Dūtā rājānaṃ vanditvā tassā santikaṃ gantvā‘‘ devi, tumhe kira kurudhammaṃ rakkhatha, taṃ no dethā’’ ti vadiṃsu."
