494370,111,2437,122,132,1,57,7,"Kaniṭṭhasuṇisā pana duggatā, tassā candanasāraṃ dassāmī’’ ti. "
494371,111,2437,133,179,1,286,36,"Sā rañño deviyā suvaṇṇamālaṃ datvā uparājabhariyāya candanasāraṃ adāsi, datvā ca panassā‘‘ ahaṃ kurudhammaṃ rakkhāmi, etāsaṃ duggatāduggatabhāvo mayhaṃ appamāṇaṃ, jeṭṭhāpacāyikakammameva pana kātuṃ mayhaṃ anurūpaṃ, kacci nu kho me tassa akatattā sīlaṃ bhinnan’’ ti kukkuccaṃ ahosi, tasmā evamāha. "
494372,111,2437,180,219,1,225,31,"Atha naṃ dūtā‘‘ attano santakaṃ nāma yathāruciyā dīyati, tumhe ettakenapi kukkuccaṃ kurumānā kiṃ aññaṃ pāpaṃ karissatha, sīlaṃ nāma evarūpena na bhijjati, detha no kurudhamman’’ ti vatvā tassāpi santike gahetvā suvaṇṇapaṭṭe likhiṃsu."
494373,111,2438,2,32,1,167,24,"‘ ‘ Tātā, evaṃ santepi neva maṃ ārādheti, suṇisā pana me suṭṭhu rakkhati, tassā santike gaṇhathā’’ ti vuttā ca pana aggamahesiṃ upasaṅkamitvā purimanayeneva kurudhammaṃ yāciṃsu. "
494374,111,2438,33,52,1,81,14,"Sāpi purimanayeneva vatvā‘‘ idāni maṃ sīlaṃ nārādheti, tena vo dātuṃ na sakkā’’ ti āha. "
494375,111,2438,53,88,1,240,30,"Sā kira ekadivasaṃ sīhapañjare ṭhitā rañño nagaraṃ padakkhiṇaṃ karontassa pacchato hatthipiṭṭhe nisinnaṃ uparājaṃ disvā lobhaṃ uppādetvā‘‘ sacāhaṃ iminā saddhiṃ santhavaṃ kareyyaṃ, bhātu accayena rajje patiṭṭhito maṃ esa saṅgaṇheyyā’’ ti cintesi. "
494376,111,2438,89,115,1,150,19,"Athassā‘‘ ahaṃ kurudhammaṃ rakkhamānā sasāmikā hutvā kilesavasena aññaṃ purisaṃ olokesiṃ, sīlena me bhinnena bhavitabban’’ ti kukkuccaṃ ahosi, tasmā evamāha. "
494377,111,2438,116,153,1,221,29,"Atha naṃ dūtā‘‘ aticāro nāma ayye cittuppādamattena na hoti, tumhe ettakenapi kukkuccaṃ kurumānā vītikkamaṃ kiṃkarissatha, na ettakena sīlaṃ bhijjati, detha no kurudhamman’’ ti vatvā tassāpi santike gahetvā suvaṇṇapaṭṭe likhiṃsu."
494378,111,2439,2,31,1,164,23,"‘ ‘ Tātā, evaṃ santepi neva maṃ ārādheti, uparājā pana suṭṭhu rakkhati, tassa santike gaṇhathā’’ ti vuttā ca pana uparājānaṃ upasaṅkamitvā purimanayeneva kurudhammaṃ yāciṃsu. "
494379,111,2439,32,53,1,158,20,"So pana sāyaṃ rājupaṭṭhānaṃ gacchanto ratheneva rājaṅgaṇaṃ patvā sace rañño santike bhuñjitvā tattheva sayitukāmo hoti, rasmiyo ca patodañca antodhure chaḍḍeti. "
494380,111,2439,54,65,1,91,11,Tāya saññāya jano pakkamitvā punadivase pātova gantvā tassa nikkhamanaṃ olokentova tiṭṭhati. 
494381,111,2439,66,76,1,73,9,Sārathipi rathaṃ gopayitvā punadivase pātova taṃ ādāya rājadvāre tiṭṭhati. 
494382,111,2439,77,89,1,104,11,"Sace taṅkhaṇaññeva nikkhantukāmo hoti, rasmiyo ca patodañca antoratheyeva ṭhapetvā rājupaṭṭhānaṃ gacchati. "
494383,111,2439,90,102,1,69,8,Mahājano tāya saññāya‘‘ idāneva nikkhamissatī’’ ti rājadvāreyeva tiṭṭhati. 
494384,111,2439,103,113,1,82,9,"So ekadivasaṃ evaṃ katvā rājanivesanaṃ pāvisi, paviṭṭhamattassayevassa devo pāvassi. "
494385,111,2439,114,130,1,71,11,"Rājā‘‘ devo vassatī’’ ti tassa nikkhantuṃ nādāsi, so tattheva bhuñjitvā sayi. "
494386,111,2439,131,142,1,59,7,Mahājano‘‘ idāni nikkhamissatī’’ ti sabbarattiṃ temento aṭṭhāsi. 
494387,111,2439,143,195,1,293,40,"Uparājā dutiyadivase nikkhamitvā temetvā ṭhitaṃ mahājanaṃ disvā‘‘ ahaṃ kurudhammaṃ rakkhanto ettakaṃ janaṃ kilamesiṃ, sīlena me bhinnena bhavitabban’’ ti kukkuccaṃ ahosi, tena tesaṃ dūtānaṃ‘‘ saccāhaṃ kurudhammaṃ rakkhāmi, idāni pana me kukkuccaṃ atthi, tena vo na sakkā dātun’’ ti vatvā tamatthaṃ ārocesi. "
494388,111,2439,196,235,1,214,29,"Atha naṃ dūtā‘‘ tumhākaṃ, deva,‘ ete kilamantū’ ti cittaṃ natthi, acetanakaṃ kammaṃ na hoti, ettakenapi kukkuccaṃ karontānaṃ kathaṃ tumhākaṃ vītikkamo bhavissatī’’ ti vatvā tassapi santike sīlaṃ gahetvā suvaṇṇapaṭṭe likhiṃsu."
494389,111,2440,2,27,1,132,20,"‘ ‘ Evaṃ santepi neva maṃ ārādheti, purohito pana suṭṭhu rakkhati, tassa santike gaṇhathā’’ ti vuttā ca pana purohitaṃ upasaṅkamitvā yāciṃsu. "
494390,111,2440,28,80,1,272,37,"Sopi ekadivasaṃ rājupaṭṭhānaṃ gacchanto ekena raññā tassa rañño pesitaṃ taruṇaravivaṇṇaṃ rathaṃ antarāmagge disvā‘‘ kassāyaṃ ratho’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ rañño ābhato’’ ti sutvā‘‘ ahaṃ mahallako, sace me rājā imaṃ rathaṃ dadeyya, sukhaṃ imaṃ āruyha vicareyyan’’ ti cintetvā rājupaṭṭhānaṃ gato. "
494391,111,2440,81,88,1,47,6,Tassa jayāpetvā ṭhitakāle rañño rathaṃ dassesuṃ. 
494392,111,2440,89,106,1,66,12,"Rājā disvā‘‘ ati viya sundaro ayaṃ ratho, ācariyassa naṃ dethā’’ ti āha. "
494393,111,2440,107,115,1,53,7,"Purohito na icchi, punappunaṃ vuccamānopi na icchiyeva. "
494394,111,2440,116,117,1,9,1,Kiṃkāraṇā? 
494395,111,2440,118,121,1,18,3,Evaṃ kirassa ahosi–
494396,111,2440,122,138,1,88,11,"‘‘ ahaṃ kurudhammaṃ rakkhantova parasantake lobhaṃ akāsiṃ, bhinnena me sīlena bhavitabban’’ ti. "
494397,111,2440,139,165,1,113,19,"So etamatthaṃ ācikkhitvā‘‘ tātā, kurudhamme me kukkuccaṃ atthi, na maṃ so dhammo ārādheti, tasmā na sakkā dātun’’ ti āha. "
494398,111,2440,166,195,1,176,23,"Atha naṃ dūtā‘‘ ayya, lobhuppādamattena na sīlaṃ bhijjati, tumhe ettakenapi kukkuccaṃ karontā kiṃ vītikkamaṃ karissathā’’ ti vatvā tassapi santike sīlaṃ gahetvā suvaṇṇapaṭṭe likhiṃsu."
494399,111,2441,2,28,1,138,21,"‘ ‘ Evaṃ santepi neva maṃ ārādheti, rajjugāhako amacco pana suṭṭhu rakkhati, tassa santike gaṇhathā’’ ti vuttā ca pana tampi upasaṅkamitvā yāciṃsu. "
494400,111,2441,29,52,1,199,22,"Sopi ekadivasaṃ janapade khettaṃ minanto rajjuṃ daṇḍake bandhitvā ekaṃ koṭiṃ khettasāmikena gaṇhāpetvā ekaṃ attanā aggahesi, tena gahitarajjukoṭiyā baddhadaṇḍako ekassa kakkaṭakassa bilamajjhaṃ pāpuṇi. "
494401,111,2441,53,55,1,10,2,So cintesi–
494402,111,2441,56,66,1,59,7,"‘‘ sace daṇḍakaṃ bile otāressāmi, antobile kakkaṭako nassissati. "
494403,111,2441,67,75,1,52,7,"Sace pana parato karissāmi, rañño santakaṃ nassissati. "
494404,111,2441,76,91,1,76,11,"Sace orato karissāmi, kuṭumbikassa santakaṃ nassissati, kiṃ nu kho kātabban’’ ti? "
494405,111,2441,92,94,1,17,2,Athassa etadahosi–
494406,111,2441,95,124,1,131,17,"‘‘ bile kakkaṭakena bhavitabbaṃ, sace bhaveyya, paññāyeyya, ettheva naṃ otāressāmī’’ ti bile daṇḍakaṃ otāresi, kakkaṭako‘‘ kirī’’ ti saddamakāsi. "
494407,111,2441,125,127,1,17,2,Athassa etadahosi–
494408,111,2441,128,152,1,134,16,"‘‘ daṇḍako kakkaṭakapiṭṭhe otiṇṇo bhavissati, kakkaṭako mato bhavissati, ahañca kurudhammaṃ rakkhāmi, tena me sīlena bhinnena bhavitabban’’ ti . "
494409,111,2441,153,175,1,99,16,"So etamatthaṃ ācikkhitvā‘‘ iminā me kāraṇena kurudhamme kukkuccaṃ atthi, tena vo na sakkā dātun’’ ti āha. "
494410,111,2441,176,195,1,87,14,"Atha naṃ dūtā‘‘ tumhākaṃ‘ kakkaṭako maratū’ ti cittaṃ natthi, acetanakaṃ kammaṃ nāma na hoti. "
494411,111,2441,196,213,1,121,15,Tumhe ettakenapi kukkuccaṃ karontā kiṃ vītikkamaṃ karissathā’’ ti vatvā tassapi santike sīlaṃ gahetvā suvaṇṇapaṭṭe likhiṃsu.
494412,111,2442,2,28,1,127,20,"‘ ‘ Evaṃ santepi neva maṃ ārādheti, sārathi pana suṭṭhu rakkhati, tassa santike gaṇhathā’’ ti vuttā ca pana tampi upasaṅkamitvā yāciṃsu. "
494413,111,2442,29,35,1,42,6,So ekadivasaṃ rājānaṃ rathena uyyānaṃ nesi. 
494414,111,2442,36,51,1,125,14,"Rājā tattha divā kīḷitvā sāyaṃ nikkhamitvā rathaṃ abhiruhi, tassa nagaraṃ asampattasseva sūriyatthaṅgamanavelāya megho uṭṭhahi. "
494415,111,2442,52,57,1,57,5,Sārathi rañño temanabhayena sindhavānaṃ patodasaññamadāsi. 
494416,111,2442,58,61,1,28,3,Sindhavā javena pakkhandiṃsu. 
494417,111,2442,62,77,1,107,15,Tato paṭṭhāya ca pana te uyyānaṃ gacchantāpi tato āgacchantāpi taṃ ṭhānaṃ patvā javena gacchanti āgacchanti. 
494418,111,2442,78,80,1,10,2,Kiṃ kāraṇā? 
494419,111,2442,81,84,1,20,3,Tesaṃ kira etadahosi–
494420,111,2442,85,101,1,80,11,"‘‘ imasmiṃ ṭhāne parissayena bhavitabbaṃ, tena no sārathi tadā patodasaññaṃ adāsī’’ ti. "
494421,111,2442,102,104,1,22,2,Sārathissapi etadahosi–
494422,111,2442,105,142,1,216,29,"‘‘ rañño temane vā atemane vā mayhaṃ doso natthi, ahaṃ pana aṭṭhāne susikkhitasindhavānaṃ patodasaññaṃ adāsiṃ, tena ime idāni aparāparaṃ javantā kilamanti, ahañca kurudhammaṃ rakkhāmi, tena me bhinnena sīlena bhavitabban’’ ti. "
494423,111,2442,143,163,1,96,15,"So etamatthaṃ ācikkhitvā‘‘ iminā kāraṇena kurudhamme kukkuccaṃ atthi, tena vo na sakkā dātun’’ ti āha. "
494424,111,2442,164,203,1,212,30,"Atha naṃ dūtā‘‘ tumhākaṃ‘ sindhavā kilamantū’ ti cittaṃ natthi, acetanakaṃ kammaṃ nāma na hoti, ettakenapi ca tumhe kukkuccaṃ karontā kiṃ vītikkamaṃ karissathā’’ ti vatvā tassa santike sīlaṃ gahetvā suvaṇṇapaṭṭe likhiṃsu."
494425,111,2443,2,27,1,126,20,"‘ ‘ Evaṃ santepi neva maṃ ārādheti, seṭṭhi pana suṭṭhu rakkhati, tassa santike gaṇhathā’’ ti vuttā ca pana tampi upasaṅkamitvā yāciṃsu. "
494426,111,2443,28,49,1,173,17,Sopi ekadivasaṃ gabbhato nikkhantasālisīsaṃ attano sālikhettaṃ gantvā paccavekkhitvā nivattamāno‘‘ vīhimālaṃ bandhāpessāmī’’ ti ekaṃ sālisīsamuṭṭhiṃ gāhāpetvā thūṇāya bandhāpesi. 
494427,111,2443,50,52,1,17,2,Athassa etadahosi–
494428,111,2443,53,80,1,159,20,"‘‘ imamhā kedārā mayā rañño bhāgo dātabbo, adinnabhāgatoyeva me kedārato sālisīsamuṭṭhi gāhāpito, ahañca kurudhammaṃ rakkhāmi, tena me bhinnena sīlena bhavitabban’’ ti. "
494429,111,2443,81,102,1,99,16,"So etamatthaṃ ācikkhitvā‘‘ iminā me kāraṇena kurudhamme kukkuccaṃ atthi, tena vo na sakkā dātun’’ ti āha. "
494430,111,2443,103,139,1,219,29,"Atha naṃ dūtā‘‘ tumhākaṃ theyyacittaṃ natthi, tena vinā adinnādānaṃ nāma paññāpetuṃ na sakkā, ettakenapi kukkuccaṃ karontā tumhe parasantakaṃ nāma kiṃ gaṇhissathā’’ ti vatvā tassapi santike sīlaṃ gahetvā suvaṇṇapaṭṭe likhiṃsu."
494431,111,2444,2,29,1,140,21,"‘ ‘ Evaṃ santepi neva maṃ ārādheti, doṇamāpako pana mahāmatto suṭṭhu rakkhati, tassa santike gaṇhathā’’ ti vuttā ca pana tampi upasaṅkamitvā yāciṃsu. "
494432,111,2444,30,48,1,142,17,"So kira ekadivasaṃ koṭṭhāgāradvāre nisīditvā rājabhāge vīhiṃ mināpento amitavīhirāsito vīhiṃ gahetvā lakkhaṃ ṭhapesi, tasmiṃ khaṇe devo pāvassi. "
494433,111,2444,49,71,1,154,18,Mahāmatto lakkhāni gaṇetvā‘‘ mitavīhī ettakā nāma hontī’’ ti vatvā lakkhavīhiṃ saṃkaḍḍhitvā mitarāsimhi pakkhipitvā vegena gantvā dvārakoṭṭhake ṭhatvā cintesi–
494434,111,2444,72,87,1,74,10,"‘‘ kiṃ nu kho mayā lakkhavīhī mitavīhirāsimhi pakkhittā, udāhu amitarāsimhī’’ ti. "
494435,111,2444,88,90,1,17,2,Athassa etadahosi–
494436,111,2444,91,119,1,168,20,"‘‘ sace me mitavīhirāsimhi pakkhittā akāraṇeneva rañño santakaṃ vaḍḍhitaṃ, gahapatikānaṃ santakaṃ nāsitaṃ, ahañca kurudhammaṃ rakkhāmi, tena me bhinnena sīlena bhavitabban’’ ti. "
494437,111,2444,120,141,1,99,16,"So etamatthaṃ ācikkhitvā‘‘ iminā me kāraṇena kurudhamme kukkuccaṃ atthi, tena vo na sakkā dātun’’ ti āha. "
494438,111,2444,142,177,1,218,29,"Atha naṃ dūtā‘‘ tumhākaṃ theyyacittaṃ natthi, tena vinā adinnādānaṃ nāma paññāpetuṃ na sakkā, ettakenapi kukkuccaṃ karontā kiṃ tumhe parassa santakaṃ gaṇhissathā’’ ti vatvā tassapi santike sīlaṃ gahetvā suvaṇṇapaṭṭe likhiṃsu."
494439,111,2445,2,27,1,128,20,"‘ ‘ Evaṃ santepi neva maṃ ārādheti, dovāriko pana suṭṭhu rakkhati, tassa santike gaṇhathā’’ ti vuttā ca pana tampi upasaṅkamitvā yāciṃsu. "
494440,111,2445,28,34,1,70,6,Sopi ekadivasaṃ nagaradvāraṃ pidhānavelāya tikkhattuṃ saddamanussāvesi. 
494441,111,2445,35,52,1,154,17,Atheko daliddamanusso attano kaniṭṭhabhaginiyā saddhiṃ dārupaṇṇatthāya araññaṃ gantvā nivattanto tassa saddaṃ sutvā bhaginiṃ ādāya vegena dvāraṃ sampāpuṇi. 
494442,111,2445,53,89,1,198,28,"Atha naṃ dovāriko‘‘ tvaṃ nagare rañño atthibhāvaṃ kiṃ na jānāsi,‘ sakalasseva imassa nagarassa dvāraṃ pidhīyatī’ ti na jānāsi, attano mātugāmaṃ gahetvā araññe kāmaratikīḷaṃ kīḷanto divasaṃ vicarasī’’ ti āha. "
494443,111,2445,90,109,1,68,12,"Athassa itarena‘‘ na me, sāmi, bhariyā, bhaginī me esā’’ ti vutte etadahosi–"
494444,111,2445,110,132,1,119,16,"‘‘ akāraṇaṃ vata me kataṃ bhaginiṃ bhariyāti kathentena, ahañca kurudhammaṃ rakkhāmi, tena me bhinnena sīlena bhavitabban’’ ti. "
494445,111,2445,133,155,1,99,16,"So etamatthaṃ ācikkhitvā‘‘ iminā me kāraṇena kurudhamme kukkuccaṃ atthi, tena vo na sakkā dātun’’ ti āha. "
494446,111,2445,156,191,1,219,28,"Atha naṃ dūtā‘‘ etaṃ tumhehi tathāsaññāya kathitaṃ, ettha vo sīlabhedo natthi, ettakenapi ca tumhe kukkuccāyantā kurudhamme sampajānamusāvādaṃ nāma kiṃ karissathā’’ ti vatvā tassapi santike sīlaṃ gahetvā suvaṇṇapaṭṭe likhiṃsu."
494447,111,2446,2,27,1,129,20,"‘ ‘ Evaṃ santepi neva maṃ ārādheti, vaṇṇadāsī pana suṭṭhu rakkhati, tassa santike gaṇhathā’’ ti vuttā ca pana tampi upasaṅkamitvā yāciṃsu. "
494448,111,2446,28,31,1,28,3,Sā purimanayeneva paṭikkhipi. 
494449,111,2446,32,34,1,9,1,Kiṃkāraṇā ? 
494450,111,2446,35,63,1,162,20,Sakko kira devānamindo‘‘ tassā sīlaṃ vīmaṃsissāmī’’ ti māṇavakavaṇṇena āgantvā‘‘ ahaṃ āgamissāmī’’ ti vatvā sahassaṃ datvā devalokameva gantvā tīṇi saṃvaccharāni nāgacchi. 
494451,111,2446,64,81,1,133,16,"Sā attano sīlabhedabhayena tīṇi saṃvaccharāni aññassa purisassa hatthato tambūlamattampi na gaṇhi, sā anukkamena duggatā hutvā cintesi–"
494452,111,2446,82,111,1,201,23,"‘‘ mayhaṃ sahassaṃ datvā gatapurisassa tīṇi saṃvaccharāni anāgacchantassa duggatā jātā, jīvitavuttiṃ ghaṭetuṃ na sakkomi, ito dāni paṭṭhāya mayā vinicchayamahāmattānaṃ ārocetvā paribbayaṃ gahetuṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti. "
494453,111,2446,112,143,1,156,22,"Sā vinicchayaṃ gantvā‘‘ sāmi, paribbayaṃ datvā gatapurisassa me tīṇi saṃvaccharāni, matabhāvampissa na jānāmi, jīvitaṃ ghaṭetuṃ na sakkomi, kiṃ karomi, sāmī’’ ti āha. "
494454,111,2446,144,154,1,77,9,"Tīṇi saṃvaccharāni anāgacchante kiṃ karissasi, ito paṭṭhāya paribbayaṃ gaṇhāti. "
494455,111,2446,155,164,1,94,9,Tassā laddhavinicchayāya vinicchayato nikkhamamānāya eva eko puriso sahassabhaṇḍikaṃ upanāmesi. 
494456,111,2447,2,9,1,61,7,Tassa gahaṇatthāya hatthaṃ pasāraṇakāle sakko attānaṃ dassesi. 
494457,111,2447,10,32,1,127,16,"Sā disvāva‘‘ mayhaṃ saṃvaccharattayamatthake sahassadāyako puriso āgato, tāta, natthi me tava kahāpaṇehi attho’’ ti hatthaṃ samiñjesi. "
494458,111,2447,33,45,1,103,11,"Sakko attano sarīraññeva abhinimminitvā taruṇasūriyo viya jalanto ākāse aṭṭhāsi, sakalanagaraṃ sannipati. "
494459,111,2447,46,86,1,255,30,"Sakko mahājanamajjhe‘‘ ahaṃ etissā vīmaṃsanavasena saṃvaccharattayamatthake sahassaṃ adāsiṃ, sīlaṃ rakkhantā nāma evarūpā hutvā rakkhathā’’ ti ovādaṃ datvā tassā nivesanaṃ sattaratanehi pūretvā‘‘ ito paṭṭhāya appamattā hohī’’ ti taṃ anusāsitvā devalokameva agamāsi. "
494460,111,2447,87,117,1,164,23,"Iminā kāraṇena sā‘‘ ahaṃ gahitabhatiṃ ajīrāpetvāva aññena dīyamānāya bhatiyā hatthaṃ pasāresiṃ, iminā kāraṇena maṃ sīlaṃ nārādheti, tena vo dātuṃ na sakkā’’ ti paṭikkhipi. "
494461,111,2447,118,142,1,150,19,"Atha naṃ dūtā‘‘ hatthappasāraṇamattena sīlabhedo natthi, sīlaṃ nāma etaṃ paramavisuddhi hotī’’ ti vatvā tassāpi santike sīlaṃ gahetvā suvaṇṇapaṭṭe likhiṃsu. "
494462,111,2448,2,17,1,139,15,Iti imesaṃ ekādasannaṃ janānaṃ rakkhaṇasīlaṃ suvaṇṇapaṭṭe likhitvā dantapuraṃ gantvā kāliṅgarañño suvaṇṇapaṭṭaṃ datvā taṃ pavattiṃ ārocesuṃ. 
