494477,111,2459,2,16,1,107,12,Vassāni paññāsa {samādhikānī}ti idaṃ satthā veḷuvane viharanto bhagavato vadhāya parisakkanaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
494478,111,2459,17,19,1,28,2,Paccuppannavatthu uttānameva. 
494479,111,2460,2,16,1,132,14,Atīte pana bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto pārāvato hutvā bahupārāvataparivuto araññe pabbataguhāyaṃ vāsaṃ kappesi. 
494480,111,2460,17,34,1,154,16,Aññataropi kho tāpaso sīlasampanno tesaṃ pārāvatānaṃ vasanaṭṭhānato avidūre ekaṃ paccantagāmaṃ upanissāya assamapadaṃ māpetvā pabbataguhāyaṃ vāsaṃ kappesi. 
