494482,111,2460,43,55,1,83,11,"Tāpaso tattha ciraṃ vasitvā pakkāmi, athañño kūṭajaṭilo āgantvā tattha vāsaṃ kappesi. "
494483,111,2460,56,72,1,165,16,Bodhisatto pārāvataparivuto taṃ upasaṅkamitvā vanditvā paṭisanthāraṃ katvā assamapade vicaritvā girikandarasamīpe gocaraṃ gahetvā sāyaṃ attano vasanaṭṭhānaṃ gacchati. 
