494506,111,2469,79,126,1,243,37,"Cirappavutthā atha vā na te {ime}ti kiṃ nu kho ime ciraṃ vippavasitvā dīghassa addhuno accayena āgatattā maṃ‘‘ soyeva ayan’’ ti na sañjānanti, udāhu ye amhesu abhinibbutacittā, na te ime, aññeva āgantukapakkhino, ime kena maṃ na upasaṅkamantīti pucchati. "
