494567,111,2498,67,85,1,112,15,"Sace tumhe attano gāhaṃ vissajjetha, suṭṭhutaraṃ vo ete adhibhavissantī’’ tiādīni vatvā gāhaṃ vissajjetuṃ na denti. "
494568,111,2498,86,92,1,54,6,Tena bhaṇḍanāni ceva kalahaviggahavivādā ca pavattanti. 
494569,111,2498,93,97,1,37,4,Bhikkhū etamatthaṃ bhagavato ārocesuṃ. 
494570,111,2498,98,157,1,323,41,"Atha bhagavā etasmiṃ nidāne etasmiṃ pakaraṇe bhikkhū sannipātāpetvā paṇḍukalohitake pakkosāpetvā‘‘ saccaṃ kira tumhe, bhikkhave, attanāpi adhikaraṇaṃ ukkoṭetha, aññesampi gāhaṃ vissajjetuṃ na dethā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ saccaṃ, bhante’’ ti vutte‘‘ evaṃ sante, bhikkhave, tumhākaṃ kiriyā satapattamāṇavassa kiriyā viya hotī’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
494571,111,2499,2,30,1,251,25,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto aññatarasmiṃ kāsigāmake ekasmiṃ kule nibbattitvā vayappatto kasivaṇijjādīhi jīvikaṃ akappetvā pañcasatamatte core gahetvā tesaṃ jeṭṭhako hutvā panthadūhanasandhicchedādīni karonto jīvikaṃ kappesi. 
494572,111,2499,31,42,1,100,11,Tadā bārāṇasiyaṃ eko kuṭumbiko ekassa jānapadassa kahāpaṇasahassaṃ datvā puna aggahetvāva kālamakāsi. 
494573,111,2499,43,82,1,218,31,"Athassa bhariyā aparabhāge gilānā maraṇamañce nipannā puttaṃ āmantetvā‘‘ tāta, pitā te ekassa sahassaṃ datvā anāharāpetvāva mato, sace ahampi marissāmi, na so tuyhaṃ dassati, gaccha naṃ mayi jīvantiyā āharāpetvā gaṇhā’’ ti āha. "
494574,111,2499,83,95,1,55,8,So‘‘ sādhū’’ ti sampaṭicchitvā tattha gantvā kahāpaṇe labhi. 
494575,111,2499,96,106,1,94,10,Athassa mātā kālakiriyaṃ katvā puttasinehena tassa āgamanamagge opapātikasiṅgālī hutvā nibbati. 
