494661,111,2547,2,7,1,23,2,[ 281]1. Abbhantarajātakavaṇṇanā 
494662,111,2548,2,16,1,119,12,Abbhantaro nāma {dumo}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto sāriputtattherassa bimbādevītheriyā ambarasadānaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
494663,111,2548,17,34,1,182,17,Sammāsambuddhe hi pavattitavaradhammacakke vesāliyaṃ kūṭāgārasālāyaṃ viharante mahāpajāpatī gotamī pañca sākiyasatāni ādāya gantvā pabbajjaṃ yācitvā pabbajjañceva upasampadañca labhi. 
494664,111,2548,35,53,1,74,8,Aparabhāge tā pañcasatā bhikkhuniyo nandakovādaṃ( ma. ni.3.398 ādayo) sutvā arahattaṃ pāpuṇiṃsu. 
494665,111,2548,54,107,1,438,46,"Satthari pana sāvatthiṃ upanissāya viharante rāhulamātā bimbādevī‘‘ sāmiko me pabbajitvā sabbaññutaṃ patto, puttopi me pabbajitvā tasseva santike vasati, ahaṃ agāramajjhe kiṃkarissāmi, ahampi pabbajitvā sāvatthiṃ gantvā sammāsambuddhañca puttañca nibaddhaṃ passamānā viharissāmī’’ ti cintetvā bhikkhunupassayaṃ gantvā pabbajitvā ācariyupajjhāyāhi saddhiṃ sāvatthiṃ gantvā satthārañca piyaputtañca passamānā ekasmiṃ bhikkhunupassaye vāsaṃ kappesi. "
494666,111,2548,108,112,1,38,4,Rāhulasāmaṇero āgantvā mātaraṃ passati. 
494667,111,2549,2,7,1,37,4,Athekadivasaṃ theriyā udaravāto kuppi. 
494668,111,2549,8,21,1,104,12,"Sā putte daṭṭhuṃ āgate tassa dassanatthāya nikkhamituṃ nāsakkhi, aññāva āgantvā aphāsukabhāvaṃ kathayiṃsu. "
494669,111,2549,22,36,1,56,10,So mātu santikaṃ gantvā‘‘ kiṃ te laddhuṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti pucchi.
494670,111,2549,37,61,1,131,17,"‘‘ Tāta, agāramajjhe me sakkharayojite ambarase pīte udaravāto vūpasammati, idāni piṇḍāya caritvā jīvikaṃ kappema, kuto taṃ labhissāmā’’ ti. "
494671,111,2549,62,72,1,46,6,Sāmaṇero‘‘ labhanto āharissāmī’’ ti vatvā nikkhami. 
494672,111,2549,73,88,1,122,11,"Tassa panāyasmato upajjhāyo dhammasenāpati, ācariyo mahāmoggallāno, cūḷapitā ānandatthero, pitā sammāsambuddhoti mahāsampatti. "
494673,111,2549,89,101,1,102,12,Evaṃ santepi aññassa santikaṃ agantvā upajjhāyassa santikaṃ gantvā vanditvā dummukhākāro hutvā aṭṭhāsi. 
494674,111,2549,102,119,1,55,11,"Atha naṃ thero‘‘ kiṃ nu kho, rāhula, dummukho viyāsī’’ ti āha."
494675,111,2549,120,133,1,42,7,"‘‘ Mātu me, bhante, theriyā udaravāto kupito’’ ti."
494676,111,2549,134,142,1,22,4,‘‘ Kiṃ laddhuṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti?
494677,111,2549,143,153,1,46,6,‘‘ Sakkharayojitena kira ambarasena phāsu hotī’’ ti.
494678,111,2549,154,164,1,29,5,"‘‘ Hotu labhissāmi, mā cintayī’’ ti. "
494679,111,2550,2,14,1,97,11,So punadivase taṃ ādāya sāvatthiṃ pavisitvā sāmaṇeraṃ āsanasālāyaṃ nisīdāpetvā rājadvāraṃ agamāsi. 
494680,111,2550,15,27,1,105,11,"Kosalarājā theraṃ disvā nisīdāpesi, taṅkhaṇaññeva uyyānapālo piṇḍipakkānaṃ madhuraambānaṃ ekaṃ puṭaṃ āhari. "
494681,111,2550,28,40,1,97,12,Rājā ambānaṃ tacaṃ apanetvā sakkharaṃ pakkhipitvā sayameva madditvā therassa pattaṃ pūretvā adāsi. 
494682,111,2550,41,57,1,90,12,Thero rājanivesanā nikkhamitvā āsanasālaṃ gantvā sāmaṇerassa adāsi‘‘ haritvā mātu te dehī’’ ti. 
494683,111,2550,58,66,1,61,7,"So haritvā adāsi, theriyā paribhuttamatteva udaravāto vūpasami. "
494684,111,2550,67,70,1,22,3,Rājāpi manussaṃ pesesi–
494685,111,2550,71,87,1,81,11,"‘‘ thero idha nisīditvā ambarasaṃ na paribhuñji, gaccha kassaci dinnabhāvaṃ jānāhī’’ ti. "
494686,111,2550,88,98,1,70,10,So therena saddhiṃyeva gantvā taṃ pavattiṃ ñatvā āgantvā rañño kathesi. 
494687,111,2550,99,101,1,12,2,Rājā cintesi–
494688,111,2550,102,121,1,151,13,"‘‘ sace satthā agāraṃ ajjhāvasissa, cakkavattirājā abhavissa, rāhulasāmaṇero pariṇāyakaratanaṃ, therī itthiratanaṃ, sakalacakkavāḷarajjaṃ etesaññeva abhavissa. "
494689,111,2550,122,141,1,122,16,"Amhehi ete upaṭṭhahantehi caritabbaṃ assa, idāni pabbajitvā amhe upanissāya vasantesu etesu na yuttaṃ amhākaṃ pamajjitun’’ ti. "
494690,111,2550,142,149,1,51,7,So tato paṭṭhāya theriyā nibaddhaṃ ambarasaṃ dāpesi. 
494691,111,2550,150,157,1,73,7,Therena bimbādevītheriyā ambarasassa dinnabhāvo bhikkhusaṅghe pākaṭo jāto. 
