494795,111,2574,2,7,1,18,2,[ 282]2. Seyyajātakavaṇṇanā 
494796,111,2575,2,16,1,95,12,Seyyaṃso seyyaso {hotī}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ekaṃ kosalarañño amaccaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
494797,111,2575,17,23,1,51,6,So kira rañño bahūpakāro sabbakiccanipphādako ahosi. 
494798,111,2575,24,37,1,53,9,Rājā‘‘ bahūpakāro me ayan’’ ti tassa mahantaṃ yasaṃ adāsi. 
494799,111,2575,38,46,1,65,8,Taṃ asahamānā aññe rañño pesuññaṃ upasaṃharitvā taṃ paribhindiṃsu. 
494800,111,2575,47,60,1,137,13,Rājā tesaṃ vacanaṃ saddahitvā dosaṃ anupaparikkhitvāva taṃ sīlavantaṃ niddosaṃ saṅkhalikabandhanena bandhāpetvā bandhanāgāre pakkhipāpesi. 
494801,111,2575,61,74,1,123,13,So tattha ekako vasanto sīlasampattiṃ nissāya cittekaggataṃ labhitvā ekaggacitto saṅkhāre sammasitvā sotāpattiphalaṃ pāpuṇi. 
494802,111,2575,75,86,1,113,11,Athassa rājā aparabhāge niddosabhāvaṃ ñatvā saṅkhalikabandhanaṃ bhindāpetvā purimayasato mahantataraṃ yasaṃ adāsi. 
494803,111,2575,87,105,1,114,14,So‘‘ satthāraṃ vandissāmī’’ ti bahūni mālāgandhādīni ādāya vihāraṃ gantvā tathāgataṃ pūjetvā vanditvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. 
494804,111,2575,106,122,1,82,12,Satthā tena saddhiṃ paṭisanthāraṃ karonto‘‘ anattho kira te uppannoti assumhā’’ ti āha.
494805,111,2575,123,145,1,111,14,"‘‘ Āma, bhante, uppanno, ahaṃ pana tena anatthena atthaṃ akāsiṃ, bandhanāgāre nisīditvā sotāpattiphalaṃ nibbattesin’’ ti. "
494806,111,2575,146,173,1,143,20,"Satthā‘‘ na kho, upāsaka, tvaññeva anatthena atthaṃ āhari, porāṇakapaṇḍitāpi attano anatthena atthaṃ āhariṃ suyevā’’ ti vatvā tena yācito atītaṃ āhari. "
494807,111,2576,2,34,1,255,28,"Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto tassa aggamahesiyā kucchimhi nibbattitvā vayappatto takkasilāyaṃ sabbasippāni uggaṇhitvā pitu accayena rajje patiṭṭhāya dasa rājadhamme akopetvā dānaṃ deti, pañca sīlāni rakkhati , uposathakammaṃ karoti. "
494808,111,2576,35,39,1,33,4,Athasseko amacco antepure padussi. 
