494832,111,2585,37,66,1,227,27,"Ekena sandhiṃ katvāna, sataṃ vajjhe amocayin ti tadamināpi cetaṃ veditabbaṃ– ahañhi seyyaṃ mettābhāvanaṃ upasevanto tāya mettābhāvanāya ekena coraraññā sandhiṃ santhavaṃ katvā mettābhāvanaṃ bhāvetvā tumhe satajane vajjhe amocayiṃ. "
494833,111,2586,2,35,1,244,29,"Dutiyagāthāya attho– yasmā ahaṃ ekena saddhiṃ ekato mettābhāvanāya sandhiṃ katvā tumhe vajjhappatte satajane mocayiṃ, tasmā veditabbamevetaṃ, tasmā sabbena lokena saddhiṃ mettābhāvanāya sandhiṃ katvā ekato puggalo pecca paraloke saggaṃ nigaccheyya. "
