494849,111,2596,2,13,1,89,11,Varaṃ varaṃ tvan ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto dhanuggahatissattheraṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
494850,111,2596,14,28,1,144,14,Pasenadirañño pitā mahākosalo bimbisārarañño dhītaraṃ vedehiṃ nāma kosaladeviṃ dadamāno tassā nhānacuṇṇamūlaṃ satasahassuṭṭhānaṃ kāsigāmaṃ adāsi. 
494851,111,2596,29,36,1,68,7,Ajātasattunā pana pitari mārite kosaladevīpi sokābhibhūtā kālamakāsi. 
494852,111,2596,37,41,1,32,4,Tato pasenadi kosalarājā cintesi–
494853,111,2596,42,64,1,121,16,"‘‘ ajātasattunā pitā mārito, bhaginīpi me sāmike kālakate tena sokena kālakatā, pitughātakassa corassa kāsigāmaṃ na dassāmī’’ ti. "
494854,111,2596,65,70,1,29,5,So taṃ ajātasattussa na adāsi. 
494855,111,2596,71,88,1,109,14,"Taṃ gāmaṃ nissāya tesaṃ dvinnampi kālena kālaṃ yuddhaṃ hoti, ajātasattu taruṇo samattho, pasenadi mahallakoyeva. "
494856,111,2596,89,97,1,68,7,"So abhikkhaṇaṃ parajjati, mahākosalassāpi manussā yebhuyyena parājitā. "
494857,111,2596,98,115,1,71,12,"Atha rājā‘‘ mayaṃ abhiṇhaṃ parajjāma, kiṃ nu kho kātabban’’ ti amacce pucchi."
