494914,111,2601,89,106,1,95,14,"Etasmiṃ bhūmisīse ṭhito eko tesaṃ saṃvidhāyakopi atthi, ajja mayhaṃ gatassa jayo na paññāyatī’’ ti. "
494915,111,2601,107,112,1,45,5,So nivattitvā attano vasanaṭṭhānameva agamāsi. 
494916,111,2601,113,130,1,134,16,"Tena pana gahitamaṃsakhādako eko kūṭajaṭilo atthi, so taṃ tucchahatthameva āgacchantaṃ disvā tena saddhiṃ sallapanto paṭhamaṃ gāthamāha– "
494917,111,2602,2,4,1,0,0,97.
494918,111,2603,2,11,1,34,7,"‘ ‘ Varaṃ varaṃ tvaṃ nihanaṃ pure cari, "
494919,111,2604,2,6,1,30,4,Asmiṃ padese abhibhuyya sūkare; 
494920,111,2605,2,6,1,29,4,"Sodāni eko byapagamma jhāyasi, "
494921,111,2606,2,12,1,39,8,Balaṃ nu te byaggha na cajja vijjatī’’ ti. 
494922,111,2607,2,33,1,209,28,"Tattha varaṃ varaṃ tvaṃ nihanaṃ pure cari, asmiṃ padese abhibhuyya {sūkare}ti ambho byaggha, tvaṃ pubbe imasmiṃ padese sabbasūkare abhibhavitvā imesu sūkaresu varaṃ varaṃ tvaṃ uttamuttamaṃ sūkaraṃ nihananto vicari. "
494923,111,2607,34,49,1,110,14,Sodāni eko byapagamma {jhāyasī}ti so tvaṃ idāni aññataraṃ sūkaraṃ aggahetvā ekakova apagantvā jhāyasi pajjhāyasi. 
494924,111,2607,50,68,1,86,15,"Balaṃ nu te byaggha na cajja {vijjatī}ti kiṃ nu te, ambho byaggha, ajja kāyabalaṃ natthīti. "
494925,111,2608,2,7,1,35,5,Taṃ sutvā byaggho dutiyaṃ gāthamāha– 
494926,111,2609,2,4,1,0,0,98.
494927,111,2610,2,13,1,60,9,"‘ ‘ Ime sudaṃ yanti disodisaṃ pure, bhayaṭṭitā leṇagavesino puthū; "
494928,111,2611,2,14,1,66,9,"Te dāni saṅgamma vasanti ekato, yatthaṭṭhitā duppasahajjame mayā’’ ti. "
494929,111,2612,2,7,1,22,4,Tattha sudan ti nipāto. 
494930,111,2612,8,54,1,291,41,"Ayaṃ pana saṅkhepattho– ime sūkarā pubbe maṃ disvā bhayena aṭṭitā pīḷitā attano leṇagavesino puthū visuṃ visuṃ hutvā disodisaṃ yanti, taṃ taṃ disaṃ abhimukhā palāyanti, te dāni sabbepi samāgantvā ekato vasanti tiṭṭhanti, tañca bhūmisīsaṃ upagatā, yattha ṭhitā duppasahā dummaddayā ajja ime mayāti. "
494931,111,2613,2,24,1,120,16,"Athassa ussāhaṃ janento kūṭajaṭilo‘‘ mā bhāyi, gaccha tayi naditvā pakkhandante sabbepi bhītā bhijjitvā palāyissantī’’ ti āha. "
494932,111,2613,25,35,1,73,10,Byaggho tasmiṃ ussāhaṃ janente sūro hutvā puna gantvā pabbatatale aṭṭhāsi. 
494933,111,2613,36,41,1,46,5,Vaḍḍhakīsūkaro dvinnaṃ āvāṭānaṃ antare aṭṭhāsi. 
494934,111,2613,42,53,1,39,6,"Sūkarā‘‘ sāmi, mahācoro punāgato’’ ti āhaṃsu."
494935,111,2613,54,65,1,36,6,"‘‘ Mā bhāyittha, idāni taṃ gaṇhissāmī’’ ti. "
494936,111,2613,66,83,1,126,15,"Byaggho naditvā vaḍḍhakīsūkarassa upari patati, sūkaro tassa attano upari patanakāle parivattitvā vegena ujukaṃ khataāvāṭe pati. "
494937,111,2613,84,99,1,144,15,Byaggho vegaṃ sandhāretuṃ asakkonto uparibhāgena gantvā suppamukhassa tiriyaṃ khataāvāṭassa atisambādhe mukhaṭṭhāne patitvā puñjakato viya ahosi. 
494938,111,2613,100,129,1,244,25,Sūkaro āvāṭā uttaritvā asanivegena gantvā byagghaṃ antarasatthimhi dāṭhāya paharitvā yāva vakkapadesā phāletvā pañcamadhuramaṃsaṃ dāṭhāya paliveṭhetvā byagghassa matthake āvijjhitvā‘‘ gaṇhatha tumhākaṃ paccāmittan’’ ti ukkhipitvā bahiāvāṭe chaḍḍesi. 
494939,111,2613,130,149,1,116,14,"Paṭhamaṃ āgatā byagghamaṃsaṃ labhiṃsu, pacchā āgatā‘‘ byagghamaṃsaṃ kīdisaṃ hotī’’ ti tesaṃ mukhaṃ upasiṅghantā vicariṃsu. "
494940,111,2614,2,6,1,23,4,Sūkarā na tāva tussanti. 
494941,111,2614,7,23,1,71,12,Vaḍḍhakīsūkaro tesaṃ iṅghitaṃ disvā‘‘ kiṃ nu kho tumhe na tussathā’’ ti āha.
494942,111,2614,24,41,1,91,11,"‘‘ Sāmi, kiṃ etena byagghena ghātitena, añño pana byagghaāṇāpanasamattho kūṭajaṭilo atthiyevā’’ ti."
494943,111,2614,42,49,1,12,3,‘‘ Ko nāmeso’’ ti?
494944,111,2614,50,57,1,20,3,‘‘ Eko dussīlatāpaso’’ ti.
494945,111,2614,58,78,1,91,14,"‘‘ Byagghopi mayā ghātito, so me kiṃ pahoti, etha gaṇhissāma nan’’ ti sūkaraghaṭāya saddhiṃ pāyāsi. "
494946,111,2614,79,110,1,223,27,Kūṭatāpasopi byagghe cirāyante‘‘ kiṃ nu kho sūkarā byagghaṃ gaṇhiṃsū’’ ti paṭipathaṃ gacchanto te sūkare āgacchante disvā attano parikkhāraṃ ādāya palāyanto tehi anubandhito parikkhāraṃ chaḍḍetvā vegena udumbararukkhaṃ abhiruhi. 
494947,111,2614,111,129,1,71,10,"Sūkarā‘‘ idānimha, sāmi, naṭṭhā, tāpaso palāyitvā rukkhaṃ abhiruhī’’ ti āhaṃsu."
494948,111,2614,130,138,1,19,4,‘‘ Kiṃ rukkhaṃ nāmā’’ ti?
494949,111,2614,139,145,1,18,2,‘‘ Udumbararukkhan’’ ti. 
494950,111,2614,146,184,1,263,30,"So‘‘ sūkariyo udakaṃ āharantu, sūkarapotakā pathaviṃ khaṇantu, dīghadāṭhā sūkarā mūlāni chindantu, sesā parivāretvā ārakkhantū’’ ti saṃvidahitvā tesu tathā karontesu sayaṃ udumbarassa ujukaṃ thūlamūlaṃ pharasunā paharanto viya ekappahārameva katvā udumbararukkhaṃ pātesi. "
494951,111,2614,185,211,1,267,25,"Parivāretvā ṭhitasūkarā kūṭajaṭilaṃ bhūmiyaṃ pātetvā khaṇḍākhaṇḍikaṃ katvā yāva aṭṭhito khāditvā vaḍḍhakīsūkaraṃ udumbarakhandheyeva nisīdāpetvā kūṭajaṭilassa paribhogasaṅkhena udakaṃ āharitvā abhisiñcitvā rājānaṃ kariṃsu, ekañca taruṇasūkariṃ tassa aggamahesiṃ akaṃsu. "
494952,111,2614,212,222,1,96,10,Tato paṭṭhāya kira yāvajjatanā rājāno udumbarabhaddapīṭhe nisīdāpetvā tīhi saṅkhehi abhisiñcanti. 
494953,111,2615,2,17,1,119,14,Tasmiṃ vanasaṇḍe adhivatthā devatā taṃ acchariyaṃ disvā ekasmiṃ viṭapantare sūkarānaṃ abhimukhā hutvā tatiyaṃ gāthamāha– 
494954,111,2616,2,4,1,0,0,99.
494955,111,2617,2,13,1,64,9,"‘ ‘ Namatthu saṅghāna samāgatānaṃ, disvā sayaṃ sakhya vadāmi abbhutaṃ; "
494956,111,2618,2,14,1,69,9,"Byagghaṃ migā yattha jiniṃsu dāṭhino, sāmaggiyā dāṭhabalesu muccare’’ ti. "
494957,111,2619,2,12,1,82,10,Tattha namatthu saṅghānan ti ayaṃ mama namakkāro samāgatānaṃ sūkarasaṅghānaṃ atthu. 
494958,111,2619,13,28,1,109,15,Disvā sayaṃ sakhya vadāmi abbhutan ti idaṃ pubbe abhūtapubbaṃ abbhutaṃ sakhyaṃ mittabhāvaṃ sayaṃ disvā vadāmi. 
494959,111,2619,29,46,1,105,15,"Byagghaṃ migā yattha jiniṃsu {dāṭhino}ti yatra hi nāma dāṭhino sūkaramigā byagghaṃ jiniṃsu, ayameva vā pāṭho. "
494960,111,2619,47,69,1,164,20,"Sāmaggiyā dāṭhabalesu {muccare}ti yā sā dāṭhabalesu sūkaresu sāmaggī ekajjhāsayatā, tāya tesu sāmaggiyā te dāṭhabalā paccāmittaṃ gahetvā ajja maraṇabhayā muttāti attho. "
494961,111,2620,2,8,1,54,6,Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–
494962,111,2620,9,23,1,77,9,"‘‘ tadā dhanuggahatisso vaḍḍhakīsūkaro ahosi, rukkhadevatā pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
494963,111,2621,2,4,1,34,2,Vaḍḍhakīsūkarajātakavaṇṇanā tatiyā.
494964,111,2623,2,7,1,17,2,[ 284]4. Sirijātakavaṇṇanā 
494965,111,2624,2,15,1,94,11,Yaṃ ussukā {saṅgharantī}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ekaṃ siricorabrāhmaṇaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
494966,111,2624,16,32,1,73,6,Imasmiṃ jātake paccuppannavatthu heṭṭhā khadiraṅgārajātake( jā.1.1.40) vitthāritameva. 
494967,111,2624,33,52,1,189,19,Idhāpi pana sā anāthapiṇḍikassa ghare catutthe dvārakoṭṭhake vasanakā micchādiṭṭhidevatā daṇḍakammaṃ karontī catupaññāsahiraññakoṭiyo āharitvā koṭṭhe pūretvā seṭṭhinā saddhiṃ sahāyikā ahosi. 
494968,111,2624,53,60,1,38,7,Atha naṃ so ādāya satthu santikaṃ nesi. 
494969,111,2624,61,71,1,60,9,"Satthā tassā dhammaṃ desesi, sā dhammaṃ sutvā sotāpannā ahosi. "
494970,111,2624,72,78,1,46,6,Tato paṭṭhāya seṭṭhino yaso yathāporāṇova jāto. 
494971,111,2624,79,84,1,52,5,Atheko sāvatthivāsī sirilakkhaṇaññū brāhmaṇo cintesi–
494972,111,2624,85,107,1,125,17,"‘‘ anāthapiṇḍiko duggato hutvā puna issaro jāto, yaṃnūnāhaṃ taṃ daṭṭhukāmo viya gatvā tassa gharato siriṃ thenetvā āgaccheyyan’’ ti. "
494973,111,2624,108,135,1,142,19,So tassa gharaṃ gantvā tena katasakkārasammāno sāraṇīyakathāya vattamānāya‘‘ kimatthaṃ āgatosī’’ ti vutte‘‘ kattha nu kho sirī patiṭṭhitā’’ ti olokesi. 
494974,111,2624,136,151,1,120,13,"Seṭṭhino ca sabbaseto dhotasaṅkhapaṭibhāgo kukkuṭo suvaṇṇapañjare pakkhipitvā ṭhapito atthi, tassa cūḷāya sirī patiṭṭhāsi. "
494975,111,2624,152,159,1,61,7,Brāhmaṇo olokayamāno siriyā tattha patiṭṭhitabhāvaṃ ñatvā āha–
494976,111,2624,160,195,1,177,25,"‘‘ ahaṃ, mahāseṭṭhi, pañcasate māṇave mante vācemi, akālaraviṃ ekaṃ kukkuṭaṃ nissāya te ca mayañca kilamāma, ayañca kira kukkuṭo kālaravī, imassatthāya āgatomhi, dehi me etaṃ kukkuṭan’’ ti."
494977,111,2624,196,208,1,34,6,"‘‘ Gaṇha, brāhmaṇa, demi te kukkuṭan’’ ti."
494978,111,2624,209,225,1,95,12,‘‘ Demī’’ ti ca vuttakkhaṇeyeva sirī tassa cūḷato apagantvā ussīsake ṭhapite maṇikkhandhe patiṭṭhāsi. 
494979,111,2625,2,9,1,59,7,Brāhmaṇo siriyā maṇimhi patiṭṭhitabhāvaṃ ñatvā maṇimpi yāci.
494980,111,2625,10,24,1,97,10,‘‘ Maṇimpi demī’’ ti vuttakkhaṇeyeva sirī maṇito apagantvā ussīsake ṭhapitaārakkhayaṭṭhiyaṃ patiṭṭhāsi. 
494981,111,2625,25,32,1,56,7,Brāhmaṇo siriyā tattha patiṭṭhitabhāvaṃ ñatvā tampi yāci.
494982,111,2625,33,50,1,122,13,‘‘ Gahetvā gacchāhī’’ ti vuttakkhaṇeyeva sirī yaṭṭhito apagantvā puññalakkhaṇadeviyā nāma seṭṭhino aggamahesiyā sīse patiṭṭhāsi. 
494983,111,2625,51,69,1,119,13,"Siricorabrāhmaṇo tattha patiṭṭhitabhāvaṃ ñatvā‘‘ avissajjiyabhaṇḍaṃ etaṃ, yācitumpi na sakkā’’ ti cintetvā seṭṭhiṃ etadavoca–"
494984,111,2625,70,143,1,419,55,"‘‘ mahāseṭṭhi, ahaṃ tumhākaṃ gehe‘ siriṃ thenetvā gamissāmī’ ti āgacchiṃ, sirī pana te kukkuṭassa cūḷāyaṃ patiṭṭhitā ahosi, tasmiṃ mama dinne tato apagantvā maṇimhi patiṭṭhahi, maṇimhi dinne ārakkhayaṭṭhiyaṃ patiṭṭhahi, ārakkhayaṭṭhiyā dinnāya tato apagantvā puññalakkhaṇadeviyā sīse patiṭṭhahi,‘ idaṃ kho pana avissajjiyabhaṇḍan’ ti imampi me na gahitaṃ, na sakkā tava siriṃ thenetuṃ, tava santakaṃ taveva hotū’’ ti uṭṭhāyāsanā pakkāmi. "
494985,111,2625,144,164,1,135,16,Anāthapiṇḍiko‘‘ imaṃ kāraṇaṃ satthu kathessāmī’’ ti vihāraṃ gantvā satthāraṃ pūjetvā vanditvā ekamantaṃ nisinno sabbaṃ tathāgatassa ārocesi. 
494986,111,2625,165,196,1,176,24,"Satthā taṃ sutvā‘‘ na kho, gahapati, idāneva aññesaṃ sirī aññattha gacchati, pubbepi appapuññehi uppāditasirī pana puññavantānaṃyeva pādamūlaṃ gatā’’ ti vatvā tena yācito atītaṃ āhari. "
494987,111,2626,2,44,1,434,42,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto kāsiraṭṭhe brāhmaṇakule nibbattitvā vayappatto takkasilāyaṃ sippaṃ uggaṇhitvā agāraṃ ajjhāvasanto mātāpitūnaṃ kālakiriyāya saṃviggo nikkhamitvā himavantapadese isipabbajjaṃ pabbajitvā abhiññā ca samāpattiyo ca uppādetvā dīghassa addhuno accayena loṇambilasevanatthāya janapadaṃ gantvā bārāṇasirañño uyyāne vasitvā punadivase bhikkhaṃ caramāno hatthācariyassa gharadvāraṃ agamāsi. 
494988,111,2626,45,55,1,77,10,So tassa ācāravihāre pasanno bhikkhaṃ datvā uyyāne vasāpetvā niccaṃ paṭijaggi. 
494989,111,2626,56,68,1,92,11,Tasmiṃ kāle eko kaṭṭhahārako araññato dārūni āharanto velāya nagaradvāraṃ pāpuṇituṃ nāsakkhi. 
494990,111,2626,69,86,1,126,16,"Sāyaṃ ekasmiṃ devakule dārukalāpaṃ ussīsake katvā nipajji, devakule vissaṭṭhā bahū kukkuṭā tassa avidūre ekasmiṃ rukkhe sayiṃsu. "
494991,111,2626,87,95,1,87,8,Tesu uparisayitakukkuṭo paccūsakāle vaccaṃ pātento heṭṭhāsayitakukkuṭassa sarīre pātesi.
494992,111,2626,96,115,1,53,11,‘‘ Kena me sarīre vaccaṃ pātitan’’ ti ca vutte‘‘ mayā’’ ti āha.
494993,111,2626,116,133,1,58,9,‘‘ Kiṃkāraṇā’’ ti ca vutte‘‘ anupadhāretvā’’ ti vatvā punapi pātesi. 
494994,111,2626,134,152,1,74,13,"Tato ubhopi aññamaññaṃ kuddhā‘‘ kiṃ te balaṃ, kiṃ te balan’’ ti kalahaṃ kariṃsu. "
494995,111,2626,153,156,1,28,3,Atha heṭṭhāsayitakukkuṭo āha–
494996,111,2626,157,171,1,74,9,‘‘ maṃ māretvā aṅgāre pakkamaṃsaṃ khādanto pātova kahāpaṇasahassaṃ labhatī’’ ti. 
494997,111,2626,172,174,1,22,2,Uparisayitakukkuṭo āha–
494998,111,2626,175,203,1,145,19,"‘‘ ambho, mā tvaṃ ettakena gajji, mama thūlamaṃsaṃ khādanto rājā hoti, bahimaṃsaṃ khādanto puriso ce, senāpatiṭṭhānaṃ, itthī ce, aggamahesiṭṭhānaṃ labhati. "
494999,111,2626,204,221,1,99,12,"Aṭṭhimaṃsaṃ pana me khādanto gihī ce, bhaṇḍāgārikaṭṭhānaṃ, pabbajito ce, rājakulūpakabhāvaṃ labhatī’’ ti. "
495000,111,2627,2,50,1,300,36,Kaṭṭhahārako tesaṃ vacanaṃ sutvā‘‘ rajje patte sahassena kiccaṃ natthī’’ ti saṇikaṃ abhiruhitvā uparisayitakukkuṭaṃ gahetvā māretvā ucchaṅge katvā‘‘ rājā bhavissāmī’’ ti gantvā vivaṭadvāreneva nagaraṃ pavisitvā kukkuṭaṃ nittacaṃ katvā udaraṃ sodhetvā‘‘ idaṃ kukkuṭamaṃsaṃ sādhukaṃ sampādehī’’ ti pajāpatiyā adāsi. 
495001,111,2627,51,65,1,70,9,"Sā kukkuṭamaṃsañca bhattañca sampādetvā‘‘ bhuñja, sāmī’’ ti tassa upanāmesi."
495002,111,2627,66,100,1,214,26,"‘‘ Bhadde, etaṃ maṃsaṃ mahānubhāvaṃ, etaṃ khāditvā ahaṃ rājā bhavissāmi, tvaṃ aggamahesī bhavissasi, taṃ bhattañca maṃsañca ādāya gaṅgātīraṃ gantvā nhāyitvā bhuñjissāmā’’ ti bhattabhājanaṃ tīre ṭhapetvā nhānatthāya otariṃsu. "
495003,111,2627,101,110,1,73,9,Tasmiṃ khaṇe vātena khubhitaṃ udakaṃ āgantvā bhattabhājanaṃ ādāya agamāsi. 
495004,111,2627,111,130,1,133,15,Taṃ nadīsotena vuyhamānaṃ heṭṭhānadiyaṃ hatthiṃ nhāpento eko hatthācariyo mahāmatto disvā ukkhipāpetvā vivarāpetvā‘‘ kimetthā’’ ti pucchi.
495005,111,2627,131,139,1,35,4,‘‘ Bhattañceva kukkuṭamaṃsañca sāmī’’ ti. 
495006,111,2627,140,159,1,97,14,"So taṃ pidahāpetvā lañchāpetvā‘‘ yāva mayaṃ āgacchāma, tāvimaṃ bhattaṃ mā vivarā’’ ti bhariyāya pesesi. "
495007,111,2627,160,168,1,75,8,Sopi kho kaṭṭhahārako mukhato paviṭṭhena vālukodakena uddhumātaudaro palāyi. 
495008,111,2628,2,36,1,248,29,"Atheko tassa hatthācariyassa kulūpako dibbacakkhukatāpaso‘‘ mayhaṃ upaṭṭhāko hatthiṭṭhānaṃ na vijahati, kadā nu kho sampattiṃ pāpuṇissatī’’ ti dibbacakkhunā upadhārento taṃ purisaṃ disvā taṃ kāraṇaṃ ñatvā puretaraṃ gantvā hatthācariyassa nivesane nisīdi. "
495009,111,2628,37,56,1,120,14,Hatthācariyo āgantvā taṃ vanditvā ekamantaṃ nisinno taṃ bhattabhājanaṃ āharāpetvā‘‘ tāpasaṃ maṃsodanena parivisathā’’ ti āha. 
495010,111,2628,57,98,1,240,29,"Tāpaso bhattaṃ gahetvā maṃse dīyamāne aggahetvā‘‘ imaṃ maṃsaṃ ahaṃ vicāremī’’ ti vatvā‘‘ vicāretha , bhante’’ ti vutte thūlamaṃsādīni ekekaṃ koṭṭhāsaṃ kāretvā thūlamaṃsaṃ hatthācariyassa dāpesi, bahimaṃsaṃ tassa bhariyāya, aṭṭhimaṃsaṃ attanā paribhuñji. "
495011,111,2628,99,117,1,100,13,"So bhattakiccāvasāne gacchanto‘‘ tvaṃ ito tatiyadivase rājā bhavissasi, appamatto hohī’’ ti vatvā pakkāmi. "
495012,111,2628,118,124,1,57,6,Tatiyadivase eko sāmantarājā āgantvā bārāṇasiṃ parivāresi. 
