495157,111,2700,2,10,1,44,5,"Jaraggavā vicintesuṃ, varamhākaṃ bhusāmivā’’ ti. "
495158,111,2701,2,10,1,58,7,Tattha {bhusāmivā}ti bhusameva amhākaṃ varaṃ uttamanti attho. 
495159,111,2702,2,16,1,125,13,"Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā saccāni pakāsetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi, saccapariyosāne so bhikkhu sotāpattiphale patiṭṭhahi."
