495359,111,2790,2,4,1,11,2,5 . Kumbhavaggo
495360,111,2792,2,7,1,22,2,[ 291]1. Surāghaṭajātakavaṇṇanā 
495361,111,2793,2,15,1,101,11,Sabbakāmadadaṃ kumbhan ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto anāthapiṇḍikassa bhāgineyyaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
495362,111,2793,16,27,1,99,11,So kira mātāpitūnaṃ santakā cattālīsa hiraññakoṭiyo pānabyasanena nāsetvā seṭṭhino santikaṃ agamāsi. 
495363,111,2793,28,43,1,67,10,"Sopissa‘‘ vohāraṃ karohī’’ ti sahassaṃ adāsi, tampi nāsetvā puna agamāsi. "
495364,111,2793,44,56,1,79,11,"Punassa pañca satāni dāpesi, tānipi nāsetvā puna āgatassa dve thūlasāṭake dāpesi. "
495365,111,2793,57,64,1,53,7,Tepi nāsetvā puna āgataṃ gīvāyaṃ gāhāpetvā nīharāpesi. 
495366,111,2793,65,76,1,78,10,"So anātho hutvā parakuṭṭaṃ nissāya kālamakāsi, tamenaṃ kaḍḍhitvā bahi chaḍḍesuṃ. "
495367,111,2793,77,86,1,83,9,Anāthapiṇḍiko vihāraṃ gantvā sabbaṃ taṃ bhāgineyyassa pavattiṃ tathāgatassa ārocesi. 
495368,111,2793,87,110,1,138,18,"Satthā‘‘ tvaṃ etaṃ kathaṃ santappessasi, yamahaṃ pubbe sabbakāmadadaṃ kumbhaṃ datvāpi santappetuṃ nāsakkhin’’ ti vatvā tena yācito atītaṃ āhari. "
495369,111,2794,2,14,1,112,12,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto seṭṭhikule nibbattitvā pitu accayena seṭṭhiṭṭhānaṃ labhi. 
495370,111,2794,15,25,1,72,8,"Tassa gehe bhūmigatameva cattālīsakoṭidhanaṃ ahosi, putto panassa ekoyeva. "
495371,111,2794,26,35,1,72,9,Bodhisatto dānādīni puññāni katvā kālakato sakko devarājā hutvā nibbatti. 
495372,111,2794,36,47,1,92,11,Athassa putto vīthiṃ āvaritvā maṇḍapaṃ kāretvā mahājanaparivuto nisīditvā suraṃ pātuṃ ārabhi. 
495373,111,2794,48,84,1,306,29,"So laṅghanadhāvananaccagītādīni karontānaṃ sahassaṃ sahassaṃ dadamāno itthisoṇḍasurāsoṇḍamaṃsasoṇḍādibhāvaṃ āpajjitvā‘‘ kva gītaṃ, kva naccaṃ, kva vāditan’’ ti samajjatthiko pamatto hutvā āhiṇḍanto nacirasseva cattālīsakoṭidhanaṃ upabhogaparibhogūpakaraṇāni ca vināsetvā duggato kapaṇo pilotikaṃ nivāsetvā vicari. "
495374,111,2794,85,126,1,242,33,"Sakko āvajjento tassa duggatabhāvaṃ ñatvā puttapemena āgantvā sabbakāmadadaṃ kumbhaṃ datvā‘‘ tāta, yathā ayaṃ kumbho na bhijjati, tathā naṃ rakkha, imasmiṃ te sati dhanassa paricchedo nāma na bhavissati, appamatto hohī’’ ti ovaditvā devalokameva gato. "
495375,111,2794,127,132,1,34,5,Tato paṭṭhāya suraṃ pivanto vicari. 
495376,111,2794,133,148,1,110,13,"Athekadivasaṃ matto taṃ kumbhaṃ ākāse khipitvā sampaṭicchanto ekavāraṃ virajjhi , kumbho bhūmiyaṃ patitvā bhijji. "
