495402,111,2810,2,7,1,20,2,[ 292]2. Supattajātakavaṇṇanā 
495403,111,2811,2,20,1,153,14,"Bārāṇasyaṃ , {mahārājā}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto bimbādeviyā sāriputtattherena dinnaṃ rohitamaccharasaṃ navasappimissakaṃ sālibhattaṃ ārabbha kathesi. "
495404,111,2811,21,35,1,55,5,Vatthu heṭṭhā kathita abbhantarajātake( jā.1.3.91-93) vatthusadisameva. 
495405,111,2811,36,45,1,63,8,"Tadāpi hi theriyā udaravāto kuppi, rāhulabhaddo therassa ācikkhi. "
495406,111,2811,46,59,1,132,13,Thero taṃ āsanasālāyaṃ nisīdāpetvā kosalarañño nivesanaṃ gantvā rohitamaccharasaṃ navasappimissakaṃ sālibhattaṃ āharitvā tassa adāsi. 
495407,111,2811,60,70,1,75,9,"So āharitvā mātu theriyā adāsi, tassā bhuttamattāya udaravāto paṭippassambhi. "
495408,111,2811,71,81,1,82,10,Rājā purise pesetvā pariggaṇhāpetvā tato paṭṭhāya theriyā tathārūpaṃ bhattaṃ adāsi. 
495409,111,2811,82,87,1,57,5,Athekadivasaṃ bhikkhū dhammasabhāyaṃ kathaṃ samuṭṭhāpesuṃ–
495410,111,2811,88,101,1,66,8,"‘‘ āvuso dhammasenāpati, theriṃ evarūpena nāma bhojanena santappesī’’ ti. "
495411,111,2811,102,146,1,195,27,"Satthā āgantvā‘‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ imāya nāmā’’ ti vutte‘‘ na, bhikkhave, idāneva sāriputto rāhulamātāya patthitaṃ deti, pubbepi adāsiyevā’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
495412,111,2812,2,29,1,216,25,"Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto kākayoniyaṃ nibbattitvā vayappatto asītiyā kākasahassānaṃ jeṭṭhako supatto nāma kākarājā ahosi, aggamahesī panassa suphassā nāma kākī ahosi, senāpati sumukho nāma. "
495413,111,2812,30,37,1,59,7,So asītiyā kākasahassehi parivuto bārāṇasiṃ upanissāya vasi. 
495414,111,2812,38,48,1,90,9,So ekadivasaṃ suphassaṃ ādāya gocaraṃ pariyesanto bārāṇasirañño mahānasamatthakena agamāsi. 
495415,111,2812,49,60,1,113,11,Sūdo rañño nānāmacchamaṃsavikatiparivāraṃ bhojanaṃ sampādetvā thokaṃ bhājanāni vivaritvā usumaṃ palāpento aṭṭhāsi. 
495416,111,2812,61,128,1,329,44,"Suphassā macchamaṃsagandhaṃ ghāyitvā rājabhojanaṃ bhuñjitukāmā hutvā taṃ divasaṃ akathetvā dutiyadivase‘‘ ehi, bhadde, gocarāya gamissāmā’’ ti vuttā‘‘ tumhe gacchatha, mayhaṃ eko dohaḷo atthī’’ ti vatvā‘‘ kīdiso dohaḷo’’ ti vutte‘‘ bārāṇasirañño bhojanaṃ bhuñjitukāmāmhi, na kho pana sakkā mayā taṃ laddhuṃ, tasmā jīvitaṃ pariccajissāmi, devā’’ ti āha. "
495417,111,2812,129,132,1,29,3,Bodhisatto cintayamāno nisīdi. 
495418,111,2812,133,150,1,74,10,"Sumukho āgantvā‘‘ kiṃ, mahārāja, anattamanosī’’ ti pucchi, rājā tamatthaṃ ārocesi. "
495419,111,2812,151,179,1,117,18,"Senāpati‘‘ mā cintayi, mahārājā’’ ti te ubhopi assāsetvā‘‘ ajja tumhe idheva hotha, mayaṃ bhattaṃ āharissāmā’’ ti vatvā pakkāmi. "
495420,111,2813,2,41,1,282,34,So kāke sannipātetvā taṃ kāraṇaṃ kathetvā‘‘ etha bhattaṃ āharissāmā’’ ti kākehi saddhiṃ bārāṇasiṃ pavisitvā mahānasassa avidūre kāke vagge vagge katvā tasmiṃ tasmiṃ ṭhāne ārakkhatthāya ṭhapetvā sayaṃ aṭṭhahi kākayodhehi saddhiṃ mahānasachadane nisīdi rañño bhattaharaṇakālaṃ olokayamāno. 
495421,111,2813,42,46,1,14,4,Te ca kāke āha–
495422,111,2813,47,92,1,264,33,"‘‘ ahaṃ rañño bhatte hariyamāne bhājanāni pātessāmi, bhājanesu patitesu mayhaṃ jīvitaṃ natthi, tumhesu cattāro janā mukhapūraṃ bhattaṃ, cattāro macchamaṃsaṃ gahetvā netvā supattaṃ sapajāpatikaṃ kākarājānaṃ bhojetha,‘ kahaṃ senāpatī’ ti vutte‘ pacchato ehitī’ ti vadeyyāthā’’ ti. "
495423,111,2813,93,102,1,73,9,Atha sūdo rañño bhojanavikatiṃ sampādetvā kājena gahetvā rājakulaṃ pāyāsi. 
