495502,111,2849,14,44,1,269,25,"Tadā hi devadatte parihīnalābhasakkāre kokāliko kulāni upasaṅkamitvā‘‘ devadattatthero nāma mahāsammatapaveṇiyā okkākarājavaṃse jāto asambhinnakhattiyavaṃse vaḍḍhito tipiṭakadharo jhānalābhī madhurakatho dhammakathiko, detha karotha therassā’’ ti devadattassa vaṇṇaṃ bhāsati. "
