495637,111,2932,73,87,1,74,9,‘‘ ekenupāyena imaṃ bhikkhuṃ vañcetvā nikkaḍḍhitvā imaṃ vihāraṃ gaṇhissāmī’’ ti. 
495638,111,2932,88,93,1,37,5,Atha naṃ therūpaṭṭhānaṃ āgataṃ pucchi–
495639,111,2932,94,105,1,35,5,"‘‘ kiṃ, āvuso, buddhūpaṭṭhānaṃ nākāsī’’ ti?"
495640,111,2932,106,121,1,63,9,"‘‘ Bhante, imaṃ vihāraṃ paṭijagganto natthi, tenamhi na gatapubbo’’ ti."
495641,111,2932,122,136,1,68,8,"‘‘ Yāva tvaṃ buddhūpaṭṭhānaṃ gantvā āgacchasi, tāvāhaṃ paṭijaggissāmī’’ ti."
495642,111,2932,137,159,1,89,13,"‘‘ Sādhu, bhante’’ ti nevāsiko‘‘ yāva mamāgamanā there mā pamajjitthā’’ ti manussānaṃ vatvā pakkāmi. "
495643,111,2933,2,18,1,84,12,Tato paṭṭhāya āgantuko‘‘ tassa nevāsikassa ayañca ayañca doso’’ ti te manusse paribhindi. 
495644,111,2933,19,29,1,65,9,"Itaropi satthāraṃ vanditvā punāgato, athassa so senāsanaṃ na adāsi. "
495645,111,2933,30,43,1,90,12,"So ekasmiṃ ṭhāne vasitvā punadivase piṇḍāya gāmaṃ pāvisi, manussā sāmīcimattampi na kariṃsu. "
495646,111,2933,44,54,1,73,10,So vippaṭisārī hutvā puna jetavanaṃ gantvā taṃ kāraṇaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ ārocesi. 
495647,111,2933,55,60,1,46,5,Te bhikkhū dhammasabhāyaṃ kathaṃ samuṭṭhāpesuṃ–
495648,111,2933,61,78,1,81,12,"‘‘ āvuso, asuko kira bhikkhu asukaṃ bhikkhuṃ vihārā nikkaḍḍhitvā sayaṃ tattha vasī’’ ti. "
495649,111,2933,79,122,1,182,26,"Satthā āgantvā‘‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ imāya nāmā’’ ti vutte‘‘ na, bhikkhave, idāneva, pubbepi so imaṃ vasanaṭṭhānā nikkaḍḍhiyevā’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
495650,111,2934,2,12,1,90,10,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto araññe rukkhadevatā hutvā nibbatti. 
