495652,111,2934,19,31,1,124,11,Atheko rattamukhakhuddakamakkaṭo ekissā anovassikāya pāsāṇadariyā vasamāno ekadivasaṃ daridvāre atemanaṭṭhāne sukhena nisīdi. 
495653,111,2934,32,62,1,217,26,Tattha eko kāḷamukhamahāmakkaṭo tinto sītena pīḷiyamāno vicaranto taṃ tathānisinnaṃ disvā‘‘ upāyena naṃ nīharitvā ettha vasissāmī’’ ti cintetvā kucchiṃ olambetvā suhitākāraṃ dassetvā tassa purato ṭhatvā paṭhamaṃ gāthamāha– 
