495710,111,2964,25,46,1,117,19,"Tuvan ti tesu ekaṃ tāpasaṃ ālapanto idāni mā maṃ tvaṃ pure viya sañjāni, nāhaṃ purimasadiso, ācariyo me laddhoti dīpeti. "
