495818,112,15,2,10,1,44,5,"Sīhena susiṭṭhena, surakkhitaṃ nandisenenā’’ ti. "
495819,112,16,2,20,1,117,14,"Tattha {aruṇarājassā}ti so hi rajje patiṭṭhitakāle raṭṭhanāmavasena assako nāma jāto, kuladattiyaṃ panassa nāmaṃ aruṇoti . "
495820,112,16,21,28,1,22,3,Tenāha‘‘ aruṇarājassā’’ ti. 
495821,112,16,29,32,1,21,2,{Sīhenā}ti purisasīhena. 
495822,112,16,33,38,1,41,4,{Susiṭṭhenā}ti ācariyehi suṭṭhu anusāsitena. 
495823,112,16,39,44,1,35,4,{Nandisenenā}ti mayā nandisenena nāma. 
495824,112,17,2,54,1,316,40,"So evaṃ vatvā dvāraṃ vivarāpetvā tā gahetvā assakarañño datvā‘‘ tumhe mā bhāyittha, yuddhe sati ahaṃ jinissāmi, imā uttamarūpadharā rājadhītaro mahesiyo karothā’’ ti tāsaṃ abhisekaṃ dāpetvā tāhi saddhiṃ āgate purise‘‘ gacchatha, tumhe rājadhītūnaṃ assakarājena mahesiṭṭhāne ṭhapitabhāvaṃ tumhākaṃ rañño ācikkhathā’’ ti uyyojesi. "
495825,112,17,55,58,1,18,3,Te gantvā ārocesuṃ. 
495826,112,17,59,77,1,84,14,Kāliṅgo‘‘ na hi nūna so mayhaṃ balaṃ jānātī’’ ti vatvā tāvadeva mahatiyā senāya nikkhami. 
495827,112,17,78,105,1,162,21,"Nandiseno tassa āgamanaṃ ñatvā‘‘ attano kira rajjasīmāyameva hotu, mā amhākaṃ rañño rajjasīmaṃ okkamatu, ubhinnaṃ rajjānaṃ antare yuddhaṃ bhavissatī’’ ti sāsanaṃ pesesi. "
495828,112,17,106,112,1,50,6,So sāsanaṃ sutvā attano rajjapariyanteyeva aṭṭhāsi. 
495829,112,17,113,117,1,38,4,Assakopi attano rajjapariyante aṭṭhāsi. 
495830,112,17,118,128,1,89,10,Tadā bodhisatto isipabbajjaṃ pabbajitvā tesaṃ dvinnaṃ rajjānaṃ antare paṇṇasālāyaṃ vasati. 
495831,112,17,129,189,1,349,45,"Kāliṅgo cintesi‘‘ samaṇā nāma kiñci jānissanti, ko jānāti, kiṃ bhavissati, kassa jayo vā parājayo vā bhavissati, tāpasaṃ pucchissāmī’’ ti aññātakavesena bodhisattaṃ upasaṅkamitvā vanditvā ekamantaṃ nisīditvā paṭisanthāraṃ katvā‘‘ bhante, kāliṅgo ca assako ca yujjhitukāmā attano attano rajjasīmāyameva ṭhitā, etesu kassa jayo bhavissati, kassa parājayo’’ ti pucchi. "
495832,112,17,190,217,1,140,18,"Mahāpuñña, ahaṃ‘‘ asukassa jayo, asukassa parājayo’’ ti na jānāmi, sakko pana devarājā idhāgacchati, tamahaṃ pucchitvā kathessāmi, sve āgaccheyyāsīti. "
495833,112,17,218,230,1,82,10,"Sakko bodhisattassa upaṭṭhānaṃ āgantvā nisīdi, atha naṃ bodhisatto tamatthaṃ pucchi. "
495834,112,17,231,242,1,84,8,"Bhante, kāliṅgo jinissati, assako parājissati, idañcidañca pubbanimittaṃ paññāyissatīti. "
495835,112,18,2,9,1,57,6,"Kāliṅgo punadivase āgantvā pucchi, bodhisattopissa ācikkhi. "
495836,112,18,10,32,1,100,14,So‘‘ kiṃ nāma pubbanimittaṃ bhavissatī’’ ti apucchitvāva‘‘ ahaṃ kira jinissāmī’’ ti uṭṭhāya tuṭṭhiyā pakkāmi. 
495837,112,18,33,37,1,25,4,Sā kathā vitthārikā ahosi. 
495838,112,18,38,61,1,109,16,"Taṃ sutvā assako nandisenaṃ pakkosāpetvā‘‘ kāliṅgo kira jinissatiṃ , mayaṃ parājissāma, kiṃ nu kho kātabban’’ ti āha. "
495839,112,18,62,102,1,192,28,"So‘‘ ko etaṃ jānāti mahārāja, kassa jayo vā parājayo vā, tumhe mā cintayitthā’’ ti rājānaṃ assāsetvā bodhisattaṃ upasaṅkamitvā vanditvā ekamantaṃ nisinno‘‘ bhante, ko jinissati, ko parājissatī’’ ti pucchi."
495840,112,18,103,113,1,39,5,"‘‘ Kāliṅgo jinissati, assako parājissatī’’ ti?"
495841,112,18,114,128,1,68,8,"‘‘ Bhante, jinantassa pubbanimittaṃ kiṃ bhavissati, kiṃ parājinantassā’’ ti?"
495842,112,18,129,150,1,146,14,"‘‘ Mahāpuñña, jinantassa ārakkhadevatā sabbaseto usabho bhavissati, itarassa sabbakāḷako, ubhinnampi ārakkhadevatā yujjhitvā jayaparājayaṃ karissantī’’ ti. "
495843,112,18,151,177,1,162,21,"Nandiseno taṃ sutvā uṭṭhāya gantvā rañño sahāye sahassamatte mahāyodhe gahetvā avidūre pabbataṃ abhiruyha‘‘ ambho, amhākaṃ rañño jīvitaṃ dātuṃ sakkhissathā’’ ti pucchi."
495844,112,18,178,186,1,18,3,"‘‘ Āma, sakkhissāmā’’ ti."
