495848,112,18,224,226,1,18,2,Te sampaṭicchiṃsuṃ. 
495849,112,19,2,41,1,211,27,"Atha saṅgāme upaṭṭhite kāliṅgo‘‘ ahaṃ kira jinissāmī’’ ti vosānaṃ āpajji, balakāyāpissa‘‘ amhākaṃ kira jayo’’ ti vosānaṃ āpajjitvā sannāhaṃ akatvā vaggavaggā hutvā yathāruci pakkamiṃsu, vīriyakaraṇakāle vīriyaṃ na kariṃsu. "
495850,112,19,42,54,1,71,8,Ubhopi rājāno assaṃ abhiruhitvā‘‘ yujjhissāmā’’ ti aññamaññaṃ upasaṅkamanti. 
495851,112,19,55,67,1,107,11,"Ubhinnaṃ ārakkhadevatā purato gantvā kāliṅgarañño ārakkhadevatā sabbaseto usabho ahosi, itarassa sabbakāḷako. "
