496253,112,212,2,15,1,94,12,Sabbamidaṃ carimaṃ katan ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto chabbaggiye bhikkhū ārabbha kathesi. 
496254,112,212,16,25,1,34,4,Vatthu vinaye( pāci.646) vitthārato āgatameva. 
496255,112,212,26,90,1,346,45,"Ayaṃ panettha saṅkhepo– satthā chabbaggiye pakkosāpetvā‘‘ saccaṃ kira tumhe, bhikkhave, nīce āsane nisīditvā ucce āsane nisinnassa dhammaṃ desethā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ evaṃ, bhante’’ ti vutte te bhikkhū garahitvā‘‘ ayuttaṃ, bhikkhave, tumhākaṃ mama dhamme agāravakaraṇaṃ, porāṇakapaṇḍitā hi nīce āsane nisīditvā bāhirakamantepi vācente garahiṃsū’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
496256,112,213,2,14,1,110,11,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto caṇḍālakule nibbattitvā vayappatto kuṭumbaṃ saṇṭhapesi. 
496257,112,213,15,31,1,74,11,"Tassa bhariyā ambadohaḷinī hutvā taṃ āha‘‘ sāmi, icchāmahaṃ ambaṃ khāditun’’ ti."
496258,112,213,32,48,1,71,10,"‘‘ Bhadde, imasmiṃ kāle ambaṃ natthi, aññaṃ kiñci ambilaphalaṃ āharissāmī’’ ti."
496259,112,213,49,64,1,71,9,"‘‘ Sāmi, ambaphalaṃ labhamānāva jīvissāmi, alabhamānāya me jīvitaṃ natthī’’ ti. "
496260,112,213,65,80,1,70,10,So tassā paṭibaddhacitto ‘‘ kahaṃ nu kho ambaphalaṃ labhissāmī’’ ti cintesi. 
496261,112,213,81,90,1,64,9,Tena kho pana samayena bārāṇasirañño uyyāne ambo dhuvaphalo hoti. 
496262,112,213,91,114,1,153,19,So‘‘ tato ambapakkaṃ āharitvā imissā dohaḷaṃ paṭippassambhessāmī’’ ti rattibhāge uyyānaṃ gantvā ambaṃ abhiruhitvā nilīno sākhāya sākhaṃ ambaṃ olokento vicari. 
496263,112,213,115,120,1,38,5,Tassa tathā karontasseva ratti vibhāyi. 
496264,112,213,121,143,1,94,14,"So cintesi‘‘ sace idāni otaritvā gamissāmi, disvā maṃ‘ coro’ ti gaṇhissanti, rattibhāge gamissāmī’’ ti. "
496265,112,213,144,149,1,40,5,Athekaṃ viṭapaṃ abhiruhitvā nilīno acchi. 
496266,112,214,2,25,1,159,19,Tadā bārāṇasirājā‘‘ purohitassa santike mante uggaṇhissāmī’’ ti uyyānaṃ pavisitvā ambarukkhamūle ucce āsane nisīditvā ācariyaṃ nīce āsane nisīdāpetvā mante uggaṇhi. 
496267,112,214,26,30,1,31,4,Bodhisatto upari nilīno cintesi–
496268,112,214,31,43,1,62,9,"‘‘ yāva adhammiko ayaṃ rājā, yo uccāsane nisīditvā mante uggaṇhāti. "
496269,112,214,44,53,1,60,8,"Ayaṃ brāhmaṇopi adhammiko, yo nīcāsane nisīditvā mante vāceti. "
496270,112,214,54,69,1,83,12,"Ahampi adhammiko, yo mātugāmassa vasaṃ gantvā mama jīvitaṃ agaṇetvā ambaṃ āharāmī’’ ti. "
496271,112,214,70,97,1,136,19,"So rukkhato otaranto ekaṃ olambanasākhaṃ gahetvā tesaṃ ubhinnampi antare patiṭṭhāya‘‘ mahārāja, ahaṃ naṭṭho, tvaṃ mūḷho, purohito mato’’ ti āha. "
496272,112,214,98,109,1,47,7,So raññā‘‘ kiṃkāraṇā’’ ti puṭṭho paṭhamaṃ gāthamāha– 
496273,112,215,2,4,1,0,0,33.
496274,112,216,2,12,1,48,8,"‘ ‘ Sabbamidaṃ carimaṃ kataṃ, ubho dhammaṃ na passare; "
496275,112,217,2,9,1,41,6,"Ubho pakatiyā cutā, yo cāyaṃ mantejjhāpeti; "
496276,112,218,2,9,1,24,5,Yo ca mantaṃ adhīyatī’’ ti. 
496277,112,219,2,19,1,114,16,"Tattha sabbamidaṃ carimaṃ katan ti yaṃ amhehi tīhi janehi kataṃ, sabbaṃ idaṃ kiccaṃ lāmakaṃ nimmariyādaṃ adhammikaṃ. "
496278,112,219,20,41,1,121,16,Evaṃ attano corabhāvaṃ tesañca mantesu agāravaṃ garahitvā puna itare dveyeva garahanto‘‘ ubho dhammaṃ na passare’’ tiādimāha. 
496279,112,219,42,56,1,95,12,"Tattha {ubho}ti ime dvepi janā garukārārahaṃ porāṇakadhammaṃ na passanti, tato dhammapakatito cutā. "
496280,112,219,57,62,1,41,5,Dhammo hi paṭhamuppattivasena pakati nāma. 
496281,112,219,63,65,1,14,2,Vuttampi cetaṃ–
