496288,112,226,2,13,1,45,8,"Tasmā etaṃ na sevāmi, dhammaṃ isīhi sevitan’’ ti. "
496289,112,227,2,30,1,207,26,"Tassattho – ahañhi bho imassa rañño santakaṃ sālīnaṃ odanaṃ suciṃ paṇḍaraṃ nānappakārāya maṃsavikatiyā sittaṃ maṃsūpasecanaṃ bhuñjāmi, tasmā udare baddho hutvā etaṃ esitaguṇehi isīhi sevitaṃ dhammaṃ na sevāmīti. "
