496296,112,234,2,11,1,41,6,"Yā vutti vinipātena, adhammacaraṇena vā’’ ti. "
496297,112,235,2,8,1,38,5,Tattha {paribbajā}ti ito aññattha gaccha. 
496298,112,235,9,15,1,26,5,{Mahā}ti ayaṃ loko nāma mahā. 
496299,112,235,16,27,1,77,9,"Pacantaññepi {pāṇino}ti imasmiṃ jambudīpe aññepi pāṇino pacanti, nāyameveko rājā. "
496300,112,235,28,34,1,41,5,Asmā {kumbhamivābhidā}ti pāsāṇo ghaṭaṃ viya. 
496301,112,235,35,58,1,129,21,"Idaṃ vuttaṃ hoti– yaṃ tvaṃ aññattha agantvā idha vasanto adhammaṃ ācarasi, so adhammo evaṃ ācarito pāsāṇo ghaṭaṃ viya mā taṃ bhindi."
496302,112,236,2,26,1,120,19,"‘ ‘ Dhiratthū’’ ti gāthāya ayaṃ saṅkhepattho– brāhmaṇa yo esa evaṃ tava yasalābho ca dhanalābho ca dhiratthu, taṃ garahāma mayaṃ. "
496303,112,236,27,28,1,5,1,Kasmā? 
496304,112,236,29,63,1,213,29,"Yasmā ayaṃ tayā laddhalābho āyatiṃ apāyesu vinipātanahetunā sampati ca adhammacaraṇena jīvitavutti nāma hoti, yā cesā vutti iminā āyatiṃ vinipātena idha adhammacaraṇena vā nippajjati, kiṃ tāya, tena taṃ evaṃ vadāmīti. "
496305,112,237,2,17,1,69,9,"Athassa dhammakathāya rājā pasīditvā‘‘ bho, purisa, kiṃjātikosī’’ ti pucchi."
496306,112,237,18,27,1,20,4,"‘‘ Caṇḍālo ahaṃ, devā’’ ti. "
496307,112,237,28,66,1,220,31,"Bho‘‘ sace tvaṃ jātisampanno abhavisssa, rajjaṃ te ahaṃ adassaṃ, ito paṭṭhāya pana ahaṃ divā rājā bhavissāmi, tvaṃ rattiṃ rājā hohī’’ ti attano kaṇṭhe piḷandhanaṃ pupphadāmaṃ tassa gīvāyaṃ piḷandhāpetvā taṃ nagaraguttikaṃ akāsi. "
496308,112,237,67,71,1,59,4,Ayaṃ nagaraguttikānaṃ kaṇṭhe rattapupphadāmapiḷandhanavaṃso. 
496309,112,237,72,86,1,99,14,Tato paṭṭhāya pana rājā tassovāde ṭhatvā ācariye gāravaṃ karitvā nīce āsane nisinno mante uggaṇhīti. 
496310,112,238,2,22,1,113,15,"Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi‘‘ tadā rājā ānando ahosi, caṇḍālaputto pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
496311,112,239,2,4,1,25,2,Chavajātakavaṇṇanā navamā.
496312,112,241,2,7,1,18,2,[ 310]10. Seyyajātakavaṇṇanā 
496313,112,242,2,12,1,87,9,Sasamuddapariyāyan ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ukkaṇṭhitabhikkhuṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
496314,112,242,13,26,1,108,13,So hi sāvatthiyaṃ piṇḍāya caranto ekaṃ abhirūpaṃ alaṅkatapaṭiyattaṃ itthiṃ disvā ukkaṇṭhito sāsane nābhirami. 
496315,112,242,27,31,1,31,4,Atha bhikkhū bhagavato ārocesuṃ. 
496316,112,242,32,65,1,130,20,"So bhagavatā‘‘ saccaṃ kira tvaṃ bhikkhu ukkaṇṭhitosī’’ ti puṭṭho‘‘ saccaṃ, bhante’’ ti vatvā‘‘ ko taṃ ukkaṇṭhāpesī’’ ti vutte tamatthaṃ ārocesi. "
496317,112,242,66,89,1,157,18,"Satthā‘‘ kasmā tvaṃ evarūpe niyyānikasāsane pabbajitvā ukkaṇṭhitosi, pubbe paṇḍitā purohitaṭṭhānaṃ labhantāpi taṃ paṭikkhipitvā pabbajiṃsū’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
496318,112,243,2,19,1,148,16,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto purohitassa brāhmaṇiyā kucchimhi paṭisandhiṃ gaṇhitvā rañño puttena saddhiṃ ekadivase vijāyi. 
496319,112,243,20,37,1,73,13,Rājā‘‘ atthi nu kho koci me puttena saddhiṃ ekadivase jāto’’ ti amacce pucchi.
496320,112,243,38,49,1,35,5,"‘‘ Atthi, mahārāja, purohitassa putto’’ ti. "
496321,112,243,50,59,1,72,9,Rājā taṃ āharāpetvā dhātīnaṃ datvā puttena saddhiṃ ekatova paṭijaggāpesi. 
496322,112,243,60,67,1,64,7,Ubhinnaṃ ābharaṇāni ceva pānabhojanādīni ca ekasadisāneva ahesuṃ. 
496323,112,243,68,77,1,72,8,Te vayappattā ekatova takkasilaṃ gantvā sabbasippāni uggaṇhitvā āgamaṃsu. 
496324,112,243,78,85,1,44,6,"Rājā puttassa oparajjaṃ adāsi, mahāyaso ahosi. "
496325,112,243,86,100,1,105,13,"Tato paṭṭhāya bodhisatto rājaputtena saddhiṃ ekatova khādati pivati sayati, aññamaññaṃ vissāso thiro ahosi. "
496326,112,244,2,10,1,74,8,Aparabhāge rājaputto pitu accayena rajje patiṭṭhāya mahāsampattiṃ anubhavi. 
496327,112,244,11,35,1,164,17,"Bodhisatto cintesi‘‘ mayhaṃ sahāyo rajjamanusāsati, sallakkhitakkhaṇeyeva kho pana mayhaṃ purohitaṭṭhānaṃ dassati, kiṃ me gharāvāsena, pabbajitvā vivekamanubrūhessāmī’’ ti? "
496328,112,244,36,61,1,237,25,So mātāpitaro vanditvā pabbajjaṃ anujānāpetvā mahāsampattiṃ chaḍḍetvā ekakova nikkhamitvā himavantaṃ pavisitvā manorame bhūmibhāge paṇṇasālaṃ māpetvā isipabbajjaṃ pabbajitvā abhiññā ca samāpattiyo ca nibbattetvā jhānakīḷaṃ kīḷanto vihāsi. 
496329,112,244,62,79,1,71,12,"Tadā rājā taṃ anussaritvā‘‘ mayhaṃ sahāyo na paññāyati, kahaṃ so’’ ti pucchi. "
496330,112,244,80,94,1,78,10,Amaccā tassa pabbajitabhāvaṃ ārocetvā‘‘ ramaṇīye kira vanasaṇḍe vasatī’’ ti āhaṃsu. 
496331,112,244,95,117,1,117,16,"Rājā tassa vasanokāsaṃ pucchitvā seyyaṃ nāma amaccaṃ‘‘ gaccha sahāyaṃ me gahetvā ehi, purohitaṭṭhānamassa dassāmī’’ ti āha. "
496332,112,244,118,166,1,340,37,"So‘‘ sādhū’’ ti paṭissuṇitvā bārāṇasito nikkhamitvā anupubbena paccantagāmaṃ patvā tattha khandhāvāraṃ ṭhapetvā vanacarakehi saddhiṃ bodhisattassa vasanokāsaṃ gantvā bodhisattaṃ paṇṇasāladvāre suvaṇṇapaṭimaṃ viya nisinnaṃ disvā vanditvā ekamantaṃ nisīditvā katapaṭisanthāro‘‘ bhante, rājā tuyhaṃ purohitaṭṭhānaṃ dātukāmo, āgamanaṃ te icchatī’’ ti āha. "
496333,112,245,2,36,1,238,27,"Bodhisatto ‘‘ tiṭṭhatu purohitaṭṭhānaṃ, ahaṃ sakalaṃ kāsikosalajambudīparajjaṃ cakkavattisirimeva vā labhantopi na gacchissāmi, na hi paṇḍitā sakiṃ jahitakilese puna gaṇhanti, sakiṃ jahitañhi niṭṭhubhakheḷasadisaṃ hotī’’ ti vatvā imā gāthā abhāsi– "
