496347,112,258,21,29,1,78,8,Sāgarakuṇḍalan ti sāgaramajjhe dīpavasena ṭhitattā tassa kuṇḍalabhūtanti attho. 
496348,112,258,30,39,1,81,8,{Nindāyā}ti jhānasukhasampannaṃ pabbajjaṃ chaḍḍetvā issariyaṃ gaṇhīti imāya nindāya. 
496349,112,258,40,44,1,24,3,{Seyyā}ti taṃ nāmenālapati. 
496350,112,258,45,49,1,27,3,{Vijānahī}ti dhammaṃ vijānāhi. 
496351,112,258,50,71,1,203,19,"Yā vutti {vinipātenā}ti yā purohitaṭṭhānavasena laddhā yasalābhadhanalābhavutti jhānasukhato attavinipātanasaṅkhātena vinipātena ito gantvā issariyamadamattassa adhammacaraṇena vā hoti, taṃ vuttiṃ dhiratthu. "
496352,112,259,2,7,1,37,3,{Pattamādāyā}ti bhikkhābhājanaṃ gahetvā. 
496353,112,259,8,15,1,52,6,{Anagāro}ti api ahaṃ agāravirahito parakulesu careyyaṃ. 
496354,112,259,16,25,1,47,8,Sāyeva {jīvikā}ti sā eva me jīvikā seyyo varatarā. 
496355,112,259,26,34,1,43,7,Yā cādhammena {esanā}ti yā ca adhammena esanā. 
496356,112,259,35,47,1,67,10,"Idaṃ vuttaṃ hoti– yā adhammena esanā, tato esāva jīvikā sundaratarāti. "
496357,112,259,48,51,1,24,3,Ahiṃsayan ti aviheṭhento. 
496358,112,259,52,64,1,98,11,Api {rajjenā}ti evaṃ paraṃ aviheṭhento kapālahatthassa mama jīvikakappanaṃ rajjenāpi varaṃ uttamanti. 
496359,112,260,2,8,1,43,6,Iti so punappunaṃ yācantampi taṃ paṭikkhipi. 
496360,112,260,9,20,1,85,11,Seyyopi tassa manaṃ alabhitvā taṃ vanditvā gantvā tassa anāgamanabhāvaṃ rañño ārocesi. 
496361,112,261,2,21,1,178,16,"Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā saccāni pakāsetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi, saccapariyosāne ukkaṇṭhitabhikkhu sotāpattiphale patiṭṭhahi, aparepi bahū sotāpattiphalādīni sacchikariṃsu. "
