496416,112,295,2,15,1,91,11,Api kassapa {mandiyā}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ekaṃ mahallakabhikkhuṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
496417,112,295,16,31,1,127,15,Sāvatthiyaṃ kireko kulaputto kāmesu ādīnavaṃ disvā satthu santike pabbajitvā kammaṭṭhāne anuyutto na cirasseva arahattaṃ pāpuṇi. 
496418,112,295,32,36,1,32,4,Tassa aparabhāge mātā kālamakāsi. 
496419,112,295,37,59,1,218,22,So mātu accayena pitarañca kaniṭṭhabhātarañca pabbājetvā jetavane vasitvā vassūpanāyikasamaye cīvarapaccayassa sulabhataṃ sutvā ekaṃ gāmakāvāsaṃ gantvā tayopi tattheva vassaṃ upagantvā vutthavassā jetavanameva āgamaṃsu. 
496420,112,295,60,81,1,146,16,"Daharabhikkhu jetavanassa āsannaṭṭhāne‘‘ sāmaṇera tvaṃ theraṃ vissāmetvā āneyyāsi, ahaṃ puretaraṃ gantvā pariveṇaṃ paṭijaggissāmī’’ ti jetavanaṃ pāvisi. "
496421,112,295,82,85,1,33,3,Mahallakatthero saṇikaṃ āgacchati. 
496422,112,295,86,106,1,93,13,"Sāmaṇero punappunaṃ sīsena uppīḷento viya‘‘ gaccha, bhante, gaccha, bhante’’ ti taṃ balakkārena neti. "
496423,112,295,107,123,1,78,12,Thero‘‘ tvaṃ maṃ attano vasaṃ ānesī’’ ti puna nivattitvā koṭito paṭṭhāya āgacchati. 
496424,112,295,124,134,1,77,9,"Tesaṃ evaṃ aññamaññaṃ kalahaṃ karontānaññeva sūriyo atthaṅgato, andhakāro jāto. "
496425,112,296,2,26,1,153,19,Itaropi pariveṇaṃ sammajjitvā udakaṃ upaṭṭhapetvā tesaṃ āgamanaṃ apassanto ukkaṃ gahetvā paccuggamanaṃ katvā te āgacchante disvā‘‘ kiṃ cirāyitthā’’ ti pucchi. 
496426,112,296,27,31,1,29,4,Mahallako taṃ kāraṇaṃ kathesi. 
496427,112,296,32,38,1,36,6,So te dvepi vissāmetvā saṇikaṃ ānesi. 
496428,112,296,39,45,1,45,6,Taṃ divasaṃ buddhupaṭṭhānassa okāsaṃ na labhi. 
496429,112,296,46,62,1,93,12,Atha naṃ dutiyadivase buddhupaṭṭhānaṃ āgantvā vanditvā nisinnaṃ satthā‘‘ kadā āgatosī’’ ti pucchi.
496430,112,296,63,71,1,15,3,"‘‘ Hiyyo, bhante’’ ti."
