496697,112,403,2,7,1,24,2,[ 316]6. Sasapaṇḍitajātakavaṇṇanā 
496698,112,404,2,15,1,92,11,Satta me rohitā {macchā}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto sabbaparikkhāradānaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
496699,112,404,16,47,1,359,31,Sāvatthiyaṃ kira eko kuṭumbiko buddhappamukhassa bhikkhusaṅghassa sabbaparikkhāradānaṃ sajjetvā gharadvāre maṇḍapaṃ kāretvā buddhappamukhaṃ bhikkhusaṅghaṃ nimantetvā susajjitamaṇḍape paññattavarāsane nisīdāpetvā nānaggarasaṃ paṇītadānaṃ datvā puna svātanāyāti sattāhaṃ nimantetvā sattame divase buddhappamukhānaṃ pañcannaṃ bhikkhusatānaṃ sabbaparikkhāre adāsi. 
496700,112,404,48,83,1,243,28,"Satthā bhattakiccāvasāne anumodanaṃ karonto‘‘ upāsaka, tayā pītisomanassaṃ kātuṃ vaṭṭati, idañhi dānaṃ nāma porāṇakapaṇḍitānaṃ vaṃso, porāṇakapaṇḍitā hi sampattayācakānaṃ jīvitaṃ pariccajitvā attano maṃsampi adaṃsū’’ ti vatvā tena yācito atītaṃ āhari. "
496701,112,405,2,12,1,91,10,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto sasayoniyaṃ nibbattitvā araññe vasi. 
496702,112,405,13,23,1,76,10,Tassa pana araññassa ekato pabbatapādo ekato nadī ekato paccantagāmako ahosi. 
496703,112,405,24,34,1,61,10,Aparepissa tayo sahāyā ahesuṃ makkaṭo ca siṅgālo ca uddo cāti. 
496704,112,405,35,49,1,112,13,Te cattāropi paṇḍitā ekatova vasantā attano attano gocaraṭṭhāne gocaraṃ gahetvā sāyanhasamaye ekato sannipatanti. 
496705,112,405,50,69,1,114,13,"Sasapaṇḍito‘‘ dānaṃ dātabbaṃ, sīlaṃ rakkhitabbaṃ, uposathakammaṃ kātabban’’ ti tiṇṇaṃ janānaṃ ovādavasena dhammaṃ deseti. "
496706,112,405,70,79,1,75,9,Te tassa ovādaṃ sampaṭicchitvā attano attano nivāsagumbaṃ pavisitvā vasanti. 
496707,112,405,80,130,1,297,39,"Evaṃ kāle gacchante ekadivasaṃ bodhisatto ākāsaṃ oloketvā candaṃ disvā‘‘ sve uposathadivaso’’ ti ñatvā itare tayo āha‘‘ sve uposatho, tumhepi tayo janā sīlaṃ samādiyitvā uposathikā hotha, sīle patiṭṭhāya dinnadānaṃ mahapphalaṃ hoti, tasmā yācake sampatte tumhehi khāditabbāhārato dānaṃ datvā khādeyyāthā’’ ti. "
496708,112,405,131,143,1,63,8,Te‘‘ sādhū’’ ti sampaṭicchitvā attano attano vasanaṭṭhānesu vasiṃsu. 
496709,112,406,2,16,1,80,10,Punadivase tesu uddo pātova‘‘ gocaraṃ pariyesissāmī’’ ti nikkhamitvā gaṅgātīraṃ gato. 
496710,112,406,17,37,1,158,18,Atheko bālisiko satta rohitamacche uddharitvā valliyā āvuṇitvā netvā gaṅgātīre vālukaṃ viyūhitvā vālikāya paṭicchādetvā puna macche gaṇhanto adhogaṅgaṃ gacchi. 
496711,112,406,38,77,1,246,31,Uddo macchagandhaṃ ghāyitvā vālukaṃ viyūhitvā macche disvā nīharitvā‘‘ atthi nu kho etesaṃ sāmiko’’ ti tikkhattuṃ ghosetvā sāmikaṃ apassanto vallikoṭiṃ ḍaṃsitvā netvā attano vasanagumbe ṭhapetvā‘‘ velāyameva khādissāmī’’ ti attano sīlaṃ āvajjento nipajji. 
496712,112,406,78,133,1,388,46,Siṅgālopi vasanaṭṭhānato nikkhamitvā gocaraṃ pariyesanto ekassa khettagopakassa kuṭiyaṃ dve maṃsasūlāni ekaṃ godhaṃ ekañca dadhivārakaṃ disvā‘‘ atthi nu kho etesaṃ sāmiko’’ ti tikkhattuṃ ghosetvā sāmikaṃ adisvā dadhivārakassa uggahaṇarajjukaṃ gīvāya pavesetvā dve maṃsasūle ca godhañca mukhena ḍaṃsitvā netvā attano vasanagumbe ṭhapetvā‘‘ velāyameva khādissāmī’’ ti attano sīlaṃ āvajjento nipajji. 
496713,112,406,134,155,1,161,17,Makkaṭopi vasanaṭṭhānato nikkhamitvā vanasaṇḍaṃ pavisitvā ambapiṇḍaṃ āharitvā attano vasanagumbe ṭhapetvā‘‘ velāyameva khādissāmī’’ ti attano sīlaṃ āvajjento nipajji. 
496714,112,407,2,45,1,273,32,"Bodhisatto pana‘‘ velāyameva vasanaṭṭhānato nikkhamitvā dabbatiṇāni khādissāmī’’ ti attano vasanagumbeyeva nipanno cintesi‘‘ mama santikaṃ āgatānaṃ yācakānaṃ tiṇāni dātuṃ na sakkā, tilataṇḍulādayopi mayhaṃ natthi, sace me santikaṃ yācako āgacchissati, attano sarīramaṃsaṃ dassāmī’’ ti. "
496715,112,407,46,52,1,65,6,Tassa sīlatejena sakkassa paṇḍukambalasilāsanaṃ uṇhākāraṃ dassesi. 
496716,112,407,53,71,1,121,14,So āvajjamāno idaṃ kāraṇaṃ disvā‘‘ sasarājānaṃ vīmaṃsissāmī’’ ti paṭhamaṃ uddassa vasanaṭṭhānaṃ gantvā brāhmaṇavesena aṭṭhāsi.
496717,112,407,72,91,1,99,13,"‘‘ Brāhmaṇa, kimatthaṃ ṭhitosī’’ ti vutte paṇḍita sace kiñci āhāraṃ labheyyaṃ, uposathiko hutvā vaseyyanti. "
