496740,112,420,2,10,1,42,6,"‘ ‘ Ambapakkaṃ dakaṃ sītaṃ, sītacchāyā manoramā; "
496741,112,421,2,14,1,47,9,"Idaṃ brāhmaṇa me atthi, etaṃ bhutvā vane vasā’’ ti. "
496742,112,422,2,6,1,38,4,Tattha ambapakkan ti madhuraambaphalaṃ. 
496743,112,422,7,13,1,37,6,Dakaṃ sītan ti gaṅgāya udakaṃ sītalaṃ. 
496744,112,422,14,35,1,175,20,Etaṃ bhutvā vane {vasā}ti brāhmaṇa etaṃ ambapakkaṃ paribhuñjitvā sītalaṃ udakaṃ pivitvā yathābhirucite ramaṇīye rukkhamūle nisinno samaṇadhammaṃ karonto imasmiṃ vanasaṇḍe vasāti. 
496745,112,423,2,17,1,74,10,"Brāhmaṇo ‘‘ pageva tāva hotu, pacchā jānissāmī’’ ti sasapaṇḍitassa santikaṃ gato. "
496746,112,423,18,28,1,43,6,Tenāpi‘‘ kimatthaṃ ṭhitosī’’ ti vutto tathevāha. 
496747,112,423,29,50,1,135,16,"Taṃ sutvā bodhisatto somanassappatto‘‘ brāhmaṇa, suṭṭhu te kataṃ āhāratthāya mama santikaṃ āgacchantena, ajjāhaṃ adinnapubbaṃ dānaṃ dassāmi . "
496748,112,423,51,76,1,158,19,"Tvaṃ pana sīlavā pāṇātipātaṃ na karissasi, gaccha, brāhmaṇa, nānādārūni saṅkaḍḍhitvā aṅgāre katvā mayhaṃ ārocehi, ahaṃ attānaṃ pariccajitvā aṅgāramajjhe patissāmi . "
496749,112,423,77,93,1,109,14,Mama sarīre pakke tvaṃ maṃsaṃ khāditvā samaṇadhammaṃ kareyyāsī’’ ti tena saddhiṃ sallapanto catutthaṃ gāthamāha– 
496750,112,424,2,4,1,0,0,64.
496751,112,425,2,13,1,43,9,"‘ ‘ Na sasassa tilā atthi, na muggā napi taṇḍulā; "
496752,112,426,2,13,1,45,8,"Iminā agginā pakkaṃ, mamaṃ bhutvā vane vasā’’ ti. "
496753,112,427,2,30,1,173,25,"Tattha mamaṃ {bhutvā}ti yaṃ taṃ ahaṃ aggiṃ karohīti vadāmi, iminā agginā pakkaṃ maṃ bhuñjitvā imasmiṃ vane vasa, ekassa sasassa sarīraṃ nāma ekassa purisassa yāpanamattaṃ hotīti. "
496754,112,428,2,13,1,90,11,Sakko tassa vacanaṃ sutvā attano ānubhāvena ekaṃ aṅgārarāsiṃ māpetvā bodhisattassa ārocesi. 
496755,112,428,14,46,1,224,27,"So dabbatiṇasayanato uṭṭhāya tattha gantvā‘‘ sace me lomantaresu pāṇakā atthi, te mā mariṃsū’’ ti tikkhattuṃ sarīraṃ vidhunitvā sakalasarīraṃ dānamukhe ṭhapetvā laṅghitvā padumasare rājahaṃso viya pamuditacitto aṅgārarāsimhi pati. "
496756,112,428,47,61,1,103,13,"So pana aggi bodhisattassa sarīre lomakūpamattampi uṇhaṃ kātuṃ nāsakkhi, himagabbhaṃ paviṭṭho viya ahosi. "
496757,112,428,62,88,1,126,19,"Atha sakkaṃ āmantetvā‘‘ brāhmaṇa, tayā kato aggi atisītalo, mama sarīre lomakūpamattampi uṇhaṃ kātuṃ na sakkoti, kiṃ nāmetan’’ ti āha."
496758,112,428,89,104,1,72,8,"‘‘ Sasapaṇḍita, nāhaṃ brāhmaṇo, sakkohamasmi, tava vīmaṃsanatthāya āgatomhī’’ ti."
496759,112,428,105,130,1,129,18,"‘‘ Sakka, tvaṃ tāva tiṭṭha, sakalopi ce lokasannivāso maṃ dānena vīmaṃseyya, neva me adātukāmataṃ passeyyā’’ ti bodhisatto sīhanādaṃ nadi. "
496760,112,428,131,165,1,257,28,"Atha naṃ sakko‘‘ sasapaṇḍita, tava guṇo sakalakappaṃ pākaṭo hotū’’ ti pabbataṃ pīḷetvā pabbatarasaṃ ādāya candamaṇḍale sasalakkhaṇaṃ likhitvā bodhisattaṃ ānetvā tasmiṃ vanasaṇḍe tasmiṃyeva vanagumbe taruṇadabbatiṇapiṭṭhe nipajjāpetvā attano vasanaṭṭhānameva gato. "
496761,112,428,166,179,1,104,13,Tepi cattāro paṇḍitā samaggā sammodamānā sīlaṃ pūretvā dānaṃ datvā uposathakammaṃ katvā yathākammaṃ gatā. 
496762,112,429,2,17,1,149,13,"Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā saccāni pakāsetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi, saccapariyosāne sabbaparikkhāradānadāyako gahapati sotāpattiphale patiṭṭhahi. "
496763,112,430,2,20,1,109,14,"Tadā uddo ānando ahosi, siṅgālo moggallāno, makkaṭo sāriputto, sakko anuruddho, sasapaṇḍito pana ahameva ahosinti. "
496764,112,431,2,4,1,32,2,Sasapaṇḍitajātakavaṇṇanā chaṭṭhā.
496765,112,433,2,7,1,23,2,[ 317]7. Matarodanajātakavaṇṇanā 
496766,112,434,2,17,1,107,13,Mataṃ mataṃ eva {rodathā}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto aññataraṃ sāvatthivāsiṃ kuṭumbikaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
496767,112,434,18,22,1,27,4,Tassa kira bhātā kālamakāsi. 
496768,112,434,23,39,1,113,15,"So tassa kālakiriyāya sokābhibhūto na nhāyati na bhuñjati na vilimpati, pātova susānaṃ gantvā sokasamappito rodati. "
496769,112,434,40,101,1,416,48,"Satthā paccūsasamaye lokaṃ olokento tassa sotāpattiphalūpanissayaṃ disvā‘‘ imassa atītakāraṇaṃ āharitvā sokaṃ vūpasametvā sotāpattiphalaṃ dātuṃ ṭhapetvā maṃ añño koci samattho natthi, imassa mayā avassayena bhavituṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti punadivase pacchābhattaṃ piṇḍapātapaṭikkanto pacchāsamaṇaṃ ādāya tassa gharadvāraṃ gantvā‘‘ satthā āgato’’ ti sutvā āsanaṃ paññapetvā‘‘ pavesethā’’ ti kuṭumbikena vutto pavisitvā paññatte āsane nisīdi. "
496770,112,434,102,108,1,55,6,Kuṭumbikopi āgantvā satthāraṃ vanditvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. 
496771,112,434,109,121,1,44,8,Atha naṃ satthā‘‘ kiṃ kuṭumbika cintesī’’ ti āha.
496772,112,434,122,136,1,52,8,"‘‘ Āma, bhante, mama bhātu matakālato paṭṭhāya cintemī’’ ti."
496773,112,434,137,170,1,191,23,"‘‘ Āvuso, sabbe saṅkhārā aniccā, bhijjitabbayuttakaṃ bhijjati, na tattha cintetabbaṃ, porāṇakapaṇḍitāpi bhātari matepi‘ bhijjitabbayuttakaṃ bhijjatī’ ti na cintayiṃsū’’ ti vatvā tena yācito atītaṃ āhari. "
496774,112,435,2,16,1,135,13,"Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto asītikoṭivibhave seṭṭhikule nibbatti, tassa vayappattassa mātāpitaro kālamakaṃsu. "
496775,112,435,17,29,1,83,10,"Tesu kālakatesu bodhisattassa bhātā kuṭumbaṃ vicāreti, bodhisatto taṃ nissāya jīvati. "
496776,112,435,30,35,1,45,5,So aparabhāge tathārūpena byādhinā kālamakāsi. 
496777,112,435,36,55,1,137,17,"Ñātimittā suhajjā sannipatitvā bāhā paggayha kandanti rodanti, ekopi sakabhāvena saṇṭhātuṃ nāsakkhi, bodhisatto pana neva kandati na rodati. "
496778,112,435,56,88,1,187,22,"Manussā‘‘ passatha bho, imassa bhātari mate mukhasaṅkocanamattampi natthi, ativiya thaddhahadayo,‘ dvepi koṭṭhāse ahameva paribhuñjissāmī’ ti bhātu maraṇaṃ icchati maññe’’ ti bodhisattaṃ garahiṃsu. "
496779,112,435,89,102,1,57,9,Ñātakāpi naṃ‘‘ tvaṃ bhātari mate na rodasī’’ ti garahiṃsuyeva. 
496780,112,435,103,138,1,188,26,"So tesaṃ kathaṃ sutvā‘‘ tumhe attano andhabālabhāvena aṭṭha lokadhamme ajānantā‘ mama bhātā mato’ ti rodatha, ahampi marissāmi, tumhepi marissatha, attānampi‘ mayampi marissāmā’ ti kasmā na rodatha. "
496781,112,435,139,151,1,96,11,"Sabbe saṅkhārā aniccā hutvā nirujjhanti, teneva sabhāvena saṇṭhātuṃ samattho ekasaṅkhāropi natthi. "
496782,112,435,152,170,1,111,15,"Tumhe andhabālā aññāṇatāya aṭṭha lokadhamme ajānitvā rodatha, ahaṃ kimatthaṃ rodissāmī’’ ti vatvā imā gāthā abhāsi– "
496783,112,436,2,4,1,0,0,65.
496784,112,437,2,16,1,54,11,"‘ ‘ Mataṃ mataṃ eva rodatha, na hi taṃ rodatha yo marissati; "
496785,112,438,2,8,1,48,5,"Sabbepi sarīradhārino, anupubbena jahanti jīvitaṃ. "
496786,112,439,2,4,1,0,0,66.
496787,112,440,2,11,1,49,7,"‘ ‘ Devamanussā catuppadā, pakkhigaṇā uragā ca bhogino; "
496788,112,441,2,9,1,48,6,"Samhi sarīre anissarā, ramamānāva jahanti jīvitaṃ. "
496789,112,442,2,4,1,0,0,67.
496790,112,443,2,10,1,54,6,"‘ ‘ Evaṃ calitaṃ asaṇṭhitaṃ, sukhadukkhaṃ manujesvapekkhiya; "
496791,112,444,2,8,1,51,5,"Kanditaruditaṃ niratthakaṃ, kiṃ vo sokagaṇābhikīrare. "
496792,112,445,2,4,1,0,0,68.
496793,112,446,2,12,1,39,8,"‘ ‘ Dhuttā ca soṇḍā akatā, bālā sūrā ayogino; "
496794,112,447,2,12,1,46,7,"Dhīraṃ maññanti bāloti, ye dhammassa akovidā’’ ti. "
496795,112,448,2,10,1,40,6,Tattha mataṃ mataṃ {evā}ti mataṃ mataṃyeva. 
496796,112,448,11,32,1,142,17,"{Anupubbenā}ti attano attano maraṇavāre sampatte paṭipāṭiyā jahanti jīvitaṃ, na ekatova sabbe maranti, yadi evaṃ mareyyuṃ, lokappavatti ucchijjeyya. "
496797,112,448,33,38,1,45,4,{Bhogino}ti mahantena sarīrabhogena samannāgatā. 
496798,112,448,39,55,1,137,15,{Ramamānāvā}ti tattha tattha nibbattā sabbepi ete devādayo sattā attano attano nibbattaṭṭhāne abhiramamānāva anukkaṇṭhitāva jīvitaṃ jahanti. 
496799,112,448,56,69,1,98,13,Evaṃ calitan ti evaṃ tīsu bhavesu niccalabhāvassa ca saṇṭhitabhāvassa ca abhāvā calitaṃ asaṇṭhitaṃ. 
496800,112,448,70,79,1,78,8,Kiṃ vo {sokagaṇābhikīrare}ti kiṃkāraṇā tumhe sokarāsī abhikiranti ajjhottharanti. 
496801,112,449,2,18,1,113,14,Dhuttā ca soṇḍā {akatā}ti itthidhuttā surādhuttā akkhadhuttā ca surāsoṇḍādayo soṇḍā ca akatabuddhino asikkhitakā ca. 
496802,112,449,19,24,1,37,4,{Bālā}ti bālyena samannāgatā aviddasuno. 
496803,112,449,25,34,1,65,7,"Sūrā {ayogino}ti ayonisomanasikārena sūrā, yogesu ayuttatāya ayogino."
496804,112,449,35,48,1,68,8,"‘‘ Ayodhino’’ tipi pāṭho, kilesamārena saddhiṃ yujjhituṃ asamatthāti attho. "
496805,112,449,49,91,1,294,35,"Dhīraṃ maññanti bāloti, ye dhammassa {akovidā}ti ye evarūpā dhuttādayo aṭṭhavidhassa lokadhammassa akovidā, te appamattakepi dukkhadhamme uppanne attanā kandamānā rodamānā aṭṭha lokadhamme kathato jānitvā ñātimaraṇādīsu akandantaṃ arodantaṃ mādisaṃ dhīraṃ paṇḍitaṃ‘‘ bālo ayaṃ na rodatī’’ ti maññantīti. "
496806,112,450,2,11,1,62,9,Evaṃ bodhisatto tesaṃ dhammaṃ desetvā sabbepi te nissoke akāsi. 
496807,112,451,2,16,1,124,12,"Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā saccāni pakāsetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi, saccapariyosāne kuṭumbiko sotāpattiphale patiṭṭhahi. "
496808,112,451,17,25,1,79,8,Tadā mahājanasssa dhammaṃ desetvā nissokabhāvakarapaṇḍito pana ahameva ahosinti. 
496809,112,452,2,4,1,31,2,Matarodanajātakavaṇṇanā sattamā.
496810,112,454,2,7,1,21,2,[ 318]8. Kaṇaverajātakavaṇṇanā 
496811,112,455,2,14,1,96,11,Yaṃ taṃ vasanta {samaye}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto purāṇadutiyikāpalobhanaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
496812,112,455,15,29,1,35,4,Vatthu indriyajātake( jā.1.8.60 ādayo) āvi bhavissati. 
496813,112,455,30,52,1,118,18,Satthā pana taṃ bhikkhuṃ‘‘ pubbe tvaṃ bhikkhu etaṃ nissāya asinā sīsacchedaṃ paṭilabhī’’ ti vatvā tena yācito atītaṃ āhari. 
496814,112,456,2,30,1,218,26,"Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto kāsigāmake ekassa gahapatikassa ghare coranakkhattena jāto vayappatto corakammaṃ katvā jīvikaṃ kappento loke pākaṭo ahosi sūro nāgabalo, koci naṃ gaṇhituṃ nāsakkhi. "
496815,112,456,31,40,1,72,9,So ekadivasaṃ ekasmiṃ seṭṭhighare sandhiṃ chinditvā bahuṃ dhanaṃ avahari. 
496816,112,456,41,60,1,90,12,"Nāgarā rājānaṃ upasaṅkamitvā‘‘ deva, eko mahācoro nagaraṃ vilumpati, taṃ gaṇhāpethā’’ ti vadiṃsu. "
496817,112,456,61,66,1,46,5,Rājā tassa gahaṇatthāya nagaraguttikaṃ āṇāpesi. 
496818,112,456,67,79,1,98,12,So rattibhāge tattha tattha vaggabandhanena manusse ṭhapetvā taṃ sahoḍḍhaṃ gāhāpetvā rañño ārocesi. 
496819,112,456,80,90,1,51,6,Rājā‘‘ sīsamassa chindā’’ ti nagaraguttikaññeva āṇāpesi. 
496820,112,456,91,110,1,192,19,Nagaraguttiko taṃ pacchābāhaṃ gāḷhabandhanaṃ bandhāpetvā gīvāyassa rattakaṇavīramālaṃ laggetvā sīse iṭṭhakacuṇṇaṃ okiritvā catukke catukke kasāhi tāḷāpento kharassarena paṇavena āghātanaṃ neti.
496821,112,456,111,124,1,71,9,‘‘ Imasmiṃ kira nagare vilopakārako coro gahito’’ ti sakalanagaraṃ saṅkhubhi. 
496822,112,457,2,13,1,99,11,Tadā ca bārāṇasiyaṃ sahassaṃ gaṇhantī sāmā nāma gaṇikā hoti rājavallabhā pañcasatavaṇṇadāsīparivārā. 
496823,112,457,14,22,1,59,8,Sā pāsādatale vātapānaṃ vivaritvā ṭhitā taṃ nīyamānaṃ passi. 
496824,112,457,23,33,1,96,10,So pana abhirūpo pāsādiko ativiya sobhaggappatto devavaṇṇo sabbesaṃ matthakamatthakena paññāyati. 
496825,112,457,34,94,1,314,44,"Sāmā taṃ disvā paṭibaddhacittā hutvā‘‘ kena nu kho upāyenāhaṃ imaṃ purisaṃ attano sāmikaṃ kareyyan’’ ti cintayantī‘‘ attheko upāyo’’ ti attano atthacarikāya ekissā hatthe nagaraguttikassa sahassaṃ pesesi‘‘ ayaṃ coro sāmāya bhātā, aññatra sāmāya añño etassa avassayo natthi, tumhe kira idaṃ sahassaṃ gahetvā etaṃ vissajjethā’’ ti . "
496826,112,457,95,99,1,21,4,Sā gantvā tathā akāsi. 
496827,112,457,100,125,1,141,19,"Nagaraguttiko‘‘ ayaṃ coro pākaṭo, na sakkā etaṃ vissajjetuṃ, aññaṃ pana manussaṃ labhitvā imaṃ paṭicchannayānake nisīdāpetvā pesetuṃ sakkā’’ ti āha. "
496828,112,457,126,130,1,23,4,Sā gantvā tassā ārocesi. 
496829,112,458,2,10,1,70,8,Tadā paneko seṭṭhiputto sāmāya paṭibaddhacitto devasikaṃ sahassaṃ deti. 
496830,112,458,11,20,1,77,9,So taṃ divasampi sūriyatthaṅgamanavelāya sahassaṃ gaṇhitvā taṃ gharaṃ agamāsi. 
496831,112,458,21,29,1,69,8,Sāmāpi sahassabhaṇḍikaṃ gahetvā ūrūsu ṭhapetvā parodantī nisinnā hoti.
496832,112,458,30,70,1,175,27,"‘‘ Kiṃ etan’’ ti ca vuttā‘‘ sāmi, ayaṃ coro mama bhātā,‘ ahaṃ nīcakammaṃ karomī’ ti mayhaṃ santikaṃ na eti, nagaraguttikassa pahitaṃ‘ sahassaṃ labhamāno vissajjessāmi nan’ ti sāsanaṃ pesesi. "
496833,112,458,71,84,1,80,11,Idāni imaṃ sahassaṃ ādāya nagaraguttikassa santikaṃ gacchantaṃ na labhāmī’’ ti āha. 
496834,112,458,85,96,1,50,7,So tassā paṭibaddhacittatāya‘‘ ahaṃ gamissāmī’’ ti āha.
496835,112,458,97,109,1,43,7,‘‘ Tena hi tayā ābhatameva gahetvā gacchāhī’’ ti. 
496836,112,458,110,116,1,44,6,So taṃ gahetvā nagaraguttikassa gehaṃ gañchi. 
496837,112,458,117,164,1,368,41,"So taṃ seṭṭhiputtaṃ paṭicchannaṭṭhāne ṭhapetvā coraṃ paṭicchannayānake nisīdāpetvā sāmāya pahiṇitvā‘‘ ayaṃ coro raṭṭhe pākaṭo, tamandhakāraṃ tāva hotu, atha naṃ manusssānaṃ paṭisallīnavelāya ghātāpessāmī’’ ti apadesaṃ katvā muhuttaṃ vītināmetvā manussesu paṭisallīnesu seṭṭhiputtaṃ mahantenārakkhena āghātanaṃ netvā asinā sīsaṃ chinditvā sarīraṃ sūle āropetvā nagaraṃ pāvisi. "
496838,112,459,2,15,1,89,12,"Tato paṭṭhāya sāmā aññesaṃ hatthato kiñci na gaṇhāti, teneva saddhiṃ abhiramamānā vicarati. "
496839,112,459,16,61,1,288,36,"So cintesi‘‘ sace ayaṃ aññasmiṃ paṭibaddhacittā bhavissati, mampi mārāpetvā tena saddhiṃ abhiramissati, accantaṃ mittadubbhinī esā, mayā idha avasitvā khippaṃ palāyituṃ vaṭṭati, gacchanto ca pana tucchahattho agantvā etissā ābharaṇabhaṇḍaṃ gahetvā gacchissāmī’’ ti cintetvā ekasmiṃ divase taṃ āha–"
496840,112,459,62,80,1,100,12,"‘‘ bhadde, mayaṃ pañjare pakkhittakukkuṭā viya niccaṃ ghareyeva homa, ekadivasaṃ uyyānakīḷaṃ karissāmā’’ ti. "
496841,112,459,81,99,1,146,14,Sā‘‘ sādhū’’ ti sampaṭicchitvā khādanīyabhojanīyādiṃ sabbaṃ paṭiyādetvā sabbābharaṇapaṭimaṇḍitā tena saddhiṃ paṭicchannayāne nisīditvā uyyānaṃ agamāsi. 
496842,112,459,100,140,1,311,36,So tattha tāya saddhiṃ kīḷanto‘‘ idāni mayhaṃ palāyituṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti tāya saddhiṃ kilesaratiyā ramitukāmo viya ekaṃ kaṇavīragacchantaraṃ pavisitvā taṃ āliṅganto viya nippīḷetvā visaññaṃ katvā pātetvā sabbābharaṇāni omuñcitvā tassāyeva uttarāsaṅgena bandhitvā bhaṇḍikaṃ khandhe ṭhapetvā uyyānavatiṃ laṅghitvā pakkāmi. 
496843,112,460,2,17,1,85,10,Sāpi paṭiladdhasaññā uṭṭhāya paricārikānaṃ santikaṃ āgantvā‘‘ ayyaputto kahan’’ ti pucchi.
496844,112,460,18,27,1,17,4,"‘‘ Na jānāma, ayye’’ ti."
496845,112,460,28,58,1,179,22,‘‘ Maṃ matāti saññāya bhāyitvā palāto bhavissatī’’ ti anattamanā hutvā tatoyeva gehaṃ gantvā‘‘ mama piyasāmikassa adiṭṭhakālato paṭṭhāyeva alaṅkatasayane na sayissāmī’’ ti bhūmiyaṃ nipajji. 
496846,112,460,59,90,1,189,24,"Tato paṭṭhāya manāpaṃ sāṭakaṃ na nivāseti, dve bhattāni na bhuñjati, gandhamālādīni na paṭisevati,‘‘ yena kenaci upāyena ayyaputtaṃ pariyesitvā pakkosāpessāmī’’ ti naṭe pakkosāpetvā sahassaṃ adāsi."
496847,112,460,91,165,1,429,54,"‘‘ Kiṃ karoma, ayye’’ ti vutte ‘‘ tumhākaṃ agamanaṭṭhānaṃ nāma natthi, tumhe gāmanigamarājadhāniyo carantā samajjaṃ katvā samajjamaṇḍale paṭhamameva imaṃ gītaṃ gāyeyyāthā’’ ti naṭe sikkhāpentī paṭhamaṃ gāthaṃ vatvā‘‘ tumhehi imasmiṃ gītake gīte sace ayyaputto tasmiṃ parisantare bhavissati, tumhehi saddhiṃ kathessati, athassa mama arogabhāvaṃ kathetvā taṃ ādāya āgaccheyyātha, no ce āgacchati, sāsanaṃ peseyyāthā’’ ti paribbayaṃ datvā naṭe uyyojesi. "
