496917,112,498,20,37,1,145,16,{Abyāvaṭassā}ti evaṃ sante pāpakammakaraṇatthāya abyāvaṭassa ussukkaṃ anāpannassa tava bhadrassa suddhasseva sato pāpaṃ na upalimpati na allīyatīti. 
