496927,112,508,2,49,1,325,42,"Tassattho – yadi tava pāpakiriyāya mano na padussati, tanninno tappono tappabbhāro na hoti, evaṃ sante luddena āyasmantaṃ paṭicca katampi pāpakammaṃ taṃ na phusati na allīyati, pāpakiriyāya hi appossukkassa nirālayassa bhadrassa parisuddhasseva sato tava pāṇātipātacetanāya abhāvā taṃ pāpaṃ na upalimpati, tava cittaṃ na allīyatīti. "
