496932,112,511,2,4,1,27,2,Tittirajātakavaṇṇanā navamā.
496933,112,513,2,7,1,20,2,[ 320]10. Succajajātakavaṇṇanā 
496934,112,514,2,14,1,86,11,Succajaṃ vata {naccajī}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ekaṃ kuṭumbikaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
496935,112,514,15,50,1,192,26,So kira‘‘ gāmake uddhāraṃ sādhessāmī’’ ti bhariyāya saddhiṃ tattha gantvā sādhetvā dhanaṃ āharitvā‘‘ pacchā nessāmī’’ ti ekasmiṃ kule ṭhapetvā puna sāvatthiṃ gacchanto antarāmagge ekaṃ pabbataṃ addasa. 
496936,112,514,51,73,1,91,15,"Atha naṃ bhariyā āha‘‘ sace, sāmi, ayaṃ pabbato suvaṇṇamayo bhaveyya, dadeyyāsi pana me kiñcī’’ ti."
496937,112,514,74,85,1,29,6,"‘‘ Kāsi tvaṃ, na kiñci dassāmī’’ ti. "
496938,112,514,86,106,1,100,14,"Sā‘‘ yāva thaddhahadayo vatāyaṃ, pabbate suvaṇṇamaye jātepi mayhaṃ kiñci na dassatī’’ ti anattamanā ahosi. "
496939,112,514,107,121,1,81,10,Te jetavanasamīpaṃ āgantvā‘‘ pānīyaṃ pivissāmā’’ ti vihāraṃ pavisitvā pānīyaṃ piviṃsu. 
496940,112,514,122,135,1,142,12,Satthāpi paccūsakāleyeva tesaṃ sotāpattiphalassa upanissayaṃ disvā āgamanaṃ olokayamāno gandhakuṭipariveṇe nisīdi chabbaṇṇarasmiyo vissajjento. 
496941,112,514,136,143,1,57,7,Tepi pānīyaṃ pivitvā āgantvā satthāraṃ vanditvā nisīdiṃsu. 
496942,112,514,144,157,1,64,9,Satthā tehi saddhiṃ paṭisanthāraṃ katvā‘‘ kahaṃ gatātthā’’ ti pucchi.
496943,112,514,158,169,1,47,6,"‘‘ Amhākaṃ gāmake uddhāraṃ sādhanatthāya, bhante’’ ti."
496944,112,514,170,187,1,71,11,"‘‘ Kiṃ, upāsike tava sāmiko tuyhaṃ hitaṃ paṭikaṅkhati, upakāraṃ te karotī’’ ti. "
496945,112,514,188,233,1,199,31,"Bhante, ahaṃ imasmiṃ sasinehā, ayaṃ pana mayi nissineho, ajja mayā pabbataṃ disvā‘‘ sacāyaṃ pabbato suvaṇṇamayo assa, kiñci me dadeyyāsī’’ ti vutto‘‘ kāsi tvaṃ, na kiñci dassāmī’’ ti āha, evaṃ thaddhahadayo ayanti."
496946,112,514,234,268,1,134,22,"‘‘ Upāsike, evaṃ nāmesa vadati, yadā pana tava guṇaṃ sarati, tadā sabbissariyaṃ te detī’’ ti vatvā‘‘ kathetha, bhante’’ ti tehi yācito atītaṃ āhari. "
496947,112,515,2,12,1,91,10,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto tassa sabbakiccakārako amacco ahosi. 
496948,112,515,13,53,1,216,29,"Athekadivasaṃ rājā puttaṃ uparājānaṃ upaṭṭhānaṃ āgacchantaṃ disvā‘‘ ayaṃ mama antepure dubbheyyā’’ ti taṃ pakkosāpetvā‘‘ tāta, yāvāhaṃ jīvāmi, tāva nagare vasituṃ na lacchasi, aññattha vasitvā mamaccayena rajjaṃ kārehī’’ ti āha. "
496949,112,515,54,76,1,159,18,So‘‘ sādhū’’ ti pitaraṃ vanditvā jeṭṭhabhariyāya saddhiṃ nagarā nikkhamitvā paccantaṃ gantvā araññaṃ pavisitvā paṇṇasālaṃ māpetvā vanamūlaphalāphalehi yāpento vasi. 
496950,112,515,77,80,1,26,3,Aparabhāge rājā kālamakāsi. 
496951,112,515,81,93,1,108,12,Uparājā nakkhattaṃ olokento tassa kālakatabhāvaṃ ñatvā bārāṇasiṃ āgacchanto antarāmagge ekaṃ pabbataṃ addasa. 
496952,112,515,94,115,1,82,14,"Atha naṃ bhariyā āha‘‘ sace, deva, ayaṃ pabbato suvaṇṇamayo assa, dadeyyāsi me kiñcī’’ ti."
496953,112,515,116,127,1,29,6,"‘‘ Kāsi tvaṃ, na kiñci dassāmī’’ ti. "
496954,112,515,128,159,1,167,23,"Sā‘‘ ahaṃ imasmiṃ sinehaṃ chindituṃ asakkontī araññaṃ pāvisiṃ, ayañca evaṃ vadati, ativiya thaddhahadayo , rājā hutvāpi esa mayhaṃ kiṃ kalyāṇaṃ karissatī’’ ti anattamanā ahosi. "
496955,112,515,160,172,1,83,10,"So āgantvā rajje patiṭṭhito taṃ aggamahesiṭṭhāne ṭhapesi , idaṃ yasamattakameva adāsi. "
496956,112,515,173,182,1,63,8,"Uttari pana sakkārasammāno natthi, tassā atthibhāvampi na jānāti. "
496957,112,516,2,15,1,77,10,Bodhisatto ‘‘ ayaṃ devī imassa rañño upakārikā dukkhaṃ agaṇetvā araññavāsaṃ vasi. 
496958,112,516,16,59,1,267,33,"Ayaṃ panetaṃ agaṇetvā aññāhi saddhiṃ abhiramanto vicarati, yathā esā sabbissariyaṃ labhati, tathā karissāmī’’ ti cintetvā ekadivasaṃ taṃ upasaṅkamitvā‘‘ mahādevi mayaṃ tumhākaṃ santikā piṇḍapātamattampi na labhāma, kasmā amhesu pamajjittha, ativiya thaddhahadayā atthā’’ ti āha."
496959,112,516,60,113,1,255,38,"‘‘ Tāta, sacāhaṃ attanā labheyyaṃ, tuyhampi dadeyyaṃ, alabhamānā pana kiṃ dassāmi, rājāpi mayhaṃ idāni kiṃ nāma dassati, so antarāmagge‘ imasmiṃ pabbate suvaṇṇamaye jāte mayhaṃ kiñci dassasī’ ti vutto‘ kāsi tvaṃ, na kiñci dassāmī’ ti āha, supariccajampi na pariccajī’’ ti."
496960,112,516,114,127,1,59,9,‘‘ Kiṃ pana rañño santike imaṃ kathaṃ kathetuṃ sakkhissathā’’ ti?
496961,112,516,128,136,1,19,3,"‘‘ Sakkhissāmi, tātā’’ ti."
496962,112,516,137,152,1,65,10,"‘‘ Tena hi ahaṃ rañño santike ṭhito pucchissāmi, tumhe katheyyāthā’’ ti."
496963,112,516,153,161,1,13,3,"‘‘ Sādhu, tātā’’ ti. "
496964,112,516,162,184,1,109,16,"Bodhisatto deviyā rañño upaṭṭhānaṃ āgantvā ṭhitakāle āha‘‘ nanu, ayye, mayaṃ tumhākaṃ santikā kiñci na labhāmā’’ ti?"
496965,112,516,185,251,1,338,49,"‘‘ Tāta, ahaṃ labhamānā tuyhaṃ dadeyyaṃ, ahameva kiñci na labhāmi, alabhamānā tuyhaṃ kiṃ dassāmi, rājāpi idāni mayhaṃ kiṃ nāma dassati, so araññato āgamanakāle ekaṃ pabbataṃ disvā‘ sacāyaṃ pabbato suvaṇṇamayo assa, kiñci me dadeyyāsī’ ti vutto‘ kāsi tvaṃ, na kiñci dassāmī’ ti vadati, supariccajampi na pariccajī’’ ti etamatthaṃ dīpentī paṭhamaṃ gāthamāha– "
