497003,112,541,2,4,1,15,2,3 . Kuṭidūsakavaggo
497004,112,543,2,7,1,23,2,[ 321]1. Kuṭidūsakajātakavaṇṇanā 
497005,112,544,2,17,1,125,13,Manussasseva te sīsan ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto mahākassapattherassa paṇṇasālajhāpakaṃ daharabhikkhuṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
497006,112,544,18,22,1,32,4,Vatthu pana rājagahe samuṭṭhitaṃ. 
497007,112,544,23,36,1,92,12,"Tadā kira thero rājagahaṃ nissāya araññakuṭiyaṃ viharati, tassa dve daharā upaṭṭhānaṃ karonti. "
497008,112,544,37,49,1,79,11,"Tesu eko therassa upakārako, eko dubbaco itarena kataṃ attanā katasadisaṃ karoti. "
497009,112,544,50,70,1,121,14,"Tena mukhodakādīsu upaṭṭhāpitesu therassa santikaṃ gantvā vanditvā‘‘ bhante, udakaṃ ṭhapitaṃ, mukhaṃ dhovathā’’ tiādīni vadati. "
497010,112,544,71,88,1,145,17,Tena kālasseva vuṭṭhāya therassa pariveṇe sammaṭṭhe therassa nikkhamanavelāya ito cito ca paharanto sakalapariveṇaṃ attanā sammaṭṭhaṃ viya karoti. 
497011,112,544,89,108,1,111,14,"Vattasampanno cintesi‘‘ ayaṃ dubbaco mayā kataṃ attanā katasadisaṃ karoti, etassa saṭhakammaṃ pākaṭaṃ karissāmī’’ ti. "
497012,112,545,2,17,1,131,14,Tasmiṃ antogāme bhutvā āgantvā niddāyanteva nhānodakaṃ tāpetvā piṭṭhikoṭṭhake ṭhapetvā aññaṃ aḍḍhanāḷimattaṃ udakaṃ uddhane ṭhapesi. 
497013,112,545,18,50,1,177,22,"Itaro pabujjhitvāva gantvā usumaṃ uṭṭhahantaṃ disvā‘‘ udakaṃ tāpetvā koṭṭhake ṭhapitaṃ bhavissatī’’ ti therasssa santikaṃ gantvā‘‘ bhante, nhānakoṭṭhake udakaṃ ṭhapitaṃ, nhāyathā’’ ti āha. "
497014,112,545,51,71,1,90,13,Thero‘ nhāyissāmī’’ ti tena saddhiṃyeva āgantvā koṭṭhake udakaṃ aditvā‘‘ kahaṃ udakan’’ ti pucchi. 
497015,112,545,72,91,1,114,14,"So vegena aggisālaṃ gantvā tucchabhājane uḷuṅkaṃ otāresi, uḷuṅko tucchabhājanassa tale paṭihato‘‘ tatā’’ ti saddamakāsi. "
497016,112,545,92,103,1,51,7,Tato paṭṭhāya tassa‘‘ uḷuṅkasaddako’’ tveva nāmaṃ jātaṃ. 
497017,112,546,2,17,1,74,10,"Tasmiṃ khaṇe itaro piṭṭhikoṭṭhakato udakaṃ āharitvā‘‘ nhāyatha, bhante’’ ti āha. "
497018,112,546,18,58,1,225,30,"Thero nhatvā āvajjento uḷuṅkasaddakassa dubbacabhāvaṃ ñatvā taṃ sāyaṃ therupaṭṭhānaṃ āgataṃ ovadi‘‘ āvuso, samaṇena nāma attanā katameva‘ kataṃ me’ ti vattuṃ vaṭṭati, aññathā sampajānamusāvādo hoti, ito paṭṭhāya evarūpaṃ mā akāsī’’ ti. "
497019,112,546,59,69,1,72,10,So therassa kujjhitvā punadivase therena saddhiṃ piṇḍāya gāmaṃ na pāvisi. 
497020,112,546,70,74,1,30,4,Thero itareneva saddhiṃ pāvisi. 
497021,112,546,75,125,1,232,30,"Uḷuṅkasaddakopi therassa upaṭṭhākakulaṃ gantvā‘‘ bhante, thero kahan’’ ti vutte‘‘ aphāsukena vihāreyeva nisinno’’ ti vatvā‘‘ kiṃ, bhante, laddhuṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti vutte‘‘ idañcidañca dethā’’ ti gahetvā attano rucitaṭṭhānaṃ gantvā bhuñjitvā vihāraṃ agamāsi. "
497022,112,547,2,8,1,40,6,Punadivase thero taṃ kulaṃ gantvā nisīdi. 
497023,112,547,9,83,1,402,53,"Manussehi‘‘ kiṃ, bhante, ayyassa aphāsukaṃ, hiyyo kirattha vihāreyeva nisinnā, asukadaharassa hatthe āhāraṃ pesayimha, paribhutto ayyenā’’ ti vutte thero tuṇhībhūtova bhattakiccaṃ katvā vihāraṃ gantvā sāyaṃ therupaṭṭhānakāle āgataṃ āmantetvā‘‘ āvuso, asukagāme nāma asukakule‘ therassa idañcidañca laddhuṃ vaṭṭatī’ ti viññāpetvā kira te bhuttan’’ ti vatvā‘‘ viññatti nāma na vaṭṭati, mā puna evarūpaṃ anācāraṃ carā’’ ti āha. "
497024,112,547,84,129,1,322,38,"So ettakena there āghātaṃ bandhitvā‘‘ ayaṃ hiyyopi udakamattaṃ nissāya mayā saddhiṃ kalahaṃ kari, idāni panassa upaṭṭhākānaṃ gehe mayā bhattamuṭṭhi bhuttāti asahanto puna kalahaṃ karoti, jānissāmissa kattabbayuttakan’’ ti punadivase there piṇḍāya paviṭṭhe muggaraṃ gahetvā paribhogabhājanāni bhinditvā paṇṇasālaṃ jhāpetvā palāyi. "
497025,112,547,130,139,1,77,9,So jīvamānova manussapeto hutvā sussitvā kālaṃ katvā avīcimahāniraye nibbatti. 
497026,112,547,140,148,1,51,8,So tena kato anācāro mahājanassa majjhe pākaṭo jāto. 
497027,112,548,2,15,1,124,13,Athekacce bhikkhū rājagahā sāvatthiṃ gantvā sabhāgaṭṭhāne pattacīvaraṃ paṭisāmetvā satthu santikaṃ gantvā vanditvā nisīdiṃsu. 
497028,112,548,16,29,1,64,9,Satthā tehi saddhiṃ paṭisanthāraṃ katvā‘‘ kuto āgatatthā’’ ti pucchi.
