497116,112,583,2,41,1,332,35,Evaṃ vutte sīho beluvarukkhamūlaṃ gantvā tālapaṇṇassa heṭṭhā sasakena nipannaṭṭhānañceva tālapaṇṇamatthake patitaṃ beluvapakkañca disvā pathaviyā asaṃvaṭṭanabhāvaṃ tathato jānitvā sasakaṃ piṭṭhiyaṃ āropetvā sīhavegena khippaṃ migasaṅghānaṃ santikaṃ gantvā sabbaṃ pavattiṃ ārocetvā‘‘ tumhe mā bhāyathā’’ ti migagaṇaṃ assāsetvā vissajjesi. 
