497209,112,625,67,126,1,299,37,"Bhikkhū dhammasabhāyaṃ kathaṃ samuṭṭhāpesuṃ‘‘ āvuso, cammasāṭakaparibbājako asantapaggahaṃ katvā vināsaṃ patto’’ ti satthā āgantvā‘‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ imāya nāmā’’ ti vutte‘‘ na, bhikkhave, idāneva, pubbepesa asantapaggahaṃ katvā vināsaṃ pattoyevā’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
