497291,112,676,46,53,1,74,7,Dvādasayojanikaṃ bārāṇasinagaraṃ tesaṃ pupphānaṃ gandhena ekagandhaṃ ahosi. 
497292,112,676,54,66,1,65,8,Manussā‘‘ imāni pupphāni kena piḷandhitānī’’ ti upadhārentā vicaranti. 
