497302,112,676,164,178,1,148,11,"Devaputtā‘‘ dibbakakkārupupphāni mahānubhāvāni devānaññeva anucchavikāni, manussaloke lāmakānaṃ duppaññānaṃ hīnādhimuttikānaṃ dussīlānaṃ nānucchavikāni. "
497303,112,676,179,196,1,88,14,"Ye pana manussā imehi ca imehi ca guṇehi samannāgatā, tesaṃ etāni anucchavikānī’’ ti āhaṃsu. "
