497310,112,681,32,55,1,161,21,"Yaso {laddhā}ti issariyañca labhitvā yo issariyamadamatto satiṃ vissajjetvā pāpakammaṃ na karoti, sa ve evarūpo imehi guṇehi yutto puggalo imaṃ dibbapupphaṃ arahati. "
497311,112,681,56,70,1,83,12,"Tasmā yo imehi guṇehi samannāgato, so imāni pupphāni yācituṃ arahati, tassa dassāmīti. "
497312,112,682,2,34,1,169,24,"Taṃ sutvā purohito cintesi‘‘ mayhaṃ imesu guṇesu ekopi natthi, musāvādaṃ pana vatvā etāni pupphāni gahetvā piḷandhissāmi, evaṃ maṃ mahājano‘ guṇasampanno ayan’ ti jānissatī’’ ti. "
