497606,112,829,2,17,1,92,12,Api hantvā hato {brūtī}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto kosalarañño purohitaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
497607,112,829,18,48,1,226,26,So kira rathena attano bhogagāmaṃ gacchanto sambādhe magge rathaṃ pājento ekaṃ sakaṭasatthaṃ disvā‘‘ tumhākaṃ sakaṭaṃ apanethā’’ ti gacchanto sakaṭe anapanīyamāne kujjhitvā patodalaṭṭhiyā purimasakaṭe sākaṭikassa rathadhure pahari. 
497608,112,829,49,56,1,56,7,Sā rathadhure paṭihatā nivattitvā tasseva nalāṭaṃ pahari. 
497609,112,829,57,61,1,32,4,Tāvadevassa nalāṭe gaṇḍo uṭṭhahi. 
497610,112,829,62,73,1,51,7,So nivattitvā‘‘ sākaṭikehi pahaṭomhī’’ ti rañño ārocesi. 
497611,112,829,74,80,1,59,6,Sākaṭike pakkosāpetvā vinicchinantā tasseva dosaṃ addasaṃsu. 
497612,112,829,81,106,1,141,17,"Athekadivasaṃ bhikkhū dhammasabhāyaṃ kathaṃ samuṭṭhāpesuṃ‘‘ āvuso, rañño kira purohito‘ sākaṭikehi pahaṭomhī’ ti aḍḍaṃ karonto sayameva parajjī’’ ti. "
497613,112,829,107,148,1,168,24,"Satthā āgantvā‘‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ imāya nāmā’’ ti vutte‘‘ na, bhikkhave, idāneva, pubbepesa evarūpaṃ akāsiyevā’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
497614,112,830,2,11,1,85,9,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto tasseva vinicchayāmacco ahosi. 
497615,112,830,12,21,1,81,9,Atha rañño purohito rathena attano bhogagāmaṃ gacchantoti sabbaṃ purimasadisameva. 
497616,112,830,22,57,1,202,27,Idha pana tena rañño ārocite rājā sayaṃ vinicchaye nisīditvā sākaṭike pakkosāpetvā kammaṃ asodhetvāva‘‘ tumhehi mama purohitaṃ koṭṭetvā nalāṭe gaṇḍo uṭṭhāpito’’ ti vatvā‘‘ sabbassaharaṇaṃ tesaṃ karothā’’ ti āha. 
497617,112,830,58,105,1,261,36,"Atha naṃ bodhisatto‘‘ tumhe, mahārāja, kammaṃ asodhetvāva etesaṃ sabbassaṃ harāpetha, ekacce pana attanāva attānaṃ paharitvāpi‘ parena pahaṭamhā’ ti vadanti, tasmā avicinitvā kātuṃ na yuttaṃ, rajjaṃ kārentena nāma nisāmetvā kammaṃ kātuṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti vatvā imā gāthā abhāsi. "
