497655,112,851,26,33,1,54,7,Rājadhītā taṃ valliyā bandhitvā ādāya maggaṃ paṭipajji. 
497656,112,851,34,42,1,56,8,Te ekaṃ saraṃ disvā maggā okkamma assatthamūle nisīdiṃsu. 
497657,112,851,43,60,1,84,11,"Rājaputto‘‘ gaccha bhadde, sarato paduminipattena udakaṃ āhara, maṃsaṃ khādissāmā’’ ti āha. "
497658,112,851,61,67,1,44,6,Sā godhaṃ sākhāya laggetvā pānīyatthāya gatā. 
497659,112,851,68,76,1,69,8,Itaro sabbaṃ godhaṃ khāditvā agganaṅguṭṭhaṃ gahetvā parammukho nisīdi. 
497660,112,851,77,107,1,179,23,"So tāya pānīyaṃ gahetvā āgatāya‘‘ bhadde, godhā sākhāya otaritvā vammikaṃ pāvisi, ahaṃ dhāvitvā agganaṅguṭṭhaṃ aggahesiṃ, gahitaṭṭhānaṃ hattheyeva katvā chijjitvā bilaṃ paviṭṭhā’’ ti āha."
497661,112,851,108,124,1,64,9,"‘‘ Hotu, deva, pakkagodhāya palāyantiyā kiṃ karissāma, ehi gacchāmā’’ ti. "
