497748,112,900,2,7,1,20,2,[ 335]5. Jambukajātakavaṇṇanā 
497749,112,901,2,14,1,101,11,Brahā pavaḍḍhakāyo soti idaṃ satthā veḷuvane viharanto devadattassa sugatālayakaraṇaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
497750,112,901,15,22,1,51,6,"Vatthu heṭṭhā vitthāritameva, ayaṃ panettha saṅkhepo. "
497751,112,901,23,51,1,133,20,"Satthārā‘‘ sāriputta, devadatto tumhe disvā kiṃ akāsī’’ ti vutto thero āha‘‘ bhante, so tumhākaṃ anukaronto mama hatthe bījaniṃ datvā nipajji. "
497752,112,901,52,68,1,83,13,"Atha naṃ kokāliko ure jaṇṇunā pahari, iti so tumhākaṃ anukaronto dukkhaṃ anubhavī’’ ti. "
497753,112,901,69,96,1,141,20,"Taṃ sutvā satthā‘‘ na kho, sāriputta, devadatto idāneva mama anukaronto dukkhaṃ anubhoti, pubbepesa anubhosiyevā’’ ti vatvā tena yācito atītaṃ āhari. "
497754,112,902,2,23,1,182,20,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto sīhayoniyaṃ nibbattitvā himavante guhāyaṃ vasanto ekadivasaṃ mahiṃsaṃ vadhitvā maṃsaṃ khāditvā pānīyaṃ pivitvā guhaṃ āgacchati. 
497755,112,902,24,52,1,115,18,"Eko siṅgālo taṃ disvā palāyituṃ asakkonto urena nipajji,‘‘ kiṃ jambukā’’ ti ca vutte‘‘ upaṭṭhahissāmi taṃ, bhaddante’’ ti āha. "
497756,112,902,53,71,1,87,14,Sīho‘‘ tena hi ehī’’ ti taṃ attano vasanaṭṭhānaṃ netvā divase divase maṃsaṃ āharitvā posesi. 
497757,112,902,72,79,1,67,7,Tassa sīhavighāsena thūlasarīrataṃ pattassa ekadivasaṃ māno uppajji. 
497758,112,902,80,117,1,199,28,"So sīhaṃ upasaṅkamitvā āha‘‘ ahaṃ, sāmi, niccakālaṃ tumhākaṃ palibodho, tumhe niccaṃ maṃsaṃ āharitvā maṃ posetha, ajja tumhe idheva hotha, ahaṃ ekaṃ vāraṇaṃ vadhitvā maṃsaṃ khāditvā tumhākampi āharissāmī’’ ti. "
497759,112,902,118,161,1,215,31,"Sīho‘‘ mā te , jambuka, etaṃ rucci, na tvaṃ vāraṇaṃ vadhitvā maṃsakhādakayoniyaṃ nibbatto, ahaṃ te vāraṇaṃ vadhitvā dassāmi, vāraṇo nāma mahākāyo pavaḍḍhakāyo, mā vāraṇaṃ gaṇhi, mama vacanaṃ karohī’’ ti vatvā paṭhamaṃ gāthamāha. "
