497761,112,904,2,11,1,43,7,"‘ ‘ Brahā pavaḍḍhakāyo so, dīghadāṭho ca jambuka; "
497762,112,905,2,14,1,52,9,"Na tvaṃ tattha kule jāto, yattha gaṇhanti kuñjaran’’ ti. "
497763,112,906,2,6,1,22,3,Tattha {brahā}ti mahanto. 
