497765,112,906,12,22,1,76,8,{Dīghadāṭho}ti dīghadanto tehi dantehi tumhādise paharitvā jīvitakkhaye pāpeti. 
497766,112,906,23,40,1,103,14,"{Yatthā}ti yasmiṃ sīhakule jātā mattavāraṇaṃ gaṇhanti, tvaṃ na tattha jāto, siṅgālakule pana jātosīti attho. "
497767,112,907,2,39,1,247,29,Siṅgālo sīhena vāritoyeva guhā nikkhamitvā tikkhattuṃ‘‘ bukka bukkā’’ ti siṅgālikaṃ nadaṃ naditvā pabbatakūṭe ṭhito pabbatapādaṃ olokento ekaṃ kāḷavāraṇaṃ pabbatapādena āgacchantaṃ disvā ullaṅghitvā‘‘ tassa kumbhe patissāmī’’ ti parivattitvā pādamūle pati. 
497768,112,907,40,52,1,93,10,"Vāraṇo purimapādaṃ ukkhipitvā tassa matthake patiṭṭhāpesi, sīsaṃ bhijjitvā cuṇṇavicuṇṇaṃ jātaṃ . "
497769,112,907,53,62,1,63,8,"So tattheva anutthunanto sayi, vāraṇo koñcanādaṃ karonto pakkāmi. "
497770,112,907,63,83,1,121,16,Bodhisatto gantvā pabbatamatthake ṭhito taṃ vināsappattaṃ disvā‘‘ attano mānaṃ nissāya naṭṭho siṅgālo’’ ti tisso gāthā abhāsi– 
