497797,112,919,59,88,1,200,26,"So vipulaṃ {jinātī}ti yo evarūpo hoti, yaṃ kiñci kammaṃ kurumāno attano thāmañca balañca ñatvā jappamantavasena paricchinditvā subhāsitaṃ bhāsanto karoti, so vipulaṃ mahantaṃ atthaṃ jināti na parihāyatīti. "
