497831,112,931,2,12,1,40,8,"‘ ‘ Tiṇaṃ tiṇanti lapasi, ko nu te tiṇamāhari; "
497832,112,932,2,12,1,45,7,"Kiṃ nu te tiṇakiccatthi, tiṇameva pabhāsasī’’ ti. "
