497904,112,972,51,71,1,139,20,Uttamaṃ viya ñātakan ti mātaraṃ viya pitaraṃ viya ca mayaṃ dhammikaṃ samaṇaṃ vā brāhmaṇaṃ vā disvā sakkaccaṃ sahatthena upaṭṭhahāmāti attho. 
