497908,112,975,2,4,1,26,2,Pīṭhajātakavaṇṇanā sattamā.
497909,112,977,2,7,1,18,2,[ 338]8. Thusajātakavaṇṇanā 
497910,112,978,2,13,1,76,10,Viditaṃ thusan ti idaṃ satthā veḷuvane viharanto ajātasattuṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
497911,112,978,14,25,1,124,11,Tasmiṃ kira mātukucchigate tassa mātu kosalarājadhītāya bimbisārarañño dakkhiṇajāṇulohitapivanadohaḷo uppajjitvā paṇḍu ahosi. 
497912,112,978,26,32,1,48,6,Sā paricārikāhi pucchitā tāsaṃ tamatthaṃ ārocesi. 
497913,112,978,33,52,1,99,14,"Rājāpi sutvā nemittake pakkosāpetvā‘‘ deviyā kira evarūpo dohaḷo uppanno, tassa kā nipphattī’’ ti pucchi. "
497914,112,978,53,67,1,84,10,Nemittakā‘‘ deviyā kucchimhi nibbattakasatto tumhe māretvā rajjaṃ gaṇhissatī’’ ti āhaṃsu. 
497915,112,978,68,93,1,150,20,"Rājā‘‘ sace mama putto maṃ māretvā rajjaṃ gaṇhissati, ko ettha doso’’ ti dakkhiṇajāṇuṃ satthena phālāpetvā lohitaṃ suvaṇṇataṭṭakena gāhāpetvā deviyā pāyesi. "
497916,112,978,94,113,1,78,13,"Sā cintesi‘‘ sace mama kucchiyaṃ nibbatto putto pitaraṃ māressati, kiṃ me tenā’’ ti. "
497917,112,978,114,119,1,38,4,Sā gabbhapātanatthaṃ kucchiṃ maddāpesi . 
497918,112,979,2,38,1,182,29,"Rājā ñatvā taṃ pakkosāpetvā‘‘ bhadde mayhaṃ kira putto maṃ māretvā rajjaṃ gaṇhissati, na kho panāhaṃ ajaro amaro, puttamukhaṃ passituṃ me dehi, mā ito pabhuti evarūpaṃ kammaṃ akāsī’’ ti āha. "
497919,112,979,39,46,1,49,7,Sā tato paṭṭhāya uyyānaṃ gantvā kucchiṃ maddāpesi. 
497920,112,979,47,53,1,47,6,Rājā ñatvā tato paṭṭhāya uyyānagamanaṃ nivāresi. 
497921,112,979,54,58,1,32,4,Sā paripuṇṇagabbhā puttaṃ vijāyi. 
497922,112,979,59,71,1,81,8,Nāmaggahaṇadivase cassa ajātasseva pitu sattubhāvato‘‘ ajātasattu’’ tveva nāmamakaṃsu. 
497923,112,979,72,82,1,106,10,Tasmiṃ kumāraparihārena vaḍḍhante satthā ekadivasaṃ pañcasatabhikkhuparivuto rañño nivesanaṃ gantvā nisīdi. 
497924,112,979,83,94,1,119,11,Rājā buddhappamukhaṃ bhikkhusaṅghaṃ paṇītena khādanīyabhojanīyena parivisitvā satthāraṃ vanditvā dhammaṃ suṇanto nisīdi. 
497925,112,979,95,101,1,42,6,Tasmiṃ khaṇe kumāraṃ maṇḍetvā rañño adaṃsu. 
497926,112,979,102,115,1,110,13,Rājā balavasinehena puttaṃ gahetvā ūrumhi nisīdāpetvā puttagatena pemena puttameva mamāyanto na dhammaṃ suṇāti. 
497927,112,979,116,147,1,186,24,"Satthā tassa pamādabhāvaṃ ñatvā‘‘ mahārāja, pubbe rājāno putte āsaṅkamānā paṭicchanne kāretvā‘ amhākaṃ accayena nīharitvā rajje patiṭṭhāpeyyāthā’ ti āṇāpesun’’ ti vatvā tena yācito atītaṃ āhari. "
497928,112,980,2,18,1,145,16,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto takkasilāyaṃ disāpāmokkhaācariyo hutvā bahū rājakumāre ca brāhmaṇakumāre ca sippaṃ vācesi. 
497929,112,980,19,34,1,131,15,Bārāṇasiraññopi putto soḷasavassakāle tassa santikaṃ gantvā tayo vede ca sabbasippāni ca uggaṇhitvā paripuṇṇasippo ācariyaṃ āpucchi. 
497930,112,980,35,99,1,416,48,"Ācariyo aṅgavijjāvasena taṃ olokento‘‘ imassa puttaṃ nissāya antarāyo paññāyati, tamahaṃ attano ānubhāvena harissāmī’’ ti cintetvā catasso gāthā bandhitvā rājakumārassa adāsi, evañca pana taṃ vadesi‘‘ tāta, paṭhamaṃ gāthaṃ rajje patiṭṭhāya tava puttassa soḷasavassakāle bhattaṃ bhuñjanto vadeyyāsi, dutiyaṃ mahāupaṭṭhānakāle, tatiyaṃ pāsādaṃ abhiruhamāno sopānasīse ṭhatvā, catutthaṃ sayanasirigabbhaṃ pavisanto ummāre ṭhatvā’’ ti. "
497931,112,980,100,118,1,100,13,So‘‘ sādhū’’ ti sampaṭicchitvā ācariyaṃ vanditvā gato oparajje patiṭṭhāya pitu accayena rajje patiṭṭhāsi. 
497932,112,980,119,136,1,159,17,Tassa putto soḷasavassakāle rañño uyyānakīḷādīnaṃ atthāya nikkhamantassa sirivibhavaṃ disvā pitaraṃ māretvā rajjaṃ gahetukāmo hutvā attano upaṭṭhākānaṃ kathesi. 
497933,112,980,137,161,1,127,18,"Te‘‘ sādhu deva, mahallakakāle laddhena issariyena ko attho, yena kenaci upāyena rājānaṃ māretvā rajjaṃ gaṇhituṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti vadiṃsu. "
497934,112,980,162,178,1,92,12,Kumāro‘‘ visaṃ khādāpetvā māressāmī’’ ti pitarā saddhiṃ sāyamāsaṃ bhuñjanto visaṃ gahetvā nisīdi. 
497935,112,980,179,185,1,59,6,Rājā bhattapātiyaṃ bhatte acchupanteyeva paṭhamaṃ gāthamāha– 
