498019,112,1021,2,7,1,39,4,Tattha {sikhino}ti sikhāya samannāgatassa. 
498020,112,1021,8,11,1,30,2,{Mañjubhāṇino}ti madhurassarassa. 
498021,112,1021,12,15,1,22,3,Apūjesun ti apūjayiṃsu. 
498022,112,1021,16,25,1,61,8,Maṃsena ca phalena {cā}ti nānappakārena maṃsena phalāphalena ca. 
