498032,112,1023,2,4,1,26,2,Bāverujātakavaṇṇanā navamā.
498033,112,1025,2,7,1,20,2,[ 340]10. Visayhajātakavaṇṇanā 
498034,112,1026,2,13,1,76,9,Adāsi {dānānī}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto anāthapiṇḍikaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
498035,112,1026,14,27,1,47,4,Vatthu heṭṭhā khadiraṅgārajātake( jā.1.1.40) vitthāritameva. 
498036,112,1026,28,32,1,31,4,Idha pana satthā anāthapiṇḍikaṃ. 
498037,112,1026,33,60,1,160,21,Āmantetvā‘‘ porāṇakapaṇḍitāpi gahapati‘ dānaṃ mā dadāsī’ ti ākāse ṭhatvā vārentaṃ sakkaṃ devānamindaṃ paṭibāhitvā dānaṃ adaṃsuyevā’’ ti vatvā tena yācito atītaṃ āhari. 
498038,112,1027,2,20,1,156,17,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto asītikoṭivibhavo visayho nāma seṭṭhi hutvā pañcahi sīlehi samannāgato dānajjhāsayo dānābhirato ahosi. 
498039,112,1027,21,41,1,148,17,"So catūsu nagaradvāresu, nagaramajjhe, attano gharadvāreti chasu ṭhānesu dānasālāyo kāretvā dānaṃ pavattesi, divase divase cha satasahassāni vissajjeti. "
498040,112,1027,42,48,1,64,6,Bodhisattassa ca vanibbakayācakānañca ekasadisameva bhattaṃ hoti. 
498041,112,1027,49,66,1,143,15,"Tassa jambudīpaṃ unnaṅgalaṃ katvā dānaṃ dadato dānānubhāvena sakkassa bhavanaṃ kampi, sakkassa devarañño paṇḍukambalasilāsanaṃ uṇhākāraṃ dassesi. "
498042,112,1027,67,125,1,384,47,"Sakko‘‘ ko nu kho maṃ ṭhānā cāvetukāmo’’ ti upadhārento mahāseṭṭhiṃ disvā‘‘ ayaṃ visayho ativiya pattharitvā sakalajambudīpaṃ unnaṅgalaṃ karonto dānaṃ deti, iminā dānena maṃ cāvetvā sayaṃ sakko bhavissati maññe, dhanamassa nāsetvā etaṃ daliddaṃ katvā yathā dānaṃ na deti, tathā karissāmī’’ ti cintetvā sabbaṃ dhanadhaññaṃ telamadhuphāṇitasakkarādīni antamaso dāsakammakaraporisampi antaradhāpesi. "
498043,112,1028,2,19,1,101,12,"Tadā dānabyāvaṭā āgantvā‘‘ sāmi dānaggaṃ pacchinnaṃ, ṭhapitaṭhapitaṭṭhāne na kiñci passāmā’’ ti ārocayiṃsu."
498044,112,1028,20,44,1,101,14,"‘‘ Ito paribbayaṃ haratha, mā dānaṃ pacchindathā’’ ti bhariyaṃ pakkosāpetvā‘‘ bhadde, dānaṃ pavattāpehī’’ ti āha. "
498045,112,1028,45,68,1,139,17,"Sā sakalagehaṃ vicinitvā aḍḍhamāsakamattampi adisvā‘‘ ayya, amhākaṃ nivatthavatthaṃ ṭhapetvā aññaṃ kiñci na passāmi, sakalagehaṃ tucchan’’ ti āha. "
498046,112,1028,69,83,1,119,13,"Sattaratanagabbhesu dvāraṃ vivarāpetvā na kiñci addasa, seṭṭhiñca bhariyañca ṭhapetvā aññe dāsakammakarāpi na paññāyiṃsu. "
498047,112,1028,84,86,1,14,2,Puna mahāsatto. 
498048,112,1028,87,107,1,103,13,"Bhariyaṃ āmantetvā‘‘ bhadde, na sakkā dānaṃ pacchindituṃ, sakalanivesanaṃ vicinitvā kiñci upadhārehī’’ ti āha. "
498049,112,1028,108,118,1,93,10,Tasmiṃ khaṇe eko tiṇahārako asitañca kājañca tiṇabandhanarajjuñca dvārantare chaḍḍetvā palāyi. 
498050,112,1028,119,137,1,77,12,"Seṭṭhibhariyā taṃ disvā‘‘ sāmi, idaṃ ṭhapetvā aññaṃ na passāmī’’ ti āharitvā adāsi. "
