498284,112,1152,2,7,1,19,2,[ 346]6. Kesavajātakavaṇṇanā 
498285,112,1153,2,12,1,86,9,Manussindaṃ {jahitvānā}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto vissāsabhojanaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
498286,112,1153,13,28,1,150,13,"Anāthapiṇḍikassa kira gehe pañcannaṃ bhikkhusatānaṃ nibaddhabhattaṃ hoti, gehaṃ niccakālaṃ bhikkhusaṅghassa opānabhūtaṃ kāsāvapajjotaṃ isivātapaṭivātaṃ. "
498287,112,1153,29,57,1,226,24,Athekadivasaṃ rājā nagaraṃ padakkhiṇaṃ karonto seṭṭhino nivesane bhikkhusaṅghaṃ disvā‘‘ ahampi ariyasaṅghassa nibaddhaṃ bhikkhaṃ dassāmī’’ ti vihāraṃ gantvā satthāraṃ vanditvā pañcannaṃ bhikkhusatānaṃ nibaddhaṃ bhikkhaṃ paṭṭhapesi. 
498288,112,1153,58,67,1,88,8,"Tato paṭṭhāya rājanivesane nibaddhaṃ bhikkhā diyyati, tivassikagandhasālibhojanaṃ paṇītaṃ. "
498289,112,1153,68,76,1,62,7,"Vissāsenapi sinehenapi sahatthā dāyakā natthi, rājayutte dāpesi. "
498290,112,1153,77,101,1,169,22,"Bhikkhū nisīditvā bhuñjituṃ na icchanti, nānaggarasabhattaṃ gahetvā attano attano upaṭṭhākakulaṃ gantvā taṃ bhattaṃ tesaṃ datvā tehi dinnaṃ lūkhaṃ vā paṇītaṃ vā bhuñjanti. "
498291,112,1154,2,7,1,46,5,Athekadivasaṃ rañño bahuṃ phalāphalaṃ āhariṃsu. 
498292,112,1154,8,17,1,27,5,Rājā‘‘ saṅghassa dethā’’ ti āha. 
498293,112,1154,18,33,1,85,11,Manussā bhattaggaṃ gantvā ekabhikkhumpi adisvā‘‘ eko bhikkhupi natthī’’ ti rañño ārocesuṃ.
498294,112,1154,34,42,1,21,4,‘‘ Nanu velāyeva tāvā’’ ti?
498295,112,1154,43,73,1,162,24,"‘‘ Āma, velā, bhikkhū pana tumhākaṃ gehe bhattaṃ gahetvā attano attano vissāsikānaṃ upaṭṭhākānaṃ gehaṃ gantvā tesaṃ datvā tehi dinnaṃ lūkhaṃ vā paṇītaṃ vā bhuñjantī’’ ti. "
498296,112,1154,74,100,1,148,20,"Rājā‘‘ amhākaṃ bhattaṃ paṇītaṃ, kena nu kho kāraṇena abhutvā aññaṃ bhuñjanti, satthāraṃ pucchissāmī’’ ti cintetvā vihāraṃ gantvā satthāraṃ vanditvā pucchi. "
498297,112,1154,101,125,1,178,19,"Satthā‘‘ mahārāja, bhojanaṃ nāma vissāsaparamaṃ, tumhākaṃ gehe vissāsaṃ paccupaṭṭhāpetvā sinehena dāyakānaṃ abhāvā bhikkhū bhattaṃ gahetvā attano attano vissāsikaṭṭhāne paribhuñjanti. "
498298,112,1154,126,143,1,126,15,"Mahārāja, vissāsasadiso añño raso nāma natthi, avissāsikena dinnaṃ catumadhurampi hi vissāsikena dinnaṃ sāmākabhattaṃ na agghati. "
498299,112,1154,144,173,1,249,27,Porāṇakapaṇḍitāpi roge uppanne raññā pañca vejjakulāni gahetvā bhesajje kāritepi roge avūpasante vissāsikānaṃ santikaṃ gantvā aloṇakaṃ sāmākanīvārayāguñceva udakamattasittaṃ aloṇakapaṇṇañca paribhuñjitvā nirogā jātā’’ ti vatvā tena yācito atītaṃ āhari. 
498300,112,1155,2,21,1,119,13,"Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto kāsiraṭṭhe brāmhaṇakule nibbatti,‘‘ kappakumāro’’ tissa nāmaṃ akaṃsu. "
498301,112,1155,22,30,1,82,8,So vayappatto takkasilāyaṃ sabbasippāni uggaṇhitvā aparabhāge isipabbajjaṃ pabbaji. 
498302,112,1155,31,42,1,87,11,Tadā kesavo nāma tāpaso pañcahi tāpasasatehi parivuto gaṇasatthā hutvā himavante vasati. 
498303,112,1155,43,57,1,133,13,"Bodhisatto tassa santikaṃ gantvā pañcannaṃ antevāsikasatānaṃ jeṭṭhantevāsiko hutvā vihāsi, kesavatāpasassa hitajjhāsayo sasineho ahosi. "
498304,112,1155,58,63,1,38,5,Te aññamaññaṃ ativiya vissāsikā ahesuṃ. 
498305,112,1155,64,82,1,168,18,Aparabhāge kesavo te tāpase ādāya loṇambilasevanatthāya manussapathaṃ gantvā bārāṇasiṃ patvā rājuyyāne vasitvā punadivase nagaraṃ bhikkhāya pavisitvā rājadvāraṃ agamāsi. 
