498434,112,1227,2,7,1,24,2,[ 349]9. Sandhibhedajātakavaṇṇanā 
498435,112,1228,2,13,1,90,11,Neva itthīsu sāmaññan ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto pesuññasikkhāpadaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
498436,112,1228,14,98,1,514,60,"Ekasmiṃ kira samaye satthā‘‘ chabbaggiyā bhikkhū pesuññaṃ upasaṃharantī’’ ti sutvā te pakkosāpetvā‘‘ saccaṃ kira tumhe, bhikkhave, bhikkhūnaṃ bhaṇḍanajātānaṃ kalahajātānaṃ vivādāpannānaṃ pesuññaṃ upasaṃharatha, tena anuppannāni ceva bhaṇḍanāni uppajjanti, uppannāni ca bhiyyobhāvāya saṃvattantī’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ saccan’’ ti vutte te bhikkhū garahitvā‘‘ bhikkhave, pisuṇā vācā nāma tikhiṇasattipahārasadisā, daḷho vissāsopi tāya khippaṃ bhijjati, tañca pana gahetvā attano mettibhindanakajano sīhausabhasadiso hotī’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
