498551,112,1303,61,115,1,276,40,"Taṃ disvā bodhisatto‘‘ pitā me ayyakassa matakālato paṭṭhāya sokābhibhūto carati, ṭhapetvā pana maṃ añño etaṃ saññāpetuṃ na sakkoti, ekena naṃ upāyena nissokaṃ karissāmī’’ ti bahigāme ekaṃ matagoṇaṃ disvā tiṇañca pānīyañca āharitvā tassa purato ṭhapetvā‘‘ khāda, khāda, piva, pivā’’ ti āha. "
