498574,112,1317,2,11,1,47,6,"Rudaṃ mattikathūpasmiṃ, nanu tvaññeva dummatī’’ ti. "
498575,112,1318,2,11,1,52,7,"Tattha {tathevā}ti yathā pubbe ṭhitaṃ, tatheva tiṭṭhati. "
498576,112,1318,12,22,1,75,9,{Maññe}ti etesaṃ sīsādīnaṃ tatheva ṭhitattā ayaṃ goṇo samuṭṭhaheyyāti maññāmi. 
498577,112,1318,23,33,1,71,9,Nevayyakassa {sīsañcā}ti ayyakassa pana sīsañca hatthapādā ca na dissanti.
498578,112,1318,34,43,1,32,5,‘‘ Piṭṭhipādā na dissare’’ tipi pāṭho. 
498579,112,1318,44,67,1,154,20,"Nanu tvaññeva {dummatī}ti ahaṃ tāva sīsādīni passanto evaṃ karomi, tvaṃ pana na kiñci passasi, jhāpitaṭṭhānato aṭṭhīni āharitvā mattikāthūpaṃ katvā paridevasi. "
498580,112,1318,68,77,1,80,9,Iti maṃ paṭicca sataguṇena sahassaguṇena satasahassaguṇena nanu tvaññeva dummati. 
498581,112,1318,78,86,1,61,7,"Bhijjanadhammā nāma saṅkhārā bhijjanti, tattha kā paridevanāti. "
498582,112,1319,2,56,1,293,38,"Taṃ sutvā bodhisattassa pitā‘‘ mama putto paṇḍito idhalokaparalokakiccaṃ jānāti, mama saññāpanatthāya etaṃ kammaṃ akāsī’’ ti cintetvā‘‘ tāta sujātapaṇḍita,‘ sabbe saṅkhārā aniccā’ ti me ñātā, ito paṭṭhāya na socissāmi, pitusokaharaṇakaputtena nāma tādisena bhavitabban’’ ti vatvā puttassa thutiṃ karonto āha– "
498583,112,1320,2,4,1,0,0,10.
498584,112,1321,2,11,1,45,7,"‘ ‘ Ādittaṃ vata maṃ santaṃ, ghatasittaṃva pāvakaṃ; "
498585,112,1322,2,9,1,42,6,"Vārinā viya osiñcaṃ, sabbaṃ nibbāpaye daraṃ. "
