498595,112,1332,2,6,1,28,3,Tattha {nibbāpaye}ti nibbāpayi. 
498596,112,1332,7,10,1,21,3,Daran ti sokadarathaṃ. 
498597,112,1332,11,32,1,152,19,"Sujāto pitaraṃ {yathā}ti yathā mama putto sujāto maṃ pitaraṃ samānaṃ attano sappaññatāya sokamhā vinivattayi, evaṃ aññepi sappaññā sokamhā vinivattayantīti. "
498598,112,1333,2,15,1,124,12,"Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā saccāni pakāsetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi, saccapariyosāne kuṭumbiko sotāpattiphale patiṭṭhahi. "
