498600,112,1334,2,4,1,26,2,Sujātajātakavaṇṇanā dutiyā.
498601,112,1336,2,7,1,22,2,[ 353]3. Venasākhajātakavaṇṇanā 
498602,112,1337,2,16,1,130,14,Nayidaṃ niccaṃ bhavitabban ti idaṃ satthā bhaggesu saṃsumāragiraṃ nissāya bhesakaḷāvane viharanto bodhirājakumāraṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
498603,112,1337,17,39,1,181,21,Bodhirājakumāro nāma udenassa rañño putto tasmiṃ kāle saṃsumāragire vasanto ekaṃ pariyodātasippaṃ vaḍḍhakiṃ pakkosāpetvā aññehi rājūhi asadisaṃ katvā kokanadaṃ nāma pāsādaṃ kārāpesi. 
498604,112,1337,40,60,1,114,15,Kārāpetvā ca pana‘‘ ayaṃ vaḍḍhakī aññassapi rañño evarūpaṃ pāsādaṃ kareyyā’’ ti maccharāyanto tassa akkhīni uppāṭāpesi. 
498605,112,1337,61,67,1,56,6,Tenassa akkhīnaṃ uppāṭitabhāvo bhikkhusaṅghe pākaṭo jāto. 
498606,112,1337,68,91,1,152,17,"Tasmā bhikkhū dhammasabhāyaṃ kathaṃ samuṭṭhāpesuṃ‘‘ āvuso, bodhirājakumāro kira tathārūpassa vaḍḍhakino akkhīni uppāṭāpesi, aho kakkhaḷo pharuso sāhasiko’’ ti. "
498607,112,1337,92,128,1,155,21,"Satthā āgantvā‘‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ imāya nāmā’’ ti vutte‘‘ na, bhikkhave, idāneva, pubbepesa kakkhaḷo pharuso sāhasikova. "
498608,112,1337,129,148,1,131,16,"Na kevalañca idāneva, pubbepesa khattiyasahassānaṃ akkhīni uppāṭāpetvā māretvā tesaṃ maṃsena balikammaṃ kāresī’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
498609,112,1338,2,13,1,95,10,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto takkasilāyaṃ disāpāmokkho ācariyo ahosi. 
498610,112,1338,14,22,1,80,8,Jambudīpatale khattiyamāṇavā brāhmaṇamāṇavā ca tasseva santike sippaṃ uggaṇhiṃsu. 
498611,112,1338,23,32,1,74,9,Bārāṇasirañño putto brahmadattakumāro nāma tassa santike tayo vede uggaṇhi. 
498612,112,1338,33,40,1,50,7,So pana pakatiyāpi kakkhaḷo pharuso sāhasiko ahosi. 
498613,112,1338,41,84,1,279,35,"Bodhisatto aṅgavijjāvasena tassa kakkhaḷapharusasāhasikabhāvaṃ ñatvā‘‘ tāta, tvaṃ kakkhaḷo pharuso sāhasiko, pharusena nāma laddhaṃ issariyaṃ aciraṭṭhitikaṃ hoti, so issariye vinaṭṭhe bhinnanāvo viya samudde patiṭṭhaṃ na labhati, tasmā mā evarūpo ahosī’’ ti taṃ ovadanto dve gāthā abhāsi– "
498614,112,1339,2,4,1,0,0,14.
498615,112,1340,2,14,1,72,10,"‘ ‘ Nayidaṃ niccaṃ bhavitabbaṃ brahmadatta, khemaṃ subhikkhaṃ sukhatā ca kāye; "
498616,112,1341,2,10,1,59,7,"Atthaccaye mā ahu sampamūḷho, bhinnaplavo sāgarasseva majjhe. "
498617,112,1342,2,4,1,0,0,15.
498618,112,1343,2,11,1,38,7,"‘ ‘ Yāni karoti puriso, tāni attani passati; "
498619,112,1344,2,8,1,40,5,"Kalyāṇakārī kalyāṇaṃ, pāpakārī ca pāpakaṃ; "
498620,112,1345,2,12,1,45,7,"Yādisaṃ vapate bījaṃ, tādisaṃ harate phalan’’ ti. "
498621,112,1346,2,36,1,194,29,"Tattha sukhatā ca {kāye}ti tāta brahmadatta, yadetaṃ khemaṃ vā subhikkhaṃ vā yā vā esā sukhatā kāye, idaṃ sabbaṃ imesaṃ sattānaṃ niccaṃ sabbakālameva na bhavati, idaṃ pana aniccaṃ hutvā abhāvadhammaṃ. "
498622,112,1346,37,63,1,188,23,"{Atthaccaye}ti so tvaṃ aniccatāvasena issariye vigate attano atthassa accaye yathā nāma bhinnaplavo bhinnanāvo manusso sāgaramajjhe patiṭṭhaṃ alabhanto sampamūḷho hoti, evaṃ mā ahu sampamūḷho. "
498623,112,1346,64,76,1,78,11,Tāni attani {passatī}ti tesaṃ kammānaṃ vipākaṃ vindanto tāni attani passati nāma. 
498624,112,1347,2,16,1,106,14,So ācariyaṃ vanditvā bārāṇasiṃ gantvā pitu sippaṃ dassetvā oparajje patiṭṭhāya pitu accayena rajjaṃ pāpuṇi. 
498625,112,1347,17,25,1,59,8,Tassa piṅgiyo nāma purohito ahosi kakkhaḷo pharuso sāhasiko. 
498626,112,1347,26,49,1,145,17,"So yasalobhena cintesi‘‘ yaṃnūnāhaṃ iminā raññā sakalajambudīpe sabbe rājāno gāhāpeyyaṃ, evamesa ekarājā bhavissati, ahampi ekapurohito bhavissāmī’’ ti. "
498627,112,1347,50,56,1,37,6,So taṃ rājānaṃ attano kathaṃ gāhāpesi. 
498628,112,1347,57,69,1,88,12,Rājā mahatiyā senāya nagarā nikkhamitvā ekassa rañño nagaraṃ rundhitvā taṃ rājānaṃ gaṇhi. 
498629,112,1347,70,84,1,104,10,Etenupāyena sakalajambudīpe rajjaṃ gahetvā rājasahassaparivuto‘‘ takkasilāyaṃ rajjaṃ gaṇhissāmī’’ ti agamāsi. 
498630,112,1347,85,91,1,61,6,Bodhisatto nagaraṃ paṭisaṅkharitvā parehi appadhaṃsiyaṃ akāsi. 
498631,112,1348,2,17,1,136,14,Bārāṇasirājā gaṅgānadītīre mahato nigrodharukkhasssa mūle sāṇiṃ parikkhipāpetvā upari vitānaṃ kārāpetvā sayanaṃ paññapetvā nivāsaṃ gaṇhi. 
498632,112,1348,18,50,1,205,26,"So jambudīpatale sahassarājāno gahetvā yujjhamānopi takkasilaṃ gahetuṃ asakkonto attano purohitaṃ pucchi‘‘ ācariya, mayaṃ ettakehi rājūhi saddhiṃ āgantvāpi takkasilaṃ gahetuṃ na sakkoma, kiṃ nu kho kātabban’’ ti."
498633,112,1348,51,84,1,247,26,"‘‘ Mahārāja, sahassarājūnaṃ akkhīni uppāṭetvā māretvā kucchiṃ phāletvā pañcamadhuramaṃsaṃ ādāya imasmiṃ nigrodhe adhivatthāya devatāya balikammaṃ katvā antavaṭṭīhi rukkhaṃ parikkhipitvā lohitapañcaṅgulikāni karoma, evaṃ no khippameva jayo bhavissatī’’ ti. "
498634,112,1348,85,118,1,259,29,Rājā‘‘ sādhū’’ ti paṭissuṇitvā antosāṇiyaṃ mahābale malle ṭhapetvā ekamekaṃ rājānaṃ pakkosāpetvā nippīḷanena visaññaṃ kāretvā akkhīni uppāṭetvā māretvā maṃsaṃ ādāya kaḷevarāni gaṅgāyaṃ pavāhetvā vuttappakāraṃ balikammaṃ kāretvā balibheriṃ ākoṭāpetvā yuddhāya gato. 
498635,112,1349,2,16,1,99,12,"Athassa aṭṭālakato eko yakkho āgantvā dakkhiṇakkhiṃ uppāṭetvā agamāsi, athassa mahatī vedanā uppajji. "
498636,112,1349,17,24,1,72,7,So vedanāppatto āgantvā nigrodharukkhamūle paññattāsane uttānako nipajji. 
498637,112,1349,25,49,1,182,23,"Tasmiṃ khaṇe eko gijjho ekaṃ tikhiṇakoṭikaṃ aṭṭhiṃ gahetvā rukkhagge nisinno maṃsaṃ khāditvā aṭṭhiṃ vissajjesi, aṭṭhikoṭi āgantvā rañño vāmakkhimhi ayasūlaṃ viya patitvā akkhiṃ bhindi. "
498638,112,1349,50,55,1,46,5,Tasmiṃ khaṇe bodhisattassa vacanaṃ sallakkhesi. 
498639,112,1349,56,85,1,156,23,So‘‘ amhākaṃ ācariyo‘ ime sattā bījānurūpaṃ phalaṃ viya kammānurūpaṃ vipākaṃ anubhontī’ ti kathento idaṃ disvā kathesi maññe’’ ti vatvā vilapanto dve gāthā abhāsi– 
498640,112,1350,2,4,1,0,0,16.
498641,112,1351,2,9,1,40,5,"‘ ‘ Idaṃ tadācariyavaco, pārāsariyo yadabravi;"
498642,112,1352,2,15,1,49,11,"‘ Mā su tvaṃ akari pāpaṃ, yaṃ tvaṃ pacchā kataṃ tape’. "
498643,112,1353,2,4,1,0,0,17.
498644,112,1354,2,13,1,65,9,"‘ ‘ Ayameva so piṅgiya venasākho, yamhi ghātayiṃ khattiyānaṃ sahasssaṃ; "
498645,112,1355,2,12,1,62,7,"Alaṅkate candanasārānulitte, tameva dukkhaṃ paccāgataṃ maman’’ ti. "
498646,112,1356,2,11,1,56,7,Tattha idaṃ {tadācariyavaco}ti idaṃ taṃ ācariyassa vacanaṃ. 
498647,112,1356,12,17,1,32,4,{Pārāsariyo}ti taṃ gottena kitteti. 
498648,112,1356,18,42,1,124,21,"Pacchā katan ti yaṃ pāpaṃ tayā kataṃ, pacchā taṃ tapeyya kilameyya, taṃ mā karīti ovādaṃ adāsi, ahaṃ panassa vacanaṃ na karinti. "
498649,112,1356,43,48,1,43,4,{Ayamevā}ti nigrodharukkhaṃ dassento vilapati. 
498650,112,1356,49,52,1,25,2,{Venasākho}ti patthaṭasākho. 
498651,112,1356,53,60,1,55,7,Yamhi ghātayin ti yamhi rukkhe khattiyasahassaṃ māresiṃ. 
498652,112,1356,61,84,1,182,20,"Alaṅkate {candanasārānulitte}ti rājālaṅkārehi alaṅkate lohitacandanasārānulitte te khattiye yatthāhaṃ ghātesiṃ , ayameva so rukkho idāni mayhaṃ kiñci parittāṇaṃ kātuṃ na sakkotīti dīpeti. "
498653,112,1356,85,106,1,146,19,"Tameva dukkhan ti yaṃ mayā paresaṃ akkhiuppāṭanadukkhaṃ kataṃ, idaṃ me tatheva paṭiāgataṃ, idāni no ācariyassa vacanaṃ matthakaṃ pattanti paridevati. "
498654,112,1357,2,8,1,44,5,So evaṃ paridevamāno aggamahesiṃ anussaritvā– 
498655,112,1358,2,4,1,0,0,18.
498656,112,1359,2,12,1,61,8,"‘ ‘ Sāmā ca kho candanalittagattā, laṭṭhīva sobhañjanakassa uggatā; "
498657,112,1360,2,15,1,67,10,"Adisvā kālaṃ karissāmi ubbariṃ, taṃ me ito dukkhataraṃ bhavissatī’’ ti."
498658,112,1360,16,16,1,0,0,– 
498659,112,1361,2,3,1,9,1,Gāthamāha – 
498660,112,1362,2,40,1,288,34,"Tassattho – mama bhariyā suvaṇṇasāmā ubbarī yathā nāma siggurukkhassa uju uggatā sākhā mandamāluteritā kampamānā sobhati, evaṃ itthivilāsaṃ kurumānā sobhati, tamahaṃ idāni akkhīnaṃ bhinnattā ubbariṃ adisvāva kālaṃ karissāmi, taṃ me tassā adassanaṃ ito maraṇadukkhatopi dukkhataraṃ bhavissatīti. "
498661,112,1363,2,8,1,43,6,So evaṃ vilapantova maritvā niraye nibbatti. 
498662,112,1363,9,20,1,74,10,"Na naṃ issariyaluddho purohito parittāṇaṃ kātuṃ sakkhi, na attano issariyaṃ. "
498663,112,1363,21,26,1,46,5,Tasmiṃ matamatteyeva balakāyo bhijjitvā palāyi. 
498664,112,1364,2,8,1,54,6,Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–
498665,112,1364,9,26,1,99,11,"‘‘ tadā bārāṇasirājā bodhirājakumāro ahosi, piṅgiyo devadatto, disāpāmokkhācariyo pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
498666,112,1365,2,4,1,29,2,Venasākhajātakavaṇṇanā tatiyā.
498667,112,1367,2,7,1,18,2,[ 354]4. Uragajātakavaṇṇanā 
498668,112,1368,2,15,1,94,12,Uragova tacaṃ jiṇṇan ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto mataputtakaṃ kuṭumbikaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
498669,112,1368,16,19,1,49,3,Vatthu pana matabhariyamatapitikavatthusadisameva. 
498670,112,1368,20,127,1,589,77,"Idhāpi tatheva satthā tassa nivesanaṃ gantvā taṃ āgantvā vanditvā nisinnaṃ‘‘ kiṃ, āvuso, socasī’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ āma, bhante , puttassa me matakālato paṭṭhāya socāmī’’ ti vutte‘‘ āvuso, bhijjanadhammaṃ nāma bhijjati, nassanadhammaṃ nāma nassati, tañca kho na ekasmiṃyeva kule, nāpi ekasmiññeva gāme, atha kho aparimāṇesu cakkavāḷesu tīsu bhavesu amaraṇadhammo nāma natthi, tabbhāveneva ṭhātuṃ samattho ekasaṅkhāropi sassato nāma natthi, sabbe sattā maraṇadhammā, sabbe saṅkhārā bhijjanadhammā, porāṇakapaṇḍitāpi putte mate‘ maraṇadhammaṃ mataṃ, nassanadhammaṃ naṭṭhan’ ti na sociṃsū’’ ti vatvā tena yācito atītaṃ āhari. "
498671,112,1369,2,17,1,153,15,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto bārāṇasiyaṃ dvāragāmake brāhmaṇakule nibbattitvā kuṭumbaṃ saṇṭhapetvā kasikammena jīvikaṃ kappesi. 
498672,112,1369,18,26,1,43,8,Tassa putto ca dhītā cāti dve dārakā ahesuṃ. 
498673,112,1369,27,54,1,146,20,"So puttassa vayappattassa samānakulato kumārikaṃ āharitvā adāsi, iti te dāsiyā saddhiṃ cha janā ahesuṃ– bodhisatto, bhariyā, putto, dhītā, suṇisā, dāsīti. "
498674,112,1369,55,60,1,41,5,Te samaggā sammodamānā piyasaṃvāsā ahesuṃ. 
498675,112,1369,61,108,1,309,35,"Bodhisatto sesānaṃ pañcannaṃ evaṃ ovādaṃ deti‘‘ tumhe yathāladdhaniyāmeneva dānaṃ detha, sīlaṃ rakkhatha, uposathakammaṃ karotha, maraṇassatiṃ bhāvetha, tumhākaṃ maraṇabhāvaṃ sallakkhetha, imesañhi sattānaṃ maraṇaṃ dhuvaṃ, jīvitaṃ addhuvaṃ, sabbe saṅkhārā aniccā khayavayadhamminova, rattiñca divā ca appamattā hothā’’ ti. "
498676,112,1369,109,121,1,65,8,Te‘‘ sādhū’’ ti ovādaṃ sampaṭicchitvā appamattā maraṇassatiṃ bhāventi. 
498677,112,1370,2,10,1,62,7,Athekadivasaṃ bodhisatto puttena saddhiṃ khettaṃ gantvā kasati. 
498678,112,1370,11,15,1,36,4,Putto kacavaraṃ saṅkaḍḍhitvā jhāpeti. 
498679,112,1370,16,21,1,41,5,Tassāvidūre ekasmiṃ vammike āsīviso atthi. 
498680,112,1370,22,26,1,26,4,Dhūmo tassa akkhīni pahari. 
498681,112,1370,27,48,1,111,16,"So kuddho nikkhamitvā‘‘ imaṃ nissāya mayhaṃ bhayan’’ ti catasso dāṭhā nimujjāpento taṃ ḍaṃsi, so parivattitvā patito. "
498682,112,1370,49,70,1,164,21,Bodhisatto parivattitvā taṃ patitaṃ disvā goṇe ṭhapetvā gantvā tassa matabhāvaṃ ñatvā taṃ ukkhipitvā ekasmiṃ rukkhamūle nipajjāpetvā pārupitvā neva rodi na paridevi–
498683,112,1370,71,90,1,125,13,"‘‘ bhijjanadhammaṃ pana bhinnaṃ, maraṇadhammaṃ mataṃ, sabbe saṅkhārā aniccā maraṇanipphattikā’’ ti aniccabhāvameva sallakkhetvā kasi. "
498684,112,1370,91,151,1,351,45,"So khettasamīpena gacchantaṃ ekaṃ paṭivissakaṃ purisaṃ disvā‘‘ tāta, gehaṃ gacchasī’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ āmā’’ ti vutte tena hi amhākampi gharaṃ gantvā brāhmaṇiṃ vadeyyāsi‘‘ ajja kira pubbe viya dvinnaṃ bhattaṃ anāharitvā ekassevāhāraṃ āhareyyātha, pubbe ca ekikāva dāsī āhāraṃ āharati, ajja pana cattāropi janā suddhavatthanivatthā gandhapupphahatthā āgaccheyyāthā’’ ti. "
