498827,112,1436,2,20,1,138,16,"Ṭhitaṃ maṃ {nāgamissatī}ti samma dhaṅkarāja, etesu gāmādīsu yattha katthaci ṭhitaṃ maṃ paṇḍukisabhāvādikaṃ sokamūlakaṃ byasanaṃ na āgamissati. "
498828,112,1436,21,33,1,76,10,"Evaṃ {diṭṭhapado}ti yathā taṃ byasanaṃ nāgacchati, evaṃ mayā jhānapadaṃ diṭṭhaṃ."
498829,112,1436,34,42,1,38,3,‘‘ Aṭṭhalokadhammapadan’’ tipi vadantiyeva . 
498830,112,1436,43,58,1,71,10,"Pāḷiyaṃ pana‘‘ na mattaṃ nāgamissatī’’ ti likhitaṃ, taṃ aṭṭhakathāyaṃ natthi. "
498831,112,1436,59,65,1,102,6,Pariyosānagāthāya icchitapatthitatthena jhānasukhasaṅkhātaṃ sabbakāmarasaṃ āharatīti sabbakāmarasāharo. 
498832,112,1436,66,92,1,186,23,"Idaṃ vuttaṃ hoti– yassa rañño pahāya aññasahāye attāva eko sabbakāmarasāharo nālaṃ, sabbaṃ jhānasukhasaṅkhātaṃ kāmarasaṃ āharituṃ asamattho, tassa rañño sabbāpi pathavī na sukhaṃ āvahissati. "
498833,112,1436,93,110,1,113,15,"Kāmāturassa hi sukhaṃ nāma natthi, yo pana kilesadaratharahitaṃ jhānasukhaṃ āharituṃ samattho, so rājā sukhī hotīti. "
498834,112,1436,111,126,1,70,10,"Yo panetāya gāthāya‘‘ yassatthā nālameko’’ tipi pāṭho, tassattho na dissati. "
498835,112,1437,2,14,1,86,11,Iti dhaṅko imā catasso gāthā sutvā bodhisattaṃ khamāpetvā rajjaṃ paṭicchāpetvā pakkāmi. 
498836,112,1437,15,26,1,133,11,Bodhisattopi rajjaṃ amaccānaṃ paṭiniyyādetvā himavantapadesaṃ gantvā isipabbajjaṃ pabbajitvā aparihīnajjhāno brahmalokaparāyaṇo ahosi. 
498837,112,1438,2,8,1,54,6,Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–
498838,112,1438,9,23,1,61,9,"‘‘ tadā dhaṅkarājā ānando ahosi, ghaṭarājā pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
498839,112,1439,2,4,1,26,2,Ghaṭajātakavaṇṇanā pañcamā.
498840,112,1441,2,7,1,22,2,[ 356]6. Koraṇḍiyajātakavaṇṇanā 
498841,112,1442,2,12,1,75,9,Eko {araññe}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto dhammasenāpatiṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
498842,112,1442,13,31,1,127,13,"Thero kira āgatāgatānaṃ dussīlānaṃ migaluddakamacchabandhādīnaṃ diṭṭhadiṭṭhānaññeva‘‘ sīlaṃ gaṇhatha, sīlaṃ gaṇhathā’’ ti sīlaṃ deti. "
498843,112,1442,32,52,1,129,18,"Te there garubhāvena tassa kathaṃ bhindituṃ asakkontā sīlaṃ gaṇhanti, gahetvā ca pana na rakkhanti, attano attano kammameva karonti. "
498844,112,1442,53,78,1,113,17,"Thero saddhivihārike āmantetvā ‘‘ āvuso, ime manussā mama santike sīlaṃ gaṇhiṃsu, gaṇhitvā ca pana na rakkhantī’’ ti āha."
498845,112,1442,79,106,1,138,20,"‘‘ Bhante, tumhe etesaṃ aruciyā sīlaṃ detha, ete tumhākaṃ kathaṃ bhindituṃ asakkontā gaṇhanti, tumhe ito paṭṭhāya evarūpānaṃ sīlaṃ mā adatthā’’ ti. "
498846,112,1442,107,110,1,22,3,Thero anattamano ahosi. 
498847,112,1442,111,118,1,62,7,Taṃ pavattiṃ sutvā bhikkhū dhammasabhāyaṃ kathaṃ samuṭṭhāpesuṃ–
498848,112,1442,119,131,1,60,7,"‘‘ āvuso, sāriputtatthero kira diṭṭhadiṭṭhānaññeva sīlaṃ detī’’ ti. "
498849,112,1442,132,175,1,192,26,"Satthā āgantvā‘‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ imāya nāmā’’ ti vutte‘‘ na, bhikkhave, idāneva, pubbepesa diṭṭhadiṭṭhānaṃ ayācantānaññeva sīlaṃ detī’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
498850,112,1443,2,18,1,168,16,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto brāhmaṇakule nibbattitvā vayappatto takkasilāyaṃ disāpāmokkhassa ācariyassa jeṭṭhantevāsiko koraṇḍiyo nāma ahosi. 
498851,112,1443,19,37,1,104,13,"Tadā so ācariyo diṭṭhadiṭṭhānaṃ kevaṭṭādīnaṃ ayācantānaññeva‘‘ sīlaṃ gaṇhatha, sīlaṃ gaṇhathā’’ ti sīlaṃ deti. "
498852,112,1443,38,47,1,65,8,Te gahetvāpi na rakkhanti ācariyo tamatthaṃ antevāsikānaṃ ārocesi. 
498853,112,1443,48,74,1,136,18,"Antevāsikā‘‘ bhante, tumhe etesaṃ aruciyā sīlaṃ detha, tasmā bhindanti, ito dāni paṭṭhāya yācantānaññeva dadeyyātha, mā ayācantānan’’ ti vadiṃsu. "
498854,112,1443,75,84,1,64,8,"So vippaṭisārī ahosi, evaṃ santepi diṭṭhadiṭṭhānaṃ sīlaṃ detiyeva. "
498855,112,1444,2,10,1,86,8,Athekadivasaṃ ekasmā gāmā manussā āgantvā brāhmaṇavācanakatthāya ācariyaṃ nimantayiṃsu. 
498856,112,1444,11,38,1,165,21,"So koraṇḍiyamāṇavaṃ pakkositvā‘‘ tāta, ahaṃ na gacchāmi, tvaṃ ime pañcasate māṇave gahetvā tattha gantvā vācanakāni sampaṭicchitvā amhākaṃ dinnakoṭṭhāsaṃ āharā’’ ti pesesi. "
498857,112,1444,39,69,1,190,24,"So gantvā paṭinivattanto antarāmagge ekaṃ kandaraṃ disvā cintesi‘‘ amhākaṃ ācariyo diṭṭhadiṭṭhānaṃ ayācantānaññeva sīlaṃ deti, ito dāni paṭṭhāya yathā yācantānaññeva deti, tathā naṃ karissāmī’’ ti. "
498858,112,1444,70,85,1,112,13,"So tesu māṇavesu sukhanisinnesu uṭṭhāya mahantaṃ mahantaṃ selaṃ ukkhipitvā kandarāyaṃ khipi, punappunaṃ khipiyeva. "
498859,112,1444,86,101,1,55,10,"Atha naṃ te māṇavā uṭṭhāya‘‘ ācariya, kiṃ karosī’’ ti āhaṃsu. "
498860,112,1444,102,112,1,56,9,"So na kiñci kathesi, te vegena gantvā ācariyassa ārocesuṃ. "
498861,112,1444,113,120,1,58,7,Ācariyo āgantvā tena saddhiṃ sallapanto paṭhamaṃ gāthamāha– 
498862,112,1445,2,4,1,0,0,34.
498863,112,1446,2,12,1,60,8,"‘ ‘ Eko araññe girikandarāyaṃ, paggayha paggayha silaṃ pavecchasi; "
498864,112,1447,2,13,1,60,8,"Punappunaṃ santaramānarūpo, koraṇḍiya ko nu tava yidhattho’’ ti. "
498865,112,1448,2,15,1,76,12,Tattha ko nu tava {yidhattho}ti ko nu tava idha kandarāyaṃ silākhipanena attho. 
498866,112,1449,2,11,1,63,8,So tassa vacanaṃ sutvā ācariyaṃ pabodhetukāmo dutiyaṃ gāthamāha– 
498867,112,1450,2,4,1,0,0,35.
498868,112,1451,2,11,1,55,7,"‘ ‘ Ahañhimaṃ sāgarasevitantaṃ, samaṃ karissāmi yathāpi pāṇi; "
498869,112,1452,2,15,1,64,10,"Vikiriya sānūni ca pabbatāni ca, tasmā silaṃ dariyā pakkhipāmī’’ ti. "
498870,112,1453,2,9,1,44,6,Tattha ahañhiman ti ahañhi imaṃ mahāpathaviṃ. 
498871,112,1453,10,15,1,47,5,Sāgarasevitantan ti sāgarehi sevitaṃ cāturantaṃ. 
498872,112,1453,16,23,1,47,6,Yathāpi {pāṇī}ti hatthatalaṃ viya samaṃ karissāmi. 
498873,112,1453,24,27,1,20,2,{Vikiriyā}ti vikiritvā. 
498874,112,1453,28,37,1,55,8,Sānūni ca pabbatāni {cā}ti paṃsupabbate ca silāpabbate ca. 
498875,112,1454,2,7,1,36,5,Taṃ sutvā brāhmaṇo tatiyaṃ gāthamāha– 
