498877,112,1456,2,13,1,60,9,"‘ ‘ Nayimaṃ mahiṃ arahati pāṇikappaṃ, samaṃ manusso karaṇāya meko; "
498878,112,1457,2,12,1,58,7,"Maññāmimaññeva dariṃ jigīsaṃ, koraṇḍiya hāhasi jīvalokan’’ ti. "
498879,112,1458,2,13,1,61,9,Tattha karaṇāya {meko}ti karaṇāya eko kātuṃ na sakkotīti dīpeti. 
498880,112,1458,14,41,1,203,25,"Maññāmimaññeva dariṃ jigīsan ti ahaṃ maññāmi tiṭṭhatu pathavī, imaññeva ekaṃ dariṃ jigīsaṃ pūraṇatthāya vāyamanto silā pariyesanto upāyaṃ vicinantova tvaṃ imaṃ jīvalokaṃ hāhasi jahissasi, marissasīti attho. "
498881,112,1459,2,7,1,36,5,Taṃ sutvā māṇavo catutthaṃ gāthamāha– 
498882,112,1460,2,4,1,0,0,37.
498883,112,1461,2,14,1,58,10,"‘ ‘ Sace ayaṃ bhūtadharaṃ na sakkā, samaṃ manusso karaṇāya meko; "
498884,112,1462,2,14,1,62,9,"Evameva tvaṃ brahme ime manusse, nānādiṭṭhike nānayissasi te’’ ti. "
498885,112,1463,2,53,1,278,38,"Tassattho – sace ayaṃ eko manusso imaṃ bhūtadharaṃ pathaviṃ samaṃ kātuṃ na sakkā na samattho, evameva tvaṃ ime dussīlamanusse nānādiṭṭhike nānayissasi, te evaṃ‘‘ sīlaṃ gaṇhatha, sīlaṃ gaṇhathā’’ ti vadanto attano vasaṃ na ānayissasi, paṇḍitapurisāyeva hi pāṇātipātaṃ‘‘ akusalan’’ ti garahanti. "
498886,112,1463,54,69,1,123,13,"Saṃsāramocakādayo panettha kusalasaññino, te tvaṃ kathaṃ ānayissasi, tasmā diṭṭhadiṭṭhānaṃ sīlaṃ adatvā yācantānaññeva dehīti. "
498887,112,1464,2,24,1,119,16,"Taṃ sutvā ācariyo‘‘ yuttaṃ vadati koraṇḍiyo, idāni na evarūpaṃ karissāmī’’ ti attano viraddhabhāvaṃ ñatvā pañcamaṃ gāthamāha– "
498888,112,1465,2,4,1,0,0,38.
498889,112,1466,2,12,1,59,7,"‘ ‘ Saṃkhittarūpena bhavaṃ mamatthaṃ, akkhāsi koraṇḍiya evametaṃ; "
498890,112,1467,2,15,1,64,10,"Yathā na sakkā pathavī samāyaṃ, kattuṃ manussena tathā manussā’’ ti. "
498891,112,1468,2,7,1,28,5,Tattha samāyan ti samaṃ ayaṃ. 
498892,112,1468,8,20,1,71,11,"Evaṃ ācariyo māṇavassa thutiṃ akāsi, sopi naṃ bodhetvā sayaṃ gharaṃ nesi. "
