498956,112,1506,2,7,1,27,2,[ 358]8. Cūḷadhammapālajātakavaṇṇanā 
498957,112,1507,2,16,1,107,12,Ahameva dūsiyā {bhūnahatā}ti idaṃ satthā veḷuvane viharanto devadattassa vadhāya parisakkanaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
498958,112,1507,17,38,1,187,19,"Aññesu jātakesu devadatto bodhisattassa tāsamattampi kātuṃ nāsakkhi, imasmiṃ pana cūḷadhammapālajātake bodhisattassa sattamāsikakāle hatthapāde ca sīsañca chedāpetvā asimālakaṃ nāma kāresi. "
498959,112,1507,39,56,1,64,8,Daddarajātake( jā.1.2.43-44) gīvaṃ gahetvā māretvā uddhane maṃsaṃ pacitvā khādi. 
498960,112,1507,57,85,1,171,18,Khantīvādījātake( jā.1.4.49 ādayo) dvīhipi kasāhi pahārasahassehi tāḷāpetvā hatthapāde ca kaṇṇanāsañca chedāpetvā jaṭāsu gahetvā kaḍḍhāpetvā uttānakaṃ nipajjāpetvā ure pādena paharitvā gato. 
498961,112,1507,86,91,1,47,5,Bodhisatto taṃ divasaṃyeva jīvitakkhayaṃ pāpuṇi. 
498962,112,1507,92,114,1,47,3,Cūḷanandiyajātakepi( jā.1.2.143-144) mahākapijātakepi( jā.1.7.83 ādayo) māresiyeva. 
498963,112,1507,115,122,1,70,7,Evameva so dīgharattaṃ vadhāya parisakkanto buddhakālepi parisakkiyeva. 
498964,112,1507,123,128,1,57,5,Athekadivasaṃ bhikkhū dhammasabhāyaṃ kathaṃ samuṭṭhāpesuṃ–
498965,112,1507,129,155,1,146,16,"‘‘ āvuso, devadatto buddhānaṃ māraṇatthameva upāyaṃ karoti,‘ sammāsambuddhaṃ mārāpessāmī’ ti dhanuggahe payojesi, silaṃ pavijjhi, nāḷāgiriṃ vissajjāpesī’’ ti. "
498966,112,1507,156,216,1,316,41,"Satthā āgantvā‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ imāya nāmā’’ ti vutte‘‘ na, bhikkhave, idāneva, pubbepesa mayhaṃ vadhāya parisakkiyeva, idāni pana tāsamattampi kātuṃ na sakkoti , pubbe maṃ cūḷadhammapālakumārakāle attano puttaṃ samānaṃ jīvatakkhayaṃ pāpetvā asimālakaṃ kāresī’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
498967,112,1508,2,23,1,140,16,"Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ mahāpatāpe nāma rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto tassa aggamahesiyā candādeviyā kucchimhi nibbatti,‘‘ dhammapālo’’ tissa nāmaṃ kariṃsu. "
498968,112,1508,24,32,1,82,8,Tamenaṃ sattamāsikakāle mātā gandhodakena nhāpetvā alaṅkaritvā kīḷāpayamānā nisīdi. 
498969,112,1508,33,37,1,32,4,Rājā tassā vasanaṭṭhānaṃ agamāsi. 
498970,112,1508,38,48,1,82,10,Sā puttaṃ kīḷāpayamānā puttasinehena samappitā hutvā rājānaṃ passitvāpi na uṭṭhahi. 
498971,112,1508,49,84,1,165,26,"So cintesi‘‘ ayaṃ idāneva tāva puttaṃ nissāya mānaṃ karoti, maṃ kismiñci na maññati, putte pana vaḍḍhante mayi‘ manusso’ tipi saññaṃ na karissati, idāneva naṃ ghātessāmī’’ ti. "
498972,112,1508,85,100,1,87,10,So nivattitvā rājāsane nisīditvā‘‘ attano vidhānena āgacchatū’’ ti coraghātakaṃ pakkosāpesi. 
498973,112,1508,101,124,1,164,17,"So kāsāyavatthanivattho rattamālādharo pharasuṃ aṃse ṭhapetvā upadhānaghaṭikaṃ hatthapādaṭhapanadaṇḍakañca ādāya āgantvā rājānaṃ vanditvā‘‘ kiṃ karomi, devā’’ ti aṭṭhāsi. "
498974,112,1508,125,130,1,45,5,Deviyā sirigabbhaṃ gantvā dhammapālaṃ ānehīti. 
498975,112,1508,131,141,1,89,10,Devīpi rañño kujjhitvā nivattanabhāvaṃ ñatvā bodhisattaṃ ure nipajjāpetvā rodamānā nisīdi. 
498976,112,1508,142,165,1,132,18,"Coraghātako gantvā taṃ piṭṭhiyaṃ hatthena paharitvā hatthato kumāraṃ acchinditvā ādāya rañño santikaṃ āgantvā‘‘ kiṃ karomi, devā’’ ti āha. "
498977,112,1508,166,181,1,78,11,Rājā ekaṃ phalakaṃ āharāpetvā purato nikkhipāpetvā‘‘ idha naṃ nipajjāpehī’’ ti āha. 
498978,112,1508,182,185,1,14,3,So tathā akāsi. 
