499046,112,1541,2,7,1,24,2,[ 359]9. Suvaṇṇamigajātakavaṇṇanā 
499047,112,1542,2,16,1,98,12,Vikkama re {haripādā}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto sāvatthiyaṃ ekaṃ kuladhītaraṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
499048,112,1542,17,32,1,159,15,Sā kira sāvatthiyaṃ dvinnaṃ aggasāvakānaṃ upaṭṭhākakulassa dhītā saddhā pasannā buddhamāmakā dhammamāmakā saṅghamāmakā ācārasampannā paṇḍitā dānādipuññābhiratā. 
499049,112,1542,33,39,1,65,6,Taṃ aññaṃ sāvatthiyameva samānajātikaṃ micchādiṭṭhikakulaṃ vāresi. 
499050,112,1542,40,89,1,324,42,"Athassā mātāpitaro‘‘ amhākaṃ dhītā saddhā pasannā tīṇi ratanāni mamāyati dānādipuññābhiratā, tumhe micchādiṭṭhikā imissāpi yathāruciyā dānaṃ vā dātuṃ dhammaṃ vā sotuṃ vihāraṃ vā gantuṃ sīlaṃ vā rakkhituṃ uposathakammaṃ vā kātuṃ na dassatha, na mayaṃ tumhākaṃ dema, attanā sadisaṃ micchādiṭṭhikakulāva kumārikaṃ gaṇhathā’’ ti āhaṃsu. "
499051,112,1542,90,132,1,222,32,"Te tehi paṭikkhittā‘‘ tumhākaṃ dhītā amhākaṃ gharaṃ gantvā yathādhippāyena sabbametaṃ karotu, mayaṃ na vāressāma, detha no etan’’ ti vatvā‘‘ tena hi gaṇhathā’’ ti vuttā bhaddakena nakkhattena maṅgalaṃ katvā taṃ attano gharaṃ nayiṃsu. "
499052,112,1542,133,141,1,77,7,"Sā vattācārasampannā patidevatā ahosi, sassusasurasāmikavattāni katāneva honti. "
499053,112,1543,2,6,1,25,4,Sā ekadivasaṃ sāmikaṃ āha–
499054,112,1543,7,20,1,61,7,"‘‘ icchāmahaṃ, ayyaputta, amhākaṃ kulūpakattherānaṃ dānaṃ dātun’’ ti. "
499055,112,1543,21,28,1,41,5,"Sādhu, bhadde, yathājjhāsayena dānaṃ dehīti. "
499056,112,1543,29,73,1,260,35,"Sā there nimantāpetvā mahantaṃ sakkāraṃ katvā paṇītabhojanaṃ bhojetvā ekamantaṃ nisīditvā‘‘ bhante, imaṃ kulaṃ micchādiṭṭhikaṃ assaddhaṃ tiṇṇaṃ ratanānaṃ guṇaṃ na jānāti, sādhu, ayyā, yāva imaṃ kulaṃ tiṇṇaṃ ratanānaṃ guṇaṃ jānāti, tāva idheva bhikkhaṃ gaṇhathā’’ ti āha. "
499057,112,1543,74,79,1,44,5,Therā adhivāsetvā tattha nibaddhaṃ bhuñjanti. 
499058,112,1543,80,100,1,89,13,"Puna sāmikaṃ āha‘‘ ayyaputta, therā idha nibaddhaṃ āgacchanti, kiṃkāraṇā tumhe na passathā’’ ti."
499059,112,1543,101,109,1,19,3,"‘‘ Sādhu, passissāmī’’ ti. "
499060,112,1543,110,117,1,58,6,Sā punadivase therānaṃ bhattakiccapariyosāne tassa ārocesi . 
499061,112,1543,118,126,1,69,8,So upasaṅkamitvā therehi saddhiṃ paṭisanthāraṃ katvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. 
499062,112,1543,127,131,1,43,4,Athassa dhammasenāpati dhammakathaṃ kathesi. 
499063,112,1543,132,156,1,184,21,"So therassa dhammakathāya ca iriyāpathesu ca pasīditvā tato paṭṭhāya therānaṃ āsanaṃ paññapeti, pānīyaṃ parissāveti, antarābhatte dhammakathaṃ suṇāti, tassa aparabhāge micchādiṭṭhi bhijji. "
499064,112,1544,2,16,1,132,12,"Athekadivasaṃ thero dvinnampi dhammakathaṃ kathento saccāni pakāsesi, saccapariyosāne ubhopi jayampatikā sotāpattiphale patiṭṭhahiṃsu. "
499065,112,1544,17,30,1,130,13,Tato paṭṭhāya tassa mātāpitaro ādiṃ katvā antamaso dāsakammakarāpi sabbe micchādiṭṭhiṃ bhinditvā buddhadhammasaṅghamāmakāyeva jātā. 
