499072,112,1544,114,162,1,221,31,"Satthā āgantvā‘‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ imāya nāmā’’ ti vutte‘‘ na, bhikkhave, idāneva tāva esā sāmikaṃ rāgapāsā mocesi, pubbepesā porāṇakapaṇḍite pana maraṇapāsā mocesī’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
499073,112,1545,2,27,1,284,24,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto migayoniyaṃ nibbattitvā vayappatto abhirūpo ahosi pāsādiko dassanīyo suvaṇṇavaṇṇo lākhārasaparikammakatehi viya hatthapādehi rajatadāmasadisehi visāṇehi maṇiguḷikapaṭibhāgehi akkhīhi rattakambalageṇḍusadisena mukhena samannāgato. 
