499128,112,1575,2,13,1,90,11,Vāti gandho timirānan ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ukkaṇṭhitabhikkhuṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
499129,112,1575,14,72,1,273,37,"Tañhi satthā‘‘ saccaṃ kira tvaṃ bhikkhu ukkaṇṭhitosī’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ saccan’’ ti vutte‘‘ kiṃ disvā’’ ti vatvā‘‘ alaṅkatamātugāman’’ ti vutte‘‘ mātugāmo nāmesa bhikkhu na sakkā rakkhituṃ, porāṇakapaṇḍitā supaṇṇabhavane katvā rakkhantāpi rakkhituṃ nāsakkhiṃsū’’ ti vatvā tena yācito atītaṃ āhari. "
499130,112,1576,2,8,1,46,6,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ tambarājā nāma rajjaṃ kāresi. 
499131,112,1576,9,15,1,53,6,Tassa suyonandī nāma aggamahesī ahosi uttamarūpadharā. 
499132,112,1576,16,27,1,82,10,"Tadā bodhisatto supaṇṇayoniyaṃ nibbatti, tasmiṃ kāle nāgadīpo sedumadīpo nāma ahosi. "
499133,112,1576,28,33,1,44,5,Bodhisatto tasmiṃ dīpe supaṇṇabhavane vasati. 
499134,112,1576,34,42,1,67,8,So bārāṇasiṃ gantvā tambarājena saddhiṃ māṇavakavesena jūtaṃ kīḷati. 
499135,112,1576,43,62,1,117,15,Tassa rūpasampattiṃ disvā paricārikā‘‘ amhākaṃ raññā saddhiṃ evarūpo nāma māṇavako jūtaṃ kīḷatī’’ ti suyonandiyā ārocesuṃ. 
499136,112,1576,63,78,1,112,14,Sā sutvā taṃ daṭṭhukāmā hutvā ekadivasaṃ alaṅkaritvā jūtamaṇḍalaṃ āgantvā paricārikānaṃ antare ṭhitā naṃ olokesi. 
499137,112,1576,79,82,1,18,3,Sopi deviṃ olokesi. 
499138,112,1576,83,87,1,39,4,Dvepi aññamaññaṃ paṭibaddhacittā ahesuṃ. 
499139,112,1576,88,99,1,106,10,"Supaṇṇarājā attano ānubhāvena nagare vātaṃ samuṭṭhāpesi, gehapatanabhayena rājanivesanā manussā nikkhamiṃsu. "
499140,112,1576,100,120,1,144,18,So attano ānubhāvena andhakāraṃ katvā deviṃ gahetvā ākāsena āgantvā nāgadīpe attano bhavanaṃ pāvisi suyonandiyā gataṭṭhānaṃ jānantā nāma nāhesuṃ. 
499141,112,1576,121,130,1,62,9,So tāya saddhiṃ abhiramamāno gantvā raññā saddhiṃ jūtaṃ kīḷati. 
499142,112,1577,2,33,1,188,24,"Rañño pana saggo nāma gandhabbo atthi, so deviyā gataṭṭhānaṃ ajānanto taṃ gandhabbaṃ āmantetvā‘‘ gaccha, tāta, gandhabba sabbaṃ thalajalapathaṃ anuvicaritvā deviyā gataṭṭhānaṃ passā’’ ti uyyojesi. "
499143,112,1577,34,42,1,71,8,So paribbayaṃ gahetvā dvāragāmato paṭṭhāya vicinanto kurukacchaṃ pāpuṇi. 
499144,112,1577,43,48,1,52,5,Tadā kurukacchavāṇijā nāvāya suvaṇṇabhūmiṃ gacchanti. 
499145,112,1577,49,69,1,108,15,"So te upasaṅkamitvā‘‘ ahaṃ gandhabbo nāvāya vetanaṃ khaṇḍetvā tumhākaṃ gandhabbaṃ karissāmi, mampi nethā’’ ti āha. "
499146,112,1577,70,81,1,44,7,Te‘‘ sādhū’’ ti tampi āropetvā nāvaṃ vissajjesuṃ. 
499147,112,1577,82,96,1,69,10,Te sukhapayātāya nāvāya taṃ pakkositvā‘‘ gandhabbaṃ no karohī’’ ti āhaṃsu.
