499149,112,1577,119,133,1,71,9,"‘‘ Manussamatte gandhabbaṃ karonte macchānaṃ calanaṃ nāma natthi, karohī’’ ti."
499150,112,1577,134,154,1,126,15,"‘‘ Tena hi mā mayhaṃ kujjhitthā’’ ti vīṇaṃ mucchitvā tantissarena gītassaraṃ, gītassarena tantissaraṃ anatikkamitvā gandhabbaṃ akāsi. "
499151,112,1577,155,161,1,42,6,Tena saddena sammattā hutvā macchā caliṃsu. 
