499201,112,1605,2,7,1,22,2,[ 361]1. Vaṇṇārohajātakavaṇṇanā 
499202,112,1606,2,14,1,75,9,{Vaṇṇārohenā}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto dve aggasāvake ārabbha kathesi. 
499203,112,1606,15,42,1,204,23,Ekasmiñhi samaye ubhopi mahātherā‘‘ imaṃ antovassaṃ suññāgāraṃ anubrūhessāmā’’ ti satthāraṃ āpucchitvā gaṇaṃ pahāya sayameva pattacīvaraṃ ādāya jetavanā nikkhamitvā ekaṃ paccantagāmaṃ nissāya araññe vihariṃsu. 
499204,112,1606,43,51,1,77,8,Aññataropi vighāsādapuriso therānaṃ upaṭṭhānaṃ karonto tattheva ekamante vasi. 
499205,112,1606,52,94,1,232,31,"So therānaṃ samaggavāsaṃ disvā‘‘ ime ativiya samaggā vasanti, sakkā nu kho ete aññamaññaṃ bhinditun’’ ti cintetvā sāriputtattheraṃ upasaṅkamitvā‘‘ kiṃ nu kho, bhante, ayyena mahāmoggallānattherena saddhiṃ tumhākaṃ kiñci veraṃ atthī’’ ti pucchi."
499206,112,1606,95,102,1,15,3,‘‘ Kiṃ panāvuso’’ ti. 
499207,112,1606,103,128,1,151,18,"Esa, bhante, mama āgatakāle‘‘ sāriputto nāma jātigottakulapadesehi vā sutaganthapaṭivedhaiddhīhi vā mayā saddhiṃ kiṃ pahotī’’ ti tumhākaṃ aguṇameva kathesīti. "
499208,112,1606,129,141,1,42,8,Thero sitaṃ katvā‘‘ gaccha tvaṃ āvuso’’ ti āha. 
499209,112,1607,2,9,1,75,7,So aparasmimpi divase mahāmoggallānattherampi upasaṅkamitvā tatheva kathesi. 
499210,112,1607,10,41,1,139,20,"Sopi naṃ sitaṃ katvā‘‘ gaccha, tvaṃ, āvuso’’ ti vatvā sāriputtattheraṃ upasaṅkamitvā‘‘ āvuso, eso vighāsādo tumhākaṃ santike kiñci kathesī’’ ti pucchi."
499211,112,1607,42,56,1,58,8,"‘‘ Āmāvuso, mayhampi santike kathesi, imaṃ nīharituṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti."
499212,112,1607,57,81,1,79,14,"‘‘ Sādhu, āvuso, nīharā’’ ti vutte thero‘‘ mā idha vasī’’ ti accharaṃ paharitvā taṃ nīhari. "
499213,112,1607,82,91,1,72,9,Te ubhopi samaggavāsaṃ vasitvā satthu santikaṃ gantvā vanditvā nisīdiṃsu. 
499214,112,1607,92,147,1,264,37,"Satthā paṭisanthāraṃ katvā‘‘ sukhena vassaṃ vasitthā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ bhante, eko vighāsādo amhe bhinditukāmo hutvā bhindituṃ asakkonto palāyī’’ ti vutte‘‘ na kho so, sāriputta, idāneva, pubbepesa tumhe‘ bhindissāmī’ ti bhindituṃ asakkonto palāyī’’ ti vatvā tehi yācito atītaṃ āhari. "
499215,112,1608,2,11,1,81,9,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto araññe rukkhadevatā ahosi. 
499216,112,1608,12,21,1,53,8,Tadā sīho ca byaggho ca araññe pabbataguhāyaṃ vasanti. 
499217,112,1608,22,59,1,219,30,"Eko siṅgālo te upaṭṭhahanto tesaṃ vighāsaṃ khāditvā mahākāyo hutvā ekadivasaṃ cintesi‘‘ mayā sīhabyagghānaṃ maṃsaṃ na khāditapubbaṃ, mayā ime dve jane bhindituṃ vaṭṭati, tato nesaṃ kalahaṃ katvā matānaṃ maṃsaṃ khādissāmī’’ ti. "
499218,112,1608,60,79,1,86,13,"So sīhaṃ upasaṅkamitvā‘‘ kiṃ, sāmi, tumhākaṃ byagghena saddhiṃ kiñci veraṃ atthī’’ ti pucchi."
499219,112,1608,80,89,1,17,4,"‘‘ Kiṃ pana, sammā’’ ti? "
499220,112,1608,90,115,1,151,19,"Esa, bhante, mamāgatakāle‘‘ sīho nāma sarīravaṇṇena vā ārohapariṇāhena vā jātibalavīriyehi vā mama kalabhāgampi na pāpuṇātī’’ ti tumhākaṃ aguṇameva kathesīti. "
499221,112,1608,116,132,1,54,11,"Atha naṃ sīho‘‘ gaccha tvaṃ, na so evaṃ kathessatī’’ ti āha. "
499222,112,1608,133,138,1,48,5,Byagghampi upasaṅkamitvā eteneva upāyena kathesi. 
499223,112,1608,139,158,1,106,14,"Taṃ sutvā byagghopi sīhaṃ upasaṅkamitvā‘‘ samma, tvaṃ kira idañcidañca vadesī’’ ti pucchanto paṭhamaṃ gāthamāha– "
