499264,112,1632,123,169,1,215,34,"‘‘ Na, mahārāja, kuṭumbaṃ vilumpāmi, mayhaṃ pana‘ sīlaṃ nu kho mahantaṃ, sutaṃ nu kho’ ti kukkuccaṃ ahosi, svāhaṃ‘ etesu kataraṃ nu kho mahantan’ ti vīmaṃsanto tayo vāre kahāpaṇaṃ gaṇhiṃ, taṃ maṃ esa bandhāpetvā tumhākaṃ dasseti. "
499265,112,1632,170,195,1,172,20,"Idāni me sutato sīlassa mahantabhāvo ñāto, na me gharāvāsenattho, pabbajissāmahan’’ ti pabbajjaṃ anujānāpetvā gharadvāraṃ anoloketvāva jetavanaṃ gantvā satthāraṃ pabbajjaṃ yāci. "
