499644,112,1850,13,61,1,314,39,"So pana dīghāvukumāro araññe attano aṅke nipannaṃ bārāṇasirājānaṃ cūḷāya gahetvā‘‘ idāni mayhaṃ mātāpitughātakaṃ coraṃ khaṇḍākhaṇḍaṃ katvā chindissāmī’’ ti asiṃ ukkhipanto tasmiṃ khaṇe mātāpitūhi dinnaṃ ovādaṃ saritvā‘‘ jīvitaṃ cajantopi tesaṃ ovādaṃ na bhindissāmi, kevalaṃ imaṃ tajjessāmī’’ ti cintetvā paṭhamaṃ gāthamāha– "
