499800,112,1937,2,4,1,0,0,127.
499801,112,1938,2,9,1,44,4,"‘ ‘ Sabbaṃ sutamadhīyetha, hīnamukkaṭṭhamajjhimaṃ; "
499802,112,1939,2,10,1,45,7,"Sabbassa atthaṃ jāneyya, na ca sabbaṃ payojaye; "
499803,112,1940,2,12,1,45,7,"Hoti tādisako kālo, yattha atthāvahaṃ sutan’’ ti. "
499804,112,1941,2,22,1,167,16,"Tattha {nāntalikkhabhavanenā}ti antalikkhabhavanaṃ vuccati dibbavimānaṃ, ahaṃ ajja antalikkhabhavanampi na āruḷho, tasmā antalikkhabhavanenāpi ajja maraṇato na pamocitomhi. "
499805,112,1941,23,31,1,67,7,Nāṅgaputtapinena {vā}ti aṅgasarikkhakena vā puttapinenapi na pamocito. 
499806,112,1941,32,43,1,72,10,Puttena hi {patthayito}ti ahaṃ pana attano putteneva ajja māretuṃ patthito. 
499807,112,1941,44,53,1,70,8,Silokehi {pamocito}ti sohaṃ ācariyena bandhitvā dinnāhi gāthāhi pamocito. 
499808,112,1942,2,6,1,19,3,Sutan ti pariyattiṃ. 
499809,112,1942,7,11,1,30,3,{Adhīyethā}ti gaṇheyya sikkheyya. 
499810,112,1942,12,25,1,95,12,"Hīnamukkaṭṭhamajjhiman ti hīnaṃ vā hotu uttamaṃ vā majjhimaṃ vā, sabbaṃ adhīyitabbamevāti dīpeti. "
499811,112,1942,26,44,1,105,16,"Na ca sabbaṃ {payojaye}ti hīnaṃ mantaṃ vā sippaṃ vā majjhimaṃ vā na payojaye, uttamameva payojayeyyāti attho. "
499812,112,1942,45,63,1,157,17,"Yattha atthāvahaṃ sutan ti yasmiṃ kāle mahosadhapaṇḍitassa kumbhakārakammakaraṇaṃ viya yaṃkiñci sikkhitasippaṃ atthāvahaṃ hoti, tādisopi kālo hotiyevāti attho. "
