499816,112,1944,2,4,1,26,2,Mūsikajātakavaṇṇanā tatiyā.
499817,112,1946,2,7,1,27,2,[ 374]4. Cūḷadhanuggahajātakavaṇṇanā 
499818,112,1947,2,12,1,89,10,Sabbaṃ bhaṇḍan ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto purāṇadutiyikāpalobhanaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
499819,112,1947,13,54,1,202,29,"Tena bhikkhunā‘‘ purāṇadutiyikā maṃ, bhante, ukkaṇṭhāpetī’’ ti vutte satthā‘‘ esā bhikkhu, itthī na idāneva tuyhaṃ anatthakārikā, pubbepi te etaṃ nissāya asinā sīsaṃ chinnan’’ ti vatvā bhikkhūhi yācito atītaṃ āhari. "
499820,112,1948,2,11,1,72,8,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto sakkattaṃ kāresi. 
499821,112,1948,12,25,1,134,13,Tadā eko bārāṇasivāsī brāhmaṇamāṇavo takkasilāyaṃ sabbasippāni uggaṇhitvā dhanukamme nipphattiṃ patto cūḷadhanuggahapaṇḍito nāma ahosi. 
499822,112,1948,26,41,1,73,11,Athassa ācariyo‘‘ ayaṃ mayā sadisaṃ sippaṃ uggaṇhī’’ ti attano dhītaraṃ adāsi. 
499823,112,1948,42,54,1,54,8,So taṃ gahetvā‘‘ bārāṇasiṃ gamissāmī’’ ti maggaṃ paṭipajji. 
499824,112,1948,55,68,1,85,12,"Antarāmagge eko vāraṇo ekaṃ padesaṃ suññamakāsi, taṃ ṭhānaṃ abhiruhituṃ na koci ussahi. "
499825,112,1948,69,77,1,85,7,Cūḷadhanuggahapaṇḍito manussānaṃ vārentānaññeva bhariyaṃ gahetvā aṭavimukhaṃ abhiruhi. 
499826,112,1948,78,88,1,62,9,"Athassa aṭavimajjhe vāraṇo uṭṭhahi, so taṃ kumbhe sarena vijjhi. "
499827,112,1948,89,93,1,41,4,Saro vinivijjhitvā pacchābhāgena nikkhami. 
499828,112,1948,94,107,1,89,12,"Vāraṇo tattheva pati, dhanuggahapaṇḍito taṃ ṭhānaṃ khemaṃ katvā purato aññaṃ aṭaviṃ pāpuṇi. "
499829,112,1948,108,113,1,36,5,Tatthāpi paññāsa corā maggaṃ hananti. 
499830,112,1948,114,129,1,126,15,Tampi so manussehi vāriyamāno abhiruyha tesaṃ corānaṃ mige vadhitvā maggasamīpe maṃsaṃ pacitvā khādantānaṃ ṭhitaṭṭhānaṃ pāpuṇi. 
499831,112,1949,2,20,1,103,13,Tadā taṃ corā alaṅkatapaṭiyattāya bhariyāya saddhiṃ āgacchantaṃ disvā‘‘ gaṇhissāma nan’’ ti ussāhaṃ kariṃsu. 
499832,112,1949,21,38,1,105,12,"Corajeṭṭhako purisalakkhaṇakusalo, so taṃ oloketvāva‘‘ uttamapuriso ayan’’ ti ñatvā ekassapi uṭṭhahituṃ nādāsi. "
499833,112,1949,39,60,1,112,15,Dhanuggahapaṇḍito‘‘ gaccha‘ amhākampi ekaṃ maṃsasūlaṃ dethā’ ti vatvā maṃsaṃ āharā’’ ti tesaṃ santikaṃ bhariyaṃ pesesi. 
499834,112,1949,61,73,1,43,8,Sā gantvā‘‘ ekaṃ kira maṃsasūlaṃ dethā’’ ti āha. 
499835,112,1949,74,84,1,48,6,Corajeṭṭhako‘‘ anaggho puriso’’ ti maṃsasūlaṃ dāpesi. 
499836,112,1949,85,97,1,59,8,Corā‘‘ amhehi kira pakkaṃ khāditan’’ ti apakkamaṃsasūlaṃ adaṃsu. 
499837,112,1949,98,111,1,80,9,Dhanuggaho attānaṃ sambhāvetvā‘‘ mayhaṃ apakkamaṃsasūlaṃ dadantī’’ ti corānaṃ kujjhi. 
499838,112,1949,112,126,1,63,9,"Corā‘‘ kiṃ ayameveko puriso, mayaṃ itthiyo’’ ti kujjhitvā uṭṭhahiṃsu. "
499839,112,1949,127,133,1,65,6,Dhanuggaho ekūnapaññāsa jane ekūnapaññāsakaṇḍehi vijjhitvā pātesi. 
499840,112,1949,134,138,1,37,4,Corajeṭṭhakaṃ vijjhituṃ kaṇḍaṃ nāhosi. 
499841,112,1949,139,144,1,47,5,Tassa kira kaṇḍanāḷiyaṃ samapaṇṇāsayeva kaṇḍāni. 
499842,112,1949,145,169,1,159,19,"Tesu ekena vāraṇaṃ vijjhi, ekūnapaññāsakaṇḍehi core vijjhitvā corajeṭṭhakaṃ pātetvā tassa ure nisinno‘‘ sīsamassa chindissāmī’’ ti bhariyāya hatthato asiṃ āharāpesi. "
499843,112,1949,170,185,1,96,12,"Sā taṅkhaṇaññeva corajeṭṭhake lobhaṃ katvā corassa hatthe tharuṃ, sāmikassa hatthe dhāraṃ ṭhapesi. "
499844,112,1949,186,194,1,70,8,Coro tharudaṇḍaṃ parāmasitvā asiṃ nīharitvā dhanuggahassa sīsaṃ chindi. 
499845,112,1950,2,10,1,56,8,So taṃ ghātetvā itthiṃ ādāya gacchanto jātigottaṃ pucchi. 
499846,112,1950,11,21,1,53,6,Sā‘‘ takkasilāyaṃ disāpāmokkhācariyassa dhītāmhī’’ ti āha.
499847,112,1950,22,31,1,27,5,‘‘ Kathaṃ tvaṃ iminā laddhā’’ ti. 
499848,112,1950,32,58,1,143,21,"Mayhaṃ pitā‘‘ ayaṃ mayā sadisaṃ katvā sippaṃ sikkhī’’ ti tussitvā imassa maṃ adāsi, sāhaṃ tayi sinehaṃ katvā attano kuladattiyaṃ sāmikaṃ mārāpesinti. "
499849,112,1950,59,103,1,258,32,"Corajeṭṭhako‘‘ kuladattiyaṃ tāvesā sāmikaṃ māresi, aññaṃ panekaṃ disvā mampi evamevaṃ karissati, imaṃ chaḍḍetuṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti cintetvā gacchanto antarāmagge ekaṃ kunnadiṃ uttānatalaṃ taṅkhaṇodakapūraṃ disvā‘‘ bhadde, imissaṃ nadiyaṃ susumārā kakkhaḷā, kiṃ karomā’’ ti āha."
499850,112,1950,104,124,1,113,15,"‘‘ Sāmi, sabbaṃ ābharaṇabhaṇḍaṃ mama uttarāsaṅgena bhaṇḍikaṃ katvā paratīraṃ netvā puna āgantvā maṃ gahetvā gacchā’’ ti. "
499851,112,1950,125,144,1,105,15,So‘‘ sādhū’’ ti sabbaṃ ābharaṇabhaṇḍaṃ ādāya nadiṃ otaritvā taranto viya paratīraṃ patvā taṃ chaḍḍetvā pāyāsi. 
499852,112,1950,145,174,1,136,22,"Sā taṃ disvā‘‘ sāmi, kiṃ maṃ chaḍḍetvā viya gacchasi, kasmā evaṃ karosi, ehi mampi ādāya gacchā’’ ti tena saddhiṃ sallapantī paṭhamaṃ gāthamāha– "
499853,112,1951,2,4,1,0,0,128.
499854,112,1952,2,11,1,46,7,"‘ ‘ Sabbaṃ bhaṇḍaṃ samādāya, pāraṃ tiṇṇosi brāhmaṇa; "
