499977,112,2038,18,38,1,113,17,"So kira bālo ahosi aññāṇo, neva so buddhādīnaṃ ratanānaṃ, na aññesaṃ puggalānaṃ guṇaṃ jānāti, caṇḍo pharuso sāhasiko. "
499978,112,2038,39,68,1,149,19,"Atheko jānapado bhikkhu‘‘ buddhupaṭṭhānaṃ karissāmī’’ ti āgacchanto sāyaṃ aciravatītitthaṃ patvā taṃ evamāha‘‘ upāsaka, paratīraṃ gamissāmi, nāvaṃ me dehī’’ ti."
