499984,112,2039,2,30,1,290,27,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto brāhmaṇakule nibbattitvā vayappatto takkasilāyaṃ sabbasippāni uggaṇhitvā isipabbajjaṃ pabbajitvā dīghamaddhānaṃ himavante phalāphalena yāpetvā loṇambilasevanatthāya bārāṇasiṃ patvā rājuyyāne vasitvā punadivase nagaraṃ bhikkhāya pāvisi. 
